#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_calculator.html:4
msgid "Annuity Calculator - Present & Future Value"
msgstr "Calculadora de anualidades: valor presente y futuro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate annuity present value, future value, and payments. Plan retirement"
" income with our free annuity calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el valor presente de la anualidad, el valor futuro y los pagos. "
"Planifique los ingresos de jubilación con nuestra calculadora de anualidades"
" gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"annuity calculator, present value annuity, future value annuity, retirement "
"calculator, annuity payment"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de anualidad, anualidad de valor presente, anualidad de valor "
"futuro, calculadora de jubilación, pago de anualidad"

