#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_calculator.html:187
msgid ""
"Payments are made at the end of each period. Most loans and mortgages use "
"ordinary annuity calculations."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos se realizan al final de cada período. La mayoría de los préstamos "
"e hipotecas utilizan cálculos de anualidades ordinarias."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_calculator.html:191
msgid ""
"Payments are made at the beginning of each period. Rent and insurance "
"premiums are typically annuity due."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos se realizan al inicio de cada período. Las primas de alquiler y "
"seguro suelen pagarse en anualidades."

