"Payments are made at the beginning of each period. Common for rent and "
"insurance premiums."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos se realizan al inicio de cada período. Común para alquileres y "
"primas de seguros."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/annuity_payout_calculator.html:261
