msgid "Enter Loan Info"
msgstr "Ingrese la información del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:243
msgid "Input the loan amount, stated interest rate, and term."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el monto del préstamo, la tasa de interés indicada y el plazo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:249
msgid "Add All Fees"
msgstr "Agregar todas las tarifas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:250
msgid "Include origination fees, points, and other closing costs."
msgstr "Incluya tarifas de originación, puntos y otros costos de cierre."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:256
msgid "Compare APR"
msgstr "Comparar TAE"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:257
msgid "Use APR to compare loan offers from different lenders."
msgstr ""
"Utilice la APR para comparar ofertas de préstamos de diferentes "
"prestamistas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:269
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:390
msgid "What's the difference between APR and interest rate?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre APR y tasa de interés?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:275
msgid ""
"The interest rate is just the cost of borrowing the principal. APR includes "
"the interest rate plus fees (origination, points, etc.), giving you the true"
" yearly cost. APR is always equal to or higher than the stated rate."
msgstr ""
"La tasa de interés es simplemente el costo de pedir prestado el principal. "
"La APR incluye la tasa de interés más las tarifas (originación, puntos, "
"etc.), lo que le brinda el costo anual real. La APR siempre es igual o "
"superior a la tasa indicada."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:281
msgid "Why should I compare APR?"
msgstr "¿Por qué debería comparar la APR?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:287
msgid ""
"APR lets you compare apples to apples. A loan with a lower interest rate but"
" high fees might have a higher APR than one with a slightly higher rate but "
"fewer fees. Always compare APR when shopping for loans."
msgstr ""
"APR te permite comparar manzanas con manzanas. Un préstamo con una tasa de "
"interés más baja pero tarifas altas puede tener una APR más alta que uno con"
" una tasa ligeramente más alta pero menos tarifas. Siempre compare la APR "
"cuando busque préstamos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:293
msgid "What are discount points?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los puntos de descuento?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:299
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Discount points are upfront fees you pay to lower your interest rate. Each "
"point typically costs 1%% of the loan amount and reduces your rate by "
"0.25%%. Points make sense if you'll keep the loan long enough to recoup the "
"upfront cost."
msgstr ""
"Los puntos de descuento son tarifas iniciales que paga para reducir su tasa "
"de interés. Cada punto normalmente cuesta el 1%% del monto del préstamo y "
"reduce su tasa en un 0,25%%. Los puntos tienen sentido si conserva el "
"préstamo el tiempo suficiente para recuperar el costo inicial."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:307
msgid "APR Shopping Tips"
msgstr "Consejos de compra para la APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:313
msgid "Get at least 3 loan quotes and compare APRs, not just rates."
msgstr ""
"Obtenga al menos 3 cotizaciones de préstamos y compare las APR, no solo las "
"tasas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:319
msgid "Lenders are required by law to disclose APR - always ask for it."
msgstr ""
"Los prestamistas están obligados por ley a revelar la APR; solicítela "
"siempre."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:325
msgid "Consider total costs - a lower APR may not be best if you move soon."
msgstr ""
"Considere los costos totales: una APR más baja puede no ser la mejor opción "
"si se muda pronto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:331
msgid "Negotiate fees - origination fees and points are often negotiable."
msgstr ""
"Negociar tarifas: las tarifas de originación y los puntos suelen ser "
"negociables."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/apr_calculator.html:431
msgid "Fees"
msgstr "Honorarios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:4
msgid "Auto Loan Calculator - Car Payment Calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de préstamos para automóviles - Calculadora de pagos de "
"automóviles"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly car payment with our free auto loan calculator. "
"Include trade-in value, sales tax, and fees. Compare different loan terms."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el pago mensual de su automóvil con nuestra calculadora gratuita de "
"préstamos para automóviles. Incluya el valor de intercambio, el impuesto "
"sobre las ventas y las tarifas. Compare diferentes términos de préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"auto loan calculator, car payment calculator, vehicle financing, car loan, "
"trade-in value, sales tax"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de préstamos para automóviles, calculadora de pagos de "
"automóviles, financiación de vehículos, préstamo de automóviles, valor de "
"intercambio, impuesto sobre las ventas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:66
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:72
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:30
msgid "Auto Loan Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de préstamos para automóviles"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:10
msgid "Calculate your car payment with trade-in, taxes, and fees included."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el pago de su automóvil con intercambio, impuestos y tarifas "
"incluidos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:18
msgid ""
"Calculate auto loan payments with trade-in value, taxes, and compare loan "
"terms."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos de préstamos para automóviles con valor de intercambio, "
"impuestos y compare los términos del préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:32
msgid "What is a good interest rate for an auto loan?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es una buena tasa de interés para un préstamo para automóvil?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:35
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Good rates depend on your credit score. Excellent credit (750+) typically "
"gets 3-5%%, good credit (700-749) gets 5-7%%, and fair credit (650-699) gets"
" 7-10%%."
msgstr ""
"Las buenas tasas dependen de su puntaje crediticio. El crédito excelente "
"(750+) normalmente obtiene entre el 3% y el 5%, el buen crédito (700-749) "
"obtiene entre el 5% y el 7% y el crédito justo (650-699) obtiene entre el 7%"
" y el 10%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/auto_loan_calculator.html:73
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly car payment including trade-in value, sales tax, and "
"fees. Compare different loan terms to find the best option."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el pago mensual de su automóvil, incluido el valor de intercambio, "
"el impuesto sobre las ventas y las tarifas. Compare diferentes términos de "
"préstamo para encontrar la mejor opción."

