#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:325
msgid "The 50/30/20 Budget Rule"
msgstr "La regla presupuestaria 50/30/20"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:329
msgid "Needs"
msgstr "Necesidades"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:330
msgid "Housing, utilities, groceries, insurance, minimum debt payments"
msgstr ""
"Vivienda, servicios públicos, comestibles, seguros, pagos mínimos de deuda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:334
msgid "Wants"
msgstr "Quiere"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:335
msgid "Dining, entertainment, shopping, hobbies, subscriptions"
msgstr "Restaurantes, entretenimiento, compras, pasatiempos, suscripciones."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:340
msgid "Emergency fund, retirement, extra debt payments, investments"
msgstr "Fondo de emergencia, jubilación, pagos extra de deuda, inversiones."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:351
msgid "How much should I spend on housing?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto debería gastar en vivienda?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:357
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The general guideline is to spend no more than 30%% of your gross income on "
"housing costs, including rent/mortgage, utilities, and insurance."
msgstr ""
"La pauta general es no gastar más del 30%% de sus ingresos brutos en costos "
"de vivienda, incluidos alquiler/hipoteca, servicios públicos y seguros."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:363
msgid "How do I build an emergency fund?"
msgstr "¿Cómo creo un fondo de emergencia?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:369
msgid ""
"Start by saving $1,000, then work toward 3-6 months of expenses. Automate "
"transfers to a separate savings account. Any 'remaining' budget should go "
"here first."
msgstr ""
"Comience ahorrando $1000 y luego trabaje para cubrir entre 3 y 6 meses de "
"gastos. Automatiza transferencias a una cuenta de ahorros separada. "
"Cualquier presupuesto \"restante\" debería ir aquí primero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:485
msgid "Living"
msgstr "Viviendo"

