#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:269
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:723
msgid "Contributions"
msgstr "Contribuciones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:270
msgid "See Your Money Grow"
msgstr "Vea crecer su dinero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:271
msgid ""
"Enter your investment details to see how compound interest can grow your "
"wealth over time."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su inversión para ver cómo el interés compuesto "
"puede hacer crecer su patrimonio con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:285
msgid "Enter the amount you're starting with or plan to invest initially."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la cantidad con la que está comenzando o planea invertir "
"inicialmente."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:291
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/payment_calculator.html:221
msgid "Set Rate & Term"
msgstr "Establecer tarifa y plazo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:292
msgid "Enter the expected annual return and how long you plan to invest."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el rendimiento anual esperado y durante cuánto tiempo planea "
"invertir."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:298
msgid "Add Contributions"
msgstr "Agregar contribuciones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:299
msgid "Optionally add regular contributions to see their impact."
msgstr "Opcionalmente, agregue contribuciones periódicas para ver su impacto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:305
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:284
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/payment_calculator.html:228
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:389
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/common_factor_calculator.html:95
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/distance_calculator.html:100
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/exponent_calculator.html:100
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:95
msgid "View Results"
msgstr "Ver resultados"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:306
msgid "See your projected growth with detailed charts and breakdowns."
msgstr "Vea su crecimiento proyectado con gráficos y desgloses detallados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:314
msgid "Understanding Compound Interest"
msgstr "Comprender el interés compuesto"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:317
msgid "The Power of Compounding"
msgstr "El poder de la capitalización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Compound interest is often called the eighth wonder of the world. Unlike "
"simple interest, compound interest earns interest on your interest, leading "
"to exponential growth over time."
msgstr ""
"Al interés compuesto se le suele llamar la octava maravilla del mundo. A "
"diferencia del interés simple, el interés compuesto genera intereses sobre "
"sus intereses, lo que genera un crecimiento exponencial con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:320
msgid "Compound Frequency Matters"
msgstr "La frecuencia compuesta importa"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:321
msgid ""
"The more frequently interest compounds, the more you earn. Daily compounding"
" earns more than monthly, which earns more than annually. However, the "
"differences are usually small."
msgstr ""
"Cuanto más frecuentemente se acumulen los intereses, más ganará. La "
"capitalización diaria gana más que la mensual, que gana más que anualmente. "
"Sin embargo, las diferencias suelen ser pequeñas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:324
msgid "Time Is Your Greatest Asset"
msgstr "El tiempo es su mayor activo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"The longer your money compounds, the more dramatic the growth. Starting "
"early, even with smaller amounts, often beats starting later with larger "
"amounts."
msgstr ""
"Cuanto más se capitalice su dinero, más dramático será el crecimiento. "
"Comenzar temprano, incluso con cantidades más pequeñas, a menudo es mejor "
"que comenzar más tarde con cantidades mayores."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:327
msgid "The Rule of 72"
msgstr "La regla del 72"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:328
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Divide 72 by your interest rate to estimate how many years it takes to "
"double your money. At 7%% interest, your money doubles approximately every "
"10 years."
msgstr ""
"Divide 72 por tu tasa de interés para estimar cuántos años se necesitan para"
" duplicar tu dinero. Con un interés del 7%%, su dinero se duplica "
"aproximadamente cada 10 años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:339
msgid "What is the difference between simple and compound interest?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre interés simple y compuesto?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Simple interest is calculated only on the original principal. Compound "
"interest is calculated on the principal plus any accumulated interest, "
"leading to faster growth over time."
msgstr ""
"El interés simple se calcula únicamente sobre el capital original. El "
"interés compuesto se calcula sobre el capital más cualquier interés "
"acumulado, lo que conduce a un crecimiento más rápido con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:351
msgid "How does compound frequency affect my returns?"
msgstr "¿Cómo afecta la frecuencia compuesta a mis rendimientos?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"More frequent compounding means your interest starts earning interest "
"sooner, resulting in higher total returns. However, the difference between "
"daily and monthly compounding is often minimal."
msgstr ""
"Una capitalización más frecuente significa que su interés comienza a generar"
" intereses antes, lo que genera rendimientos totales más altos. Sin embargo,"
" la diferencia entre la capitalización diaria y mensual suele ser mínima."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:363
msgid "What is a realistic interest rate to use?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es una tasa de interés realista a utilizar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:369
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Savings accounts typically offer 0.5-5%%. Bonds may return 2-6%%. Stock "
"market has historically returned around 7-10%% annually (inflation-"
"adjusted). Use rates appropriate for your investment type."
msgstr ""
"Las cuentas de ahorro suelen ofrecer entre un 0,5% y un 5%%. Los bonos "
"pueden tener una rentabilidad del 2 al 6%%. Históricamente, el mercado de "
"valores ha tenido una rentabilidad de alrededor del 7% al 10%% anual "
"(ajustado a la inflación). Utilice tasas apropiadas para su tipo de "
"inversión."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:375
msgid "Should I contribute at the beginning or end of the period?"
msgstr "¿Debo cotizar al inicio o al final del período?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:381
msgid ""
"Contributing at the beginning of each period results in slightly higher "
"returns because your money has more time to compound. This is often called "
"'annuity due' vs 'ordinary annuity'."
msgstr ""
"Contribuir al comienzo de cada período genera rendimientos ligeramente "
"mayores porque su dinero tiene más tiempo para capitalizarse. Esto a menudo "
"se denomina \"anualidad adeudada\" frente a \"anualidad ordinaria\"."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:389
msgid "Investment Tips"
msgstr "Consejos de inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:395
msgid "Start investing as early as possible - time is your biggest advantage."
msgstr "Empiece a invertir lo antes posible: el tiempo es su mayor ventaja."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:401
msgid ""
"Consistent small contributions can outperform large one-time investments."
msgstr ""
"Las pequeñas contribuciones constantes pueden tener mejores resultados que "
"las grandes inversiones únicas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:407
msgid "Reinvest your dividends and interest to maximize compounding."
msgstr ""
"Reinvierta sus dividendos e intereses para maximizar la capitalización."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/compound_interest_calculator.html:413
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Keep fees low - even 1%% in fees can significantly reduce long-term returns."
msgstr ""
"Mantenga las tarifas bajas: incluso un 1%% en tarifas puede reducir "
"significativamente los retornos a largo plazo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:4
msgid "Credit Card Payoff Calculator - Debt Free Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de pago de tarjetas de crédito - Calculadora sin deudas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate how to pay off credit card debt faster. Compare payment "
"strategies, see total interest, and create a debt-free plan with our free "
"calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cómo liquidar la deuda de tarjetas de crédito más rápido. Compare "
"estrategias de pago, vea el interés total y cree un plan libre de deudas con"
" nuestra calculadora gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"credit card calculator, debt payoff, credit card interest, minimum payment, "
"debt free calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de tarjetas de crédito, pago de deudas, intereses de tarjetas de"
" crédito, pago mínimo, calculadora libre de deudas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:17
