msgstr ""
"Calcule cuánto tiempo tardará en liquidar la deuda de la tarjeta de crédito "
"y compare estrategias de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:18
msgid ""
"Calculate credit card payoff time and compare different payment strategies."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el tiempo de pago de la tarjeta de crédito y compare diferentes "
"estrategias de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:32
