#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:241
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:199
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:170
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:209
msgid "Payment Schedule"
msgstr "Calendario de pagos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:267
msgid "Get Debt-Free Faster"
msgstr "Libérese de sus deudas más rápido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:268
msgid ""
"Enter your credit card details to see how long it will take to pay off and "
"how much you'll pay in interest."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su tarjeta de crédito para ver cuánto tiempo tomará "
"liquidarse y cuánto pagará en intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:281
msgid "Enter Card Details"
msgstr "Ingrese los detalles de la tarjeta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:282
msgid ""
"Input your current balance and APR (interest rate) from your statement."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su saldo actual y APR (tasa de interés) de su estado de cuenta."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:288
msgid "Choose Your Goal"
msgstr "Elige tu objetivo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"Select how you want to pay: fixed amount, target date, or minimum payments."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione cómo desea pagar: monto fijo, fecha objetivo o pagos mínimos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:295
msgid "Compare Strategies"
msgstr "Comparar estrategias"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:296
msgid ""
"See how different payment amounts affect your payoff time and interest."
msgstr ""
"Vea cómo los diferentes montos de pago afectan su tiempo de pago y sus "
"intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:308
msgid "Why is paying only the minimum bad?"
msgstr "¿Por qué es malo pagar sólo el mínimo?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:314
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Minimum payments are designed to maximize interest for the credit card "
"company. A $5,000 balance at 20%% APR with minimum payments could take 20+ "
"years to pay off and cost over $8,000 in interest."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos mínimos están diseñados para maximizar el interés para la compañía"
" de tarjetas de crédito. Un saldo de $5,000 con una tasa de interés anual "
"del 20%% con pagos mínimos podría tardar más de 20 años en liquidarse y "
"costar más de $8,000 en intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:320
msgid "What is APR?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la TAE?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:326
msgid ""
"APR (Annual Percentage Rate) is the yearly interest rate on your credit "
"card. It's divided by 12 to calculate monthly interest. Find your APR on "
"your credit card statement or online account."
msgstr ""
"APR (tasa de porcentaje anual) es la tasa de interés anual de su tarjeta de "
"crédito. Se divide por 12 para calcular el interés mensual. Encuentre su APR"
" en el extracto de su tarjeta de crédito o en su cuenta en línea."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:332
msgid "How can I pay off debt faster?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo liquidar mis deudas más rápido?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Pay more than the minimum, make extra payments when possible, consider "
"balance transfer cards with 0%% intro APR, or use the debt avalanche "
"(highest rate first) or snowball (smallest balance first) methods."
msgstr ""
"Pague más del mínimo, realice pagos adicionales cuando sea posible, "
"considere tarjetas de transferencia de saldo con una tasa de interés anual "
"inicial del 0 % o utilice los métodos de avalancha de deuda (la tasa más "
"alta primero) o bola de nieve (el saldo más pequeño primero)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:344
msgid "Should I use savings to pay off credit cards?"
msgstr "¿Debo utilizar ahorros para liquidar tarjetas de crédito?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Generally yes, if your credit card APR (typically 15-25%%) exceeds your "
"savings interest (typically 0.5-5%%). However, keep an emergency fund of at "
"least $1,000 before aggressively paying debt."
msgstr ""
"Generalmente sí, si la APR de su tarjeta de crédito (normalmente entre el "
"15% y el 25%) excede el interés de sus ahorros (normalmente entre el 0,5% y "
"el 5%). Sin embargo, mantenga un fondo de emergencia de al menos $1,000 "
"antes de pagar deudas de manera agresiva."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:358
msgid "Debt Payoff Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para pagar la deuda"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:364
msgid "Pay more than the minimum - even $20 extra makes a big difference."
msgstr ""
"Pague más que el mínimo: incluso $20 adicionales hacen una gran diferencia."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:370
#, python-format
msgid "Consider a balance transfer to a 0%% APR card if you have good credit."
msgstr ""
"Considere una transferencia de saldo a una tarjeta con 0%% APR si tiene buen"
" crédito."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Stop using the card while paying it off to avoid increasing the balance."
msgstr ""
"Deja de usar la tarjeta mientras la liquidas para evitar aumentar el saldo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Call your card company to ask for a lower interest rate - it often works!"
msgstr ""
"Llame a la compañía de su tarjeta para solicitar una tasa de interés más "
"baja; ¡a menudo funciona!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:498
msgid "Making only minimum payments will take"
msgstr "Realizar solo pagos mínimos tomará"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:498
msgid "years and cost"
msgstr "años y costo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_card_calculator.html:498
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:171
msgid "in interest!"
msgstr "¡en interés!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:5
msgid "Credit Card Payoff Calculator - Pay Off Debt Faster"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de liquidación de tarjetas de crédito: liquidación de deudas más"
" rápido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate how long to pay off credit card debt. Compare debt snowball vs "
"avalanche strategies. See how extra payments reduce interest."
msgstr ""
"Calcule en cuánto tiempo saldar la deuda de la tarjeta de crédito. Compare "
"las estrategias de bola de nieve con las de avalancha de deuda. Vea cómo los"
" pagos adicionales reducen los intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"credit card payoff calculator, debt payoff, debt snowball, debt avalanche, "
"credit card interest, pay off debt"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de liquidación de tarjetas de crédito, liquidación de deudas, "
"bola de nieve de deudas, avalancha de deudas, intereses de tarjetas de "
"crédito, liquidación de deudas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate how to pay off credit card debt faster."
msgstr "Calcule cómo liquidar la deuda de tarjetas de crédito más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:37
msgid ""
"See how long it will take to pay off your credit card debt and how much "
"interest you'll pay. Compare strategies to become debt-free faster."
msgstr ""
"Vea cuánto tiempo le llevará liquidar la deuda de su tarjeta de crédito y "
"cuánto interés pagará. Compare estrategias para liberarse de sus deudas más "
"rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:51
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/pension_calculator.html:47
msgid "Calculator Type"
msgstr "Tipo de calculadora"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:53
msgid "Single Card"
msgstr "Tarjeta única"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:54
msgid "Multiple Cards"
msgstr "Varias tarjetas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:69
