msgstr "Tiempo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:157
msgid "Saved"
msgstr "Guardado"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:196
msgid "Plan Your Debt Freedom"
msgstr "Planifique su libertad de endeudamiento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:197
msgid "Enter your debt details to see your payoff timeline."
msgstr "Ingrese los detalles de su deuda para ver el cronograma de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:205
msgid "Debt Payoff Strategies"
msgstr "Estrategias de pago de deuda"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:209
msgid ""
"Pay minimums on all debts, then put extra toward the highest interest rate "
"debt. Saves the most money in interest."
msgstr ""
"Pague los mínimos en todas las deudas y luego dedique más a la deuda con la "
"tasa de interés más alta. Ahorra la mayor cantidad de dinero en intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:213
msgid ""
"Pay minimums on all debts, then put extra toward the smallest balance. Quick"
" wins boost motivation."
msgstr ""
"Pague los mínimos en todas las deudas y luego aporte más al saldo más "
"pequeño. Las victorias rápidas aumentan la motivación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:224
msgid "How much extra should I pay?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto extra debo pagar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:230
msgid ""
"Even $25-50 extra per month makes a difference. Pay as much as your budget "
"allows after covering essentials and building a small emergency fund."
msgstr ""
"Incluso entre 25 y 50 dólares adicionales al mes marcan la diferencia. Pague"
" todo lo que le permita su presupuesto después de cubrir lo esencial y crear"
" un pequeño fondo de emergencia."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:236
msgid "Should I save or pay off debt?"
msgstr "¿Debo ahorrar o saldar mis deudas?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_payoff_calculator.html:242
#, python-format
msgid ""
"First save $1,000 for emergencies. Then focus on high-interest debt (over "
"7-8%%). For lower rates, balance between saving and paying debt."
msgstr ""
"Primero, ahorre $1,000 para emergencias. Luego, céntrese en la deuda con "
"intereses altos (más del 7-8%%). Para tasas más bajas, equilibre entre "
"ahorrar y pagar deuda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:5
msgid "Debt-to-Income (DTI) Calculator - Check Mortgage Qualification"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de deuda-ingresos (DTI) - Verifique la calificación de la "
"hipoteca"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your debt-to-income ratio to see if you qualify for a mortgage. "
"Check front-end and back-end DTI ratios against lender guidelines."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su relación deuda-ingresos para ver si califica para una hipoteca. "
"Verifique los índices de DTI inicial y final con las pautas del prestamista."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"DTI calculator, debt to income ratio, mortgage qualification, housing ratio,"
" front end DTI, back end DTI"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora DTI, relación deuda-ingresos, calificación hipotecaria, relación"
" de vivienda, DTI inicial, DTI final"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:43
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:49
msgid "Debt-to-Income Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de deuda a ingresos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your DTI ratio and check mortgage qualification status."
msgstr ""
