#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:318
#, python-format
msgid "Room for Additional Debt (to reach 43%% DTI)"
msgstr "Espacio para deuda adicional (para llegar al 43%% DTI)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:330
msgid "Understanding DTI Ratios"
msgstr "Comprensión de las relaciones DTI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:333
msgid "Front-End Ratio (Housing Ratio)"
msgstr "Relación inicial (relación de vivienda)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:334
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This measures what percentage of your gross income goes toward housing costs"
" (mortgage, taxes, insurance, HOA). Most lenders prefer this to be under "
"28%%."
msgstr ""
"Esto mide qué porcentaje de sus ingresos brutos se destina a los costos de "
"vivienda (hipoteca, impuestos, seguros, HOA). La mayoría de los prestamistas"
" prefieren que sea inferior al 28%%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:337
msgid "Back-End Ratio (Total DTI)"
msgstr "Ratio back-end (DTI total)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This includes all your monthly debt payments divided by your gross income. "
"The qualified mortgage (QM) limit is 43%%, though some loans allow up to "
"50%%."
msgstr ""
"Esto incluye todos los pagos mensuales de su deuda divididos por su ingreso "
"bruto. El límite de la hipoteca calificada (QM) es del 43%%, aunque algunos "
"préstamos permiten hasta el 50%%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:343
msgid "Tips to Improve Your DTI"
msgstr "Consejos para mejorar su DTI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:349
msgid "Pay off credit cards and small loans first"
msgstr "Pague primero las tarjetas de crédito y los préstamos pequeños"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:355
msgid "Avoid taking on new debt before applying"
msgstr "Evite contraer nuevas deudas antes de presentar la solicitud"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:361
msgid "Increase your income with side jobs or raises"
msgstr "Aumente sus ingresos con trabajos secundarios o aumentos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/debt_to_income_calculator.html:367
msgid "Consider a larger down payment for a smaller loan"
msgstr "Considere un pago inicial mayor para un préstamo más pequeño"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/discount_calculator.html:5
msgid "Discount Calculator - Calculate Sale Price & Savings"
msgstr "Calculadora de descuentos: calcular el precio de venta y los ahorros"

