msgid "View Your Plan"
msgstr "Vea su plan"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:268
msgid "See when you'll reach your goal and compare options."
msgstr "Vea cuándo alcanzará su objetivo y compare opciones."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:280
msgid "How much down payment do I need?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto pago inicial necesito?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:286
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Conventional loans typically require 5-20%% down. FHA loans allow as little "
"as 3.5%%. However, 20%% down avoids PMI and gets better rates."
msgstr ""
"Los préstamos convencionales suelen requerir un pago inicial del 5% al "
"​​20%. Los préstamos de la FHA permiten tan solo el 3,5%%. Sin embargo, un "
"20%% evita el PMI y obtiene mejores tasas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:292
msgid "What is PMI?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el PMI?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:298
#, python-format
msgid ""
"PMI (Private Mortgage Insurance) protects the lender if you default. It's "
"required with less than 20%% down and typically costs 0.5-1%% of the loan "
"annually. It can be removed once you reach 20%% equity."
msgstr ""
"PMI (seguro hipotecario privado) protege al prestamista en caso de "
"incumplimiento. Se requiere con menos del 20%% de pago inicial y normalmente"
" cuesta entre el 0,5% y el 1%% del préstamo anualmente. Se puede eliminar "
"una vez que alcance el 20%% del capital."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:304
msgid "What are closing costs?"
msgstr "¿Cuáles son los costos de cierre?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:310
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Closing costs include appraisal, title insurance, attorney fees, and more. "
"They typically range from 2-5%% of the home price. Some can be negotiated or"
" included in the loan."
msgstr ""
"Los costos de cierre incluyen tasación, seguro de título, honorarios de "
"abogados y más. Por lo general, oscilan entre el 2% y el 5% del precio de la"
" vivienda. Algunos pueden negociarse o incluirse en el préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:318
msgid "Down Payment Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para el pago inicial"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:324
msgid "Set up a dedicated savings account for your down payment."
msgstr "Configure una cuenta de ahorros dedicada para su pago inicial."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:330
msgid "Check for first-time homebuyer programs in your area."
msgstr ""
"Consulte los programas para compradores de vivienda por primera vez en su "
"área."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:336
#, python-format
msgid "Save at least 20%% to avoid PMI if possible."
msgstr "Ahorre al menos un 20%% para evitar el PMI si es posible."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:342
msgid "Don't forget to budget for emergency reserves after purchase."
msgstr ""
"No olvide hacer un presupuesto para reservas de emergencia después de la "
"compra."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:444
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:261
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:319
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:411
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:693
msgid "None"
msgstr "Ninguno"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/down_payment_calculator.html:466
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:319
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:166
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:247
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:371
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:323
msgid "Goal"
msgstr "Meta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:4
msgid "Future Value Calculator - Calculate Investment Growth"
msgstr "Calculadora de valor futuro: calcular el crecimiento de la inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate the future value of your investments with regular contributions. "
"See how your money grows over time with compound interest."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el valor futuro de sus inversiones con aportaciones periódicas. Vea "
"cómo crece su dinero con el tiempo con interés compuesto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"future value calculator, investment calculator, compound interest, FV "
"calculator, investment growth"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de valor futuro, calculadora de inversión, interés compuesto, "
"calculadora FV, crecimiento de la inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:37
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:43
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:46
