msgstr "Calculadora de valor futuro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:10
msgid "Calculate the future value of investments with compound interest."
msgstr "Calcular el valor futuro de las inversiones con interés compuesto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:18
msgid "Calculate future value of investments with regular contributions."
msgstr ""
"Calcular el valor futuro de las inversiones con aportaciones periódicas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:44
msgid ""
"Calculate how much your money will grow over time with compound interest and"
" regular contributions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cuánto crecerá su dinero con el tiempo con interés compuesto y "
"contribuciones periódicas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:59
msgid "Starting Amount"
msgstr "Cantidad inicial"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:69
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:101
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:132
msgid "Monthly Contribution"
msgstr "Contribución Mensual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:117
msgid "Total Contributed"
msgstr "Total aportado"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:125
msgid "Growth Multiple"
msgstr "Crecimiento múltiple"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:133
msgid "Contributions vs Interest"
msgstr "Contribuciones versus intereses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:149
msgid "Monthly Contribution Scenarios"
msgstr "Escenarios de contribución mensual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:156
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:180
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:399
msgid "Contributed"
msgstr "Contribuido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:169
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/inflation_calculator.html:160
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:199
msgid "Yearly Breakdown"
msgstr "Desglose anual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:199
msgid "Project Your Investments"
msgstr "Proyecte sus inversiones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:200
msgid "Enter your investment details to see your future value."
msgstr "Ingrese los detalles de su inversión para ver su valor futuro."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:208
msgid "Understanding Future Value"
msgstr "Comprender el valor futuro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:211
msgid "The Power of Compound Interest"
msgstr "El poder del interés compuesto"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:212
msgid ""
"Compound interest means you earn interest on your interest. The longer your "
"money compounds, the faster it grows. Starting early is the most powerful "
"factor."
msgstr ""
"El interés compuesto significa que usted gana intereses sobre sus intereses."
" Cuanto más se capitalice su dinero, más rápido crecerá. Comenzar temprano "
"es el factor más poderoso."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:215
msgid "Regular Contributions Matter"
msgstr "Las contribuciones regulares son importantes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:216
msgid ""
"Consistent monthly contributions can often contribute more to your final "
"balance than your initial investment, especially over long time periods."
msgstr ""
"Las contribuciones mensuales constantes a menudo pueden contribuir más a su "
"saldo final que su inversión inicial, especialmente durante períodos "
"prolongados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:227
msgid "What interest rate should I use?"
msgstr "¿Qué tasa de interés debo utilizar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:233
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Stock market average: ~7-10%% annually. Bonds: ~3-5%%. Savings accounts: "
"~4-5%%. Use conservative estimates for long-term planning."
msgstr ""
"Promedio del mercado de valores: ~7-10%% anual. Bonos: ~3-5%%. Cuentas de "
"ahorro: ~4-5%%. Utilice estimaciones conservadoras para la planificación a "
"largo plazo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:239
msgid "Does this account for inflation?"
msgstr "¿Esto tiene en cuenta la inflación?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:245
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No, this shows nominal future value. For real (inflation-adjusted) value, "
"subtract expected inflation (~2-3%%) from your interest rate."
msgstr ""
"No, esto muestra el valor futuro nominal. Para obtener el valor real "
"(ajustado a la inflación), reste la inflación esperada (~2-3%%) de su tasa "
"de interés."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:4
msgid "House Affordability Calculator - How Much House Can I Afford?"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de asequibilidad de la vivienda: ¿cuánta casa puedo permitirme?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Find out how much house you can afford based on your income and debts. "
"Calculate DTI ratios, monthly payments, and compare affordability scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Descubra cuánta casa puede pagar en función de sus ingresos y deudas. "
"Calcule índices de DTI, pagos mensuales y compare escenarios de "
"asequibilidad."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"house affordability calculator, how much house can I afford, mortgage "
"affordability, DTI calculator, home buying budget"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de asequibilidad de la casa, cuánta casa puedo pagar, "
"asequibilidad de la hipoteca, calculadora DTI, presupuesto de compra de "
"vivienda"

