#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:256
msgid "How Much House Can You Afford?"
msgstr "¿Cuánta casa puedes pagar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:257
msgid "Enter your income and expenses to see how much house fits your budget."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus ingresos y gastos para ver cuánta casa se ajusta a su "
"presupuesto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:270
msgid "Enter Income"
msgstr "Ingrese ingresos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:271
msgid "Your gross annual household income before taxes."
msgstr "Su ingreso familiar bruto anual antes de impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:277
msgid "Add Debts"
msgstr "Agregar deudas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:278
msgid "Include all monthly debt payments (excluding rent)."
msgstr "Incluya todos los pagos mensuales de la deuda (excluido el alquiler)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:285
msgid "See your max home price and compare scenarios."
msgstr "Vea el precio máximo de su vivienda y compare escenarios."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:297
msgid "What is DTI ratio?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la relación DTI?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:303
#, python-format
msgid ""
"DTI (Debt-to-Income) ratio compares your monthly debts to income. Front-end "
"DTI is just housing costs. Back-end DTI includes all debts. Lenders "
"typically want front-end under 28%% and back-end under 36%%."
msgstr ""
"La relación DTI (deuda-ingresos) compara sus deudas mensuales con sus "
"ingresos. La DTI inicial son solo costos de vivienda. DTI back-end incluye "
"todas las deudas. Los prestamistas normalmente quieren un front-end inferior"
" al 28%% y un back-end inferior al 36%%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:309
msgid "How much house can I really afford?"
msgstr "¿Cuánta casa puedo realmente pagar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:315
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A common rule is 2.5-3x your annual income, but this varies by location and "
"interest rates. Use the 28/36 rule: spend no more than 28%% of income on "
"housing and 36%% on all debts combined."
msgstr ""
"Una regla común es entre 2,5 y 3 veces su ingreso anual, pero esto varía "
"según la ubicación y las tasas de interés. Utilice la regla 28/36: no gaste "
"más del 28%% de los ingresos en vivienda y el 36%% en todas las deudas "
"combinadas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:321
msgid "What's included in the monthly payment?"
msgstr "¿Qué está incluido en el pago mensual?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:327
#, python-format
msgid ""
"PITI: Principal, Interest, Taxes, and Insurance. May also include PMI (if "
"less than 20%% down) and HOA fees. Budget for maintenance (1%% of home value"
" yearly) and utilities separately."
msgstr ""
"PITI: Principal, Intereses, Impuestos y Seguros. También puede incluir PMI "
"(si el pago inicial es inferior al 20%) y tarifas de HOA. Presupuesto de "
"mantenimiento (1%% del valor de la vivienda anual) y servicios públicos por "
"separado."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:335
msgid "Home Buying Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para comprar una vivienda"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:341
msgid "Get pre-approved before house hunting to know your real budget."
msgstr ""
"Obtenga una aprobación previa antes de buscar una casa para conocer su "
"presupuesto real."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:347
msgid "Don't max out your budget - leave room for unexpected costs."
msgstr "No exceda su presupuesto: deje espacio para costos inesperados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:353
msgid "Pay down debt before buying to improve your DTI and get better rates."
msgstr ""
"Pague sus deudas antes de comprar para mejorar su DTI y obtener mejores "
"tarifas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:359
msgid "Keep 3-6 months of expenses in reserves after closing."
msgstr "Mantenga de 3 a 6 meses de gastos en reservas después del cierre."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:485
msgid "P&I"
msgstr "PI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/house_affordability_calculator.html:485
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:461
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:225
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:311
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:71
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:72
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:73
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:74
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:75
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:27
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:80
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:88
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:71
msgid "Income Tax Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de Impuesto sobre la Renta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:5
msgid "Free 2024 Federal Tax Estimator"
msgstr "Estimador de impuestos federales gratuito para 2024"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free income tax calculator for 2024. Estimate your federal income tax, FICA,"
" state tax, and take-home pay. Includes all filing statuses, deductions, and"
" tax credits."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora gratuita de impuestos sobre la renta para 2024. Calcule su "
"impuesto federal sobre la renta, FICA, impuestos estatales y salario neto. "
"Incluye todos los estados civiles, deducciones y créditos fiscales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"income tax calculator, federal tax calculator, 2024 tax brackets, tax "
"estimator, take home pay calculator, effective tax rate, marginal tax rate, "
"FICA calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de impuesto sobre la renta, calculadora de impuestos federales, "
"tramos impositivos de 2024, estimador de impuestos, calculadora de salario "
"neto, tasa impositiva efectiva, tasa impositiva marginal, calculadora FICA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:20
msgid "Income Tax Calculator 2024"
msgstr "Calculadora de Impuesto sobre la Renta 2024"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:14
msgid "Estimate Your Federal & State Taxes"
msgstr "Calcule sus impuestos federales y estatales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your income tax with 2024 federal brackets. Includes FICA, state "
"tax, deductions, and credits."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su impuesto sobre la renta con los tramos federales de 2024. Incluye"
" FICA, impuestos estatales, deducciones y créditos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:21
msgid "Free income tax estimator with 2024 federal brackets."
msgstr ""
"Estimador de impuestos sobre la renta gratuito con tramos federales de 2024."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:28
msgid ""
"Calculate federal income tax, FICA, and state tax with 2024 tax brackets"
msgstr ""
"Calcule el impuesto federal sobre la renta, FICA y el impuesto estatal con "
"los tramos impositivos de 2024"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:43
msgid "What are the 2024 federal tax brackets?"
msgstr "¿Cuáles son los tramos impositivos federales de 2024?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:46
#, python-format
msgid ""
"For 2024, the federal tax brackets range from 10%% to 37%%. The brackets "
"depend on your filing status (single, married filing jointly, married filing"
" separately, or head of household)."
msgstr ""
"Para 2024, los tramos impositivos federales oscilan entre el 10%% y el 37%%."
" Los paréntesis dependen de su estado civil para efectos de la declaración "
"(soltero, casado que presenta una declaración conjunta, casado que presenta "
"una declaración por separado o cabeza de familia)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:51
msgid "What is the difference between marginal and effective tax rate?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre tasa impositiva marginal y efectiva?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:54
msgid ""
"Your marginal tax rate is the rate you pay on your last dollar of income. "
"Your effective tax rate is your total tax divided by total income, "
"representing your average tax burden."
msgstr ""
"Su tasa impositiva marginal es la tasa que paga por su último dólar de "
"ingresos. Su tasa impositiva efectiva es su impuesto total dividido por el "
"ingreso total, lo que representa su carga tributaria promedio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:59
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:523
msgid "What is FICA tax?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el impuesto FICA?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:62
#, python-format
msgid ""
"FICA includes Social Security (6.2%% up to $168,600) and Medicare (1.45%%, "
"plus 0.9%% additional on income over $200,000 for single filers)."
msgstr ""
"FICA incluye el Seguro Social (6,2%% hasta $168,600) y Medicare (1,45%%, más"
" 0,9%% adicional sobre ingresos superiores a $200,000 para contribuyentes "
"solteros)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/income_tax_calculator.html:89
msgid ""
"Estimate your 2024 federal income tax, FICA taxes, and take-home pay. "
"Includes all filing statuses, deductions, and tax credits."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su impuesto federal sobre la renta de 2024, sus impuestos FICA y su "
"salario neto. Incluye todos los estados civiles, deducciones y créditos "
"fiscales."

