#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:224
msgid "Calculate Your Interest"
msgstr "Calcule su interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:225
msgid "Enter your principal, rate, and time to see how your money grows."
msgstr "Ingrese su capital, tasa y tiempo para ver cómo crece su dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:238
msgid "Enter Amount"
msgstr "Ingrese el monto"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:239
msgid "Input your principal (starting) amount."
msgstr "Ingrese su monto principal (inicial)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:245
msgid "Set Rate & Time"
msgstr "Establecer velocidad y tiempo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:246
msgid "Enter the annual interest rate and time period."
msgstr "Ingrese la tasa de interés anual y el período de tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:252
msgid "Choose Type"
msgstr "Elija tipo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:253
msgid "Select simple or compound interest."
msgstr "Seleccione interés simple o compuesto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:265
msgid "What's the difference between simple and compound interest?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre interés simple y compuesto?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:271
msgid ""
"Simple interest is calculated only on the principal. Compound interest is "
"calculated on the principal plus accumulated interest. Compound interest "
"grows faster because you earn 'interest on interest'."
msgstr ""
"El interés simple se calcula únicamente sobre el principal. El interés "
"compuesto se calcula sobre el capital más el interés acumulado. El interés "
"compuesto crece más rápido porque se gana \"interés sobre interés\"."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:277
msgid "What is effective interest rate?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la tasa de interés efectiva?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:283
msgid ""
"The effective rate is the actual annual return when compounding is factored "
"in. For simple interest, it equals the stated rate. For compound interest, "
"it's higher due to compounding effects."
msgstr ""
"La tasa efectiva es el rendimiento anual real cuando se tiene en cuenta la "
"capitalización. Para el interés simple, es igual a la tasa indicada. Para el"
" interés compuesto, es mayor debido a los efectos compuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:289
msgid "How does compounding frequency matter?"
msgstr "¿Qué importancia tiene la frecuencia de capitalización?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"More frequent compounding means more interest. Daily compounding earns "
"slightly more than monthly, which earns more than annually. However, the "
"difference becomes smaller at higher frequencies."
msgstr ""
"Una capitalización más frecuente significa más interés. La capitalización "
"diaria gana un poco más que la mensual, que gana más que anualmente. Sin "
"embargo, la diferencia se vuelve menor a frecuencias más altas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:303
msgid "Interest Tips"
msgstr "Consejos de interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"For savings, look for accounts with daily compounding to maximize returns."
msgstr ""
"Para ahorrar, busque cuentas con capitalización diaria para maximizar la "
"rentabilidad."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:315
msgid ""
"The Rule of 72: Divide 72 by your interest rate to estimate years to double."
msgstr ""
"La regla del 72: divida 72 por su tasa de interés para estimar los años que "
"se duplicarán."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:321
msgid ""
"Start saving early - time is the most powerful factor in compound growth."
msgstr ""
"Empiece a ahorrar temprano: el tiempo es el factor más poderoso en el "
"crecimiento compuesto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/interest_calculator.html:327
msgid "For loans, prefer simple interest to pay less over time."
msgstr ""
"Para préstamos, prefiera el interés simple para pagar menos con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:4
msgid "Investment Calculator - ROI & Portfolio Growth Calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de inversiones - Calculadora de ROI y crecimiento de cartera"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate investment returns, ROI, and portfolio growth. See inflation-"
"adjusted values, tax impact, and compare scenarios with our free investment "
"calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el rendimiento de la inversión, el ROI y el crecimiento de la "
"cartera. Vea los valores ajustados por inflación, el impacto fiscal y "
"compare escenarios con nuestra calculadora de inversiones gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"investment calculator, ROI calculator, portfolio growth, compound returns, "
"investment planning, future value"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de inversiones, calculadora de ROI, crecimiento de cartera, "
"rendimientos compuestos, planificación de inversiones, valor futuro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:66
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:72
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:45
msgid "Investment Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de inversiones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"Calculate your investment growth, ROI, and compare different scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el crecimiento de su inversión, el ROI y compare diferentes "
"escenarios."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:18
msgid "Calculate investment returns with inflation and tax adjustments."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el rendimiento de las inversiones con ajustes por inflación y "
"impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:32
msgid "What is ROI?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el retorno de la inversión?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:35
msgid ""
"ROI (Return on Investment) measures how much profit or loss your investment "
"generates relative to its cost, expressed as a percentage."
msgstr ""
"El ROI (retorno de la inversión) mide cuánta ganancia o pérdida genera su "
"inversión en relación con su costo, expresado como porcentaje."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:73
msgid ""
"Project your investment growth, analyze ROI, and see how inflation and taxes"
" affect your returns."
msgstr ""
"Proyecte el crecimiento de su inversión, analice el ROI y vea cómo la "
"inflación y los impuestos afectan sus retornos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:107
msgid "Monthly contribution amount"
msgstr "Monto de contribución mensual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:118
msgid "Expected annual return percentage"
msgstr "Porcentaje de retorno anual esperado"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:121
#, python-format
msgid "S&P 500 historical average: ~10%%"
msgstr "Promedio histórico del S&P 500: ~10%%"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:126
msgid "Investment Period (Years)"
msgstr "Período de inversión (años)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:130
msgid "Investment period in years"
msgstr "Periodo de inversión en años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:135
