msgstr "Tasa de inflación esperada"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:152
msgid "Capital Gains Tax Rate"
msgstr "Tasa impositiva sobre las ganancias de capital"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:157
msgid "Capital gains tax rate"
msgstr "Tasa impositiva sobre las ganancias de capital"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:184
msgid "Total Gains"
msgstr "Ganancias totales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:188
msgid "ROI"
msgstr "retorno de la inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:192
msgid "CAGR"
msgstr "CAGR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:200
msgid "Inflation Impact"
msgstr "Impacto de la inflación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:203
msgid "Inflation-Adjusted Value"
msgstr "Valor ajustado a la inflación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:213
msgid "Tax Impact"
msgstr "Impacto fiscal"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:216
msgid "Taxes Owed on Gains"
msgstr "Impuestos adeudados sobre las ganancias"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:220
msgid "After-Tax Value"
msgstr "Valor después de impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:229
msgid "Portfolio Growth Over Time"
msgstr "Crecimiento de la cartera a lo largo del tiempo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:238
msgid "Investment Breakdown"
msgstr "Desglose de la inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:244
msgid "Return Scenarios"
msgstr "Escenarios de retorno"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:279
msgid "Plan Your Investment Growth"
msgstr "Planifique el crecimiento de su inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:280
msgid ""
"Enter your investment details to see projected returns, ROI, and compare "
"different scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su inversión para ver los rendimientos proyectados, "
"el ROI y comparar diferentes escenarios."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:293
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:80
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:298
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:309
msgid "Initial Amount"
msgstr "Monto inicial"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:294
msgid "Enter your starting investment or lump sum amount."
msgstr "Ingrese su inversión inicial o el monto de la suma global."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:300
msgid "Monthly Additions"
msgstr "Adiciones mensuales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:301
msgid "Add any regular monthly contributions you plan to make."
msgstr "Agregue cualquier contribución mensual regular que planee hacer."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:307
msgid "Set Parameters"
msgstr "Establecer parámetros"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:308
msgid "Adjust expected return, inflation, and tax rates."
msgstr ""
"Ajustar el rendimiento esperado, la inflación y las tasas impositivas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:314
msgid "Analyze Results"
msgstr "Analizar resultados"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:315
msgid "Review ROI, inflation-adjusted values, and scenarios."
msgstr "Revise el ROI, los valores ajustados por inflación y los escenarios."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:323
msgid "Understanding Investment Returns"
msgstr "Comprensión del rendimiento de las inversiones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:326
msgid "ROI vs CAGR"
msgstr "ROI frente a CAGR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"ROI shows total return as a percentage of your investment. CAGR (Compound "
"Annual Growth Rate) shows the smoothed annual return, accounting for "
"compounding."
msgstr ""
"El ROI muestra el retorno total como porcentaje de su inversión. CAGR (tasa "
"de crecimiento anual compuesta) muestra el rendimiento anual suavizado, lo "
"que representa la capitalización."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:329
msgid "Real vs Nominal Returns"
msgstr "Rendimientos reales frente a rendimientos nominales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"Nominal returns are before inflation adjustment. Real returns (inflation-"
"adjusted) show the actual increase in purchasing power."
msgstr ""
"Los rendimientos nominales son antes del ajuste por inflación. Los "
"rendimientos reales (ajustados por inflación) muestran el aumento real del "
"poder adquisitivo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:333
msgid "Dollar-Cost Averaging"
msgstr "Promedio de costos en dólares"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"Investing a fixed amount regularly (like monthly contributions) reduces the "
"impact of volatility by buying more shares when prices are low."
msgstr ""
"Invertir una cantidad fija con regularidad (como contribuciones mensuales) "
"reduce el impacto de la volatilidad al comprar más acciones cuando los "
"precios son bajos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:336
msgid "Tax Considerations"
msgstr "Consideraciones fiscales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"Long-term capital gains (held 1+ years) are typically taxed at lower rates "
"than short-term gains. Tax-advantaged accounts like IRAs can reduce or defer"
" taxes."
msgstr ""
"Las ganancias de capital a largo plazo (mantenidas durante más de 1 año) "
"generalmente se gravan a tasas más bajas que las ganancias a corto plazo. "
"Las cuentas con ventajas fiscales, como las IRA, pueden reducir o diferir "
"impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:348
msgid "What annual return should I expect?"
msgstr "¿Qué rentabilidad anual debo esperar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:354
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Historical stock market returns average 7-10%% annually (inflation-"
"adjusted). Bonds typically return 2-5%%. Conservative estimates use 6-7%%, "
"while aggressive estimates use 9-10%%."
msgstr ""
"Los rendimientos históricos del mercado de valores promedian entre 7% y 10%%"
" anualmente (ajustados a la inflación). Los bonos suelen tener una "
"rentabilidad del 2-5%%. Las estimaciones conservadoras utilizan un 6-7%%, "
"mientras que las estimaciones agresivas utilizan un 9-10%%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:360
msgid "How does inflation affect my investments?"
msgstr "¿Cómo afecta la inflación a mis inversiones?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:366
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Inflation reduces purchasing power. If your investment grows 7%% but "
"inflation is 3%%, your real return is about 4%%. Always consider inflation-"
"adjusted (real) returns when planning."
msgstr ""
"La inflación reduce el poder adquisitivo. Si su inversión crece un 7%% pero "
"la inflación es un 3%%, su rendimiento real es aproximadamente un 4%%. "
"Considere siempre los rendimientos (reales) ajustados a la inflación al "
"planificar."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:372
msgid "When do I pay capital gains tax?"
msgstr "¿Cuándo debo pagar el impuesto sobre las ganancias de capital?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:378
msgid ""
"Capital gains tax is owed when you sell investments at a profit. Tax rates "
"depend on how long you held the investment and your income level. Tax-"
"advantaged accounts (401k, IRA) can defer or eliminate these taxes."
msgstr ""
"El impuesto sobre las ganancias de capital se debe cuando se venden "
"inversiones con ganancias. Las tasas impositivas dependen de cuánto tiempo "
"mantuvo la inversión y su nivel de ingresos. Las cuentas con ventajas "
"impositivas (401k, IRA) pueden diferir o eliminar estos impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:384
msgid "Is it better to invest lump sum or monthly?"
msgstr "¿Es mejor invertir una suma global o mensualmente?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:390
msgid ""
"Statistically, lump sum investing outperforms dollar-cost averaging about "
"2/3 of the time. However, monthly investing reduces emotional risk and is "
"more practical for most people who invest from income."
msgstr ""
"Estadísticamente, la inversión a tanto alzado supera el costo en dólares en "
"promedio aproximadamente 2/3 del tiempo. Sin embargo, la inversión mensual "
"reduce el riesgo emocional y es más práctica para la mayoría de las personas"
" que invierten con sus ingresos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:398
msgid "Investment Best Practices"
msgstr "Mejores prácticas de inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:404
msgid "Diversify across asset classes - don't put all eggs in one basket."
msgstr ""
"Diversifique entre clases de activos: no ponga todos los huevos en la misma "
"canasta."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:410
msgid "Use tax-advantaged accounts (401k, IRA) to minimize tax impact."
msgstr ""
"Utilice cuentas con ventajas fiscales (401k, IRA) para minimizar el impacto "
"fiscal."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:416
msgid "Keep investment fees low - they compound against you over time."
msgstr ""
"Mantenga bajas las tarifas de inversión: se acumulan en su contra con el "
"tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:422
msgid "Stay invested long-term - time in the market beats timing the market."
msgstr ""
"Manténgase invertido a largo plazo: el tiempo en el mercado es mejor que la "
"sincronización del mercado."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:557
msgid "return"
msgstr "devolver"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:599
msgid "Portfolio Value"
msgstr "Valor de la cartera"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:607
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:650
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:302
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:253
msgid "Total Contributions"
msgstr "Contribuciones totales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:615
msgid "Inflation-Adjusted"
msgstr "Ajustado por inflación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:5
msgid "Traditional IRA Calculator - Retirement Tax Savings"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de IRA tradicional: ahorro en impuestos para la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your Traditional IRA retirement savings with tax deductions. See "
"projected balance, tax savings, and compare with taxable accounts using our "
"free calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus ahorros para la jubilación de IRA tradicional con deducciones "
"fiscales. Vea el saldo proyectado, los ahorros de impuestos y compárelos con"
" cuentas sujetas a impuestos usando nuestra calculadora gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"IRA calculator, traditional IRA, retirement calculator, tax deduction, IRA "
"contribution limits, retirement savings"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de IRA, IRA tradicional, calculadora de jubilación, deducción de"
" impuestos, límites de contribución de IRA, ahorros para la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:86
msgid "Traditional IRA Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora IRA tradicional"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your Traditional IRA balance and tax savings at retirement."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su saldo de IRA tradicional y sus ahorros fiscales al momento de la "
"jubilación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate Traditional IRA retirement savings with tax benefits"
msgstr ""
"Calcule los ahorros para la jubilación de una IRA tradicional con beneficios"
" fiscales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:38
msgid "What is a Traditional IRA?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una IRA tradicional?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"A Traditional IRA is an individual retirement account that offers tax-"
"deductible contributions. You pay taxes when you withdraw the money in "
"retirement, potentially at a lower tax rate."
msgstr ""
"Una IRA tradicional es una cuenta de jubilación individual que ofrece "
"contribuciones deducibles de impuestos. Paga impuestos cuando retira el "
"dinero durante la jubilación, potencialmente a una tasa impositiva más baja."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:46
msgid "What are the 2024 IRA contribution limits?"
msgstr "¿Cuáles son los límites de contribución de la IRA para 2024?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:49
msgid ""
"For 2024, you can contribute up to $7,000 per year to an IRA. If you are 50 "
"or older, you can make an additional $1,000 catch-up contribution for a "
"total of $8,000."
msgstr ""
"Para 2024, puede contribuir hasta $7,000 por año a una IRA. Si tiene 50 años"
" o más, puede hacer una contribución adicional de recuperación de $1,000 "
"para un total de $8,000."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:63
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:80
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:54
msgid "IRA Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:87
msgid ""
"Calculate your Traditional IRA retirement savings, tax deductions, and "
"compare with taxable investment accounts."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus ahorros para la jubilación y las deducciones fiscales de su IRA "
"tradicional y compárelos con las cuentas de inversión sujetas a impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:125
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:100
msgid "Income & Taxes"
msgstr "Ingresos e impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:128
msgid "Annual Income"
msgstr "Renta anual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:137
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:113
msgid "Current Tax Rate"
msgstr "Tasa impositiva actual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:144
msgid "Retirement Tax Rate"
msgstr "Tasa de impuesto de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:154
msgid "I have a workplace retirement plan (401k, etc.)"
msgstr "Tengo un plan de jubilación en el lugar de trabajo (401k, etc.)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:160
msgid "IRA Contributions"
msgstr "Contribuciones IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:163
msgid "Current IRA Balance"
msgstr "Saldo actual de IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:171
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:142
msgid "Annual Contribution"
msgstr "Contribución anual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:176
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:147
msgid "2024 limit: $7,000 ($8,000 if 50+)"
msgstr "Límite de 2024: $7,000 ($8,000 si es mayor de 50 años)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:200
msgid "Calculate IRA"
msgstr "Calcular IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:206
msgid "Traditional vs Roth IRA"
msgstr "IRA tradicional frente a Roth"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:207
msgid ""
"Traditional IRA: Tax deduction now, pay taxes later. Best if you expect "
"lower tax rate in retirement."
msgstr ""
"IRA tradicional: deducción de impuestos ahora, pago de impuestos después. Es"
" mejor si espera una tasa impositiva más baja durante la jubilación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:222
msgid ""
"Fill out the form to see your projected Traditional IRA balance and tax "
"savings."
msgstr ""
"Complete el formulario para ver su saldo proyectado de IRA tradicional y sus"
" ahorros en impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:228
msgid "Calculating your IRA projection..."
msgstr "Calculando su proyección IRA..."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:251
msgid "After-tax:"
msgstr "Después de impuestos:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:256
msgid "Total Tax Savings"
msgstr "Ahorro fiscal total"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:258
#, python-format
msgid "%% deductible"
msgstr "%% deducible"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:265
msgid "Monthly Income (Pre-tax)"
msgstr "Ingreso mensual (antes de impuestos)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:269
msgid "Monthly Income (After-tax)"
msgstr "Ingreso mensual (después de impuestos)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:273
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:249
msgid "Years to Retirement"
msgstr "Años hasta la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:280
msgid "IRA vs Taxable Account Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de cuentas IRA y sujetas a impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:283
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rmd_calculator.html:87
msgid "Traditional IRA"
msgstr "IRA tradicional"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:287
msgid "Taxable Account"
msgstr "Cuenta sujeta a impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:291
msgid "IRA Advantage"
msgstr "Ventaja IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:310
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:348
msgid "Tax Savings"
msgstr "Ahorros Fiscales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:314
msgid "Tax Arbitrage"
msgstr "Arbitraje Fiscal"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:324
msgid "IRA Balance Growth"
msgstr "Crecimiento del saldo de IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:332
msgid "Source of Growth"
msgstr "Fuente de crecimiento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:347
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:313
msgid "Contribution"
msgstr "Contribución"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:366
msgid "Traditional IRA Benefits"
msgstr "Beneficios tradicionales de IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:373
msgid "Tax-Deductible Contributions"
msgstr "Contribuciones deducibles de impuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Contributions may be fully or partially tax-deductible, reducing your "
"current taxable income."
msgstr ""
"Las contribuciones pueden ser total o parcialmente deducibles de impuestos, "
"lo que reduce su ingreso imponible actual."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:382
msgid "Tax-Deferred Growth"
msgstr "Crecimiento con impuestos diferidos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:383
msgid "Your investments grow tax-free until you withdraw them in retirement."
msgstr ""
"Sus inversiones crecen libres de impuestos hasta que las retire al "
"jubilarse."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:391
msgid "Lower Retirement Tax Rate"
msgstr "Tasa impositiva de jubilación más baja"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"If you're in a lower tax bracket in retirement, you save on taxes overall."
msgstr ""
"Si se encuentra en una categoría impositiva más baja durante la jubilación, "
"ahorrará impuestos en general."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:400
msgid "2024 IRA Contribution Limits"
msgstr "Límites de contribución de IRA 2024"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:404
msgid "Under 50 years old"
msgstr "Menores de 50 años"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:410
msgid "50 and older (catch-up)"
msgstr "50 años y más (ponerse al día)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:414
msgid ""
"Note: Income limits may affect deductibility if you have a workplace "
"retirement plan."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Los límites de ingresos pueden afectar la deducibilidad si tiene un "
"plan de jubilación en el lugar de trabajo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:425
msgid "When can I withdraw from my Traditional IRA?"
msgstr "¿Cuándo puedo retirar de mi IRA Tradicional?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:430
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can withdraw penalty-free starting at age 59½. Withdrawals before this "
"age typically incur a 10%% early withdrawal penalty plus regular income tax."
" Required Minimum Distributions (RMDs) must begin at age 73."
msgstr ""
"Puede retirar dinero sin penalización a partir de los 59½ años. Los retiros "
"antes de esta edad generalmente conllevan una multa por retiro anticipado "
"del 10% más el impuesto sobre la renta regular. Las Distribuciones Mínimas "
"Requeridas (RMD) deben comenzar a los 73 años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:435
msgid "Can I contribute to both a 401(k) and an IRA?"
msgstr "¿Puedo contribuir tanto a un 401(k) como a una IRA?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Yes! You can contribute to both a 401(k) and an IRA. However, your IRA tax "
"deduction may be limited if you have a workplace retirement plan and your "
"income exceeds certain thresholds."
msgstr ""
"¡Sí! Puede contribuir tanto a un 401(k) como a una IRA. Sin embargo, su "
"deducción de impuestos IRA puede ser limitada si tiene un plan de jubilación"
" en el lugar de trabajo y sus ingresos exceden ciertos umbrales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:445
msgid "Should I choose a Traditional or Roth IRA?"
msgstr "¿Debo elegir una IRA tradicional o Roth?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/ira_calculator.html:450
msgid ""
"Choose Traditional if you expect a lower tax rate in retirement than now. "
"Choose Roth if you expect to be in the same or higher tax bracket. When in "
"doubt, consider splitting between both to diversify your tax exposure."
msgstr ""
"Elija Tradicional si espera una tasa impositiva más baja durante la "
"jubilación que la actual. Elija Roth si espera estar en la misma categoría "
"impositiva o en una superior. En caso de duda, considere dividir entre ambos"
" para diversificar su exposición fiscal."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:4
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:9
msgid "Loan Calculator - Free Monthly Payment Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de préstamos - Calculadora de pagos mensuales gratuita"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free loan calculator to compute monthly payments, total interest, and create"
" amortization schedules. Easy to use with visual charts and extra payment "
"analysis."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de préstamos gratuita para calcular pagos mensuales, intereses "
"totales y crear calendarios de amortización. Fácil de usar con gráficos "
"visuales y análisis de pagos adicionales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"loan calculator, payment calculator, amortization schedule, interest "
"calculator, extra payment, loan payoff"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de préstamos, calculadora de pagos, cronograma de amortización, "
"calculadora de intereses, pago extra, liquidación de préstamos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"Calculate monthly payments, total interest, and view complete amortization "
"schedules for any loan."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos mensuales, el interés total y vea los calendarios de "
"amortización completos de cualquier préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:13
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:20
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:64
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:81
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:87
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:29 core/templates/core/index.html:127
msgid "Loan Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de préstamos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:14
msgid ""
"Free online loan calculator with amortization schedule and extra payment "
"analysis."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de préstamos online gratuita con calendario de amortización y "
"análisis de pagos extra."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:21
msgid ""
"Calculate monthly loan payments, total interest, and create detailed "
"amortization schedules."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos mensuales del préstamo, el interés total y cree "
"cronogramas de amortización detallados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:39
msgid "How is the monthly loan payment calculated?"
msgstr "¿Cómo se calcula el pago mensual del préstamo?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:42
msgid ""
"Monthly payment is calculated using the formula: M = P × [r(1+r)^n] / "
"[(1+r)^n-1], where P is principal, r is monthly interest rate, and n is "
"number of payments."
msgstr ""
"El pago mensual se calcula mediante la fórmula: M = P × [r(1+r)^n] / "
"[(1+r)^n-1], donde P es el capital, r es la tasa de interés mensual y n es "
"el número de pagos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:47
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:357
msgid "What happens if I make extra payments?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa si hago pagos extras?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:50
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly toward your loan principal, reducing the total "
"interest paid and shortening the loan term."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales se destinan directamente al capital de su préstamo, lo"
" que reduce el interés total pagado y acorta el plazo del préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:88
msgid ""
"Calculate monthly payments, total interest, and generate a complete "
"amortization schedule for any loan."
msgstr ""
"Calcule pagos mensuales, intereses totales y genere un calendario de "
"amortización completo para cualquier préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:110
msgid "Loan amount in dollars"
msgstr "Monto del préstamo en dólares"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:133
msgid "Loan term"
msgstr "Plazo del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:152
msgid "Extra monthly payment amount"
msgstr "Monto de pago mensual adicional"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:182
msgid "Total Payment"
msgstr "Pago Total"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:198
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:261
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:349
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:162
msgid "Extra Payment Savings"
msgstr "Ahorros en pagos adicionales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:200
msgid "By adding extra payments, you will save"
msgstr "Al agregar pagos extra, ahorrarás"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:202
msgid "in interest and pay off your loan"
msgstr "en intereses y liquidar su préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:204
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:263
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:351
msgid "months earlier!"
msgstr "meses antes!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:283
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:172
msgid "Enter Your Loan Details"
msgstr "Ingrese los detalles de su préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:284
msgid ""
"Fill in the form on the left to calculate your monthly payment and view the "
"complete amortization schedule."
msgstr ""
"Rellena el formulario de la izquierda para calcular tu pago mensual y ver el"
" calendario de amortización completo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:297
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/payment_calculator.html:214
msgid "Enter Loan Amount"
msgstr "Ingrese el monto del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:298
msgid ""
"Input the total amount you want to borrow. This is the principal of your "
"loan."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el monto total que desea pedir prestado. Este es el capital de su "
"préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:304
msgid "Set Interest Rate & Term"
msgstr "Establecer tasa de interés y plazo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:305
msgid ""
"Enter the annual interest rate and choose your loan term in years or months."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la tasa de interés anual y elija el plazo de su préstamo en años o "
"meses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"View your monthly payment, total interest, and complete amortization "
"schedule."
msgstr ""
"Vea su pago mensual, interés total y calendario de amortización completo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:320
msgid "Understanding Your Loan"
msgstr "Entendiendo su préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"Your monthly payment consists of two parts: principal (the original loan "
"amount) and interest (the cost of borrowing). Early payments are mostly "
"interest, while later payments go more toward principal."
msgstr ""
"Su pago mensual consta de dos partes: capital (el monto original del "
"préstamo) e intereses (el costo del préstamo). Los pagos anticipados son "
"principalmente intereses, mientras que los pagos posteriores se destinan más"
" al capital."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:326
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:531
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:535
msgid "Amortization"
msgstr "Amortización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"Amortization is the process of paying off a loan over time with regular "
"payments. Each payment reduces your balance until the loan is fully paid."
msgstr ""
"La amortización es el proceso de liquidar un préstamo a lo largo del tiempo "
"con pagos regulares. Cada pago reduce su saldo hasta que el préstamo esté "
"completamente pagado."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:330
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:222
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:486
msgid "Extra Payments"
msgstr "Pagos adicionales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Making extra payments reduces your principal faster, which means less "
"interest over the life of the loan. Even small extra amounts can save "
"thousands in interest."
msgstr ""
"Hacer pagos adicionales reduce el capital más rápido, lo que significa menos"
" intereses durante la vigencia del préstamo. Incluso pequeñas cantidades "
"adicionales pueden ahorrar miles de dólares en intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:333
msgid "Interest Rate Impact"
msgstr "Impacto de la tasa de interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:334
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A lower interest rate significantly reduces your total cost. Even a 0.5%% "
"reduction can save thousands of dollars over a long-term loan."
msgstr ""
"Una tasa de interés más baja reduce significativamente su costo total. "
"Incluso una reducción del 0,5% puede ahorrar miles de dólares en un préstamo"
" a largo plazo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:345
msgid "How is the monthly payment calculated?"
msgstr "¿Cómo se calcula el pago mensual?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"The monthly payment is calculated using the standard loan formula: M = P × "
"[r(1+r)^n] / [(1+r)^n-1], where P is the loan principal, r is the monthly "
"interest rate, and n is the total number of payments."
msgstr ""
"El pago mensual se calcula utilizando la fórmula de préstamo estándar: M = P"
" × [r(1+r)^n] / [(1+r)^n-1], donde P es el principal del préstamo, r es la "
"tasa de interés mensual y n es el número total de pagos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly toward reducing your loan principal. This means "
"you'll pay less interest over time and pay off your loan faster. Even small "
"extra amounts can have a significant impact."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales se destinan directamente a reducir el capital de su "
"préstamo. Esto significa que pagará menos intereses con el tiempo y "
"liquidará su préstamo más rápido. Incluso pequeñas cantidades adicionales "
"pueden tener un impacto significativo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:375
msgid ""
"An amortization schedule is a table showing each payment over the life of "
"the loan. It breaks down how much of each payment goes to interest vs. "
"principal, and shows the remaining balance after each payment."
msgstr ""
"Un calendario de amortización es una tabla que muestra cada pago durante la "
"vigencia del préstamo. Desglosa cuánto de cada pago se destina a intereses "
"frente a capital y muestra el saldo restante después de cada pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:381
msgid "Should I choose a shorter or longer loan term?"
msgstr "¿Debo elegir un plazo de préstamo más corto o más largo?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"A shorter term means higher monthly payments but less total interest. A "
"longer term means lower monthly payments but more total interest. Choose "
"based on your budget and financial goals."
msgstr ""
"Un plazo más corto significa pagos mensuales más altos pero menos intereses "
"totales. Un plazo más largo significa pagos mensuales más bajos pero más "
"intereses totales. Elija según su presupuesto y objetivos financieros."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:401
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Shop around for the best interest rate - even 0.25%% can save you hundreds."
msgstr ""
"Compare precios para encontrar la mejor tasa de interés: incluso un 0,25 % "
"puede ahorrarle cientos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Make biweekly payments instead of monthly - you'll make one extra payment "
"per year."
msgstr ""
"Realice pagos quincenales en lugar de mensuales: realizará un pago adicional"
" por año."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Round up your payments - paying $500 instead of $487 adds up over time."
msgstr ""
"Redondea tus pagos: pagar $500 en lugar de $487 se suma con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:419
msgid "Put any windfalls (bonuses, tax refunds) toward your loan principal."
msgstr ""
"Coloque cualquier ganancia inesperada (bonos, reembolsos de impuestos) en el"
" capital de su préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/loan_calculator.html:645
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:558
msgid "With Extra Payments"
msgstr "Con pagos extra"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:5
msgid "Margin Calculator - Calculate Profit Margin & Markup"
msgstr "Calculadora de margen - Calcular margen de beneficio y margen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate profit margin, markup percentage, and selling price. Convert "
"between margin and markup with formulas and comparison tables."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el margen de beneficio, el porcentaje de margen y el precio de "
"venta. Convierta entre margen y margen con fórmulas y tablas de comparación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"margin calculator, markup calculator, profit margin, gross margin, price "
"markup, business calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de margen, calculadora de margen, margen de beneficio, margen "
"bruto, margen de precio, calculadora de negocios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:43
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:93
msgid "Margin Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de margen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate profit margin, markup, and selling price for your business."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el margen de beneficio, el margen de beneficio y el precio de venta "
"de su negocio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate profit margin and markup"
msgstr "Calcular el margen de beneficio y el margen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:50
msgid ""
"Calculate profit margin, markup percentage, and selling price. Understand "
"the difference between margin and markup."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el margen de beneficio, el porcentaje de margen y el precio de "
"venta. Comprenda la diferencia entre margen y margen de beneficio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:67
msgid "Margin & Markup from Cost and Price"
msgstr "Margen y margen de beneficio del costo y el precio"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:71
msgid "Selling Price from Cost and Margin"
msgstr "Precio de venta a partir del costo y el margen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:75
