#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:303
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:153
msgid "Quick Tips"
msgstr "Consejos rápidos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:309
msgid "Margin is always smaller than markup (for the same profit)"
msgstr "El margen siempre es menor que el margen (para el mismo beneficio)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:315
#, python-format
msgid "50%% margin = 100%% markup = doubling your cost"
msgstr "50%% de margen = 100%% de margen = duplicar su costo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/margin_calculator.html:321
msgid "Most businesses discuss margin; retail often uses markup"
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de las empresas discuten el margen; el comercio minorista a "
"menudo utiliza márgenes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:67
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:75
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:16
msgid "Mortgage Amortization Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de amortización de hipotecas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:5
msgid "Free Payment Schedule"
msgstr "Calendario de pago gratuito"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free mortgage amortization calculator with detailed payment schedule. See "
"how much goes to principal vs interest each month and how extra payments "
"save money."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de amortización de hipotecas gratuita con calendario de pagos "
"detallado. Vea cuánto se destina al capital y a los intereses cada mes y "
"cómo los pagos adicionales ahorran dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage amortization calculator, amortization schedule, loan payoff "
"schedule, mortgage payment breakdown, principal vs interest, extra payment "
"calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de amortización de hipotecas, cronograma de amortización, "
"cronograma de liquidación de préstamos, desglose de pagos de hipotecas, "
"capital versus intereses, calculadora de pagos adicionales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Generate a complete amortization schedule showing monthly payments, "
"principal, interest, and balance."
msgstr ""
"Genere un cronograma de amortización completo que muestre pagos mensuales, "
"capital, intereses y saldo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate and view your complete mortgage amortization schedule"
msgstr ""
"Calcula y consulta tu calendario completo de amortización de hipotecas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"An amortization schedule is a table showing each periodic payment on a loan,"
" broken down by how much goes to interest and how much reduces the principal"
" balance."
msgstr ""
"Un cronograma de amortización es una tabla que muestra cada pago periódico "
"de un préstamo, desglosado por cuánto se destina a intereses y cuánto se "
"reduce el saldo de capital."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:46
msgid "Why does more interest get paid at the beginning?"
msgstr "¿Por qué se pagan más intereses al principio?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:49
msgid ""
"Interest is calculated on your remaining balance. When your balance is high "
"(at the start), more of your payment goes to interest. As you pay down the "
"principal, interest charges decrease."
msgstr ""
"El interés se calcula sobre el saldo restante. Cuando su saldo es alto (al "
"principio), una mayor parte de su pago se destina a intereses. A medida que "
"paga el capital, los cargos por intereses disminuyen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:76
msgid ""
"View your complete payment schedule showing how each payment is split "
"between principal and interest."
msgstr ""
"Vea su cronograma de pagos completo que muestra cómo se divide cada pago "
"entre capital e intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:133
msgid "Loan Start Date"
msgstr "Fecha de inicio del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:162
msgid "See how extra payments save money and shorten your loan."
msgstr ""
"Vea cómo los pagos adicionales le ahorran dinero y acortan su préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:207
msgid "Your Amortization Schedule"
msgstr "Su calendario de amortización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:214
msgid "Generating schedule..."
msgstr "Generando cronograma..."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:263
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:351
msgid "You save"
msgstr "Ahorras"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:263
msgid "and pay off"
msgstr "y pagar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:271
msgid "Payment Visualization"
msgstr "Visualización de pagos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:293
msgid "CSV"
msgstr "CSV"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:331
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:399
msgid "Previous"
msgstr "Anterior"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:332
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:400
msgid "Next"
msgstr "Próximo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:348
msgid "How Amortization Works"
msgstr "Cómo funciona la amortización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"Amortization spreads your loan into fixed payments over time. Each payment "
"includes both principal and interest."
msgstr ""
"La amortización distribuye su préstamo en pagos fijos a lo largo del tiempo."
" Cada pago incluye tanto el capital como los intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:355
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:466
msgid "Early payments are mostly interest"
msgstr "Los pagos anticipados son principalmente intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:359
msgid "Later payments are mostly principal"
msgstr "Los pagos posteriores son en su mayoría principal."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:363
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:474
msgid "Extra payments reduce principal directly"
msgstr "Los pagos adicionales reducen el capital directamente"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:375
msgid "Benefits of Extra Payments"
msgstr "Beneficios de los pagos adicionales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:378
msgid "Making extra payments can significantly reduce the cost of your loan:"
msgstr ""
"Realizar pagos adicionales puede reducir significativamente el costo de su "
"préstamo:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:382
msgid "Save thousands in interest"
msgstr "Ahorre miles en intereses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:386
msgid "Pay off your mortgage years earlier"
msgstr "Paga tu hipoteca años antes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:390
msgid "Build home equity faster"
msgstr "Aumente el valor de su vivienda más rápido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:407
msgid "Why does more of my payment go to interest at first?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué una mayor parte de mi pago se destina a intereses al principio?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:408
msgid ""
"Interest is calculated on your remaining balance. When your balance is "
"highest (at the beginning), the interest charge is also highest."
msgstr ""
"El interés se calcula sobre el saldo restante. Cuando su saldo es más alto "
"(al principio), el cargo por intereses también es más alto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:411
msgid "When is the best time to make extra payments?"
msgstr "¿Cuándo es el mejor momento para realizar pagos extras?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"The earlier, the better! Extra payments in the first years have the greatest"
" impact since they reduce principal that would otherwise accrue interest."
msgstr ""
"¡Cuanto antes, mejor! Los pagos adicionales en los primeros años tienen el "
"mayor impacto ya que reducen el capital que de otro modo acumularía "
"intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:415
msgid "How do I read the amortization schedule?"
msgstr "¿Cómo leo el cronograma de amortización?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Each row shows one payment: the date, total payment amount, how much goes to"
" principal vs interest, and remaining balance after that payment."
msgstr ""
"Cada fila muestra un pago: la fecha, el monto total del pago, cuánto se "
"destina al capital frente a los intereses y el saldo restante después de ese"
" pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:429
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:529
msgid "Mortgage"
msgstr "Hipoteca"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:435
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:537
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:671
msgid "Payoff"
msgstr "Saldar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:441
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:543
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:541
msgid "Refinance"
msgstr "Refinanciar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:447
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:547
msgid "Loan"
msgstr "Préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:556
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:645
#: user/templates/user/activity_history.html:62
msgid "Showing"
msgstr "Demostración"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:556
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:645
#: user/templates/user/activity_history.html:64
#: user/templates/user/activity_history.html:76
msgid "of"
msgstr "de"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_amortization_calculator.html:687
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:707
msgid "A network error occurred."
msgstr "Se produjo un error de red."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:20
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:27
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:80
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:88
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:15 core/templates/core/index.html:109
msgid "Mortgage Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de hipotecas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:5
msgid "Free Home Loan Payment Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora gratuita de pagos de préstamos hipotecarios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free mortgage calculator to estimate monthly payments, total interest, and "
"amortization schedule. Calculate home loan costs including property tax, "
"insurance, PMI, and HOA fees."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de hipotecas gratuita para estimar pagos mensuales, intereses "
"totales y calendario de amortización. Calcule los costos de los préstamos "
"hipotecarios, incluidos impuestos a la propiedad, seguros, PMI y tarifas de "
"HOA."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage calculator, home loan calculator, monthly payment calculator, "
"amortization schedule, PMI calculator, property tax calculator, PITI "
"calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de hipotecas, calculadora de préstamos hipotecarios, calculadora"
" de pagos mensuales, calendario de amortización, calculadora de PMI, "
"calculadora de impuestos sobre la propiedad, calculadora PITI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Home Loan Payments"
msgstr "Calcular los pagos del préstamo hipotecario"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate monthly mortgage payments with taxes, insurance, and PMI. View "
"amortization schedule and see how extra payments save money."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos mensuales de la hipoteca con impuestos, seguros y PMI. Vea"
" el cronograma de amortización y vea cómo los pagos adicionales le permiten "
"ahorrar dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:21
msgid "Free mortgage payment calculator with amortization schedule."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de pago de hipoteca gratuita con calendario de amortización."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:28
msgid "Calculate monthly mortgage payments with taxes, insurance, and PMI"
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos mensuales de la hipoteca con impuestos, seguros y PMI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:43
msgid "What is included in a monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "¿Qué se incluye en el pago mensual de una hipoteca?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:46
msgid ""
"A monthly mortgage payment typically includes Principal (loan amount), "
"Interest, Property Taxes, Homeowners Insurance (PITI), and sometimes PMI and"
" HOA fees."
msgstr ""
"Un pago hipotecario mensual generalmente incluye capital (monto del "
"préstamo), intereses, impuestos a la propiedad, seguro de propietarios de "
"viviendas (PITI) y, a veces, tarifas de PMI y HOA."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:51
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:481
msgid "What is PMI and when is it required?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el PMI y cuándo se requiere?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:54
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Private Mortgage Insurance (PMI) is typically required when your down "
"payment is less than 20%% of the home price. PMI protects the lender if you "
"default on the loan."
msgstr ""
"Por lo general, se requiere un seguro hipotecario privado (PMI) cuando el "
"pago inicial es inferior al 20 % del precio de la vivienda. PMI protege al "
"prestamista si no cumple con el préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:59
msgid "How can I lower my monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo reducir el pago mensual de mi hipoteca?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:62
msgid ""
"You can lower your payment by: making a larger down payment, choosing a "
"longer loan term, shopping for lower interest rates, or buying a less "
"expensive home."
msgstr ""
"Puede reducir su pago: haciendo un pago inicial mayor, eligiendo un plazo de"
" préstamo más largo, buscando tasas de interés más bajas o comprando una "
"casa menos costosa."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:89
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly mortgage payment including principal, interest, "
"taxes, insurance, and PMI."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el pago mensual de su hipoteca, incluido el capital, los intereses, "
"los impuestos, el seguro y el PMI."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:115
msgid "Home Price in dollars"
msgstr "Precio de la vivienda en dólares"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:134
msgid "Down payment percentage"
msgstr "Porcentaje de pago inicial"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:169
msgid "Include Taxes & Costs"
msgstr "Incluir impuestos y costos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:178
msgid "Property Tax (yearly)"
msgstr "Impuesto sobre la propiedad (anual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:188
msgid "Home Insurance (yearly)"
msgstr "Seguro de Hogar (anual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:198
msgid "HOA Fees (monthly)"
msgstr "Tarifas de HOA (mensuales)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:208
#, python-format
msgid "PMI Rate (yearly %%)"
msgstr "Tasa PMI (% anual%)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:214
#, python-format
msgid "Applied when down payment < 20%%"
msgstr "Se aplica cuando el pago inicial <20%%"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:229
msgid "See how extra payments can save you money"
msgstr "Vea cómo los pagos adicionales pueden ahorrarle dinero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:275
msgid "Your Mortgage Results"
msgstr "Los resultados de su hipoteca"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:276
msgid ""
"Enter your loan details and click Calculate to see your monthly payment "
"breakdown."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su préstamo y haga clic en Calcular para ver el "
"desglose de sus pagos mensuales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:351
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:165
msgid "in interest and pay off"
msgstr "en intereses y liquidación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:421
msgid "The total purchase price of the home"
msgstr "El precio total de compra de la vivienda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:425
#, python-format
msgid "Your upfront payment (20%% avoids PMI)"
msgstr "Su pago por adelantado (20%% evita el PMI)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:429
msgid "Choose Loan Term"
msgstr "Elija el plazo del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:429
msgid "15 or 30 years are most common"
msgstr "15 o 30 años son lo más común"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:433
msgid "Enter Interest Rate"
msgstr "Ingrese la tasa de interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:433
msgid "Your loan's annual percentage rate"
msgstr "La tasa de porcentaje anual de su préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:437
msgid "Add Taxes & Insurance"
msgstr "Agregar impuestos y seguro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:437
msgid "Optional but gives accurate PITI payment"
msgstr "Opcional pero proporciona un pago PITI preciso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:448
msgid "Understanding Your Payment (PITI)"
msgstr "Comprender su pago (PITI)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:453
msgid "The amount that goes toward paying off your loan balance"
msgstr "El monto que se destina a liquidar el saldo de su préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:457
msgid "The cost of borrowing money from the lender"
msgstr "El costo de pedir dinero prestado al prestamista."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:461
msgid "Property taxes paid to local government"
msgstr "Impuestos a la propiedad pagados al gobierno local"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:465
msgid "Homeowners insurance protects your investment"
msgstr "El seguro para propietarios de viviendas protege su inversión"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:482
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Private Mortgage Insurance (PMI) is typically required when your down "
"payment is less than 20%%. It protects the lender if you default and usually"
" costs 0.3%% to 1.5%% of the loan annually."
msgstr ""
"Por lo general, se requiere un seguro hipotecario privado (PMI) cuando el "
"pago inicial es inferior al 20 %. Protege al prestamista en caso de "
"incumplimiento y generalmente cuesta entre el 0,3%% y el 1,5%% del préstamo "
"anualmente."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:485
msgid "Should I choose a 15-year or 30-year mortgage?"
msgstr "¿Debo elegir una hipoteca a 15 o 30 años?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:486
msgid ""
"A 15-year mortgage has higher monthly payments but lower total interest. A "
"30-year mortgage has lower monthly payments but you pay more interest over "
"time. Choose based on your budget and goals."
msgstr ""
"Una hipoteca a 15 años tiene pagos mensuales más altos pero un interés total"
" más bajo. Una hipoteca a 30 años tiene pagos mensuales más bajos pero usted"
" paga más intereses con el tiempo. Elija según su presupuesto y objetivos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:489
msgid "How much should I put down on a house?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto debo pagar por una casa?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:490
#, python-format
msgid ""
"20%% is ideal to avoid PMI, but many loans allow 3-5%% down. A larger down "
"payment means lower monthly payments and less interest paid overall."
msgstr ""
"El 20%% es ideal para evitar el PMI, pero muchos préstamos permiten un pago "
"inicial del 3% al 5%. Un pago inicial mayor significa pagos mensuales más "
"bajos y menos intereses pagados en general."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:493
msgid "How can extra payments save me money?"
msgstr "¿Cómo pueden ahorrarme dinero los pagos adicionales?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:494
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly toward principal, reducing your balance faster. "
"This means you pay less interest over the life of the loan and can pay off "
"your mortgage years earlier."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales se destinan directamente al capital, lo que reduce su "
"saldo más rápidamente. Esto significa que paga menos intereses durante la "
"vigencia del préstamo y puede liquidar su hipoteca años antes."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:509
msgid "Improve Your Credit Score"
msgstr "Mejore su puntaje crediticio"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:510
msgid ""
"A higher credit score can qualify you for lower interest rates, saving "
"thousands over the loan term."
msgstr ""
"Un puntaje crediticio más alto puede calificarlo para tasas de interés más "
"bajas, lo que le permitirá ahorrar miles de dólares durante el plazo del "
"préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:513
msgid "Make Biweekly Payments"
msgstr "Realizar pagos quincenales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:514
msgid ""
"Pay half your monthly payment every two weeks. You'll make 13 full payments "
"per year instead of 12."
msgstr ""
"Paga la mitad de tu pago mensual cada dos semanas. Realizará 13 pagos "
"completos por año en lugar de 12."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:517
msgid "Shop Multiple Lenders"
msgstr "Compre varios prestamistas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:518
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Get quotes from at least 3 lenders. Even a 0.25%% rate difference can save "
"thousands."
msgstr ""
"Obtenga cotizaciones de al menos 3 prestamistas. Incluso una diferencia de "
"tipos del 0,25% puede ahorrar miles de dólares."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:549
msgid "Affordability"
msgstr "Asequibilidad"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:25
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:34
msgid "UK Mortgage Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de hipotecas del Reino Unido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:5
msgid "Repayment & Interest-Only"
msgstr "Pago y sólo intereses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:8
msgid ""
"Free UK mortgage calculator to estimate monthly repayments for repayment and"
" interest-only mortgages. Supports property price, deposit, interest rate "
"and term."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de hipotecas gratuita en el Reino Unido para estimar los pagos "
"mensuales de hipotecas de pago e hipotecas de solo intereses. Admite precio "
"de propiedad, depósito, tasa de interés y plazo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:37
msgid ""
"Estimate your monthly mortgage repayments for UK repayment and interest-only"
" mortgages."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus pagos hipotecarios mensuales para el pago del Reino Unido y las "
"hipotecas de solo intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:58
msgid "Property Price"
msgstr "Precio de la propiedad"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:152
msgid "Mortgage Type"
msgstr "Tipo de hipoteca"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:156
msgid "Repayment"
msgstr "Reembolso"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:160
msgid "Interest-only"
msgstr "Sólo interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:212
msgid "Amortization Schedule (First 10 Years)"
msgstr "Calendario de amortización (primeros 10 años)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:228
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:384
msgid "Run a calculation to view the schedule."
msgstr "Ejecute un cálculo para ver el cronograma."

