msgid "Important Notes"
msgstr "Notas importantes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:292
msgid "This calculator estimates principal and interest only."
msgstr "Esta calculadora estima únicamente el capital y los intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:293
msgid ""
"UK lender fees, insurance, and taxes are not included unless you add them "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"Las tarifas, los seguros y los impuestos de los prestamistas del Reino Unido"
" no están incluidos a menos que los agregue por separado."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:294
msgid ""
"For interest-only mortgages, the schedule shows interest payments and the "
"balance remains the same."
msgstr ""
"Para las hipotecas de sólo intereses, el cronograma muestra los pagos de "
"intereses y el saldo sigue siendo el mismo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:295
msgid ""
"Results may differ from lender quotes due to rounding and product-specific "
"rules."
msgstr ""
"Los resultados pueden diferir de las cotizaciones de los prestamistas debido"
" al redondeo y a las reglas específicas del producto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:421
msgid "Expected payoff"
msgstr "recompensa esperada"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:435
msgid "No schedule available for this mortgage type."
msgstr "No hay cronograma disponible para este tipo de hipoteca."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:5
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:14
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:22
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:67
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:75
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:17
msgid "Mortgage Payoff Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de liquidación de hipotecas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:5
msgid "Calculate Payoff Date & Savings"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de pago y los ahorros"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free mortgage payoff calculator to find when your mortgage will be paid off."
" See how extra payments, biweekly payments, or lump sums can save you money."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de liquidación de hipoteca gratuita para saber cuándo se "
"liquidará su hipoteca. Vea cómo los pagos adicionales, los pagos quincenales"
" o las sumas globales pueden ahorrarle dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage payoff calculator, early mortgage payoff, extra payment calculator,"
" biweekly payment savings, mortgage interest savings"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de liquidación de hipotecas, liquidación anticipada de "
"hipotecas, calculadora de pagos extras, ahorro en pagos quincenales, ahorro "
"en intereses hipotecarios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate when your mortgage will be paid off and see how extra payments "
"save money."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cuándo se cancelará su hipoteca y vea cómo los pagos adicionales le "
"permiten ahorrar dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate mortgage payoff date and savings with extra payments"
msgstr "Calcular fecha de amortización de hipoteca y ahorro con pagos extras"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:38
msgid "How do extra payments save money?"
msgstr "¿Cómo ahorran dinero los pagos adicionales?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance that accrues "
"interest. This means you pay less interest overall and finish your loan "
"faster."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales van directamente al capital, reduciendo el saldo que "
"devenga intereses. Esto significa que pagará menos intereses en general y "
"finalizará su préstamo más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:46
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:507
msgid "What are biweekly payments?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los pagos quincenales?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:49
msgid ""
"Biweekly payments mean paying half your monthly payment every two weeks. "
"With 52 weeks per year, you make 26 half-payments (13 full payments) instead"
" of 12."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos quincenales significan pagar la mitad de su pago mensual cada dos "
"semanas. Con 52 semanas al año, realiza 26 medios pagos (13 pagos completos)"
" en lugar de 12."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:76
msgid ""
"Calculate how extra payments or biweekly payments can save on interest and "
"shorten your mortgage term."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cómo los pagos extras o pagos quincenales pueden ahorrarle intereses"
" y acortar el plazo de su hipoteca."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:87
msgid "Know Remaining Term"
msgstr "Conozca el plazo restante"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:90
msgid "Don't Know Term"
msgstr "No sé el término"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:97
msgid "Use this for new loans or loans without extra payments made."
msgstr "Úselo para préstamos nuevos o préstamos sin pagos adicionales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:104
msgid "Original Loan Amount"
msgstr "Monto original del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:114
msgid "Original Loan Term"
msgstr "Plazo del préstamo original"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:135
msgid "Remaining Term"
msgstr "Plazo restante"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:141
msgid "yrs"
msgstr "años"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:147
msgid "mos"
msgstr "mos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:154
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:250
msgid "Repayment Option"
msgstr "Opción de pago"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:158
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:254
msgid "Normal repayment"
msgstr "Pago normal"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:162
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:258
msgid "Extra payments"
msgstr "Pagos extras"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:166
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:262
msgid "Biweekly repayment"
msgstr "Pago quincenal"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:191
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:287
msgid "One-time"
msgstr "una sola vez"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:212
msgid "Find values in your monthly statement."
msgstr "Encuentre valores en su estado de cuenta mensual."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:219
msgid "Unpaid Principal Balance"
msgstr "Saldo de capital impago"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:314
msgid "Your Payoff Analysis"
msgstr "Su análisis de beneficios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:315
msgid ""
"Enter your mortgage details to see when you'll pay it off and how much you "
"can save."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su hipoteca para ver cuándo la liquidará y cuánto "
"puede ahorrar."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:341
msgid "Payoff in"
msgstr "Pago en"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:342
msgid "Your mortgage will be paid off by"
msgstr "Su hipoteca será cancelada por"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:348
msgid "Interest Savings"
msgstr "Ahorros de intereses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:351
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:359
msgid "Original:"
msgstr "Original:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:356
msgid "Time Savings"
msgstr "Ahorro de tiempo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:367
msgid "Payment Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de pagos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:374
msgid "With Payoff"
msgstr "Con recompensa"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:394
msgid "Payoff In"
msgstr "Pago en"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:405
msgid "What If You Pay Extra?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa si pagas más?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:410
msgid "Extra/Month"
msgstr "Extra/Mes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:424
msgid "View Amortization Schedule"
msgstr "Ver cronograma de amortización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:459
msgid "Principal and Interest"
msgstr "Principal e interés"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:462
msgid ""
"A mortgage payment has two parts: principal (the loan amount) and interest "
"(the cost of borrowing)."
msgstr ""
"El pago de una hipoteca consta de dos partes: principal (el monto del "
"préstamo) e interés (el costo del préstamo)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:470
msgid "As your balance decreases, interest charges fall"
msgstr "A medida que su saldo disminuye, los cargos por intereses disminuyen"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:489
msgid "Extra payments can dramatically lower your overall interest costs."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales pueden reducir drásticamente sus costos generales de "
"intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:491
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A one-time $1,000 payment on a $200,000 loan at 5%% can save $3,420 in "
"interest and pay off 4 months early."
msgstr ""
"Un pago único de $1,000 sobre un préstamo de $200,000 al 5%% puede ahorrar "
"$3,420 en intereses y liquidarlo 4 meses antes."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:508
msgid ""
"Pay half your mortgage every two weeks. With 52 weeks/year, you make 26 "
"half-payments (13 full payments) instead of 12, paying off faster."
msgstr ""
"Paga la mitad de tu hipoteca cada dos semanas. Con 52 semanas al año, "
"realiza 26 medios pagos (13 pagos completos) en lugar de 12, lo que amortiza"
" más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:511
msgid "Are there prepayment penalties?"
msgstr "¿Existen multas por pago anticipado?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:512
msgid ""
"Some loans have penalties for paying off early. FHA, VA, and most federal "
"loans prohibit prepayment penalties. Check your loan documents."
msgstr ""
"Algunos préstamos tienen sanciones por liquidar anticipadamente. La FHA, VA "
"y la mayoría de los préstamos federales prohíben las multas por pago "
"anticipado. Verifique los documentos de su préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:515
msgid "Should I pay extra or invest instead?"
msgstr "¿Debo pagar más o invertir en su lugar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:516
msgid ""
"It depends on your interest rate vs potential returns, tax situation, and "
"risk tolerance. Consider consulting a financial advisor."
msgstr ""
"Depende de su tasa de interés frente a los rendimientos potenciales, la "
"situación fiscal y la tolerancia al riesgo. Considere consultar a un asesor "
"financiero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:666
msgid "Pay"
msgstr "Pagar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:666
