"Many pensions include Cost of Living Adjustments (COLA) that increase your "
"benefit annually to keep pace with inflation."
msgstr ""
"Muchas pensiones incluyen ajustes por costo de vida (COLA) que aumentan su "
"beneficio anualmente para mantenerse al día con la inflación."

