#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:137
msgid "Desired Monthly Payment"
msgstr "Pago mensual deseado"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:155
msgid "Shorter terms = higher payments but less interest"
msgstr "Plazos más cortos = pagos más altos pero menos intereses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:156
msgid "Check your credit score for better rates"
msgstr "Verifique su puntaje crediticio para obtener mejores tasas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:157
msgid "Compare offers from multiple lenders"
msgstr "Compare ofertas de múltiples prestamistas"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:173
msgid ""
"Fill out the form to calculate your personal loan payments and see the full "
"amortization schedule."
msgstr ""
"Complete el formulario para calcular los pagos de su préstamo personal y ver"
" el calendario de amortización completo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:179
msgid "Calculating your loan..."
msgstr "Calculando tu préstamo..."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:201
msgid "for 36 months"
msgstr "durante 36 meses"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:206
msgid "Total cost:"
msgstr "Costo total:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:212
msgid "Loan Summary"
msgstr "Resumen del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:279
msgid "You Can Borrow Up To"
msgstr "Puedes pedir prestado hasta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid "with"
msgstr "con"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid "mo payment"
msgstr "pago mensual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:305
msgid "Loan Term Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de plazos de préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:306
msgid "Comparing loan amount:"
msgstr "Comparación del monto del préstamo:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:306
#: blog/templates/blog/post_detail.html:264
msgid "at"
msgstr "en"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:306
msgid "APR"
msgstr "ABR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:323
msgid "Interest Cost by Term"
msgstr "Costo de intereses por plazo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:335
msgid "Understanding Personal Loans"
msgstr "Comprender los préstamos personales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"A personal loan is an unsecured loan that can be used for almost any "
"purpose. Unlike a mortgage or car loan, personal loans don't require "
"collateral."
msgstr ""
"Un préstamo personal es un préstamo sin garantía que puede utilizarse para "
"casi cualquier propósito. A diferencia de una hipoteca o un préstamo para "
"automóvil, los préstamos personales no requieren garantía."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:338
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Interest rates typically range from 6%% to 36%% APR, depending on your "
"credit score, income, and the lender."
msgstr ""
"Las tasas de interés suelen oscilar entre el 6%% y el 36%% APR, según su "
"puntaje crediticio, sus ingresos y el prestamista."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:340
#, python-format
msgid "Excellent credit (750+): 6-10%% APR"
msgstr "Excelente crédito (750+): 6-10%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:341
#, python-format
msgid "Good credit (700-749): 10-15%% APR"
msgstr "Buen crédito (700-749): 10-15%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:342
#, python-format
msgid "Fair credit (650-699): 15-20%% APR"
msgstr "Crédito justo (650-699): 15-20%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:343
#, python-format
msgid "Poor credit (below 650): 20-36%% APR"
msgstr "Mal crédito (por debajo de 650): 20-36%% APR"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:348
msgid "Common Uses for Personal Loans"
msgstr "Usos comunes de los préstamos personales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:354
msgid "Debt consolidation - combine high-interest debts"
msgstr "Consolidación de deuda: combine deudas con intereses altos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:360
msgid "Home improvements and repairs"
msgstr "Mejoras y reparaciones del hogar."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:366
msgid "Major purchases or expenses"
msgstr "Compras o gastos importantes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:372
msgid "Medical bills and emergencies"
msgstr "Facturas médicas y emergencias."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:378
msgid "Wedding expenses or special events"
msgstr "Gastos de boda o eventos especiales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:395
msgid ""
"APR (Annual Percentage Rate) includes the interest rate plus any fees, "
"giving you the true cost of borrowing. The interest rate is just the cost of"
" borrowing the principal. Always compare APRs when shopping for loans."
msgstr ""
"La APR (tasa de porcentaje anual) incluye la tasa de interés más cualquier "
"tarifa, lo que le brinda el costo real del préstamo. La tasa de interés es "
"simplemente el costo de pedir prestado el principal. Compare siempre las APR"
" cuando busque préstamos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:400
msgid "Can I pay off my loan early?"
msgstr "¿Puedo liquidar mi préstamo anticipadamente?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:405
msgid ""
"Most personal loans allow early payoff without penalties, but always check "
"your loan agreement. Some lenders charge prepayment penalties. Paying off "
"early can save you significant interest."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de los préstamos personales permiten el pago anticipado sin "
"penalizaciones, pero siempre consulte su contrato de préstamo. Algunos "
"prestamistas cobran multas por pago anticipado. Pagar anticipadamente puede "
"ahorrarle importantes intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:410
msgid "How do I get the best interest rate?"
msgstr "¿Cómo obtengo la mejor tasa de interés?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"To get the best rate: 1) Check and improve your credit score, 2) Pay down "
"existing debt, 3) Compare offers from multiple lenders, 4) Consider a "
"shorter loan term, 5) Apply with a co-signer if needed."
msgstr ""
"Para obtener la mejor tasa: 1) Verifique y mejore su puntaje crediticio, 2) "
"Pague la deuda existente, 3) Compare ofertas de varios prestamistas, 4) "
"Considere un plazo de préstamo más corto, 5) Solicite con un cofirmante si "
"es necesario."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:4
msgid "Present Value Calculator - Calculate PV of Future Cash"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de valor presente: calcular el valor actual del efectivo futuro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate the present value of future money. Understand how much future cash"
" flows are worth today with our free PV calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el valor presente del dinero futuro. Comprenda cuánto valen hoy los "
"flujos de efectivo futuros con nuestra calculadora PV gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"present value calculator, PV calculator, discount cash flows, time value of "
"money, NPV calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de valor presente, calculadora de PV, flujos de efectivo "
"descontados, valor del dinero en el tiempo, calculadora de VPN"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:37
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:43
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:47
msgid "Present Value Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de valor presente"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:10
msgid "Calculate the present value of future cash flows."
msgstr "Calcule el valor presente de los flujos de efectivo futuros."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:18
msgid "Calculate present value of future cash flows."
msgstr "Calcule el valor presente de los flujos de efectivo futuros."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:44
msgid ""
"Calculate what future money is worth today. Essential for investment "
"decisions and financial planning."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cuánto vale hoy el dinero futuro. Esencial para decisiones de "
"inversión y planificación financiera."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:69
msgid "Discount Rate"
msgstr "Tasa de descuento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:114
msgid "What it's worth today"
msgstr "Lo que vale hoy"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:119
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:293
msgid "discount"
msgstr "descuento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:126
msgid "Discount Factor"
msgstr "Factor de descuento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:134
msgid "Total Discount"
msgstr "Descuento Total"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:142
msgid "Value Breakdown"
msgstr "Desglose de valor"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:148
msgid "Compare Discount Rates"
msgstr "Comparar tasas de descuento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:173
msgid "Find out what future money is worth in today's dollars."
msgstr "Descubra cuánto vale el dinero futuro en dólares de hoy."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:181
msgid "Understanding Present Value"
msgstr "Comprender el valor presente"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:184
msgid "Time Value of Money"
msgstr "Valor temporal del dinero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:185
msgid ""
"Money today is worth more than the same amount in the future because you can"
" invest it and earn returns. Present value calculates this difference."
msgstr ""
"El dinero hoy vale más que la misma cantidad en el futuro porque puedes "
"invertirlo y obtener ganancias. El valor presente calcula esta diferencia."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:188
msgid "The Discount Rate"
msgstr "La tasa de descuento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:189
msgid ""
"The discount rate reflects your required return or opportunity cost. Higher "
"rates result in lower present values, reflecting greater risk or better "
"alternatives."
msgstr ""
"La tasa de descuento refleja el rendimiento requerido o el costo de "
"oportunidad. Tasas más altas dan como resultado valores actuales más bajos, "
"lo que refleja un mayor riesgo o mejores alternativas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:200
msgid "What discount rate should I use?"
msgstr "¿Qué tasa de descuento debo utilizar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:206
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Use your required rate of return or what you could earn elsewhere. Common "
"choices: inflation rate (3%%), stock market return (7-10%%), or your cost of"
" capital."
msgstr ""
"Utilice la tasa de rendimiento requerida o lo que podría ganar en otro "
"lugar. Opciones comunes: tasa de inflación (3%%), rentabilidad del mercado "
"de valores (7-10%%) o su costo de capital."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:212
msgid "When is present value useful?"
msgstr "¿Cuándo es útil el valor presente?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:218
msgid ""
"Comparing investment options, valuing bonds, analyzing business investments,"
" retirement planning, or deciding between a lump sum and payments over time."
msgstr ""
"Comparar opciones de inversión, valorar bonos, analizar inversiones "
"comerciales, planificar la jubilación o decidir entre una suma global y "
"pagos a lo largo del tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:4
msgid "Rent vs Buy Calculator - Should You Buy or Rent?"
msgstr "Calculadora de alquiler versus compra: ¿debería comprar o alquilar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Compare the true costs of renting vs buying a home. See which option builds "
"more wealth over time with our comprehensive calculator."
msgstr ""
"Compare los costos reales de alquilar versus comprar una casa. Vea qué "
"opción genera más riqueza con el tiempo con nuestra calculadora completa."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"rent vs buy calculator, should I buy a house, rent or buy decision, home "
"buying calculator, real estate calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de alquiler versus compra, ¿debería comprar una casa?, decisión "
"de alquilar o comprar, calculadora de compra de vivienda, calculadora de "
"bienes raíces."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:37
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:43
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:24
msgid "Rent vs Buy Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de alquiler versus compra"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:10
msgid "Compare renting vs buying to make the right housing decision."
msgstr ""
"Compare el alquiler con la compra para tomar la decisión de vivienda "
"correcta."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:18
msgid "Compare the financial impact of renting vs buying a home."
msgstr "Compare el impacto financiero de alquilar versus comprar una casa."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:44
msgid ""
"Compare the true financial impact of renting vs buying to make an informed "
"housing decision."
msgstr ""
"Compare el verdadero impacto financiero del alquiler frente a la compra para"
" tomar una decisión de vivienda informada."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:59
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:159
