#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:356
msgid "Home Equity"
msgstr "Valor de la vivienda"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:174
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:195
msgid "Net Position"
msgstr "Posición neta"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:183
msgid "Starting Rent"
msgstr "Alquiler inicial"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:187
msgid "Investments"
msgstr "Inversiones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:204
msgid "Wealth Building Over Time"
msgstr "Creación de riqueza con el tiempo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:217
msgid "Rent or Buy?"
msgstr "¿Alquilar o comprar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:218
msgid "Enter your details to see which option builds more wealth."
msgstr "Ingrese sus datos para ver qué opción genera más riqueza."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:230
msgid "What factors matter most?"
msgstr "¿Qué factores importan más?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:236
msgid ""
"How long you stay, home appreciation rate, rent growth, and investment "
"returns. Location matters too - some markets favor buying, others renting."
msgstr ""
"Cuánto tiempo permanecerá, tasa de apreciación de la vivienda, crecimiento "
"del alquiler y rendimiento de la inversión. La ubicación también importa: "
"algunos mercados favorecen la compra, otros el alquiler."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:242
msgid "How long should I stay to make buying worth it?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto tiempo debo quedarme para que valga la pena comprar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:248
msgid ""
"Typically 5-7 years to break even on closing costs and early interest "
"payments. Less in appreciating markets, more in flat or declining ones."
msgstr ""
"Por lo general, se necesitan entre 5 y 7 años para alcanzar el punto de "
"equilibrio en los costos de cierre y los pagos anticipados de intereses. "
"Menos en los mercados que se aprecian y más en los que se estancan o caen."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_vs_buy_calculator.html:364
msgid "Investments (Renting)"
msgstr "Inversiones (Alquiler)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:4
msgid "Retirement Calculator - Plan Your Retirement Savings"
msgstr "Calculadora de jubilación: planifique sus ahorros para la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Plan your retirement with our free calculator. See how much you need to "
"save, calculate sustainable withdrawals, and check your retirement readiness"
" score."
msgstr ""
"Planifica tu jubilación con nuestra calculadora gratuita. Vea cuánto "
"necesita ahorrar, calcule retiros sostenibles y verifique su puntaje de "
"preparación para la jubilación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"retirement calculator, retirement planning, 401k calculator, retirement "
"savings, pension calculator, retirement income"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de jubilación, planificación de jubilación, calculadora 401k, "
"ahorros para la jubilación, calculadora de pensiones, ingresos de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:66
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:72
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:52
msgid "Retirement Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:10
msgid "Plan your retirement and see if you are on track to meet your goals."
msgstr ""
"Planifique su jubilación y vea si está en camino de alcanzar sus objetivos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:18
msgid ""
"Calculate retirement savings, sustainable withdrawals, and retirement "
"readiness."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los ahorros para la jubilación, los retiros sostenibles y la "
"preparación para la jubilación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:32
msgid "How much do I need for retirement?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto necesito para la jubilación?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:35
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A common guideline is to save 10-15x your annual income by retirement. The "
"4%% rule suggests you can withdraw 4%% of your savings annually."
msgstr ""
"Una pauta común es ahorrar entre 10 y 15 veces su ingreso anual antes de la "
"jubilación. La regla del 4%% sugiere que puedes retirar el 4%% de tus "
"ahorros anualmente."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:73
msgid ""
"Plan your retirement with confidence. Calculate how much you need to save "
"and see if you're on track."
msgstr ""
"Planifique su jubilación con confianza. Calcule cuánto necesita ahorrar y "
"vea si va por buen camino."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:82
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rmd_calculator.html:76
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:73
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:73
msgid "Your Information"
msgstr "Tu información"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:96
msgid "Retire At"
msgstr "jubilarse en"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:117
msgid "Current Retirement Savings"
msgstr "Ahorros de jubilación actuales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:164
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Suposiciones"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:169
msgid "Pre-Retire Return"
msgstr "Retorno previo a la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:178
msgid "Post-Retire Return"
msgstr "Retorno posterior a la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:200
msgid "Retirement Income"
msgstr "Ingresos de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:204
msgid "Desired Annual Income"
msgstr "Ingreso anual deseado"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:214
msgid "Expected Social Security (Monthly)"
msgstr "Seguro Social Esperado (Mensual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:224
msgid "Other Annual Income"
msgstr "Otros ingresos anuales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:250
msgid "Retirement Readiness Score"
msgstr "Puntuación de preparación para la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:258
msgid "At Retirement"
msgstr "En la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:266
msgid "Years to Save"
msgstr "Años para ahorrar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:270
msgid "Funds Last"
msgstr "Últimos fondos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:277
msgid "Projected Retirement Income (Annual)"
msgstr "Ingresos de jubilación proyectados (anual)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:280
#, python-format
msgid "From Savings (4%% rule)"
msgstr "De Ahorros (regla del 4%%)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:292
msgid "Total Annual Income"
msgstr "Ingreso Anual Total"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:300
msgid "Retirement Savings Projection"
msgstr "Proyección de ahorro para el retiro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:311
msgid "Accumulation Phase"
msgstr "Fase de acumulación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:330
msgid "Retirement Phase"
msgstr "Fase de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:354
msgid "Plan Your Retirement"
msgstr "Planifique su jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:355
msgid ""
"Enter your information to see if you're on track for a comfortable "
"retirement."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su información para ver si está encaminado hacia una jubilación "
"cómoda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:368
msgid "Enter Age Info"
msgstr "Ingrese la información de edad"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:369
msgid "Your current age, when you want to retire, and expected life span."
msgstr "Su edad actual, cuándo desea jubilarse y esperanza de vida."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:375
msgid "Add Savings"
msgstr "Agregar ahorros"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:376
msgid "Current savings and monthly contributions including employer match."
msgstr ""
"Ahorros corrientes y contribuciones mensuales, incluida la contrapartida del"
" empleador."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:382
msgid "Set Assumptions"
msgstr "Establecer supuestos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:383
msgid "Expected investment returns and inflation rate."
msgstr "Rendimientos esperados de la inversión y tasa de inflación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:390
msgid "See your readiness score and projected retirement income."
msgstr ""
"Vea su puntaje de preparación y sus ingresos de jubilación proyectados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:402
#, python-format
msgid "What is the 4%% rule?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la regla del 4%%?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:408
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The 4%% rule suggests you can withdraw 4%% of your retirement savings in the"
" first year, then adjust for inflation each year. This strategy is designed "
"to make your money last 30 years."
msgstr ""
"La regla del 4%% sugiere que puede retirar el 4%% de sus ahorros para la "
"jubilación durante el primer año y luego ajustarlo a la inflación cada año. "
"Esta estrategia está diseñada para que su dinero dure 30 años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:414
msgid "How much should I save for retirement?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto debo ahorrar para la jubilación?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:420
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A common guideline is to save 10-15%% of your income for retirement. By age "
"30, aim for 1x salary saved. By 40, 3x. By 50, 6x. By 60, 8x. By 67, 10x "
"your salary."
msgstr ""
"Una pauta común es ahorrar entre un 10% y un 15% de tus ingresos para la "
"jubilación. A los 30 años, aspira a ahorrar 1 vez el salario. A los 40, 3x. "
"A los 50, 6x. A los 60, 8x. A los 67, 10 veces tu salario."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:426
msgid "What return rate should I use?"
msgstr "¿Qué tasa de retorno debo utilizar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:432
#, python-format
msgid ""
"For pre-retirement (aggressive portfolio), 6-8%% is reasonable. For post-"
"retirement (conservative portfolio), 4-6%% is common. These are inflation-"
"adjusted estimates; actual returns vary."
msgstr ""
"Para la prejubilación (cartera agresiva), un 6-8% es razonable. Para la "
"post-jubilación (cartera conservadora), el 4-6%% es común. Estas son "
"estimaciones ajustadas a la inflación; los rendimientos reales varían."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:438
msgid "Should I include Social Security?"
msgstr "¿Debo incluir la Seguridad Social?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:444
msgid ""
"Yes, Social Security is an important income source for most retirees. You "
"can estimate your benefits at ssa.gov. The average benefit is about "
"$1,800/month, but varies based on your earnings history."
msgstr ""
"Sí, el Seguro Social es una fuente de ingresos importante para la mayoría de"
" los jubilados. Puede estimar sus beneficios en ssa.gov. El beneficio "
"promedio es de aproximadamente $1,800 al mes, pero varía según su historial "
"de ganancias."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:452
msgid "Retirement Planning Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para la planificación de la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"Always contribute enough to get your full employer match - it's free money."
msgstr ""
"Contribuya siempre lo suficiente para obtener la aportación total de su "
"empleador: es dinero gratis."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/retirement_calculator.html:464
