#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate Roth IRA tax-free retirement savings"
msgstr ""
"Calcule los ahorros para la jubilación libres de impuestos de Roth IRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:62
msgid ""
"Calculate your Roth IRA tax-free retirement savings. Contribute after-tax "
