msgid "Annual Equivalent"
msgstr "Equivalente Anual"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:402
msgid "Based on 40 hours/week, 52 weeks/year"
msgstr "Basado en 40 horas/semana, 52 semanas/año"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:405
msgid "Understanding Overtime Pay"
msgstr "Comprender el pago de horas extras"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Under the FLSA, non-exempt employees must receive overtime pay for hours "
"worked over 40 in a workweek at a rate not less than 1.5 times their regular"
" pay rate."
msgstr ""
"Según la FLSA, los empleados no exentos deben recibir pago de horas extras "
"por las horas trabajadas más de 40 en una semana laboral a una tasa no "
"inferior a 1,5 veces su tasa de pago regular."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"If your regular rate is $20/hour, your overtime rate is $30/hour (1.5x)."
msgstr ""
"Si su tarifa regular es de $20/hora, su tarifa de horas extras es de "
"$30/hora (1,5x)."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"Some states have additional overtime requirements, such as daily overtime or"
" double-time on holidays."
msgstr ""
"Algunos estados tienen requisitos adicionales de horas extras, como horas "
"extras diarias o horas extras dobles en días festivos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/sales_tax_calculator.html:4
msgid "Sales Tax Calculator - Calculate Tax Amount"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de impuestos sobre las ventas: calcular el importe del impuesto"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/sales_tax_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free sales tax calculator. Calculate sales tax, extract tax from total, or "
"find the tax rate. Easy to use with US state tax rates reference."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de impuestos sobre las ventas gratuita. Calcule el impuesto "
"sobre las ventas, extraiga el impuesto del total o encuentre la tasa "
"impositiva. Fácil de usar con referencia de tasas impositivas estatales de "
"EE. UU."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/sales_tax_calculator.html:6
