#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:4
msgid "Savings Calculator - Free Savings Goal Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de ahorros - Calculadora de objetivos de ahorro gratuita"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate how much you can save over time. Track your savings goals, see "
"interest earnings, and plan for the future with our free savings calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcula cuánto puedes ahorrar con el tiempo. Realice un seguimiento de sus "
"objetivos de ahorro, vea los ingresos por intereses y planifique para el "
"futuro con nuestra calculadora de ahorro gratuita."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"savings calculator, savings goal, interest calculator, money growth, "
"financial planning, savings tracker"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de ahorro, meta de ahorro, calculadora de intereses, crecimiento"
" del dinero, planificación financiera, rastreador de ahorros"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:66
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:72
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:59
