msgstr "Calculadora de Ahorros"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:10
msgid "Calculate your savings growth and reach your financial goals faster."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el crecimiento de sus ahorros y alcance sus objetivos financieros "
"más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:18
msgid ""
"Calculate savings growth, set goals, and track your progress to financial "
"freedom."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el crecimiento de los ahorros, establezca metas y realice un "
"seguimiento de su progreso hacia la libertad financiera."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:32
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:379
msgid "How much should I save each month?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto debo ahorrar cada mes?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:35
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Financial experts recommend saving at least 20%% of your income. Use our "
"calculator to find the exact amount needed to reach your goals."
msgstr ""
"Los expertos financieros recomiendan ahorrar al menos el 20%% de tus "
"ingresos. Utilice nuestra calculadora para encontrar la cantidad exacta "
"necesaria para alcanzar sus objetivos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:73
msgid ""
"Plan your savings journey. Calculate how much you can save, how long it "
"takes to reach your goal, or how much you need to save monthly."
msgstr ""
"Planifique su viaje de ahorro. Calcula cuánto puedes ahorrar, cuánto tiempo "
"te llevará alcanzar tu objetivo o cuánto necesitas ahorrar mensualmente."

