msgid "Enter Your Details"
msgstr "Ingrese sus datos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:339
msgid ""
"Input your initial savings, monthly deposit, interest rate, and time period."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus ahorros iniciales, depósito mensual, tasa de interés y período "
"de tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:345
msgid "View Your Results"
msgstr "Vea sus resultados"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:346
msgid "See your projected savings growth with detailed charts and breakdowns."
msgstr ""
"Vea el crecimiento de sus ahorros proyectado con gráficos y desgloses "
"detallados."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:354
msgid "Savings Strategies"
msgstr "Estrategias de ahorro"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:357
msgid "Pay Yourself First"
msgstr "Págate a ti mismo primero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"Set up automatic transfers to your savings account on payday. This ensures "
"you save before spending on discretionary items."
msgstr ""
"Configure transferencias automáticas a su cuenta de ahorros el día de pago. "
"Esto garantiza que ahorre antes de gastar en artículos discrecionales."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:360
msgid "The 50/30/20 Rule"
msgstr "La regla 50/30/20"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:361
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Allocate 50%% of income to needs, 30%% to wants, and 20%% to savings. This "
"simple framework helps maintain balance."
msgstr ""
"Asigne el 50%% de los ingresos a las necesidades, el 30%% a los deseos y el "
"20%% a los ahorros. Este marco simple ayuda a mantener el equilibrio."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:364
msgid "High-Yield Savings Accounts"
msgstr "Cuentas de ahorro de alto rendimiento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:365
msgid ""
"Online banks often offer higher interest rates than traditional banks. Even "
"small differences add up over time."
msgstr ""
"Los bancos en línea suelen ofrecer tasas de interés más altas que los bancos"
" tradicionales. Incluso las pequeñas diferencias se acumulan con el tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:367
msgid "Emergency Fund First"
msgstr "Fondo de Emergencia Primero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Before investing, build an emergency fund covering 3-6 months of expenses. "
"This provides financial security."
msgstr ""
"Antes de invertir, cree un fondo de emergencia que cubra de 3 a 6 meses de "
"gastos. Esto proporciona seguridad financiera."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:385
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A common guideline is to save at least 20%% of your income. However, the "
"right amount depends on your goals, expenses, and timeline. Use the 'Monthly"
" deposit needed' calculation to find the exact amount for your specific "
"goal."
msgstr ""
"Una pauta común es ahorrar al menos el 20%% de tus ingresos. Sin embargo, la"
" cantidad correcta depende de sus objetivos, gastos y cronograma. Utilice el"
" cálculo de 'Depósito mensual necesario' para encontrar el monto exacto para"
" su objetivo específico."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:391
msgid "What's a good interest rate for savings?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es una buena tasa de interés para los ahorros?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:397
#, python-format
msgid ""
"High-yield savings accounts currently offer 4-5%% APY. Traditional banks may"
" offer less than 0.5%%. Shop around for the best rates, and consider online "
"banks which typically offer higher rates."
msgstr ""
"Las cuentas de ahorro de alto rendimiento actualmente ofrecen un APY del 4% "
"al 5%. Los bancos tradicionales pueden ofrecer menos del 0,5%%. Busque las "
"mejores tarifas y considere los bancos en línea que normalmente ofrecen "
"tarifas más altas."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:403
msgid "What's the difference between APY and interest rate?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre APY y tasa de interés?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"APY (Annual Percentage Yield) includes the effect of compounding, showing "
"your actual annual return. The interest rate (APR) doesn't include "
"compounding. APY gives you a more accurate picture of your earnings."
msgstr ""
"APY (rendimiento porcentual anual) incluye el efecto de capitalización, "
"mostrando su rendimiento anual real. La tasa de interés (APR) no incluye "
"capitalización. APY le brinda una imagen más precisa de sus ganancias."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:415
msgid "Should I save or invest?"
msgstr "¿Debo ahorrar o invertir?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:421
msgid ""
"Use savings for short-term goals (1-3 years) and emergency funds. For long-"
"term goals (5+ years), consider investing in stocks or index funds which "
"historically provide higher returns despite more volatility."
msgstr ""
"Utilice los ahorros para objetivos a corto plazo (1-3 años) y fondos de "
"emergencia. Para objetivos a largo plazo (más de 5 años), considere invertir"
" en acciones o fondos indexados que históricamente brindan rendimientos más "
"altos a pesar de una mayor volatilidad."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:435
msgid "Automate your savings - set up automatic transfers on payday."
msgstr ""
"Automatice sus ahorros: configure transferencias automáticas el día de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:441
msgid "Save windfalls - put bonuses, tax refunds, and gifts into savings."
msgstr ""
"Ahorre ganancias inesperadas: ahorre bonificaciones, reembolsos de impuestos"
" y obsequios."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:447
msgid "Track your spending to find areas where you can cut back."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de sus gastos para encontrar áreas en las que pueda "
"recortar."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:453
msgid "Set specific goals - you're more likely to save with a clear target."
msgstr ""
"Establezca objetivos específicos: es más probable que ahorre con un objetivo"
" claro."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:581
msgid "Time to Goal"
msgstr "Tiempo para marcar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:588
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:197
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/date_calculator.html:98
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:96
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:155
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:185
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:155
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:185
msgid "End Date"
msgstr "Fecha de finalización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:597
msgid "You will reach your goal with"
msgstr "Alcanzarás tu objetivo con"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/savings_calculator.html:597
msgid "extra!"
msgstr "¡extra!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:5
msgid "Social Security Calculator - Estimate Your Benefits"
msgstr "Calculadora del Seguro Social: calcule sus beneficios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Estimate your Social Security retirement benefits. See how your benefit "
"changes at different retirement ages from 62 to 70."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus beneficios de jubilación del Seguro Social. Vea cómo cambia su "
"beneficio en diferentes edades de jubilación de 62 a 70 años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"social security calculator, retirement benefits, SS benefits, PIA "
"calculator, full retirement age"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de seguridad social, beneficios de jubilación, beneficios de SS,"
" calculadora de PIA, plena edad de jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:26
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:32
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:58
msgid "Social Security Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de Seguridad Social"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:33
msgid ""
"Estimate your Social Security retirement benefits and see how your claiming "
"age affects your monthly benefit amount."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus beneficios de jubilación del Seguro Social y vea cómo su edad "
"para reclamar afecta el monto de su beneficio mensual."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:61
msgid "Birth Month"
msgstr "Mes de nacimiento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:80
msgid "Current Annual Earnings"
msgstr "Ganancias anuales actuales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:88
msgid "Years Worked"
msgstr "Años trabajados"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:90
msgid "Total years you've worked (or will work)"
msgstr "Años totales que ha trabajado (o trabajará)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:94
msgid "Planned Retirement Age"
msgstr "Edad de jubilación prevista"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:109
msgid "Calculate Benefits"
msgstr "Calcular beneficios"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:114
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:578
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Nota:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:115
msgid ""
"This is an estimate. Actual benefits depend on your complete earnings "
"history."
msgstr ""
"Esta es una estimación. Los beneficios reales dependen de su historial "
"completo de ganancias."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:130
msgid ""
"Fill out the form to estimate your Social Security retirement benefits."
msgstr ""
"Complete el formulario para estimar sus beneficios de jubilación del Seguro "
"Social."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:149
msgid "Estimated Monthly Benefit at Age"
msgstr "Beneficio mensual estimado por edad"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:151
msgid "per year"
msgstr "por año"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:157
msgid "Your Full Retirement Age:"
msgstr "Su plena edad de jubilación:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:164
msgid "Benefits by Claiming Age"
msgstr "Beneficios por edad de reclamación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:172
msgid "Adjustment"
msgstr "Ajuste"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:183
msgid "Lifetime Benefits Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de beneficios de por vida"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:184
msgid "Assuming life expectancy of 85 years"
msgstr "Suponiendo una esperanza de vida de 85 años."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:197
msgid "Understanding Social Security"
msgstr "Entendiendo la Seguridad Social"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:199
msgid "Earliest age:"
msgstr "Edad más temprana:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:199
msgid "62 (reduced benefits)"
msgstr "62 (beneficios reducidos)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:200
msgid "Full Retirement Age:"
msgstr "Edad de jubilación completa:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:200
msgid "66-67 depending on birth year"
msgstr "66-67 dependiendo del año de nacimiento"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:201
msgid "Maximum age:"
msgstr "Edad máxima:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:201
#, python-format
msgid "70 (8%% increase per year after FRA)"
msgstr "70 (8%% de aumento por año después de FRA)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:202
msgid "Early claiming:"
msgstr "Reclamación anticipada:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:202
#, python-format
msgid "~6.7%% reduction per year before FRA"
msgstr "~6,7%% de reducción por año antes de FRA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:206
msgid "When to Claim?"
msgstr "¿Cuándo reclamar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:208
msgid "Claim early if you need income or have health concerns"
msgstr ""
"Reclame anticipadamente si necesita ingresos o tiene problemas de salud"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:209
msgid "Wait until 70 if you can afford to and expect to live long"
msgstr ""
"Espere hasta los 70 si puede permitírselo y espere vivir mucho tiempo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:210
msgid "Consider spousal benefits strategy"
msgstr "Considere la estrategia de beneficios conyugales"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/social_security_calculator.html:211
msgid "Factor in other retirement income sources"
msgstr "Tenga en cuenta otras fuentes de ingresos para la jubilación"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:4
msgid "Student Loan Calculator - Repayment Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de préstamos para estudiantes - Calculadora de pagos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate student loan payments and compare repayment plans. See total "
"interest, payoff timeline, and how extra payments can save you money."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos de préstamos estudiantiles y compare planes de pago. Vea "
"el interés total, el cronograma de pago y cómo los pagos adicionales pueden "
"ahorrarle dinero."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"student loan calculator, loan repayment, student debt, loan payoff, "
"education loan calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de préstamos estudiantiles, pago de préstamos, deuda "
"estudiantil, liquidación de préstamos, calculadora de préstamos educativos"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:9
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:17
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:32
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:49
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:55
#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:33
msgid "Student Loan Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de préstamos estudiantiles"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"Calculate student loan payments and compare different repayment strategies."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos de préstamos estudiantiles y compare diferentes "
"estrategias de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:18
msgid "Calculate student loan payments and compare repayment plans."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los pagos de préstamos estudiantiles y compare planes de pago."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:56
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly student loan payment, compare repayment plans, and "
"see how extra payments can help you become debt-free faster."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el pago mensual de su préstamo estudiantil, compare planes de pago y"
" vea cómo los pagos adicionales pueden ayudarlo a liberarse de sus deudas "
"más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:72
msgid "Total Loan Amount"
msgstr "Monto total del préstamo"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:90
#, python-format
msgid "Federal loans: 5-7%%, Private: varies"
msgstr "Préstamos federales: 5-7%%, Privados: varía"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:95
msgid "Repayment Term"
msgstr "Plazo de amortización"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:102
msgid "Extended"
msgstr "Extendido"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:117
msgid "See how extra payments save you money"
msgstr "Vea cómo los pagos adicionales le ahorran dinero"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:164
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Ahorrar"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:165
msgid "years earlier!"
msgstr "años antes!"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:189
msgid "Compare Repayment Plans"
msgstr "Comparar planes de pago"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:194
msgid "Plan"
msgstr "Plan"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:259
msgid "Plan Your Student Loan Payoff"
msgstr "Planifique el pago de su préstamo estudiantil"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:260
msgid ""
"Enter your loan details to see payment options and how to pay off your loans"
" faster."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los detalles de su préstamo para ver las opciones de pago y cómo "
"liquidar sus préstamos más rápido."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Input your total loan balance and interest rate from your loan servicer."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el saldo total de su préstamo y la tasa de interés de su "
"administrador de préstamos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:280
msgid "Choose Term"
msgstr "Elige Término"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Select your repayment term - shorter terms mean higher payments but less "
"interest."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione su plazo de pago: plazos más cortos significan pagos más altos "
"pero menos intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:287
msgid "Compare Plans"
msgstr "Comparar planes"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:288
msgid ""
"See how different plans and extra payments affect your payoff timeline."
msgstr ""
"Vea cómo los diferentes planes y pagos adicionales afectan su cronograma de "
"liquidación."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:300
msgid "What repayment plan should I choose?"
msgstr "¿Qué plan de pago debo elegir?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"Standard 10-year is best if you can afford it - you'll pay the least "
"interest. If payments are too high, consider income-driven plans or extended"
" repayment. Always pay as much as you can afford."
msgstr ""
"El plazo estándar de 10 años es mejor si puede permitírselo: pagará el menor"
" interés. Si los pagos son demasiado altos, considere planes basados ​​en "
"los ingresos o pagos extendidos. Pague siempre tanto como pueda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance faster. This "
"means less interest over time and earlier payoff. Even $50/month extra can "
"save thousands and years on your loan."
msgstr ""
"Los pagos adicionales van directamente al capital, lo que reduce el saldo "
"más rápidamente. Esto significa menos intereses a lo largo del tiempo y un "
"pago más temprano. Incluso $50 adicionales al mes pueden ahorrarle miles y "
"años en su préstamo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:324
msgid "What about loan forgiveness?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con la condonación de préstamos?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"Public Service Loan Forgiveness (PSLF) forgives remaining balance after 120 "
"qualifying payments while working for government/nonprofit. Income-driven "
"plans forgive after 20-25 years. Forgiven amounts may be taxable."
msgstr ""
"La condonación de préstamos por servicio público (PSLF) condona el saldo "
"restante después de 120 pagos calificados mientras trabaja para el gobierno "
"o una organización sin fines de lucro. Los planes basados ​​en los ingresos "
"se perdonan después de 20 a 25 años. Los montos condonados pueden estar "
"sujetos a impuestos."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:336
msgid "Should I refinance my student loans?"
msgstr "¿Debo refinanciar mis préstamos estudiantiles?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Refinancing can lower your rate if you have good credit and stable income. "
"However, refinancing federal loans means losing benefits like income-driven "
"plans and forgiveness options. Only refinance if you don't need these "
"protections."
msgstr ""
"La refinanciación puede reducir su tasa si tiene buen crédito e ingresos "
"estables. Sin embargo, refinanciar préstamos federales significa perder "
"beneficios como planes basados ​​en ingresos y opciones de condonación. "
"Refinancia solo si no necesitas estas protecciones."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:350
msgid "Student Loan Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para préstamos estudiantiles"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:356
#, python-format
msgid "Set up autopay - most servicers offer a 0.25%% rate reduction."
msgstr ""
"Configure el pago automático: la mayoría de los administradores ofrecen una "
"reducción de tarifa del 0,25%."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Pay highest interest loans first (avalanche method) to minimize interest."
msgstr ""
"Pague primero los préstamos con el interés más alto (método de avalancha) "
"para minimizar los intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Make payments during grace period to reduce principal before interest "
"accrues."
msgstr ""
"Realice pagos durante el período de gracia para reducir el capital antes de "
"que se acumulen intereses."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Check for employer student loan assistance - it's an increasingly common "
"benefit."
msgstr ""
"Consulte la asistencia del empleador para préstamos estudiantiles: es un "
"beneficio cada vez más común."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:5
msgid "Take Home Paycheck Calculator - Calculate Net Pay"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de cheques de pago para llevar a casa: calcular el pago neto"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your take-home pay after federal taxes, state taxes, Social "
"Security, Medicare, and deductions. See your net paycheck breakdown."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su salario neto después de impuestos federales, impuestos estatales,"
" Seguro Social, Medicare y deducciones. Vea el desglose de su cheque de pago"
" neto."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/take_home_paycheck_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"paycheck calculator, take home pay, net pay calculator, salary calculator, "
"tax withholding, FICA taxes"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de sueldo, salario neto, calculadora de salario neto, "
"calculadora de salario, retención de impuestos, impuestos FICA"

