#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:200
msgid "What is VAT?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el IVA?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:201
msgid ""
"VAT (Value Added Tax) is a consumption tax placed on products whenever value"
" is added at each stage of production or distribution. It's used in over 160"
" countries worldwide."
msgstr ""
"El IVA (Impuesto al Valor Agregado) es un impuesto al consumo que se aplica "
"a los productos siempre que se agrega valor en cada etapa de producción o "
"distribución. Se utiliza en más de 160 países en todo el mundo."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:202
msgid ""
"GST (Goods and Services Tax) is similar to VAT and is used in countries like"
" Australia, Canada, and India."
msgstr ""
"El GST (impuesto sobre bienes y servicios) es similar al IVA y se utiliza en"
" países como Australia, Canadá e India."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:205
msgid "VAT Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de IVA"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:207
msgid "Add VAT:"
msgstr "Añadir IVA:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:208
msgid "Remove VAT:"
msgstr "Eliminar IVA:"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/vat_calculator.html:209
msgid "VAT Amount:"
msgstr "Monto del IVA:"

