"con la anorexia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:64
msgid "Important:"
msgstr "Importante:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:64
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational purposes only and is not a diagnostic "
"tool. Always seek help from qualified healthcare professionals if you are "
"concerned about an eating disorder."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines educativos únicamente y no es una herramienta "
"de diagnóstico. Busque siempre la ayuda de profesionales sanitarios "
"cualificados si le preocupa un trastorno alimentario."

