#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:20
msgid "Body Type Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de tipo de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:14
msgid "Ectomorph, Mesomorph, Endomorph"
msgstr "Ectomorfo, Mesomorfo, Endomorfo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Determine your body type (ectomorph, mesomorph, or endomorph) based on frame"
" size measurements."
msgstr ""
"Determine su tipo de cuerpo (ectomorfo, mesomorfo o endomorfo) según las "
"medidas del tamaño del marco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:10
msgid "body type calculator, ectomorph, mesomorph, endomorph, body frame size"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de tipo de cuerpo, ectomorfo, mesomorfo, endomorfo, tamaño de "
"estructura corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:15
msgid "Determine your body type based on frame size measurements."
msgstr ""
"Determine su tipo de cuerpo basándose en las medidas del tamaño del marco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:96
msgid "Wrist"
msgstr "Muñeca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:102
msgid "Measure around the wrist at the narrowest point"
msgstr "Mida alrededor de la muñeca en el punto más estrecho."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:107
msgid "Ankle"
msgstr "Tobillo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:113
msgid "Measure around the ankle at the narrowest point"
msgstr "Mida alrededor del tobillo en el punto más estrecho."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:132
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:586
msgid "Calculate Body Type"
msgstr "Calcular el tipo de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:162
msgid ""
"Enter your wrist, ankle, and height measurements to determine your body type"
" with detailed analysis and charts."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese las medidas de su muñeca, tobillo y altura para determinar su tipo "
"de cuerpo con análisis y gráficos detallados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:172
msgid "Your Body Type"
msgstr "Tu tipo de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:184
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:230
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:404
msgid "Frame Size"
msgstr "Tamaño del marco"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:190
msgid "Wrist Ratio"
msgstr "Relación de muñeca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:196
msgid "Ankle Ratio"
msgstr "Relación de tobillo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:202
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:217
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:398
msgid "Body Type"
msgstr "Tipo de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:244
msgid "Measurement Ratios"
msgstr "Relaciones de medición"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:253
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:422
msgid "Characteristics"
msgstr "Características"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:272
msgid "What are Body Types?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los tipos de cuerpo?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Body types, also known as somatotypes, are classifications of human body "
"shapes based on skeletal frame size and body composition. The three main "
"body types are ectomorph, mesomorph, and endomorph, originally proposed by "
"psychologist William Sheldon in the 1940s."
msgstr ""
"Los tipos de cuerpo, también conocidos como somatotipos, son clasificaciones"
" de las formas del cuerpo humano basadas en el tamaño de la estructura "
"esquelética y la composición corporal. Los tres tipos de cuerpo principales "
"son ectomorfo, mesomorfo y endomorfo, propuestos originalmente por el "
"psicólogo William Sheldon en la década de 1940."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:277
msgid ""
"While everyone is unique, understanding your body type can help you make "
"informed decisions about nutrition, exercise, and fitness goals that work "
"best with your natural body structure."
msgstr ""
"Si bien cada persona es única, comprender su tipo de cuerpo puede ayudarlo a"
" tomar decisiones informadas sobre nutrición, ejercicio y objetivos de "
"acondicionamiento físico que funcionen mejor con su estructura corporal "
"natural."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:283
msgid "The Three Body Types"
msgstr "Los tres tipos de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:286
msgid "Ectomorph"
msgstr "ectomorfo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:288
msgid "Small frame, naturally lean, fast metabolism"
msgstr "Estructura pequeña, metabolismo naturalmente delgado y rápido."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:291
msgid "Naturally thin and lean build"
msgstr "Estructura naturalmente delgada y delgada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:292
msgid "Fast metabolism"
msgstr "Metabolismo rápido"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:293
msgid "Difficulty gaining weight"
msgstr "Dificultad para ganar peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:294
msgid "Narrow shoulders and hips"
msgstr "Hombros y caderas estrechas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:295
msgid "Long limbs"
msgstr "Extremidades largas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:296
msgid "Low body fat percentage"
msgstr "Bajo porcentaje de grasa corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:300
msgid "Mesomorph"
msgstr "Mesomorfo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:302
msgid "Medium frame, athletic build, moderate metabolism"
msgstr "Estructura media, constitución atlética, metabolismo moderado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:305
msgid "Athletic and muscular build"
msgstr "Estructura atlética y musculosa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:306
msgid "Moderate metabolism"
msgstr "Metabolismo moderado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:307
msgid "Gains muscle easily"
msgstr "Gana músculo fácilmente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:308
msgid "Broad shoulders"
msgstr "hombros anchos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:309
msgid "Narrow waist"
msgstr "cintura estrecha"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:310
msgid "Naturally strong"
msgstr "Naturalmente fuerte"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:314
msgid "Endomorph"
msgstr "endomorfo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:316
msgid "Large frame, wider build, slower metabolism"
msgstr "Estructura grande, complexión más ancha, metabolismo más lento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:319
msgid "Naturally wider frame"
msgstr "Marco naturalmente más ancho"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:320
msgid "Slower metabolism"
msgstr "Metabolismo más lento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:321
msgid "Stores fat easily"
msgstr "Almacena grasa fácilmente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:322
msgid "Wider hips and shoulders"
msgstr "Caderas y hombros más anchos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:323
msgid "Gains muscle and fat easily"
msgstr "Gana músculo y grasa fácilmente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:324
msgid "Rounder body shape"
msgstr "Forma de cuerpo más redonda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:332
msgid "How Frame Size is Calculated"
msgstr "Cómo se calcula el tamaño del marco"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"This calculator uses the wrist-to-height ratio method to determine frame "
"size:"
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora utiliza el método de relación muñeca-altura para determinar"
" el tamaño del marco:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:337
msgid "Wrist-to-Height Ratio = (Wrist Circumference / Height) × 100"
msgstr "Relación muñeca-altura = (circunferencia de la muñeca / altura) × 100"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:340
msgid "Small Frame:"
msgstr "Marco pequeño:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:340
#, python-format
msgid "Wrist-to-height ratio < 9.9%%"
msgstr "Relación muñeca-altura < 9,9%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:341
msgid "Medium Frame:"
msgstr "Marco medio:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:341
#, python-format
msgid "Wrist-to-height ratio 9.9%% - 10.9%%"
msgstr "Relación muñeca-altura 9,9%% - 10,9%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:342
msgid "Large Frame:"
msgstr "Marco grande:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:342
#, python-format
msgid "Wrist-to-height ratio > 10.9%%"
msgstr "Relación muñeca-altura > 10,9%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Frame size is then used to determine body type: Small = Ectomorph, Medium = "
"Mesomorph, Large = Endomorph."
msgstr ""
"Luego, el tamaño de la estructura se utiliza para determinar el tipo de "
"cuerpo: Pequeño = Ectomorfo, Mediano = Mesomorfo, Grande = Endomorfo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:354
msgid "Measure your wrist circumference at the narrowest point"
msgstr "Mide la circunferencia de tu muñeca en el punto más estrecho."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:355
msgid "Measure your ankle circumference at the narrowest point"
msgstr "Mide la circunferencia de tu tobillo en el punto más estrecho."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:357
msgid "Click 'Calculate Body Type' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular tipo de cuerpo' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:358
msgid "Review your body type, frame size, and characteristics"
msgstr "Revise su tipo de cuerpo, tamaño de estructura y características."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:359
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your body type classification"
msgstr ""
"Utilice los gráficos para visualizar la clasificación de su tipo de cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:368
msgid "Wrist Measurement"
msgstr "Medición de muñeca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:370
msgid ""
"Measure around your wrist at the narrowest point, just above the wrist bone."
" Keep the tape measure snug but not tight. This measurement is used to "
"determine frame size."
msgstr ""
"Mide alrededor de tu muñeca en el punto más estrecho, justo encima del hueso"
" de la muñeca. Mantenga la cinta métrica ajustada pero no apretada. Esta "
"medida se utiliza para determinar el tamaño del marco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:374
msgid "Ankle Measurement"
msgstr "Medición del tobillo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Measure around your ankle at the narrowest point, just above the ankle bone."
" Keep the tape measure level and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Mide alrededor de tu tobillo en el punto más estrecho, justo por encima del "
"hueso del tobillo. Mantenga la cinta métrica nivelada y ajustada, pero no "
"apretada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:380
msgid "Height Measurement"
msgstr "Medición de altura"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Stand straight against a wall without shoes. Measure from the floor to the "
"top of your head. For best accuracy, measure in the morning when you're at "
"your tallest."
msgstr ""
"Párese derecho contra una pared sin zapatos. Mide desde el suelo hasta la "
"parte superior de tu cabeza. Para obtener la mayor precisión, mida por la "
"mañana, cuando esté en su punto más alto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Your primary body type classification (Ectomorph, Mesomorph, or Endomorph). "
"This is determined based on your frame size."
msgstr ""
"Su clasificación principal de tipo de cuerpo (ectomorfo, mesomorfo o "
"endomorfo). Esto se determina en función del tamaño de su cuadro."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"Your skeletal frame size (Small, Medium, or Large) based on your wrist-to-"
"height ratio. This is a key indicator of your body type."
msgstr ""
"El tamaño de su estructura esquelética (pequeña, mediana o grande) según la "
"relación muñeca-altura. Este es un indicador clave de tu tipo de cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:410
msgid "Wrist-to-Height Ratio"
msgstr "Relación muñeca-altura"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"The percentage ratio of your wrist circumference to your height. This ratio "
"is used to determine frame size."
msgstr ""
"La relación porcentual entre la circunferencia de tu muñeca y tu altura. "
"Esta relación se utiliza para determinar el tamaño del marco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:416
msgid "Ankle-to-Height Ratio"
msgstr "Relación tobillo-altura"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:418
msgid ""
"The percentage ratio of your ankle circumference to your height. This "
"provides additional insight into your body proportions."
msgstr ""
"La relación porcentual entre la circunferencia de su tobillo y su altura. "
"Esto proporciona información adicional sobre las proporciones de su cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:424
msgid ""
"A list of typical characteristics associated with your body type. These are "
"general tendencies and may vary from person to person."
msgstr ""
"Una lista de características típicas asociadas con tu tipo de cuerpo. Estas "
"son tendencias generales y pueden variar de persona a persona."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:432
msgid "Fitness Tips by Body Type"
msgstr "Consejos de acondicionamiento físico por tipo de cuerpo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:435
msgid "Ectomorph Tips"
msgstr "Consejos de ectomorfos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:437
msgid "Focus on strength training to build muscle mass"
msgstr ""
"Centrarse en el entrenamiento de fuerza para desarrollar masa muscular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:438
msgid "Eat calorie-dense foods and frequent meals"
msgstr "Consuma alimentos ricos en calorías y comidas frecuentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:439
msgid "Limit excessive cardio"
msgstr "Limitar el cardio excesivo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:440
msgid "Prioritize protein intake"
msgstr "Priorizar la ingesta de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:444
msgid "Mesomorph Tips"
msgstr "Consejos mesomorfos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:446
msgid "Balance strength training and cardio"
msgstr "Equilibra el entrenamiento de fuerza y ​​el cardio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:447
msgid "Maintain moderate calorie intake"
msgstr "Mantener una ingesta moderada de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:448
msgid "Focus on progressive overload"
msgstr "Centrarse en la sobrecarga progresiva"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:449
msgid "Enjoy natural athletic advantages"
msgstr "Disfrute de ventajas atléticas naturales"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:453
msgid "Endomorph Tips"
msgstr "Consejos endomorfos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:455
msgid "Focus on regular cardio exercise"
msgstr "Concéntrese en el ejercicio cardiovascular regular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:456
msgid "Monitor calorie intake carefully"
msgstr "Controle cuidadosamente la ingesta de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:457
msgid "Combine strength training with cardio"
msgstr "Combina el entrenamiento de fuerza con el cardio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:458
msgid "Pay attention to portion sizes"
msgstr "Presta atención al tamaño de las porciones"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"Body types are generalizations. Most people are a combination of types "
"rather than purely one type."
msgstr ""
"Los tipos de cuerpo son generalizaciones. La mayoría de las personas son una"
" combinación de tipos en lugar de un solo tipo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:478
msgid ""
"Your body type doesn't determine your fitness potential. With proper "
"nutrition and exercise, anyone can achieve their fitness goals regardless of"
" body type."
msgstr ""
"Tu tipo de cuerpo no determina tu potencial físico. Con una nutrición y "
"ejercicio adecuados, cualquiera puede alcanzar sus objetivos de fitness "
"independientemente del tipo de cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"Body type classifications are based on frame size measurements and are "
"estimates. Individual variations exist."
msgstr ""
"Las clasificaciones de tipos de cuerpo se basan en medidas de tamaño de "
"estructura y son estimaciones. Existen variaciones individuales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:490
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Consult "
"with fitness professionals for personalized advice."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines educativos e informativos únicamente. Consulta "
"con profesionales del fitness para obtener asesoramiento personalizado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:745
msgid "Your Type"
msgstr "tu tipo"

