#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:729
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:791
msgid "Gain Fast"
