#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:267
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:271
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:275
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:279
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:283
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:287
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:674
msgid "min"
msgstr "mín."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:306
msgid "What are MET Values?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los valores MET?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:308
msgid ""
"MET (Metabolic Equivalent of Task) is a unit used to estimate the energy "
"cost of physical activities. One MET is defined as the energy cost of "
"sitting quietly, which is approximately 1 calorie per kilogram of body "
"weight per hour."
msgstr ""
"MET (Equivalente Metabólico de Tarea) es una unidad utilizada para estimar "
"el costo energético de las actividades físicas. Un MET se define como el "
"coste energético de estar sentado tranquilamente, que es aproximadamente 1 "
"caloría por kilogramo de peso corporal por hora."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:311
msgid ""
"MET values allow you to compare the intensity of different activities. For "
"example, an activity with a MET value of 4 means you're burning 4 times the "
"energy you would burn while sitting quietly."
msgstr ""
"Los valores MET le permiten comparar la intensidad de diferentes "
"actividades. Por ejemplo, una actividad con un valor MET de 4 significa que "
"estás quemando 4 veces más energía que si estuvieras sentado tranquilamente."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:317
msgid "How Calories are Calculated"
msgstr "Cómo se calculan las calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:319
msgid "The formula used to calculate calories burned is:"
msgstr "La fórmula utilizada para calcular las calorías quemadas es:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:322
msgid "Calories Burned = MET × Weight (kg) × Time (hours)"
msgstr "Calorías quemadas = MET × Peso (kg) × Tiempo (horas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"This formula takes into account your body weight, the intensity of the "
"activity (MET value), and the duration of the exercise."
msgstr ""
"Esta fórmula tiene en cuenta su peso corporal, la intensidad de la actividad"
" (valor MET) y la duración del ejercicio."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:331
msgid "Activity Types and Intensities"
msgstr "Tipos e intensidades de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:336
msgid "MET values: Slow (2.0), Moderate (3.5), Fast (4.5), Very Fast (5.0)"
msgstr ""
"Valores MET: Lento (2,0), Moderado (3,5), Rápido (4,5), Muy Rápido (5,0)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:338
msgid "Great for beginners and low-impact exercise."
msgstr "Ideal para principiantes y ejercicios de bajo impacto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"MET values: Jogging (7.0), Moderate (8.3), Fast (9.8), Very Fast (11.0)"
msgstr ""
"Valores MET: Trotar (7,0), Moderado (8,3), Rápido (9,8), Muy rápido (11,0)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:345
msgid "High-intensity cardiovascular exercise."
msgstr "Ejercicio cardiovascular de alta intensidad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"MET values: Leisure (4.0), Moderate (6.0), Vigorous (8.0), Racing (10.0)"
msgstr ""
"Valores MET: Ocio (4,0), Moderado (6,0), Vigoroso (8,0), Carrera (10,0)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:352
msgid "Low-impact exercise suitable for all fitness levels."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio de bajo impacto apto para todos los niveles de condición física."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"MET values: Leisure (6.0), Moderate (8.0), Vigorous (10.0), Butterfly (13.8)"
msgstr ""
"Valores MET: Ocio (6,0), Moderado (8,0), Vigoroso (10,0), Mariposa (13,8)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:359
msgid "Full-body workout with minimal joint impact."
msgstr ""
"Entrenamiento de cuerpo completo con mínimo impacto en las articulaciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:362
msgid "Other Activities"
msgstr "Otras actividades"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"Weightlifting, Yoga, Dancing, Basketball, Tennis, Soccer - each with varying"
" intensity levels."
msgstr ""
"Levantamiento de pesas, yoga, baile, baloncesto, tenis, fútbol, ​​cada uno "
"con diferentes niveles de intensidad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:366
msgid "Intensity options vary by activity type."
msgstr "Las opciones de intensidad varían según el tipo de actividad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:377
msgid "Select the activity type you performed"
msgstr "Seleccione el tipo de actividad que realizó"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:378
msgid "Choose the intensity level that best matches your effort"
msgstr "Elige el nivel de intensidad que mejor se adapta a tu esfuerzo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:379
msgid "Enter the duration of your activity in minutes"
msgstr "Introduce la duración de tu actividad en minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:380
msgid "Click 'Calculate Calories Burned' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular calorías quemadas' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:381
msgid ""
"Review the charts to compare different durations, intensities, and "
"activities"
msgstr ""
"Revise los gráficos para comparar diferentes duraciones, intensidades y "
"actividades."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"The total number of calories you burned during your activity session. This "
"is calculated based on your weight, the activity's MET value, and duration."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad total de calorías que quemaste durante tu sesión de actividad. "
"Esto se calcula en función de su peso, el valor MET de la actividad y la "
"duración."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:396
msgid "Calories per Minute"
msgstr "Calorías por minuto"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"The average number of calories burned per minute during your activity. This "
"helps you understand the intensity of your workout."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad promedio de calorías quemadas por minuto durante su actividad. "
"Esto le ayuda a comprender la intensidad de su entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"The Metabolic Equivalent of Task value for your selected activity and "
"intensity. Higher MET values indicate more intense activities."
msgstr ""
"El equivalente metabólico del valor de la tarea para la actividad e "
"intensidad seleccionadas. Los valores de MET más altos indican actividades "
"más intensas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"Shows how many calories you would burn for the same activity at different "
"durations (15, 30, 45, 60, 90, 120 minutes)."
msgstr ""
"Muestra cuántas calorías quemarías con la misma actividad en diferentes "
"duraciones (15, 30, 45, 60, 90, 120 minutos)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Compares calories burned for different intensity levels of the same "
"activity. This helps you see how intensity affects calorie burn."
msgstr ""
"Compara las calorías quemadas para diferentes niveles de intensidad de la "
"misma actividad. Esto le ayuda a ver cómo la intensidad afecta la quema de "
"calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Compares calories burned across different activities for the same duration "
"and weight. This helps you choose activities that match your calorie-burning"
" goals."
msgstr ""
"Compara las calorías quemadas en diferentes actividades durante la misma "
"duración y peso. Esto le ayudará a elegir actividades que coincidan con sus "
"objetivos de quema de calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:430
msgid "Factors Affecting Calories Burned"
msgstr "Factores que afectan las calorías quemadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:432
msgid "Body Weight:"
msgstr "Peso corporal:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Heavier individuals burn more calories doing the same activity because they "
"require more energy to move their body."
msgstr ""
"Las personas más pesadas queman más calorías haciendo la misma actividad "
"porque necesitan más energía para mover su cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:433
msgid "Activity Intensity:"
msgstr "Intensidad de actividad:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:433
msgid ""
"Higher intensity activities have higher MET values and burn more calories "
"per minute."
msgstr ""
"Las actividades de mayor intensidad tienen valores MET más altos y queman "
"más calorías por minuto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:434
msgid "Duration:"
msgstr "Duración:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Longer exercise sessions burn more total calories, though the rate per "
"minute remains constant for the same intensity."
msgstr ""
"Las sesiones de ejercicio más largas queman más calorías totales, aunque la "
"velocidad por minuto permanece constante para la misma intensidad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:435
msgid "Fitness Level:"
msgstr "Nivel de condición física:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:435
msgid ""
"More fit individuals may burn slightly fewer calories at the same intensity "
"because their bodies are more efficient. However, they can exercise at "
"higher intensities."
msgstr ""
"Las personas más en forma pueden quemar un poco menos de calorías con la "
"misma intensidad porque sus cuerpos son más eficientes. Sin embargo, pueden "
"hacer ejercicio a intensidades más altas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:436
msgid "Age and Gender:"
msgstr "Edad y género:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Metabolism varies with age and gender, though MET values provide a "
"standardized way to estimate calorie burn."
msgstr ""
"El metabolismo varía según la edad y el sexo, aunque los valores MET "
"proporcionan una forma estandarizada de estimar la quema de calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:442
msgid "Tips for Maximizing Calorie Burn"
msgstr "Consejos para maximizar la quema de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:444
msgid "Increase Intensity:"
msgstr "Aumentar la intensidad:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:444
msgid ""
"Choose higher intensity levels when possible. Even small increases in "
"intensity can significantly boost calorie burn."
msgstr ""
"Elija niveles de intensidad más altos cuando sea posible. Incluso pequeños "
"aumentos de intensidad pueden aumentar significativamente la quema de "
"calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:445
msgid "Extend Duration:"
msgstr "Ampliar duración:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Longer workouts burn more total calories. Aim for at least 30 minutes of "
"moderate activity most days."
msgstr ""
"Los entrenamientos más largos queman más calorías totales. Intente realizar "
"al menos 30 minutos de actividad moderada la mayoría de los días."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:446
msgid "Mix Activities:"
msgstr "Actividades mixtas:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Combine different types of activities to work different muscle groups and "
"prevent boredom."
msgstr ""
"Combina diferentes tipos de actividades para trabajar diferentes grupos "
"musculares y evitar el aburrimiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:447
msgid "Progressive Overload:"
msgstr "Sobrecarga progresiva:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:447
msgid ""
"Gradually increase intensity or duration over time to continue challenging "
"your body."
msgstr ""
"Aumente gradualmente la intensidad o la duración con el tiempo para seguir "
"desafiando a su cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:448
msgid "Stay Consistent:"
msgstr "Manténgase consistente:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:448
msgid ""
"Regular exercise is more important than occasional intense sessions for "
"long-term calorie burn and health benefits."
msgstr ""
"El ejercicio regular es más importante que las sesiones intensas ocasionales"
" para quemar calorías a largo plazo y obtener beneficios para la salud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:460
msgid ""
"Calorie burn estimates are based on average MET values and may vary based on"
" individual factors like fitness level, body composition, and exercise "
"efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Las estimaciones de quema de calorías se basan en valores MET promedio y "
"pueden variar según factores individuales como el nivel de condición física,"
" la composición corporal y la eficiencia del ejercicio."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:466
#, python-format
msgid ""
"MET values are standardized estimates. Actual calorie burn may vary by "
"10-20%% depending on individual factors."
msgstr ""
"Los valores MET son estimaciones estandarizadas. La quema real de calorías "
"puede variar entre un 10 y un 20% dependiendo de factores individuales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"This calculator provides estimates for the calories burned during exercise "
"only. It does not account for calories burned through daily activities or "
"the afterburn effect (EPOC)."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora proporciona estimaciones de las calorías quemadas "
"únicamente durante el ejercicio. No tiene en cuenta las calorías quemadas "
"mediante las actividades diarias ni el efecto postcombustión (EPOC)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:478
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Consult "
"with fitness professionals for personalized exercise and nutrition advice."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines educativos e informativos únicamente. Consulte "
"con profesionales del fitness para obtener asesoramiento personalizado sobre"
" ejercicio y nutrición."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:515
msgid "Jogging"
msgstr "Correr"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:516
