msgid "Low Carb"
msgstr "Bajo en carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:210
msgid "High Carb"
msgstr "Alto en carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:226
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:244
msgid "Macro Distribution"
msgstr "Distribución de macros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:253
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:285
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:278
msgid "Recommendations Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de recomendaciones"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:289
msgid "Carbohydrate Sources Guide"
msgstr "Guía de fuentes de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:296
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:328
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:332
msgid "Serving"
msgstr "Servicio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:297
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:329
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:333
msgid "Servings Needed"
msgstr "Porciones necesarias"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:320
msgid "What are Carbohydrates?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los carbohidratos?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates are one of the three main macronutrients (along with protein "
"and fat) that provide energy to your body. They are broken down into "
"glucose, which is the primary fuel source for your brain and muscles."
msgstr ""
"Los carbohidratos son uno de los tres macronutrientes principales (junto con"
" las proteínas y las grasas) que proporcionan energía al cuerpo. Se "
"descomponen en glucosa, que es la principal fuente de combustible para el "
"cerebro y los músculos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram and are found in foods like "
"grains, fruits, vegetables, legumes, and dairy products. They play a crucial"
" role in maintaining energy levels, supporting physical performance, and "
"fueling brain function."
msgstr ""
"Los carbohidratos aportan 4 calorías por gramo y se encuentran en alimentos "
"como cereales, frutas, verduras, legumbres y productos lácteos. Desempeñan "
"un papel crucial en el mantenimiento de los niveles de energía, el apoyo al "
"rendimiento físico y el impulso de la función cerebral."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:331
msgid "Types of Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Tipos de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:334
msgid "Simple Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Carbohidratos simples"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Quick-digesting carbs found in fruits, milk, and processed foods. Provide "
"rapid energy but can cause blood sugar spikes."
msgstr ""
"Carbohidratos de rápida digestión que se encuentran en frutas, leche y "
"alimentos procesados. Proporcionan energía rápidamente pero pueden provocar "
"picos de azúcar en la sangre."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:338
msgid "Examples: Sugar, honey, fruit juice, white bread"
msgstr "Ejemplos: azúcar, miel, zumo de frutas, pan blanco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:341
msgid "Complex Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Carbohidratos complejos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Slow-digesting carbs found in whole grains, vegetables, and legumes. Provide"
" sustained energy and are rich in fiber."
msgstr ""
"Carbohidratos de digestión lenta que se encuentran en cereales integrales, "
"verduras y legumbres. Aportan energía sostenida y son ricos en fibra."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:345
msgid "Examples: Oats, brown rice, quinoa, sweet potatoes, beans"
msgstr "Ejemplos: avena, arroz integral, quinua, batatas, frijoles"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:348
msgid "Fiber"
msgstr "Fibra"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"A type of carbohydrate that cannot be digested. Important for digestive "
"health, blood sugar control, and satiety."
msgstr ""
"Un tipo de carbohidrato que no se puede digerir. Importante para la salud "
"digestiva, el control del azúcar en sangre y la saciedad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:352
msgid "Examples: Whole grains, vegetables, fruits, legumes"
msgstr "Ejemplos: cereales integrales, verduras, frutas, legumbres."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:361
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:393
msgid "Enter your total daily calorie intake"
msgstr "Ingrese su ingesta total diaria de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:394
msgid "Choose calculation method: By Percentage or From Remaining Macros"
msgstr "Elija el método de cálculo: Por porcentaje o de macros restantes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"If using percentage method, enter your desired carbohydrate percentage (or "
"use the slider)"
msgstr ""
"Si usa el método de porcentaje, ingrese el porcentaje de carbohidratos que "
"desee (o use el control deslizante)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"If using remaining macros method, enter your protein and fat percentages"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método de macros restantes, ingrese sus porcentajes de "
"proteína y grasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:365
msgid "Click 'Calculate Carbs' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular carbohidratos' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"Review your daily carbohydrate needs, meal distribution, and food sources"
msgstr ""
"Revise sus necesidades diarias de carbohidratos, distribución de comidas y "
"fuentes de alimentos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:367
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your carbohydrate distribution"
msgstr "Utilice los gráficos para visualizar su distribución de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:378
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The total amount of carbohydrates (in grams) you should consume daily based "
"on your calorie intake and selected percentage. This is calculated as: "
"(Total Calories × Carb %%) ÷ 4 calories per gram."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad total de carbohidratos (en gramos) que debes consumir "
"diariamente según tu ingesta de calorías y el porcentaje seleccionado. Esto "
"se calcula como: (Calorías totales × % de carbohidratos%) ÷ 4 calorías por "
"gramo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:382
msgid "Calories from Carbs"
msgstr "Calorías de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:384
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The number of calories that come from carbohydrates. This is calculated as: "
"Total Calories × (Carb %% ÷ 100)."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad de calorías que provienen de los carbohidratos. Esto se calcula "
"como: Calorías totales × (%% de carbohidratos ÷ 100)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:390
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested carbohydrate distribution across meals: Breakfast (25%%), Lunch "
"(35%%), Dinner (30%%), and Snacks (10%%). This helps maintain steady energy "
"levels throughout the day."
msgstr ""
"Distribución sugerida de carbohidratos en las comidas: Desayuno (25%%), "
"Almuerzo (35%%), Cena (30%%) y Meriendas (10%%). Esto ayuda a mantener "
"niveles de energía estables durante todo el día."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:396
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Comparison of low carb (10%%), moderate (40%%), and high carb (60%%) "
"approaches. Choose based on your goals, activity level, and personal "
"preferences."
msgstr ""
"Comparación de enfoques bajos en carbohidratos (10%), moderados (40%) y "
"altos en carbohidratos (60%). Elija según sus objetivos, nivel de actividad "
"y preferencias personales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:400
msgid "Carbohydrate Sources"
msgstr "Fuentes de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:402
msgid ""
"A guide showing common carbohydrate sources and how many servings you would "
"need to meet your daily carbohydrate target."
msgstr ""
"Una guía que muestra las fuentes comunes de carbohidratos y cuántas "
"porciones necesitarías para alcanzar tu objetivo diario de carbohidratos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:410
msgid "Carbohydrate Intake Guidelines"
msgstr "Pautas de ingesta de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:412
#, python-format
msgid "Low Carb (10-20%%):"
msgstr "Bajo en carbohidratos (10-20%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"Typically 50-150g per day. Suitable for weight loss, ketogenic diets, or "
"managing blood sugar. May require adaptation period."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente 50-150 g por día. Adecuado para perder peso, dietas cetogénicas "
"o controlar el azúcar en sangre. Puede requerir un período de adaptación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:413
#, python-format
msgid "Moderate Carb (40-50%%):"
msgstr "Carbohidratos moderados (40-50%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Typically 200-300g per day. Balanced approach suitable for most people. "
"Recommended for general health and moderate activity levels."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente 200-300 g por día. Enfoque equilibrado adecuado para la mayoría "
"de las personas. Recomendado para salud general y niveles de actividad "
"moderados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:414
#, python-format
msgid "High Carb (60%%+):"
msgstr "Alto en carbohidratos (60%%+):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:414
msgid ""
"Typically 300g+ per day. Suitable for athletes, very active individuals, or "
"those with high calorie needs. Supports intense training and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente, más de 300 g por día. Adecuado para deportistas, personas muy "
"activas o con necesidades calóricas elevadas. Apoya el entrenamiento intenso"
" y la recuperación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:420
msgid "Best Carbohydrate Sources"
msgstr "Las mejores fuentes de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:422
msgid "Whole Grains:"
msgstr "Cereales Integrales:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Oats, brown rice, quinoa, whole wheat bread, barley. Rich in fiber and "
"nutrients."
msgstr ""
"Avena, arroz integral, quinoa, pan integral, cebada. Rica en fibra y "
"nutrientes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:423
msgid "Starchy Vegetables:"
msgstr "Verduras con almidón:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:423
msgid ""
"Sweet potatoes, potatoes, corn, peas. Provide energy and essential vitamins."
msgstr ""
"Batatas, patatas, maíz, guisantes. Aporta energía y vitaminas esenciales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:424
msgid "Legumes:"
msgstr "Legumbres:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:424
msgid "Beans, lentils, chickpeas. High in fiber and protein."
msgstr "Frijoles, lentejas, garbanzos. Alto en fibra y proteínas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:425
msgid "Fruits:"
msgstr "Frutas:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Berries, bananas, apples, oranges. Natural sugars with vitamins and fiber."
msgstr ""
"Bayas, plátanos, manzanas, naranjas. Azúcares naturales con vitaminas y "
"fibra."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:426
msgid "Dairy:"
msgstr "Lácteos:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Milk, yogurt. Contains lactose (natural sugar) plus protein and calcium."
msgstr ""
"Leche, yogur. Contiene lactosa (azúcar natural) además de proteínas y "
"calcio."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:432
msgid "Tips for Optimal Carbohydrate Intake"
msgstr "Consejos para una ingesta óptima de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:434
msgid "Choose Complex Carbs:"
msgstr "Elija carbohidratos complejos:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Prioritize whole grains, vegetables, and legumes over refined and processed "
"carbohydrates."
msgstr ""
"Priorice los cereales integrales, las verduras y las legumbres sobre los "
"carbohidratos refinados y procesados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:435
msgid "Time Your Carbs:"
msgstr "Mide tus carbohidratos:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:435
msgid ""
"Consume most carbs around workouts for optimal performance and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Consuma la mayoría de los carbohidratos durante los entrenamientos para "
"obtener un rendimiento y una recuperación óptimos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:436
msgid "Include Fiber:"
msgstr "Incluye fibra:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Aim for 25-35g of fiber daily from carbohydrate sources for digestive "
"health."
msgstr ""
"Apunte a consumir entre 25 y 35 g de fibra al día procedente de fuentes de "
"carbohidratos para la salud digestiva."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:437
msgid "Match Activity Level:"
msgstr "Nivel de actividad del partido:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Increase carbs on active days and reduce on rest days if weight loss is a "
"goal."
msgstr ""
"Aumente los carbohidratos en los días activos y redúzcalos en los días de "
"descanso si su objetivo es perder peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:438
msgid "Listen to Your Body:"
msgstr "Escuche a su cuerpo:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:438
msgid ""
"Adjust carb intake based on energy levels, performance, and how you feel."
msgstr ""
"Ajuste la ingesta de carbohidratos según los niveles de energía, el "
"rendimiento y cómo se siente."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:450
msgid ""
"Individual carbohydrate needs vary based on activity level, metabolism, body"
" composition goals, and personal preferences."
msgstr ""
"Las necesidades individuales de carbohidratos varían según el nivel de "
"actividad, el metabolismo, los objetivos de composición corporal y las "
"preferencias personales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:456
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:493
msgid ""
"The calculator provides estimates. Monitor your progress and adjust based on"
" your results, energy levels, and goals."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora proporciona estimaciones. Supervise su progreso y ajústelo en"
" función de sus resultados, niveles de energía y objetivos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:462
msgid ""
"Extreme low-carb diets may not be suitable for everyone. Consult with a "
"healthcare provider or registered dietitian before making significant "
"dietary changes."
msgstr ""
"Es posible que las dietas extremadamente bajas en carbohidratos no sean "
"adecuadas para todos. Consulte con un proveedor de atención médica o un "
"dietista registrado antes de realizar cambios dietéticos importantes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:621
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:640
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:641
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:642
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:643
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:661
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:682
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:683
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:684
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:685
msgid "kcal"
msgstr "calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:660
msgid "Rice"
msgstr "Arroz"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:661
msgid "Oats"
msgstr "Avena"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:662
msgid "Bread"
msgstr "Pan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:663
msgid "Pasta"
msgstr "Pastas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:664
msgid "Potato"
msgstr "Papa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:665
msgid "Banana"
msgstr "Banana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:666
msgid "Sweet Potato"
msgstr "Batata"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:667
msgid "Quinoa"
msgstr "Quinoa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:56
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:47
msgid "Conception Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:73
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Conception Date"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date based on due date or last menstrual period. "
"Free online conception date calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su fecha de concepción según la fecha prevista de parto o el último "
"período menstrual. Calculadora online gratuita de la fecha de concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"conception calculator, conception date, pregnancy calculator, ovulation "
"calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de concepción, fecha de concepción, calculadora de embarazo, "
"calculadora de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:15
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date based on due date or last menstrual period."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su fecha de concepción según la fecha prevista de parto o el último "
"período menstrual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:85
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:298
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:85
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:77
msgid "From Due Date"
msgstr "Desde la fecha de vencimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:89
msgid "From Last Period"
msgstr "Del último período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:96
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:179
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:344
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:162
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:171
