msgstr "Semanas restantes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:265
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:278
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:197
msgid "Days Remaining"
msgstr "Días restantes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:284
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:338
msgid "What is Conception?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la Concepción?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:286
msgid ""
"Conception occurs when a sperm fertilizes an egg, typically happening during"
" ovulation. This is the moment when pregnancy begins, and it usually occurs "
"about 14 days after the start of your last menstrual period (LMP) in a "
"28-day cycle."
msgstr ""
"La concepción ocurre cuando un espermatozoide fertiliza un óvulo, lo que "
"generalmente ocurre durante la ovulación. Este es el momento en el que "
"comienza el embarazo, y suele ocurrir unos 14 días después del inicio de tu "
"último período menstrual (FUM) en un ciclo de 28 días."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"The conception date is important for tracking fetal development, "
"understanding pregnancy milestones, and calculating your due date. However, "
"it's important to note that the exact moment of conception is difficult to "
"determine precisely."
msgstr ""
"La fecha de concepción es importante para realizar un seguimiento del "
"desarrollo fetal, comprender los hitos del embarazo y calcular la fecha de "
"parto. Sin embargo, es importante señalar que el momento exacto de la "
"concepción es difícil de determinar con precisión."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:295
msgid "How Conception Date is Calculated"
msgstr "Cómo se calcula la fecha de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:300
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs approximately 266 days (38 weeks) before the due"
" date. This is calculated by subtracting 266 days from your expected due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"La concepción suele ocurrir aproximadamente 266 días (38 semanas) antes de "
"la fecha prevista. Esto se calcula restando 266 días de la fecha prevista de"
" parto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:302
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Due Date - 266 days"
msgstr "Fórmula: Fecha de concepción = Fecha de vencimiento - 266 días"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:305
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:77
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:81
msgid "From Last Menstrual Period"
msgstr "Desde el último período menstrual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:307
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs around 14 days before your next expected period."
" For a 28-day cycle, this is 14 days after the first day of your last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"La concepción suele ocurrir alrededor de 14 días antes de su próximo período"
" esperado. Para un ciclo de 28 días, esto es 14 días después del primer día "
"de su último período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:309
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Last Period + (Cycle Length - 14 days)"
msgstr ""
"Fórmula: Fecha de concepción = Último período + (Duración del ciclo - 14 "
"días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:318
msgid "Choose your calculation method: From Due Date or From Last Period"
msgstr ""
"Elija su método de cálculo: Desde la fecha de vencimiento o Desde el último "
"período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:319
msgid "If using due date method, enter your expected due date"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método de fecha de vencimiento, ingrese la fecha de "
"vencimiento prevista"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"If using last period method, enter the first day of your last menstrual "
"period and your cycle length (default: 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método del último período, ingrese el primer día de su último "
"período menstrual y la duración de su ciclo (predeterminado: 28 días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:321
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:341
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:373
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Review your conception date, pregnancy timeline, and trimester information"
msgstr ""
"Revise la fecha de concepción, el cronograma del embarazo y la información "
"del trimestre."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:323
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:343
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:365
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your pregnancy progress"
msgstr "Utilice los gráficos para visualizar el progreso de su embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception likely occurred. This is typically within"
" a 5-6 day window around ovulation when the egg is viable for fertilization."
msgstr ""
"La fecha estimada en la que probablemente ocurrió la concepción. Por lo "
"general, esto ocurre dentro de un período de 5 a 6 días alrededor de la "
"ovulación, cuando el óvulo es viable para la fertilización."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:338
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:364
msgid "Last Menstrual Period (LMP)"
msgstr "Último período menstrual (FUM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"The first day of your last menstrual period. This is used as the starting "
"point for calculating pregnancy weeks and due date."
msgstr ""
"El primer día de su último período menstrual. Esto se utiliza como punto de "
"partida para calcular las semanas de embarazo y la fecha de parto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:346
msgid ""
"The estimated date when your baby is due. This is calculated as 280 days (40"
" weeks) from the first day of your last menstrual period."
msgstr ""
"La fecha estimada en la que nacerá su bebé. Esto se calcula como 280 días "
"(40 semanas) desde el primer día de su último período menstrual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:350
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:370
msgid "Weeks and Days Pregnant"
msgstr "Semanas y días de embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:352
msgid ""
"The number of weeks and days since your last menstrual period. Pregnancy is "
"typically counted from the LMP, not from conception."
msgstr ""
"El número de semanas y días desde su último período menstrual. Por lo "
"general, el embarazo se cuenta a partir de la FUM, no desde la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"Your current trimester: First (weeks 1-13), Second (weeks 14-27), or Third "
"(weeks 28-40). Each trimester has different developmental milestones."
msgstr ""
"Su trimestre actual: primero (semanas 1 a 13), segundo (semanas 14 a 27) o "
"tercero (semanas 28 a 40). Cada trimestre tiene diferentes hitos del "
"desarrollo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:382
msgid "Progress Percentage"
msgstr "Porcentaje de progreso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"The percentage of your pregnancy completed based on a full 40-week (280-day)"
" pregnancy term."
msgstr ""
"El porcentaje de su embarazo completado basado en un embarazo completo de 40"
" semanas (280 días)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:372
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:333
msgid "Pregnancy Trimesters"
msgstr "Trimestres del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:375
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:450
msgid "First Trimester (Weeks 1-13)"
msgstr "Primer trimestre (semanas 1 a 13)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Early development, organ formation, and initial fetal growth. Many women "
"experience morning sickness and fatigue during this period."
msgstr ""
"Desarrollo temprano, formación de órganos y crecimiento fetal inicial. "
"Muchas mujeres experimentan náuseas y fatiga durante este período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Heartbeat begins, major organs form, baby's sex is "
"determined"
msgstr ""
"Hitos clave: comienzan los latidos del corazón, se forman los órganos "
"principales, se determina el sexo del bebé"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:382
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 14-27)"
msgstr "Segundo trimestre (semanas 14 a 27)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"Rapid growth, movement felt, and visible baby bump. Often called the "
"'honeymoon period' of pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Crecimiento rápido, sensación de movimiento y panza visible. A menudo se le "
"llama el \"período de luna de miel\" del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby movements felt, anatomy scan, baby can hear sounds"
msgstr ""
"Hitos clave: Sentir los movimientos del bebé, escaneo de la anatomía, el "
"bebé puede escuchar sonidos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:389
msgid "Third Trimester (Weeks 28-40)"
msgstr "Tercer trimestre (semanas 28-40)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"Final growth phase, preparation for birth, and increased discomfort. Baby "
"gains most weight during this period."
msgstr ""
"Fase final de crecimiento, preparación para el parto y aumento del malestar."
" El bebé gana más peso durante este período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby reaches full term (37 weeks), lungs mature, ready for "
"birth"
msgstr ""
"Hitos clave: el bebé llega a término (37 semanas), los pulmones maduran y "
"están listos para nacer"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:400
msgid "Understanding the Conception Window"
msgstr "Entendiendo la ventana de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:402
msgid "Conception can occur within a 5-6 day window around ovulation:"
msgstr ""
"La concepción puede ocurrir dentro de un período de 5 a 6 días alrededor de "
"la ovulación:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:405
msgid "Sperm can survive in the female reproductive tract for up to 5 days"
msgstr ""
"Los espermatozoides pueden sobrevivir en el tracto reproductivo femenino "
"hasta 5 días."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"The egg is viable for fertilization for about 12-24 hours after ovulation"
msgstr ""
"El óvulo es viable para la fertilización durante aproximadamente 12 a 24 "
"horas después de la ovulación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"The most fertile window is typically 2-3 days before ovulation and the day "
"of ovulation"
msgstr ""
"La ventana más fértil suele ser 2 o 3 días antes de la ovulación y el día de"
" la ovulación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:408
msgid ""
"The calculator provides an estimated conception date, but actual conception "
"may have occurred within a few days of this date"
msgstr ""
"La calculadora proporciona una fecha estimada de concepción, pero es posible"
" que la concepción real haya ocurrido unos días después de esta fecha."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"Conception dates are estimates. The exact moment of conception is difficult "
"to determine, and actual conception may have occurred within a 5-6 day "
"window around the calculated date."
msgstr ""
"Las fechas de concepción son estimaciones. El momento exacto de la "
"concepción es difícil de determinar y la concepción real puede haber "
"ocurrido dentro de un período de 5 a 6 días alrededor de la fecha calculada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is typically counted from the first day of your last menstrual "
"period (LMP), not from conception. This is why pregnancy is said to last 40 "
"weeks even though conception occurs about 2 weeks after LMP."
msgstr ""
"Por lo general, el embarazo se cuenta desde el primer día de su último "
"período menstrual (FUM), no desde la concepción. Es por eso que se dice que "
"el embarazo dura 40 semanas, aunque la concepción ocurre aproximadamente 2 "
"semanas después de la FUM."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Individual cycle lengths vary. If your cycle is longer or shorter than 28 "
"days, adjust the cycle length in the calculator for more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"La duración de los ciclos individuales varía. Si su ciclo dura más o menos "
"28 días, ajuste la duración del ciclo en la calculadora para obtener "
"resultados más precisos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:438
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with healthcare providers for accurate pregnancy dating, especially "
"for medical decisions and prenatal care."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines educativos e informativos únicamente. Consulte "
"siempre con proveedores de atención médica para obtener una datación precisa"
" del embarazo, especialmente para decisiones médicas y atención prenatal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:522
msgid "Please enter a due date."
msgstr "Por favor ingrese una fecha de vencimiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:533
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:550
msgid "Please enter your last menstrual period date."
msgstr "Por favor ingrese la fecha de su último período menstrual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:789
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:845
msgid "Completed"
msgstr "Terminado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:56
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:45
msgid "Due Date Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de fecha de vencimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Pregnancy Due Date"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha prevista del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your pregnancy due date based on last menstrual period or "
"conception date. Free due date calculator with trimester tracking."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la fecha prevista de su embarazo según el último período menstrual o"
" la fecha de concepción. Calculadora gratuita de fecha de parto con "
"seguimiento trimestral."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"due date calculator, pregnancy due date, due date, pregnancy calculator, "
"trimester calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de fecha de parto, fecha de parto del embarazo, fecha de parto, "
"calculadora de embarazo, calculadora de trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:15
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Calculate your pregnancy due date based on last menstrual period or "
"conception date."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la fecha prevista de su embarazo según el último período menstrual o"
" la fecha de concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:73
msgid "Calculate Due Date"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de vencimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:85
msgid "From Last Menstrual Period (LMP)"
msgstr "Desde el último período menstrual (FUM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:325
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:81
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:85
msgid "From Conception Date"
msgstr "Desde la fecha de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:109
msgid "Estimated date of conception"
msgstr "Fecha estimada de concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:152
msgid ""
"Enter your information to calculate your due date and pregnancy timeline "
"with detailed analysis and charts."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su información para calcular su fecha de parto y cronograma de "
"embarazo con análisis y gráficos detallados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:285
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:392
msgid "Pregnancy Milestones"
msgstr "Hitos del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:304
msgid "What is a Due Date?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una fecha de vencimiento?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"A due date (also called expected date of delivery or EDD) is the estimated "
"date when a pregnant woman is most likely to give birth. It's calculated as "
"40 weeks (280 days) from the first day of the last menstrual period (LMP)."
msgstr ""
"Una fecha de parto (también llamada fecha prevista de parto o EDD) es la "
"fecha estimada en la que una mujer embarazada tiene más probabilidades de "
"dar a luz. Se calcula como 40 semanas (280 días) a partir del primer día del"
" último período menstrual (FUM)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:309
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The due date is an estimate, not an exact date. Only about 5%% of babies are"
" born exactly on their due date, with most babies born within two weeks "
"before or after the due date."
msgstr ""
"La fecha de vencimiento es una estimación, no una fecha exacta. Sólo "
"alrededor del 5%% de los bebés nacen exactamente en la fecha prevista, y la "
"mayoría de los bebés nacen dentro de las dos semanas anteriores o "
"posteriores a la fecha prevista."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:315
msgid "How Due Date is Calculated"
msgstr "Cómo se calcula la fecha de vencimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:318
msgid "Naegele's Rule (From LMP)"
msgstr "La regla de Naegele (de LMP)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"The most common method: Add 1 year, subtract 3 months, and add 7 days to the"
" first day of your last menstrual period. Simplified: Add 280 days (40 "
"weeks) to LMP."
msgstr ""
"El método más común: suma 1 año, resta 3 meses y suma 7 días al primer día "
"de tu último período menstrual. Simplificado: agregue 280 días (40 semanas) "
"a LMP."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:322
msgid "Formula: Due Date = LMP + 280 days"
msgstr "Fórmula: Fecha de vencimiento = LMP + 280 días"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"If you know the conception date, add 266 days (38 weeks) to calculate the "
"due date. This accounts for the typical 2-week period between LMP and "
"conception."
msgstr ""
"Si conoce la fecha de concepción, agregue 266 días (38 semanas) para "
"calcular la fecha de parto. Esto representa el período típico de dos semanas"
" entre la FUM y la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:329
msgid "Formula: Due Date = Conception Date + 266 days"
msgstr "Fórmula: Fecha de vencimiento = Fecha de concepción + 266 días"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Last Menstrual Period or From "
"Conception Date"
msgstr ""
"Elija su método de cálculo: Desde la última menstruación o Desde la fecha de"
" concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:339
msgid ""
"If using LMP method, enter the first day of your last menstrual period and "
"your cycle length (default: 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método FUM, ingrese el primer día de su último período "
"menstrual y la duración de su ciclo (predeterminado: 28 días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"If using conception date method, enter the estimated date of conception"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método de la fecha de concepción, ingrese la fecha estimada de"
" concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Review your due date, pregnancy timeline, trimester information, and "
"milestones"
msgstr ""
"Revise su fecha de parto, cronograma de embarazo, información trimestral e "
"hitos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"The estimated date when your baby is due. This is calculated as 280 days (40"
" weeks) from your last menstrual period or 266 days from conception."
msgstr ""
"La fecha estimada en la que nacerá su bebé. Esto se calcula como 280 días "
"(40 semanas) desde su último período menstrual o 266 días desde la "
"concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception likely occurred. This is typically 14 "
"days after the first day of your last period (or cycle_length - 14 days for "
"variable cycles)."
msgstr ""
"La fecha estimada en la que probablemente ocurrió la concepción. Por lo "
"general, esto ocurre 14 días después del primer día de su último período (o "
"ciclo_longitud: 14 días para ciclos variables)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"The first day of your last menstrual period. This is the standard starting "
"point for calculating pregnancy weeks and due date."
msgstr ""
"El primer día de su último período menstrual. Este es el punto de partida "
"estándar para calcular las semanas de embarazo y la fecha de parto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:372
msgid ""
"The number of weeks and days since your last menstrual period. Pregnancy is "
"counted from LMP, not from conception."
msgstr ""
"El número de semanas y días desde su último período menstrual. El embarazo "
"se cuenta desde la FUM, no desde la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:378
msgid ""
"Your current trimester: First (weeks 1-13), Second (weeks 14-27), or Third "
"(weeks 28-40)."
msgstr ""
"Su trimestre actual: primero (semanas 1 a 13), segundo (semanas 14 a 27) o "
"tercero (semanas 28 a 40)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"The percentage of your pregnancy completed based on a full 40-week (280-day)"
" term."
msgstr ""
"El porcentaje de su embarazo completado basado en un período completo de 40 "
"semanas (280 días)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:395
msgid "First Trimester End (13 weeks)"
msgstr "Fin del primer trimestre (13 semanas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"End of the first trimester. Major organ development is complete, and the "
"risk of miscarriage decreases significantly."
msgstr ""
"Fin del primer trimestre. El desarrollo de los órganos principales está "
"completo y el riesgo de aborto espontáneo disminuye significativamente."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:401
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:675
msgid "Viability Week (24 weeks)"
msgstr "Semana de Viabilidad (24 semanas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"The point at which a baby has a chance of survival outside the womb with "
"medical intervention."
msgstr ""
"El punto en el que un bebé tiene posibilidades de sobrevivir fuera del útero"
" con intervención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:407
msgid "Second Trimester End (27 weeks)"
msgstr "Fin del segundo trimestre (27 semanas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"End of the second trimester. Baby's movements are strong, and most major "
"development is complete."
msgstr ""
"Fin del segundo trimestre. Los movimientos del bebé son fuertes y la mayor "
"parte del desarrollo principal está completo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:413
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:677
msgid "Full Term (37 weeks)"
msgstr "Término completo (37 semanas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"Baby is considered full-term and ready for birth. Lungs and other organs are"
" mature."
msgstr ""
"El bebé se considera nacido a término y listo para nacer. Los pulmones y "
"otros órganos están maduros."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:423
msgid "Due Date Accuracy"
msgstr "Precisión de la fecha de vencimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates, not exact dates. Several factors can affect the "
"accuracy:"
msgstr ""
"Las fechas de vencimiento son estimaciones, no fechas exactas. Varios "
"factores pueden afectar la precisión:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:428
msgid "Irregular menstrual cycles"
msgstr "Ciclos menstruales irregulares"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:429
msgid "Uncertainty about the exact date of LMP"
msgstr "Incertidumbre sobre la fecha exacta de LMP"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:430
msgid "Variations in the length of pregnancy (normal range: 37-42 weeks)"
msgstr "Variaciones en la duración del embarazo (rango normal: 37-42 semanas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:431
msgid "Individual differences in fetal development"
msgstr "Diferencias individuales en el desarrollo fetal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Healthcare providers often use ultrasound measurements to refine the due "
"date, especially in early pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Los proveedores de atención médica suelen utilizar mediciones ecográficas "
"para refinar la fecha de parto, especialmente al principio del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:446
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates. Only about 5%% of babies are born exactly on their "
"due date. Most babies are born within two weeks before or after the due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Las fechas de vencimiento son estimaciones. Sólo alrededor del 5%% de los "
"bebés nacen exactamente en la fecha prevista. La mayoría de los bebés nacen "
"dos semanas antes o después de la fecha prevista."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is counted from the first day of your last menstrual period (LMP),"
" not from conception. This is why pregnancy is said to last 40 weeks even "
"though conception occurs about 2 weeks after LMP."
msgstr ""
"El embarazo se cuenta desde el primer día de su último período menstrual "
"(FUM), no desde la concepción. Es por eso que se dice que el embarazo dura "
"40 semanas, aunque la concepción ocurre aproximadamente 2 semanas después de"
" la FUM."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"If your cycle is longer or shorter than 28 days, adjust the cycle length in "
"the calculator for more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"Si su ciclo dura más o menos 28 días, ajuste la duración del ciclo en la "
"calculadora para obtener resultados más precisos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:560
msgid "Please enter a conception date."
msgstr "Por favor ingrese una fecha de concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:674
msgid "First Trimester End"
msgstr "Fin del primer trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:676
msgid "Second Trimester End"
msgstr "Fin del segundo trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:56
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:35
msgid "Fat Intake Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de ingesta de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:14
msgid "Daily Fat Needs Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de necesidades diarias de grasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily fat intake needs based on total calories and macro "
"percentages. Get personalized fat recommendations for your diet."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus necesidades diarias de ingesta de grasas en función de las "
"calorías totales y los macroporcentajes. Obtenga recomendaciones "
"personalizadas de grasas para su dieta."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"fat intake calculator, fat calculator, daily fat, fat intake, healthy fats"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de ingesta de grasas, calculadora de grasas, grasa diaria, "
"ingesta de grasas, grasas saludables"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:15
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily fat intake needs based on total calories and macro "
"percentages."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus necesidades diarias de ingesta de grasas en función de las "
"calorías totales y los macroporcentajes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:73
msgid "Calculate Fat"
msgstr "Calcular grasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:128
#, python-format
msgid "Carbs %%"
msgstr "Carbohidratos %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:132
msgid "Fat will be calculated as remainder"
msgstr "La grasa se calculará como resto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:140
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:604
msgid "Calculate Fat Intake"
msgstr "Calcular la ingesta de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:175
msgid ""
"Enter your total calories and fat percentage to see your daily fat breakdown"
" with meal distribution and food sources."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su total de calorías y porcentaje de grasa para ver su desglose "
"diario de grasa con la distribución de comidas y las fuentes de alimentos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:185
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:408
msgid "Daily Fat Intake"
msgstr "Ingesta diaria de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:196
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ideal_weight_calculator.html:221
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:236
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/random_number_generator.html:337
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:547
msgid "Minimum"
msgstr "Mínimo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:221
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:420
msgid "Saturated Fat (Max)"
msgstr "Grasa saturada (máx.)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:223
#, python-format
msgid "Max 10%% of calories"
msgstr "Máximo 10%% de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:228
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:426
msgid "Unsaturated Fat"
msgstr "Grasas insaturadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:230
msgid "Healthy fats"
msgstr "Grasas saludables"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:258
msgid "Saturated vs Unsaturated"
msgstr "Saturado vs Insaturado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:321
msgid "Healthy Fat Sources Guide"
msgstr "Guía de fuentes de grasas saludables"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:352
msgid "What are Fats?"
msgstr "¿Qué son las grasas?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"Fats are one of the three main macronutrients (along with protein and "
"carbohydrates) that provide energy to your body. Fats provide 9 calories per"
" gram, making them the most calorie-dense macronutrient."
msgstr ""
"Las grasas son uno de los tres macronutrientes principales (junto con las "
"proteínas y los carbohidratos) que proporcionan energía al cuerpo. Las "
"grasas aportan 9 calorías por gramo, lo que las convierte en el "
"macronutriente más denso en calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"Fats play crucial roles in hormone production, nutrient absorption "
"(especially fat-soluble vitamins A, D, E, and K), brain function, and "
"maintaining healthy skin and hair. Despite their bad reputation, healthy "
"fats are essential for optimal health."
msgstr ""
"Las grasas desempeñan funciones cruciales en la producción de hormonas, la "
"absorción de nutrientes (especialmente las vitaminas liposolubles A, D, E y "
"K), la función cerebral y el mantenimiento de la piel y el cabello sanos. A "
"pesar de su mala reputación, las grasas saludables son esenciales para una "
"salud óptima."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:363
msgid "Types of Fats"
msgstr "Tipos de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:366
msgid "Saturated Fats"
msgstr "Grasas saturadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:368
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Found in animal products and some plant foods. Should be limited to less "
"than 10%% of total calories. Can raise LDL cholesterol when consumed in "
"excess."
msgstr ""
"Se encuentra en productos animales y algunos alimentos vegetales. Debe "
"limitarse a menos del 10%% del total de calorías. Puede aumentar el "
"colesterol LDL cuando se consume en exceso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:370
msgid "Examples: Red meat, butter, cheese, coconut oil"
msgstr "Ejemplos: carnes rojas, mantequilla, queso, aceite de coco."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:373
msgid "Unsaturated Fats (Healthy Fats)"
msgstr "Grasas insaturadas (grasas saludables)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:375
msgid ""
"Found in plant foods and fish. Beneficial for heart health, brain function, "
"and reducing inflammation. Should make up most of your fat intake."
msgstr ""
"Se encuentra en alimentos vegetales y pescado. Beneficioso para la salud del"
" corazón, la función cerebral y para reducir la inflamación. Debería "
"constituir la mayor parte de su ingesta de grasas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:377
msgid "Examples: Olive oil, avocados, nuts, seeds, fatty fish"
msgstr ""
"Ejemplos: aceite de oliva, aguacates, nueces, semillas, pescado graso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:380
msgid "Trans Fats"
msgstr "Grasas trans"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Artificial fats found in processed foods. Should be avoided completely as "
"they raise LDL cholesterol and lower HDL cholesterol."
msgstr ""
"Grasas artificiales que se encuentran en los alimentos procesados. Deben "
"evitarse por completo ya que aumentan el colesterol LDL y reducen el "
"colesterol HDL."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:384
msgid "Examples: Fried foods, baked goods, margarine (check labels)"
msgstr ""
"Ejemplos: alimentos fritos, productos horneados, margarina (consulte las "
"etiquetas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:395
msgid ""
"If using percentage method, enter your desired fat percentage (or use the "
"slider)"
msgstr ""
"Si usa el método de porcentaje, ingrese el porcentaje de grasa deseado (o "
"use el control deslizante)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:396
msgid ""
"If using remaining macros method, enter your protein and carb percentages"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método de macros restantes, ingrese sus porcentajes de "
"proteínas y carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:397
msgid "Click 'Calculate Fat Intake' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular la ingesta de grasas' para ver sus resultados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:398
msgid "Review your daily fat needs, meal distribution, and food sources"
msgstr ""
"Revise sus necesidades diarias de grasas, distribución de comidas y fuentes "
"de alimentos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:399
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your fat distribution"
msgstr "Utilice los gráficos para visualizar su distribución de grasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:410
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The total amount of fat (in grams) you should consume daily based on your "
"calorie intake and selected percentage. This is calculated as: (Total "
"Calories × Fat %%) ÷ 9 calories per gram."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad total de grasa (en gramos) que debes consumir diariamente según "
"tu ingesta de calorías y el porcentaje seleccionado. Esto se calcula como: "
"(Calorías totales × % de grasa%) ÷ 9 calorías por gramo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:414
msgid "Calories from Fat"
msgstr "Calorías de grasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:416
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The number of calories that come from fat. This is calculated as: Total "
"Calories × (Fat %% ÷ 100)."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad de calorías que provienen de la grasa. Esto se calcula como: "
"Calorías totales × (% de grasa% ÷ 100)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:422
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The maximum recommended amount of saturated fat per day. Health guidelines "
"recommend limiting saturated fat to less than 10%% of total calories."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad máxima recomendada de grasas saturadas por día. Las pautas de "
"salud recomiendan limitar las grasas saturadas a menos del 10% del total de "
"calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:428
msgid ""
"The recommended amount of healthy unsaturated fats. This is your total fat "
"minus the maximum saturated fat allowance."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad recomendada de grasas insaturadas saludables. Esta es su grasa "
"total menos la cantidad máxima de grasas saturadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:434
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested fat distribution across meals: Breakfast (25%%), Lunch (35%%), "
"Dinner (30%%), and Snacks (10%%). This helps maintain steady energy levels "
"and satiety."
msgstr ""
"Distribución sugerida de grasas en las comidas: Desayuno (25%%), Almuerzo "
"(35%%), Cena (30%%) y Meriendas (10%%). Esto ayuda a mantener niveles "
"estables de energía y saciedad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:440
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Comparison of minimum (20%%), moderate (30%%), and high (40%%) fat "
"approaches. Choose based on your goals, activity level, and personal "
"preferences."
msgstr ""
"Comparación de enfoques de grasa mínima (20%), moderada (30%) y alta (40%). "
"Elija según sus objetivos, nivel de actividad y preferencias personales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:448
msgid "Fat Intake Guidelines"
msgstr "Pautas de ingesta de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:450
#, python-format
msgid "Minimum (20%%):"
msgstr "Mínimo (20%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:450
msgid ""
"Typically 40-60g per day. Suitable for very low-fat diets or those with "
"specific medical conditions. May be difficult to maintain long-term."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente entre 40 y 60 g al día. Adecuado para dietas muy bajas en grasas"
" o con condiciones médicas específicas. Puede ser difícil de mantener a "
"largo plazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:451
#, python-format
msgid "Moderate (30%%):"
msgstr "Moderado (30%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:451
msgid ""
"Typically 60-90g per day. Balanced approach suitable for most people. "
"Recommended for general health and moderate activity levels."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente entre 60 y 90 g al día. Enfoque equilibrado adecuado para la "
"mayoría de las personas. Recomendado para salud general y niveles de "
"actividad moderados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:452
#, python-format
msgid "High (40%%):"
msgstr "Alto (40%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Typically 90g+ per day. Suitable for ketogenic diets, very active "
"individuals, or those with high calorie needs. Focus on healthy unsaturated "
"fats."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente 90 g+ por día. Adecuado para dietas cetogénicas, personas muy "
"activas o con necesidades calóricas elevadas. Concéntrese en las grasas "
"insaturadas saludables."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:458
msgid "Best Fat Sources"
msgstr "Las mejores fuentes de grasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:460
msgid "Monounsaturated Fats:"
msgstr "Grasas monoinsaturadas:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:460
msgid ""
"Olive oil, avocados, almonds, peanuts, cashews. Support heart health and "
"reduce inflammation."
msgstr ""
"Aceite de oliva, aguacates, almendras, maní, anacardos. Apoya la salud del "
"corazón y reduce la inflamación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:461
msgid "Polyunsaturated Fats (Omega-3):"
msgstr "Grasas poliinsaturadas (Omega-3):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:461
msgid ""
"Fatty fish (salmon, mackerel), walnuts, flaxseeds, chia seeds. Essential for"
" brain function and heart health."
msgstr ""
"Pescados grasos (salmón, caballa), nueces, semillas de lino, semillas de "
"chía. Esencial para la función cerebral y la salud del corazón."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:462
msgid "Polyunsaturated Fats (Omega-6):"
msgstr "Grasas poliinsaturadas (Omega-6):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:462
msgid ""
"Sunflower oil, soybean oil, nuts, seeds. Important but should be balanced "
"with omega-3s."
msgstr ""
"Aceite de girasol, aceite de soja, frutos secos, semillas. Importante pero "
"debe equilibrarse con omega-3."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:463
msgid "Saturated Fats (Limit):"
msgstr "Grasas saturadas (límite):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:463
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Red meat, butter, cheese, coconut oil. Consume in moderation, less than 10%%"
" of total calories."
msgstr ""
"Carnes rojas, mantequilla, queso, aceite de coco. Consumir con moderación, "
"menos del 10%% del total de calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:469
msgid "Tips for Optimal Fat Intake"
msgstr "Consejos para una ingesta óptima de grasas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:471
msgid "Prioritize Healthy Fats:"
msgstr "Priorice las grasas saludables:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:471
msgid ""
"Focus on unsaturated fats from plant sources and fish. These provide "
"essential fatty acids and support overall health."
msgstr ""
"Concéntrese en las grasas insaturadas de origen vegetal y pescado. Estos "
"proporcionan ácidos grasos esenciales y apoyan la salud en general."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:472
msgid "Limit Saturated Fats:"
msgstr "Limite las grasas saturadas:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:472
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Keep saturated fat intake below 10%% of total calories. Choose lean protein "
"sources and limit processed foods."
msgstr ""
"Mantenga la ingesta de grasas saturadas por debajo del 10%% del total de "
"calorías. Elija fuentes de proteínas magras y limite los alimentos "
"procesados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:473
msgid "Avoid Trans Fats:"
msgstr "Evite las grasas trans:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:473
msgid ""
"Read labels and avoid foods with partially hydrogenated oils. Trans fats "
"have no health benefits."
msgstr ""
"Lea las etiquetas y evite alimentos con aceites parcialmente hidrogenados. "
"Las grasas trans no tienen beneficios para la salud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:474
msgid "Balance Omega-3 and Omega-6:"
msgstr "Equilibra Omega-3 y Omega-6:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:474
msgid ""
"Aim for a ratio of 1:1 to 1:4 (omega-3:omega-6). Include fatty fish or "
"omega-3 supplements if needed."
msgstr ""
"Apunte a una proporción de 1:1 a 1:4 (omega-3:omega-6). Incluya pescado "
"graso o suplementos de omega-3 si es necesario."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:475
msgid "Include Fat with Meals:"
msgstr "Incluya grasas en las comidas:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"Fat helps with satiety and nutrient absorption. Include healthy fats in each"
" meal for better satisfaction and vitamin absorption."
msgstr ""
"La grasa ayuda con la saciedad y la absorción de nutrientes. Incluya grasas "
"saludables en cada comida para una mejor satisfacción y absorción de "
"vitaminas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:487
msgid ""
"Individual fat needs vary based on activity level, metabolism, body "
"composition goals, and personal preferences."
msgstr ""
"Las necesidades individuales de grasa varían según el nivel de actividad, el"
" metabolismo, los objetivos de composición corporal y las preferencias "
"personales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:499
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Very low-fat diets (below 20%%) may not be suitable for everyone and can "
"affect hormone production and nutrient absorption. Consult with a healthcare"
" provider or registered dietitian before making significant dietary changes."
msgstr ""
"Las dietas muy bajas en grasas (menos del 20%) pueden no ser adecuadas para "
"todos y pueden afectar la producción de hormonas y la absorción de "
"nutrientes. Consulte con un proveedor de atención médica o un dietista "
"registrado antes de realizar cambios dietéticos importantes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:702
msgid "Avocado"
msgstr "Palta"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:703
msgid "Olive Oil"
msgstr "Aceite de oliva"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:704
msgid "Nuts"
msgstr "Cojones"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:705
msgid "Peanut Butter"
msgstr "Manteca de cacahuete"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:706
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:754
msgid "Salmon"
msgstr "Salmón"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:707
msgid "Cheese"
msgstr "Queso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:708
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:755
msgid "Eggs"
msgstr "Huevos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:709
msgid "Coconut Oil"
msgstr "Aceite de coco"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:56
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:55
msgid "GFR Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de TFG"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:14
msgid "Glomerular Filtration Rate"
msgstr "Tasa de filtración glomerular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:15
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:24
msgid ""
"Calculate estimated glomerular filtration rate (eGFR) using CKD-EPI formula "
"for kidney function assessment."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la tasa de filtración glomerular estimada (eGFR) utilizando la "
"fórmula CKD-EPI para evaluar la función renal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"GFR calculator, eGFR calculator, kidney function, CKD-EPI, MDRD, glomerular "
"filtration rate"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de TFG, calculadora de TFGe, función renal, CKD-EPI, MDRD, tasa "
"de filtración glomerular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Calculate estimated glomerular filtration rate (eGFR) for kidney function "
"assessment."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la tasa de filtración glomerular estimada (eGFR) para evaluar la "
"función renal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:84
msgid "Range: 18-100 years"
msgstr "Rango: 18-100 años"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:104
msgid "Race"
msgstr "Carrera"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:108
msgid "Non-Black"
msgstr "No negro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/gfr_calculator.html:112
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:77
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:92
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:107
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:143
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:158
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:173
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:188
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:224
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:239
