msgstr "Calcular la masa corporal magra y la masa libre de grasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your lean body mass (LBM) and fat-free mass from body weight and "
"body fat percentage. Get detailed body composition analysis and protein "
"recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su masa corporal magra (LBM) y su masa libre de grasa a partir del "
