" de la composición corporal y recomendaciones de proteínas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:96
msgid "Range: 1-300 kg or 2-660 lbs"
msgstr "Rango: 1-300 kg o 2-660 libras"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:101
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:188
