msgstr "Comparación de masas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:244
msgid "Protein Recommendations Based on LBM"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de proteínas basadas en LBM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:259
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:108
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:161
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:711
msgid "Athlete"
msgstr "Atleta"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:267
msgid "Body Composition Category"
msgstr "Categoría de composición corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:288
msgid "What is Lean Body Mass?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la masa corporal magra?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:290
msgid ""
"Lean Body Mass (LBM) is the total weight of your body minus all fat mass. It"
" includes muscles, bones, organs, water, and all other non-fat tissues. LBM "
"is a crucial metric for understanding body composition and is often used to "
"calculate protein needs and track fitness progress."
msgstr ""
"La masa corporal magra (LBM) es el peso total de su cuerpo menos toda la "
"masa grasa. Incluye músculos, huesos, órganos, agua y todos los demás "
"tejidos no grasos. La LBM es una métrica crucial para comprender la "
"composición corporal y, a menudo, se utiliza para calcular las necesidades "
"de proteínas y realizar un seguimiento del progreso físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:296
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Fat Mass is calculated as: Total Weight × (Body Fat %% / 100). Therefore, "
"LBM represents everything in your body except fat, making it a better "
"indicator of muscle mass and overall body composition than total weight "
"alone."
msgstr ""
"La masa grasa se calcula como: Peso total × (% de grasa corporal / 100). Por"
" lo tanto, la LBM representa todo lo que hay en el cuerpo excepto la grasa, "
"lo que la convierte en un mejor indicador de la masa muscular y la "
"composición corporal general que el peso total solo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:302
msgid "Why Lean Body Mass Matters"
msgstr "Por qué es importante la masa corporal magra"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:305
msgid "Muscle Mass Indicator"
msgstr "Indicador de masa muscular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:307
msgid ""
"LBM is closely related to muscle mass. Higher LBM typically indicates more "
"muscle, which is associated with better metabolic health, strength, and "
"physical performance."
msgstr ""
"La LBM está estrechamente relacionada con la masa muscular. Una masa magra "
"más alta generalmente indica más músculo, lo que se asocia con una mejor "
"salud metabólica, fuerza y ​​rendimiento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:311
msgid "Protein Requirements"
msgstr "Requerimientos de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Protein needs are calculated based on LBM, not total weight. This provides a"
" more accurate estimate of how much protein you need to maintain or build "
"muscle."
msgstr ""
"Las necesidades de proteínas se calculan en función de la LBM, no del peso "
"total. Esto proporciona una estimación más precisa de la cantidad de "
"proteína que necesita para mantener o desarrollar músculo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:317
msgid "Fitness Progress Tracking"
msgstr "Seguimiento del progreso físico"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"Tracking LBM helps you understand if you're losing fat while maintaining or "
"gaining muscle, which is the goal of most fitness programs."
msgstr ""
"El seguimiento de la LBM le ayuda a comprender si está perdiendo grasa "
"mientras mantiene o gana músculo, que es el objetivo de la mayoría de los "
"programas de acondicionamiento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:330
msgid "Enter your current body weight accurately"
msgstr "Ingrese su peso corporal actual con precisión"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Enter your body fat percentage (you can measure this using body fat scales, "
"calipers, DEXA scan, or other methods)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su porcentaje de grasa corporal (puede medirlo usando básculas de "
"grasa corporal, calibradores, escaneo DEXA u otros métodos)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:332
msgid "Click 'Calculate LBM' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular LBM' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:333
msgid "Review the charts and detailed breakdown"
msgstr "Revise los gráficos y el desglose detallado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:334
msgid "Check protein recommendations based on your activity level"
msgstr "Consulta las recomendaciones de proteínas según tu nivel de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:343
msgid "Lean Body Mass (LBM)"
msgstr "Masa corporal magra (LBM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Your total body weight minus all fat. This includes muscles, bones, organs, "
"and water. Higher LBM generally indicates better body composition."
msgstr ""
"Su peso corporal total menos toda la grasa. Esto incluye músculos, huesos, "
"órganos y agua. Una masa magra más alta generalmente indica una mejor "
"composición corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"The total weight of fat in your body. Calculated as a percentage of your "
"total weight."
msgstr ""
"El peso total de grasa en tu cuerpo. Calculado como porcentaje de su peso "
"total."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:355
msgid "LBM Percentage"
msgstr "Porcentaje de LBM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"The percentage of your total weight that is lean body mass. Higher "
"percentages indicate better body composition."
msgstr ""
"El porcentaje de su peso total que es masa corporal magra. Los porcentajes "
"más altos indican una mejor composición corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:361
msgid "Protein Recommendations"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"Based on your LBM and activity level. Sedentary individuals need less "
"protein, while athletes and bodybuilders need more to support muscle "
"maintenance and growth."
msgstr ""
"Según su LBM y su nivel de actividad. Las personas sedentarias necesitan "
"menos proteínas, mientras que los atletas y culturistas necesitan más para "
"favorecer el mantenimiento y el crecimiento de los músculos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:371
msgid "Body Composition Categories"
msgstr "Categorías de composición corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:374
#, python-format
msgid "Essential Fat: &lt; 6%%"
msgstr "Grasas esenciales: &lt; 6%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of fat necessary for basic physical and physiological "
"health. Typically only seen in competitive bodybuilders."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad mínima de grasa necesaria para la salud física y fisiológica "
"básica. Normalmente sólo se ve en culturistas competitivos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:380
#, python-format
msgid "Athletic: 6-14%%"
msgstr "Atlético: 6-14%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Excellent body composition typical of athletes. Associated with optimal "
"performance and health."
msgstr ""
"Excelente composición corporal propia de los deportistas. Asociado con un "
"óptimo rendimiento y salud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:386
#, python-format
msgid "Fitness: 14-18%%"
msgstr "Aptitud física: 14-18%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Good body composition for fitness enthusiasts. Indicates a healthy balance "
"of muscle and fat."
msgstr ""
"Buena composición corporal para los amantes del fitness. Indica un "
"equilibrio saludable de músculo y grasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:392
#, python-format
msgid "Average: 18-25%%"
msgstr "Promedio: 18-25%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Average body composition. Consider incorporating strength training and a "
"balanced diet to improve."
msgstr ""
"Composición corporal media. Considera incorporar entrenamiento de fuerza y "
"​​una dieta equilibrada para mejorar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:398
#, python-format
msgid "Above Average: ≥ 25%%"
msgstr "Por encima del promedio: ≥ 25%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is above average. Focus on strength training, cardio, "
"and a balanced diet."
msgstr ""
"El porcentaje de grasa corporal está por encima de la media. Concéntrese en "
"el entrenamiento de fuerza, el cardio y una dieta equilibrada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:414
msgid ""
"This calculator requires an accurate body fat percentage measurement. Use "
"body fat scales, calipers, DEXA scan, or other professional methods."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora requiere una medición precisa del porcentaje de grasa "
"corporal. Utilice básculas de grasa corporal, calibradores, escaneo DEXA u "
"otros métodos profesionales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"LBM includes water weight, which can fluctuate. For more accurate muscle "
"mass tracking, consider using additional methods like DEXA scans."
msgstr ""
"LBM incluye el peso del agua, que puede fluctuar. Para un seguimiento más "
"preciso de la masa muscular, considere utilizar métodos adicionales como las"
" exploraciones DEXA."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Protein recommendations are general guidelines. Individual needs may vary "
"based on goals, training intensity, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"Las recomendaciones de proteínas son pautas generales. Las necesidades "
"individuales pueden variar según los objetivos, la intensidad del "
"entrenamiento y otros factores."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Consult with healthcare professionals or registered dietitians for "
"personalized nutrition and fitness advice."
msgstr ""
"Consulte con profesionales de la salud o dietistas registrados para obtener "
"asesoramiento personalizado sobre nutrición y acondicionamiento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:31
msgid "Macro Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de macros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:5
msgid "Macronutrient Breakdown Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de descomposición de macronutrientes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your macronutrient breakdown from total calories. Get protein, "
"fat, and carbohydrate grams and percentages for your diet goals."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su desglose de macronutrientes a partir del total de calorías. "
"Obtenga gramos y porcentajes de proteínas, grasas y carbohidratos para sus "
"objetivos dietéticos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"macro calculator, macronutrient calculator, protein calculator, carb "
"calculator, fat calculator, macro split"
msgstr ""
"calculadora macro, calculadora de macronutrientes, calculadora de proteínas,"
" calculadora de carbohidratos, calculadora de grasas, división macro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Macronutrients"
msgstr "Calcular Macronutrientes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your macronutrient breakdown from total calories. Get protein, "
"fat, and carbohydrate grams."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su desglose de macronutrientes a partir del total de calorías. "
"Consuma gramos de proteínas, grasas y carbohidratos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate macronutrient breakdown from total calories"
msgstr ""
"Calcular la descomposición de macronutrientes a partir del total de calorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your macronutrient breakdown from total calories. Get detailed "
"protein, fat, and carbohydrate grams and percentages for your diet goals."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su desglose de macronutrientes a partir del total de calorías. "
"Obtenga gramos y porcentajes detallados de proteínas, grasas y carbohidratos"
" para sus objetivos dietéticos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:65
msgid "Macro Split"
msgstr "División macro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:85
msgid "Quick Presets"
msgstr "Preajustes rápidos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:87
msgid "Balanced"
msgstr "Equilibrado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:88
msgid "High Protein"
msgstr "Alta proteína"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:90
msgid "Keto"
msgstr "cetogénico"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:131
msgid "Carbohydrates"
msgstr "carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:161
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:582
msgid "Calculate Macros"
msgstr "Calcular macros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:195
msgid ""
"Enter your total calories and macro percentages, then click Calculate to see"
" your detailed macronutrient breakdown with charts and meal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus calorías totales y porcentajes de macro, luego haga clic en "
"Calcular para ver su desglose detallado de macronutrientes con gráficos y "
"distribución de comidas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:244
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:271
msgid "Macro Breakdown"
msgstr "Desglose de macros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:257
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:411
msgid "Macro Grams"
msgstr "Macrogramos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:304
msgid "Macro Split Category"
msgstr "Categoría de división macro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:325
msgid "What are Macronutrients?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los macronutrientes?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"Macronutrients (macros) are the three main nutrients your body needs in "
"large amounts: protein, carbohydrates, and fats. Each provides energy "
"(calories) and serves unique functions in your body."
msgstr ""
"Los macronutrientes (macros) son los tres nutrientes principales que tu "
"cuerpo necesita en grandes cantidades: proteínas, carbohidratos y grasas. "
"Cada uno proporciona energía (calorías) y cumple funciones únicas en su "
"cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:330
msgid "Total Calories = Protein + Fat + Carbs"
msgstr "Calorías totales = Proteínas + Grasas + Carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:333
msgid ""
"Protein and carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram, while fat provides 9 "
"calories per gram. Understanding your macro breakdown helps you optimize "
"your diet for your specific goals."
msgstr ""
"Las proteínas y los carbohidratos aportan 4 calorías por gramo, mientras que"
" las grasas aportan 9 calorías por gramo. Comprender su desglose macro le "
"ayuda a optimizar su dieta para sus objetivos específicos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:339
msgid "Macronutrient Functions"
msgstr "Funciones de los macronutrientes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:342
msgid "Protein (4 cal/g)"
msgstr "Proteína (4 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Essential for muscle building, repair, and maintenance. Supports immune "
"function, hormone production, and satiety. Recommended: 0.8-2.2g per kg body"
" weight depending on activity level."
msgstr ""
"Esencial para la construcción, reparación y mantenimiento de los músculos. "
"Apoya la función inmune, la producción de hormonas y la saciedad. "
"Recomendado: 0,8-2,2 g por kg de peso corporal según el nivel de actividad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:348
msgid "Fat (9 cal/g)"
msgstr "Grasa (9 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Provides energy, supports hormone production, aids vitamin absorption, and "
"protects organs. Essential for brain health. Recommended: 20-35%% of total "
"calories."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona energía, apoya la producción de hormonas, ayuda a la absorción "
"de vitaminas y protege los órganos. Esencial para la salud del cerebro. "
"Recomendado: 20-35%% del total de calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:354
msgid "Carbohydrates (4 cal/g)"
msgstr "Carbohidratos (4 cal/g)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:356
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Primary energy source for your body and brain. Supports exercise performance"
" and recovery. Recommended: 45-65%% of total calories for most people, lower"
" for low-carb diets."
msgstr ""
"Fuente de energía primaria para tu cuerpo y cerebro. Apoya el rendimiento "
"del ejercicio y la recuperación. Recomendado: 45-65%% del total de calorías "
"para la mayoría de las personas, menos para dietas bajas en carbohidratos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"Enter your total daily calorie target (use a TDEE calculator if unsure)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su objetivo total de calorías diarias (use una calculadora TDEE si "
"no está seguro)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:367
msgid "Use quick presets or manually adjust macro percentages using sliders"
msgstr ""
"Utilice ajustes preestablecidos rápidos o ajuste manualmente los porcentajes"
" macro mediante controles deslizantes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:368
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Ensure percentages sum to 100%% (the calculator will warn you if they don't)"
msgstr ""
"Asegúrese de que los porcentajes sumen 100%% (la calculadora le avisará si "
"no es así)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:369
msgid "Click 'Calculate Macros' to see your breakdown"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular macros' para ver su desglose"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:370
msgid "Review the charts and meal distribution recommendations"
msgstr "Revisar los gráficos y recomendaciones de distribución de comidas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:371
msgid "Adjust percentages based on your goals and preferences"
msgstr "Ajusta los porcentajes según tus objetivos y preferencias"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:377
msgid "Common Macro Splits"
msgstr "Divisiones macro comunes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:380
#, python-format
msgid "Balanced: 30%% Protein, 30%% Fat, 40%% Carbs"
msgstr "Equilibrado: 30%% proteína, 30%% grasa, 40%% carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Standard balanced diet suitable for most people. Good for general health and"
" maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Dieta equilibrada estándar adecuada para la mayoría de las personas. Bueno "
"para la salud general y el mantenimiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:386
#, python-format
msgid "High Protein: 40%% Protein, 30%% Fat, 30%% Carbs"
msgstr ""
"Alto contenido de proteínas: 40 % % de proteínas, 30 % % de grasas, 30 % % "
"de carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Ideal for muscle building, weight loss with muscle preservation, and "
"increased satiety."
msgstr ""
"Ideal para desarrollar músculo, perder peso con preservación muscular y "
"aumentar la saciedad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:392
#, python-format
msgid "Low Carb: 35%% Protein, 40%% Fat, 25%% Carbs"
msgstr ""
"Bajo en carbohidratos: 35%% de proteína, 40%% de grasa, 25%% de "
"carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Reduced carbohydrate intake. Good for weight loss, blood sugar control, and "
"some athletes."
msgstr ""
"Ingesta reducida de carbohidratos. Bueno para perder peso, controlar el "
"azúcar en sangre y para algunos atletas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:398
#, python-format
msgid "Ketogenic: 20%% Protein, 70%% Fat, 10%% Carbs"
msgstr "Cetogénico: 20%% proteína, 70%% grasa, 10%% carbohidratos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Very low carbohydrate, high fat diet. Promotes ketosis. Requires careful "
"planning and monitoring."
msgstr ""
"Dieta muy baja en carbohidratos y alta en grasas. Promueve la cetosis. "
"Requiere una cuidadosa planificación y seguimiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"The actual amount in grams you should consume daily. Use this for meal "
"planning and tracking."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad real en gramos que debes consumir diariamente. Úselo para "
"planificar y realizar un seguimiento de las comidas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:417
msgid "Macro Calories"
msgstr "Macrocalorías"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"The calories contributed by each macronutrient. These should sum to your "
"total daily calories."
msgstr ""
"Las calorías aportadas por cada macronutriente. Estos deberían sumar el "
"total de calorías diarias."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:425
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested breakdown across meals: Breakfast (25%%), Lunch (35%%), Dinner "
"(30%%), Snacks (10%%). Adjust based on your schedule and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Desglose sugerido por comidas: Desayuno (25%%), Almuerzo (35%%), Cena "
"(30%%), Meriendas (10%%). Ajústelo según su horario y preferencias."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:439
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Macro percentages must sum to exactly 100%%. The calculator will warn you if"
" they don't."
msgstr ""
"Los porcentajes macro deben sumar exactamente 100%%. La calculadora le "
"avisará si no es así."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Optimal macro splits vary based on goals, activity level, body composition, "
"and individual preferences."
msgstr ""
"Las macrodivisiones óptimas varían según los objetivos, el nivel de "
"actividad, la composición corporal y las preferencias individuales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:451
msgid ""
"Meal distribution is a suggestion. Adjust timing based on your schedule, "
"training, and preferences."
msgstr ""
"La distribución de comidas es una sugerencia. Ajuste el tiempo según su "
"horario, entrenamiento y preferencias."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:457
msgid ""
"Consult with registered dietitians or nutritionists for personalized macro "
"recommendations, especially for specific health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Consulte con dietistas o nutricionistas registrados para obtener macro "
"recomendaciones personalizadas, especialmente para condiciones de salud "
"específicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:518
#, python-format
msgid "Percentages must sum to 100%%"
msgstr "Los porcentajes deben sumar 100%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:41
msgid "One Rep Max Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora máxima de una repetición"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:117
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:501
msgid "Calculate 1RM"
msgstr "Calcular 1RM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your one rep max (1RM) using multiple proven formulas. Includes "
"training percentages, rep estimates, and comprehensive strength analysis."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su repetición máxima (1RM) utilizando múltiples fórmulas "
"comprobadas. Incluye porcentajes de entrenamiento, estimaciones de "
"repeticiones y análisis completo de fuerza."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"one rep max calculator, 1RM calculator, max strength calculator, training "
"percentages, strength calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de una repetición máxima, calculadora de 1RM, calculadora de "
"fuerza máxima, porcentajes de entrenamiento, calculadora de fuerza"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your one rep max using multiple proven formulas."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su máximo de una repetición usando múltiples fórmulas comprobadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate one rep max using multiple formulas"
msgstr "Calcula una repetición máxima usando múltiples fórmulas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Estimate your one rep max (1RM) using multiple proven formulas. Get training"
" percentages, rep estimates, and comprehensive strength analysis."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su repetición máxima (1RM) utilizando múltiples fórmulas "
"comprobadas. Obtenga porcentajes de entrenamiento, estimaciones de "
"repeticiones y análisis de fuerza completos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:65
msgid "Your Lift"
msgstr "Tu ascensor"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:175
msgid "Weight Lifted"
msgstr "peso levantado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:96
msgid "Enter the weight you lifted"
msgstr "Ingresa el peso que levantaste"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:101
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:181
msgid "Reps Performed"
msgstr "Repeticiones realizadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:107
msgid "Range: 1-30 reps"
msgstr "Rango: 1-30 repeticiones"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:151
msgid ""
"Enter the weight you lifted and the number of reps performed, then click "
"Calculate to see your estimated one rep max with detailed analysis."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el peso que levantó y la cantidad de repeticiones realizadas, luego "
"haga clic en Calcular para ver su repetición máxima estimada con un análisis"
" detallado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:161
msgid "Estimated One Rep Max"
msgstr "Máximo estimado de una repetición"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:164
msgid "Average of all formulas"
msgstr "Promedio de todas las fórmulas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:195
msgid "1RM Gauge"
msgstr "Calibre 1RM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:222
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:231
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:347
msgid "Training Percentages"
msgstr "Porcentajes de formación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:239
msgid "Estimated Max Reps at Different Percentages"
msgstr "Repeticiones máximas estimadas en diferentes porcentajes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:247
msgid "Strength Level Category"
msgstr "Categoría de nivel de fuerza"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:268
msgid "What is One Rep Max (1RM)?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una repetición máxima (1RM)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:270
msgid ""
"One Rep Max (1RM) is the maximum amount of weight you can lift for a single "
"repetition of a given exercise. It's a fundamental metric in strength "
"training used to:"
msgstr ""
"One Rep Max (1RM) es la cantidad máxima de peso que puedes levantar para una"
" sola repetición de un ejercicio determinado. Es una métrica fundamental en "
"el entrenamiento de fuerza que se utiliza para:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:273
msgid "Determine training intensities (percentages of 1RM)"
msgstr "Determinar las intensidades del entrenamiento (porcentajes de 1RM)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:274
msgid "Track strength progress over time"
msgstr "Seguimiento del progreso de la fuerza a lo largo del tiempo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:275
msgid "Design periodized training programs"
msgstr "Diseñar programas de entrenamiento periodizados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:276
msgid "Compare strength levels"
msgstr "Comparar niveles de fuerza"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:279
msgid ""
"Since testing your true 1RM can be dangerous and requires proper "
"preparation, calculators use formulas to estimate it based on submaximal "
"lifts (lighter weights for multiple reps)."
msgstr ""
"Dado que probar tu verdadero 1RM puede ser peligroso y requiere una "
"preparación adecuada, las calculadoras usan fórmulas para estimarlo "
"basándose en levantamientos submáximos (pesos más livianos para múltiples "
"repeticiones)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:285
msgid "1RM Calculation Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de cálculo de 1RM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:288
msgid "Brzycki Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula de Brzycki"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:290
msgid "Most popular formula. Generally accurate for 1-10 reps."
msgstr "Fórmula más popular. Generalmente preciso para 1-10 repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:293
msgid "Epley Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula Epley"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:295
msgid "Simple and widely used. Good for moderate rep ranges."
msgstr ""
"Sencillo y ampliamente utilizado. Bueno para rangos de repeticiones "
"moderados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:298
msgid "Lombardi Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula Lombardi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:300
msgid "Power-based formula. Works well for higher rep ranges."
msgstr ""
"Fórmula basada en el poder. Funciona bien para rangos de repeticiones más "
"altos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:303
msgid "O'Conner Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula de O'Conner"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:305
msgid "Conservative estimate. Good for beginners."
msgstr "Estimación conservadora. Bueno para principiantes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:308
msgid "Mayhew Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula Mayhew"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:310
msgid "Exponential formula. Accurate across wide rep ranges."
msgstr "Fórmula exponencial. Preciso en amplios rangos de repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:313
msgid "Wathan Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula Wathan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:315
msgid "Another exponential formula. Good alternative to Mayhew."
msgstr "Otra fórmula exponencial. Buena alternativa a Mayhew."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"The calculator uses the average of all formulas for the most accurate "
"estimate. Different formulas may give slightly different results, which is "
"why using multiple formulas and averaging provides the best estimate."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora utiliza el promedio de todas las fórmulas para obtener la "
"estimación más precisa. Diferentes fórmulas pueden dar resultados "
"ligeramente diferentes, por lo que usar varias fórmulas y promediar "
"proporciona la mejor estimación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:327
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:398
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:450
msgid "Select your unit system (Metric or Imperial)"
msgstr "Seleccione su sistema de unidades (Métrico o Imperial)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:328
msgid ""
"Enter the weight you successfully lifted (use a weight you can lift for the "
"specified reps with good form)"
msgstr ""
"Ingresa el peso que levantaste exitosamente (usa un peso que puedas levantar"
" para las repeticiones especificadas con buena forma)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:329
msgid "Enter the number of reps you performed (1-30 reps)"
msgstr "Ingrese el número de repeticiones que realizó (1-30 repeticiones)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:330
msgid "Click 'Calculate 1RM' to see your estimated one rep max"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular 1RM' para ver su repetición máxima estimada"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:331
msgid "Review the training percentages and rep estimates for program design"
msgstr ""
"Revisar los porcentajes de entrenamiento y las estimaciones de "
"representantes para el diseño del programa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:332
msgid "Use the results to plan your training intensities"
msgstr ""
"Utilice los resultados para planificar sus intensidades de entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:341
msgid "Estimated 1RM"
msgstr "1RM estimado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"The average of all formulas. This is your best estimate of your true one rep"
" max. Use this as your reference point for training."
msgstr ""
"El promedio de todas las fórmulas. Esta es tu mejor estimación de tu "
"verdadero máximo de una repetición. Utilice esto como punto de referencia "
"para el entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:349
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The weight you should lift at different percentages of your 1RM. Common "
"training zones: 50-60%% (endurance), 70-80%% (hypertrophy), 85-95%% "
"(strength), 100%% (maximal strength)."
msgstr ""
"El peso que debes levantar en diferentes porcentajes de tu 1RM. Zonas de "
"entrenamiento habituales: 50-60%% (resistencia), 70-80%% (hipertrofia), "
"85-95%% (fuerza), 100%% (fuerza máxima)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:353
msgid "Estimated Max Reps"
msgstr "Repeticiones máximas estimadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:355
msgid ""
"Approximate number of reps you could perform at different percentages of "
"your 1RM. Useful for rep-based training programs."
msgstr ""
"Número aproximado de repeticiones que podrías realizar con diferentes "
"porcentajes de tu 1RM. Útil para programas de entrenamiento basados ​​en "
"repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:359
msgid "Formula Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de fórmulas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Shows how different formulas estimate your 1RM. The range gives you an idea "
"of the uncertainty in the estimate."
msgstr ""
"Muestra cómo diferentes fórmulas estiman tu 1RM. El rango le da una idea de "
"la incertidumbre en la estimación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:369
msgid "Training Zones by Percentage"
msgstr "Zonas de entrenamiento por porcentaje"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:372
#, python-format
msgid "50-60%%: Endurance Zone"
msgstr "50-60%%: Zona de resistencia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"High volume, low intensity. Builds muscular endurance and work capacity. "
"12-20+ reps."
msgstr ""
"Alto volumen, baja intensidad. Desarrolla la resistencia muscular y la "
"capacidad de trabajo. 12-20+ repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:378
#, python-format
msgid "70-80%%: Hypertrophy Zone"
msgstr "70-80%%: Zona de Hipertrofia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:380
msgid "Moderate volume and intensity. Optimal for muscle growth. 8-12 reps."
msgstr ""
"Volumen e intensidad moderados. Óptimo para el crecimiento muscular. 8-12 "
"repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:384
#, python-format
msgid "85-95%%: Strength Zone"
msgstr "85-95%%: Zona de Fuerza"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:386
msgid "High intensity, lower volume. Builds maximal strength. 1-5 reps."
msgstr ""
"Alta intensidad, menor volumen. Desarrolla la máxima fuerza. 1-5 "
"repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:390
#, python-format
msgid "95-100%%: Maximal Strength"
msgstr "95-100%%: Fuerza máxima"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:392
msgid "Peak intensity. Used sparingly for testing or peaking. 1 rep only."
msgstr ""
"Intensidad máxima. Se usa con moderación para pruebas o picos. 1 repetición "
"solamente."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"1RM estimates are most accurate when using 1-10 reps. Accuracy decreases "
"with higher rep counts."
msgstr ""
"Las estimaciones de 1RM son más precisas cuando se utilizan de 1 a 10 "
"repeticiones. La precisión disminuye con un mayor número de repeticiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"Always use a weight you can lift with proper form. Poor form leads to "
"inaccurate estimates and injury risk."
msgstr ""
"Utilice siempre un peso que pueda levantar con la forma adecuada. Una mala "
"forma conduce a estimaciones inexactas y a riesgo de lesiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:418
msgid ""
"1RM varies by exercise. Bench press, squat, and deadlift will have different"
" 1RMs. Calculate separately for each."
msgstr ""
"1RM varía según el ejercicio. El press de banca, la sentadilla y el peso "
"muerto tendrán 1RM diferentes. Calcule por separado para cada uno."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/one_rep_max_calculator.html:424
msgid ""
"If you want to test your true 1RM, do so with proper warm-up, spotters, and "
"safety equipment. Consider working with a qualified strength coach."
msgstr ""
"Si desea probar su verdadero 1RM, hágalo con un calentamiento adecuado, "
"observadores y equipo de seguridad. Considere trabajar con un entrenador de "
"fuerza calificado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:24
msgid "Overweight Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de sobrepeso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:5
msgid "BMI Assessment & Weight Analysis"
msgstr "Evaluación del IMC y análisis de peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate BMI and determine if you are overweight. Get detailed assessment, "
"ideal weight range, and recommendations for healthy weight management."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el IMC y determine si tiene sobrepeso. Obtenga una evaluación "
"detallada, un rango de peso ideal y recomendaciones para un control de peso "
"saludable."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"overweight calculator, BMI calculator, weight assessment, obesity "
"calculator, healthy weight"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de sobrepeso, calculadora de IMC, evaluación de peso, "
"calculadora de obesidad, peso saludable"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:14
msgid "BMI Assessment"
msgstr "Evaluación del IMC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate BMI and determine if you are overweight."
msgstr "Calcule el IMC y determine si tiene sobrepeso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate BMI and determine if overweight"
msgstr "Calcula el IMC y determina si tienes sobrepeso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your BMI and determine if you are overweight. Get detailed "
"assessment, ideal weight range, and personalized recommendations for healthy"
" weight management."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu IMC y determina si tienes sobrepeso. Obtenga una evaluación "
"detallada, un rango de peso ideal y recomendaciones personalizadas para un "
"control de peso saludable."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:171
msgid ""
"Enter your height and weight, then click Calculate to see your BMI "
"assessment with detailed analysis, ideal weight range, and recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su altura y peso, luego haga clic en Calcular para ver su evaluación"
" de IMC con análisis detallado, rango de peso ideal y recomendaciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:194
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:110
msgid "Current Weight"
msgstr "Peso actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:200
msgid "Ideal Range"
msgstr "Rango ideal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:206
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:624
msgid "Weight to Lose"
msgstr "Peso para perder"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:247
msgid "Weight Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:285
msgid "Assessment Details"
msgstr "Detalles de la evaluación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:306
msgid "What Does It Mean to Be Overweight?"
msgstr "¿Qué significa tener sobrepeso?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:308
msgid ""
"Being overweight means having a Body Mass Index (BMI) of 25 or higher. BMI "
"is calculated using your weight and height to estimate body fat. While BMI "
"is a useful screening tool, it doesn't directly measure body fat or account "
"for muscle mass."
msgstr ""
"Tener sobrepeso significa tener un índice de masa corporal (IMC) de 25 o "
"más. El IMC se calcula utilizando su peso y altura para estimar la grasa "
"corporal. Si bien el IMC es una herramienta de detección útil, no mide "
"directamente la grasa corporal ni tiene en cuenta la masa muscular."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:314
msgid ""
"BMI categories: Underweight (<18.5), Normal Weight (18.5-24.9), Overweight "
"(25-29.9), Obese (≥30). Being overweight or obese increases the risk of "
"various health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Categorías de IMC: Bajo peso (<18,5), Peso normal (18,5-24,9), Sobrepeso "
"(25-29,9), Obesidad (≥30). El sobrepeso o la obesidad aumentan el riesgo de "
"sufrir diversas afecciones de salud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"Includes severe thinness (<16), moderate thinness (16-17), and mild thinness"
" (17-18.5). May need to gain weight. Consult with a healthcare provider."
msgstr ""
"Incluye delgadez severa (<16), delgadez moderada (16-17) y delgadez leve "
"(17-18,5). Es posible que necesite aumentar de peso. Consulte con un "
"proveedor de atención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Healthy weight range. Continue maintaining a balanced diet and regular "
"physical activity."
msgstr ""
"Rango de peso saludable. Continúe manteniendo una dieta equilibrada y "
"actividad física regular."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"Above healthy weight range. Consider a balanced diet and regular exercise to"
" reach a healthy weight."
msgstr ""
"Por encima del rango de peso saludable. Considere una dieta equilibrada y "
"ejercicio regular para alcanzar un peso saludable."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Includes Obese Class I (30-35), Class II (35-40), and Class III (>40). "
"Consult with healthcare professionals for a comprehensive weight management "
"plan."
msgstr ""
"Incluye Obesos Clase I (30-35), Clase II (35-40) y Clase III (>40). Consulte"
" con profesionales de la salud para obtener un plan integral de control de "
"peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:356
msgid "Click 'Calculate BMI' to see your assessment"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular IMC' para ver su evaluación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:357
msgid "Review your BMI, category, and ideal weight range"
msgstr "Revisa tu IMC, categoría y rango de peso ideal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:358
msgid "Check the weight you need to lose or gain to reach healthy range"
msgstr ""
"Comprueba el peso que necesitas perder o ganar para alcanzar un rango "
"saludable"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:359
msgid "Read the comprehensive guide for interpretation and recommendations"
msgstr "Lea la guía completa de interpretación y recomendaciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:370
msgid ""
"Your calculated Body Mass Index. This number is used to categorize your "
"weight status."
msgstr ""
"Su índice de masa corporal calculado. Este número se utiliza para "
"categorizar su estado de peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Your weight status based on WHO BMI classification. Categories range from "
"Underweight to Obese Class III."
msgstr ""
"Su estado de peso según la clasificación del IMC de la OMS. Las categorías "
"van desde bajo peso hasta obesidad clase III."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"The weight range (BMI 18.5-24.9) considered healthy for your height. This is"
" your target range for optimal health."
msgstr ""
"El rango de peso (IMC 18,5-24,9) considerado saludable para tu altura. Este "
"es su rango objetivo para una salud óptima."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:386
msgid "Weight to Lose/Gain"
msgstr "Peso para perder/ganar"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"The amount of weight you need to lose (if overweight) or gain (if "
"underweight) to reach the healthy weight range."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad de peso que necesita perder (si tiene sobrepeso) o ganar (si "
"tiene bajo peso) para alcanzar el rango de peso saludable."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:396
msgid "Health Risks of Being Overweight"
msgstr "Riesgos para la salud por tener sobrepeso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:398
msgid "Being overweight or obese increases the risk of:"
msgstr "El sobrepeso o la obesidad aumentan el riesgo de:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:400
msgid "Type 2 diabetes"
msgstr "diabetes tipo 2"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:401
msgid "High blood pressure and heart disease"
msgstr "Presión arterial alta y enfermedades cardíacas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:403
msgid "Certain types of cancer"
msgstr "Ciertos tipos de cáncer"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:405
msgid "Osteoarthritis"
msgstr "Osteoartritis"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:406
msgid "Fatty liver disease"
msgstr "Enfermedad del hígado graso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:407
msgid "Kidney disease"
msgstr "Nefropatía"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:417
msgid "Balanced Diet"
msgstr "Alimentación equilibrada"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"Focus on whole foods, fruits, vegetables, lean proteins, and whole grains. "
"Control portion sizes and reduce processed foods."
msgstr ""
"Concéntrese en alimentos integrales, frutas, verduras, proteínas magras y "
"cereales integrales. Controle el tamaño de las porciones y reduzca los "
"alimentos procesados."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:423
msgid "Regular Exercise"
msgstr "Ejercicio regular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Aim for at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity exercise per week. "
"Include both cardio and strength training."
msgstr ""
"Intente realizar al menos 150 minutos de ejercicio de intensidad moderada "
"por semana. Incluye entrenamiento cardiovascular y de fuerza."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:429
msgid "Lifestyle Changes"
msgstr "Cambios en el estilo de vida"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"Get adequate sleep, manage stress, stay hydrated, and make sustainable "
"changes rather than quick fixes."
msgstr ""
"Duerma lo suficiente, controle el estrés, manténgase hidratado y realice "
"cambios sostenibles en lugar de soluciones rápidas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"BMI is a screening tool, not a diagnostic measure. It doesn't account for "
"muscle mass, bone density, or body composition."
msgstr ""
"El IMC es una herramienta de detección, no una medida de diagnóstico. No "
"tiene en cuenta la masa muscular, la densidad ósea ni la composición "
"corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:451
msgid ""
"Athletes or individuals with high muscle mass may have higher BMIs that "
"don't reflect excess fat."
msgstr ""
"Los atletas o personas con una gran masa muscular pueden tener un IMC más "
"alto que no refleja un exceso de grasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:457
msgid ""
"Weight loss should be gradual (0.5-1 kg or 1-2 lbs per week) for sustainable"
" results and health."
msgstr ""
"La pérdida de peso debe ser gradual (0,5 a 1 kg o 1 a 2 libras por semana) "
"para obtener resultados y salud sostenibles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"If you're concerned about your weight or BMI, please consult with qualified "
"healthcare professionals or registered dietitians for personalized advice."
msgstr ""
"Si le preocupa su peso o IMC, consulte con profesionales de la salud "
"calificados o dietistas registrados para obtener asesoramiento "
"personalizado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:633
msgid "Healthy"
msgstr "Saludable"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:46
msgid "Ovulation Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:5
msgid "Calculate Ovulation Date & Fertile Window"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de ovulación y la ventana fértil"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your ovulation date and fertile window based on your menstrual "
"cycle. Get detailed cycle analysis and fertility predictions."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu fecha de ovulación y ventana fértil en función de tu ciclo "
"menstrual. Obtenga análisis detallados del ciclo y predicciones de "
"fertilidad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"ovulation calculator, fertile window, ovulation date, menstrual cycle "
"calculator, fertility calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de ovulación, ventana fértil, fecha de ovulación, calculadora de"
" ciclo menstrual, calculadora de fertilidad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Ovulation Date"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your ovulation date and fertile window based on your menstrual "
"cycle."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu fecha de ovulación y ventana fértil en función de tu ciclo "
"menstrual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate ovulation date and fertile window"
msgstr "Calcular fecha de ovulación y ventana fértil"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your ovulation date and fertile window based on your menstrual "
"cycle. Get detailed cycle analysis, fertility predictions, and personalized "
"recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu fecha de ovulación y ventana fértil en función de tu ciclo "
"menstrual. Obtenga análisis detallados del ciclo, predicciones de fertilidad"
" y recomendaciones personalizadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:65
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:65
msgid "Cycle Information"
msgstr "Información del ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:73
msgid "Last Period Date"
msgstr "Fecha del último período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:77
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:77
msgid "First day of your last menstrual period"
msgstr "Primer día de su último período menstrual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:104
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:112
msgid "Range: 21-35 days (average: 28 days)"
msgstr "Rango: 21-35 días (promedio: 28 días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:99
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:457
msgid "Calculate Ovulation"
msgstr "Calcular la ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:133
msgid ""
"Enter your last period date and cycle length, then click Calculate to see "
"your ovulation date, fertile window, and detailed cycle analysis."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la fecha de su último período y la duración del ciclo, luego haga "
"clic en Calcular para ver la fecha de ovulación, la ventana fértil y el "
"análisis detallado del ciclo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:143
msgid "Predicted Ovulation Date"
msgstr "Fecha prevista de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:156
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:330
