msgstr "Próximo período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:170
msgid "Cycle Day"
msgstr "Día del ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:185
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:225
msgid "Phase Distribution"
msgstr "Distribución de fases"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:198
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:342
msgid "Fertility Probability"
msgstr "Probabilidad de fertilidad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:212
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:336
msgid "Cycle Timeline"
msgstr "Cronograma del ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:220
msgid "Menstruation"
msgstr "Menstruación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:224
msgid "Follicular"
msgstr "folicular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:228
msgid "Fertile"
msgstr "Fértil"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:232
msgid "Luteal"
msgstr "lútea"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:239
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:269
msgid "Current Cycle Phase"
msgstr "Fase del ciclo actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:260
msgid "What is Ovulation?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la ovulación?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:262
msgid ""
"Ovulation is the process in which a mature egg is released from one of the "
"ovaries. This typically occurs once per menstrual cycle, approximately 14 "
"days before the start of your next period. The egg travels down the "
"fallopian tube where it can be fertilized by sperm."
msgstr ""
"La ovulación es el proceso en el que un óvulo maduro se libera de uno de los"
" ovarios. Esto suele ocurrir una vez por ciclo menstrual, aproximadamente 14"
" días antes del inicio de su próximo período. El óvulo viaja por las trompas"
" de Falopio donde puede ser fertilizado por los espermatozoides."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:265
msgid ""
"Understanding when you ovulate is crucial for both conception planning and "
"natural family planning. The fertile window includes the days leading up to "
"and including ovulation, when conception is most likely to occur."
msgstr ""
"Comprender cuándo ovulas es crucial tanto para la planificación de la "
"concepción como para la planificación familiar natural. La ventana fértil "
"incluye los días previos a la ovulación inclusive, cuando es más probable "
"que se produzca la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:271
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:301
msgid "Menstrual Cycle Phases"
msgstr "Fases del ciclo menstrual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:274
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:304
msgid "Menstruation (Days 1-5)"
msgstr "Menstruación (días 1-5)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:276
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"The uterine lining is shed. This marks day 1 of your cycle. Typically lasts "
"3-7 days."
msgstr ""
"Se desprende el revestimiento del útero. Esto marca el día 1 de tu ciclo. "
"Normalmente dura de 3 a 7 días."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:280
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:310
msgid "Follicular Phase (Days 1-13)"
msgstr "Fase folicular (días 1-13)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:282
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"Follicles in the ovaries begin to mature. Estrogen levels rise, preparing "
"the uterine lining for potential pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Los folículos de los ovarios comienzan a madurar. Los niveles de estrógeno "
"aumentan, preparando el revestimiento del útero para un posible embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:286
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:316
msgid "Ovulation (Day 14, approximately)"
msgstr "Ovulación (Día 14, aproximadamente)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:288
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"A mature egg is released from the ovary. This is your most fertile day. The "
"egg survives for 12-24 hours after release."
msgstr ""
"Del ovario se libera un óvulo maduro. Este es tu día más fértil. El huevo "
"sobrevive entre 12 y 24 horas después de su liberación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:292
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:322
msgid "Fertile Window (5 days before + ovulation + 1 day after)"
msgstr "Ventana Fértil (5 días antes + ovulación + 1 día después)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:294
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"The best time for conception. Sperm can survive up to 5 days in the female "
"reproductive tract, so having intercourse in the days leading up to "
"ovulation increases chances of conception."
msgstr ""
"El mejor momento para la concepción. Los espermatozoides pueden sobrevivir "
"hasta 5 días en el tracto reproductivo femenino, por lo que tener relaciones"
" sexuales en los días previos a la ovulación aumenta las posibilidades de "
"concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:298
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:328
msgid "Luteal Phase (Days 15-28)"
msgstr "Fase lútea (días 15-28)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:300
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"After ovulation, the corpus luteum produces progesterone. If pregnancy "
"doesn't occur, hormone levels drop and menstruation begins."
msgstr ""
"Después de la ovulación, el cuerpo lúteo produce progesterona. Si no se "
"produce el embarazo, los niveles hormonales bajan y comienza la "
"menstruación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:310
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Enter the first day of your last menstrual period (the day bleeding started)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese el primer día de su último período menstrual (el día que comenzó el "
"sangrado)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:311
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:341
msgid ""
"Enter your average cycle length (number of days from day 1 of one period to "
"day 1 of the next)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la duración promedio de su ciclo (número de días desde el día 1 de "
"un período hasta el día 1 del siguiente)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:312
msgid "Click 'Calculate Ovulation' to see your predicted ovulation date"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular ovulación' para ver la fecha de ovulación prevista"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:313
msgid "Review your fertile window (the best days for conception)"
msgstr "Revisa tu ventana fértil (los mejores días para la concepción)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:314
msgid "Check the cycle timeline to see all phases of your cycle"
msgstr ""
"Consulta el cronograma del ciclo para ver todas las fases de tu ciclo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:315
msgid ""
"Use the fertility probability chart to understand your peak fertility days"
msgstr ""
"Utilice la tabla de probabilidad de fertilidad para comprender sus días de "
"mayor fertilidad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:324
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:206
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:360
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:237
msgid "Ovulation Date"
msgstr "Fecha de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:326
msgid ""
"The predicted day when ovulation occurs. This is calculated as 14 days "
"before your next expected period. This is your most fertile day."
msgstr ""
"El día previsto en el que se produce la ovulación. Esto se calcula como 14 "
"días antes de su próximo período esperado. Este es tu día más fértil."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:332
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Sperm can survive "
"up to 5 days, so having intercourse during this window maximizes chances of "
"conception."
msgstr ""
"El período de 6 a 7 días en el que es más probable la concepción. Esto "
"incluye 5 días antes de la ovulación, el día de la ovulación y 1 día "
"después. Los espermatozoides pueden sobrevivir hasta 5 días, por lo que "
"tener relaciones sexuales durante este período maximiza las posibilidades de"
" concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"A visual representation of your entire cycle showing all phases: "
"menstruation, follicular, fertile window, ovulation, and luteal phase."
msgstr ""
"Una representación visual de todo tu ciclo que muestra todas las fases: "
"menstruación, folicular, ventana fértil, ovulación y fase lútea."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Shows the estimated probability of conception on each day of your cycle. "
"Peak fertility occurs on ovulation day and the days immediately before it."
msgstr ""
"Muestra la probabilidad estimada de concepción en cada día de tu ciclo. La "
"fertilidad máxima ocurre el día de la ovulación y los días inmediatamente "
"anteriores."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:352
msgid "Signs of Ovulation"
msgstr "Signos de ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:354
msgid "Common signs that ovulation may be occurring:"
msgstr "Signos comunes de que puede estar ocurriendo la ovulación:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:356
msgid "Change in cervical mucus (becomes clear, stretchy, like egg white)"
msgstr ""
"Cambio en el moco cervical (se vuelve claro, elástico, como clara de huevo)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:357
msgid "Slight increase in basal body temperature"
msgstr "Ligero aumento de la temperatura corporal basal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:358
msgid "Mild pelvic or abdominal pain (mittelschmerz)"
msgstr "Dolor pélvico o abdominal leve"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:359
msgid "Increased libido"
msgstr "aumento de la libido"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:360
msgid "Positive ovulation predictor kit (OPK) result"
msgstr "Resultado positivo del kit de predicción de ovulación (OPK)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:373
msgid ""
"Ovulation calculators provide estimates based on average cycle patterns. "
"Actual ovulation timing can vary due to stress, illness, travel, or hormonal"
" changes."
msgstr ""
"Las calculadoras de ovulación proporcionan estimaciones basadas en patrones "
"de ciclo promedio. El momento real de la ovulación puede variar debido al "
"estrés, enfermedades, viajes o cambios hormonales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:379
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"For more accurate tracking, combine calendar method with other methods like "
"basal body temperature (BBT) charting, cervical mucus monitoring, or "
"ovulation predictor kits."
msgstr ""
"Para un seguimiento más preciso, combine el método del calendario con otros "
"métodos, como los gráficos de la temperatura corporal basal (TBC), la "
"monitorización del moco cervical o los kits de predicción de la ovulación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"If you have irregular cycles, PCOS, or other reproductive health concerns, "
"consult with a healthcare provider or fertility specialist for personalized "
"guidance."
msgstr ""
"Si tiene ciclos irregulares, síndrome de ovario poliquístico u otros "
"problemas de salud reproductiva, consulte con un proveedor de atención "
"médica o un especialista en fertilidad para obtener orientación "
"personalizada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare providers for "
"fertility planning and reproductive health concerns."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" consejo médico profesional. Consulte siempre a los proveedores de atención "
"médica si tiene dudas sobre la planificación de la fertilidad y la salud "
"reproductiva."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:516
msgid "Today!"
msgstr "¡Hoy!"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:518
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:546
msgid "days away"
msgstr "días de distancia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/ovulation_calculator.html:520
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/date_calculator.html:470
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:495
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:495
msgid "days ago"
msgstr "hace dias"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:42
msgid "Pace Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de ritmo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:5
msgid "Calculate Running Pace & Speed"
msgstr "Calcular el ritmo y la velocidad de carrera"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate running or cycling pace from distance and time. Convert between "
"pace per km and pace per mile. Get speed conversions and race time "
"predictions."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el ritmo de carrera o ciclismo a partir de la distancia y el tiempo."
" Convierta entre ritmo por km y ritmo por milla. Obtenga conversiones de "
"velocidad y predicciones de tiempo de carrera."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pace calculator, running pace, running speed, race pace calculator, marathon"
" pace calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de ritmo, ritmo de carrera, velocidad de carrera, calculadora de"
" ritmo de carrera, calculadora de ritmo de maratón"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Running Pace"
msgstr "Calcular el ritmo de carrera"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate running or cycling pace from distance and time."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el ritmo de carrera o ciclismo a partir de la distancia y el tiempo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate running pace and speed"
msgstr "Calcular el ritmo y la velocidad de carrera."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your running or cycling pace from distance and time. Convert "
"between pace per km and pace per mile. Get speed conversions and race time "
"predictions for common distances."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu ritmo de carrera o ciclismo a partir de la distancia y el tiempo."
" Convierta entre ritmo por km y ritmo por milla. Obtenga conversiones de "
"velocidad y predicciones de tiempo de carrera para distancias comunes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:65
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:101
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/average_calculator.html:115
