#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:246
msgid "Pace Gauge"
msgstr "Indicador de ritmo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:259
msgid "Speed Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de velocidad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:273
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:396
msgid "Race Time Predictions"
msgstr "Predicciones de tiempo de carrera"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:282
msgid "Common Race Distances"
msgstr "Distancias de carrera comunes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:290
msgid "Pace Category"
msgstr "Categoría de ritmo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:311
msgid "What is Running Pace?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el ritmo de carrera?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Running pace is the time it takes to cover a specific distance, typically "
"expressed as minutes per kilometer (min/km) or minutes per mile (min/mi). "
"It's a fundamental metric for runners to track performance, plan training, "
"and predict race times."
msgstr ""
"El ritmo de carrera es el tiempo que se tarda en cubrir una distancia "
"específica, normalmente expresado en minutos por kilómetro (min/km) o "
"minutos por milla (min/mi). Es una métrica fundamental para que los "
"corredores realicen un seguimiento del rendimiento, planifiquen el "
"entrenamiento y predigan los tiempos de la carrera."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:316
msgid "Pace = Time ÷ Distance"
msgstr "Ritmo = Tiempo ÷ Distancia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"For example, if you run 5 kilometers in 30 minutes, your pace is 6 minutes "
"per kilometer (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, si corres 5 kilómetros en 30 minutos, tu ritmo es de 6 minutos "
"por kilómetro (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:325
msgid "Pace Categories"
msgstr "Categorías de ritmo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:328
msgid "Elite: &lt; 3:30 min/km"
msgstr "Élite: &lt; 3:30min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:330
msgid "World-class performance. Professional and elite competitive runners."
msgstr ""
"Rendimiento de clase mundial. Corredores competitivos profesionales y de "
"élite."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:334
msgid "Advanced: 3:30-4:00 min/km"
msgstr "Avanzado: 3:30-4:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Excellent performance. Highly trained runners with years of experience."
msgstr ""
"Excelente rendimiento. Corredores altamente capacitados con años de "
"experiencia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:340
msgid "Intermediate: 4:00-5:00 min/km"
msgstr "Intermedio: 4:00-5:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:342
msgid "Good fitness level. Regular runners with consistent training."
msgstr ""
"Buen nivel de condición física. Corredores habituales con entrenamiento "
"constante."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:346
msgid "Recreational: 5:00-6:00 min/km"
msgstr "Recreativo: 5:00-6:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:348
msgid "Healthy activity level. Casual runners maintaining fitness."
msgstr ""
"Nivel de actividad saludable. Corredores casuales que mantienen su forma "
"física."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:352
msgid "Beginner: 6:00-7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Principiante: 6:00-7:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:354
msgid "Building fitness. New runners or those returning to running."
msgstr "Desarrollar la aptitud. Corredores nuevos o que vuelven a correr."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:358
msgid "Walking: &gt; 7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Caminar: &gt; 7:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:360
msgid "Walking pace. Great for health, recovery, and active rest."
msgstr ""
"Ritmo de marcha. Excelente para la salud, la recuperación y el descanso "
"activo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:370
msgid "Select calculation type: 'Pace from Time' or 'Time from Pace'"
msgstr ""
"Seleccione el tipo de cálculo: 'Ritmo a partir del tiempo' o 'Tiempo a "
"partir del ritmo'"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:371
msgid "Choose your distance unit (kilometers or miles)"
msgstr "Elija su unidad de distancia (kilómetros o millas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:372
msgid "Enter your distance and time (or pace)"
msgstr "Introduce tu distancia y tiempo (o ritmo)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:374
msgid "Review your pace, speed, and race time predictions"
msgstr "Revisa tus predicciones de ritmo, velocidad y tiempo de carrera."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:375
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your performance"
msgstr "Utilice los gráficos para visualizar su rendimiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:384
msgid "Pace per Kilometer/Mile"
msgstr "Paso por kilómetro/milla"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"The time it takes to run one kilometer or one mile. Lower numbers mean "
"faster pace. Displayed as minutes:seconds per unit distance."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo que se tarda en correr un kilómetro o una milla. Números más bajos"
" significan un ritmo más rápido. Se muestra como minutos:segundos por unidad"
" de distancia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:390
msgid "Speed (km/h or mph)"
msgstr "Velocidad (km/h o mph)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"Your average running speed. Calculated as distance divided by time. Useful "
"for comparing with other activities like cycling or driving."
msgstr ""
"Tu velocidad promedio de carrera. Calculado como distancia dividida por "
"tiempo. Útil para comparar con otras actividades como andar en bicicleta o "
"conducir."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"Estimated finish times for common race distances (1km, 5km, 10km, half "
"marathon, marathon) based on your current pace. Useful for goal setting and "
"race planning."
msgstr ""
"Tiempos de finalización estimados para distancias de carrera comunes (1 km, "
"5 km, 10 km, media maratón, maratón) según tu ritmo actual. Útil para "
"establecer objetivos y planificar carreras."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:406
msgid "Training Tips"
msgstr "Consejos de entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:409
msgid "Consistent Training"
msgstr "Entrenamiento consistente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:411
msgid ""
"Regular running improves pace over time. Aim for 3-4 runs per week with "
"gradual distance increases."
msgstr ""
"Correr regularmente mejora el ritmo con el tiempo. Intente realizar de 3 a 4"
" carreras por semana con aumentos graduales de distancia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:415
msgid "Interval Training"
msgstr "Entrenamiento por intervalos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:417
msgid ""
"Incorporate speed work (intervals, tempo runs) to improve pace. Mix fast and"
" slow runs for balanced training."
msgstr ""
"Incorporar trabajo de velocidad (intervalos, carreras de tempo) para mejorar"
" el ritmo. Mezcla carreras rápidas y lentas para un entrenamiento "
"equilibrado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:421
msgid "Recovery"
msgstr "Recuperación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:423
msgid ""
"Allow adequate rest between hard runs. Recovery is essential for improvement"
" and injury prevention."
msgstr ""
"Permita un descanso adecuado entre carreras intensas. La recuperación es "
"fundamental para la mejora y la prevención de lesiones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Pace varies with terrain, weather, elevation, and fitness level. Use this "
"calculator as a guide, not an absolute measure."
msgstr ""
"El ritmo varía según el terreno, el clima, la elevación y el nivel de "
"condición física. Utilice esta calculadora como guía, no como medida "
"absoluta."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:443
msgid ""
"Race time predictions assume you can maintain the same pace for longer "
"distances, which may not always be realistic. Adjust expectations based on "
"your training."
msgstr ""
"Las predicciones de tiempo de carrera suponen que puedes mantener el mismo "
"ritmo en distancias más largas, lo que no siempre es realista. Ajusta las "
"expectativas en función de tu formación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"For accurate pace tracking, use GPS watches, running apps, or measured "
"courses. Manual calculations are estimates."
msgstr ""
"Para realizar un seguimiento preciso del ritmo, utilice relojes GPS, "
"aplicaciones para correr o recorridos medidos. Los cálculos manuales son "
"estimaciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Always listen to your body. If you experience pain or excessive fatigue, "
"rest and consult with healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Escucha siempre a tu cuerpo. Si experimenta dolor o fatiga excesiva, "
"descanse y consulte con profesionales sanitarios."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:631
msgid "1 km"
msgstr "1 kilometro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:632
msgid "5 km"
msgstr "5 kilometros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:633
msgid "10 km"
msgstr "10 kilometros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:634
msgid "Half Marathon"
msgstr "Media Maratón"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:635
msgid "Marathon"
msgstr "Maratón"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:677
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:642
#: Other_Calculators/views/hours_calculator.py:807
msgid "Total Time"
msgstr "Tiempo total"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:51
msgid "Period Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de periodo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:14
msgid "Menstrual Cycle Tracker"
msgstr "Rastreador del ciclo menstrual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period. Free period "
"calculator with ovulation and fertile window predictions."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de su ciclo menstrual y prediga su próximo período. "
"Calculadora de período gratuita con predicciones de ovulación y ventana "
"fértil."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"period calculator, menstrual cycle calculator, period tracker, ovulation "
"calculator, fertile window"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de período, calculadora de ciclo menstrual, rastreador de "
"período, calculadora de ovulación, ventana fértil"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de su ciclo menstrual y prediga las fechas de su "
"próximo período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:24
msgid "Track menstrual cycle and predict next period dates"
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento del ciclo menstrual y prediga las fechas del próximo "
"período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates, ovulation, "
"and fertile window. Get comprehensive cycle analysis and personalized "
"predictions."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de su ciclo menstrual y prediga las fechas de su "
"próximo período, ovulación y ventana fértil. Obtenga análisis de ciclo "
"completo y predicciones personalizadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:73
msgid "Last Period Start Date"
msgstr "Fecha de inicio del último período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:94
msgid "Period Length"
msgstr "Duración del período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:101
msgid "Range: 2-7 days (average: 5 days)"
msgstr "Rango: 2-7 días (promedio: 5 días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:145
msgid ""
"Enter your cycle information to see predictions for your next periods, "
"ovulation dates, fertile windows, and comprehensive cycle analysis."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la información de su ciclo para ver predicciones para sus próximos "
"períodos, fechas de ovulación, ventanas fértiles y un análisis completo del "
"ciclo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:168
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:372
msgid "Current Cycle Day"
msgstr "Día del ciclo actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:175
msgid "Days Until Period"
msgstr "Días hasta el período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:181
msgid "Days Until Ovulation"
msgstr "Días hasta la ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:193
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/date_calculator.html:92
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:90
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:179
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:179
msgid "Start Date"
msgstr "Fecha de inicio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:203
msgid "Ovulation & Fertile Window"
msgstr "Ovulación y ventana fértil"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:238
msgid "Cycle Progress"
msgstr "Progreso del ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:252
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:261
msgid "Upcoming Cycles"
msgstr "Próximos ciclos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:290
msgid "What is the Menstrual Cycle?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el ciclo menstrual?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"The menstrual cycle is a natural process that occurs in the female "
"reproductive system, typically lasting 21-35 days (average 28 days). It "
"involves hormonal changes that prepare the body for potential pregnancy each"
" month."
msgstr ""
"El ciclo menstrual es un proceso natural que ocurre en el sistema "
"reproductivo femenino y generalmente dura entre 21 y 35 días (un promedio de"
" 28 días). Implica cambios hormonales que preparan al cuerpo para un posible"
" embarazo cada mes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"The cycle begins on the first day of menstruation (period) and ends the day "
"before the next period starts. Understanding your cycle helps with fertility"
" planning, health monitoring, and predicting period dates."
msgstr ""
"El ciclo comienza el primer día de la menstruación (período) y finaliza el "
"día antes de que comience el siguiente período. Comprender su ciclo ayuda "
"con la planificación de la fertilidad, el control de la salud y la "
"predicción de las fechas del período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Enter your average period length (how many days your period typically lasts)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la duración promedio de su período (cuántos días dura normalmente su"
" período)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see predictions for your next periods, ovulation dates,"
" and fertile windows"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver predicciones para sus próximos períodos, "
"fechas de ovulación y ventanas fértiles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:344
msgid "Review the cycle calendar and phase distribution charts"
msgstr ""
"Revisar el calendario de ciclos y los cuadros de distribución de fases."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:345
msgid "Use the predictions to plan ahead and track your cycle"
msgstr ""
"Utilice las predicciones para planificar con anticipación y realizar un "
"seguimiento de su ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:356
msgid ""
"Predicted start and end dates for your next menstrual period based on your "
"cycle length and last period date."
msgstr ""
"Fechas de inicio y finalización previstas para su próximo período menstrual "
"según la duración de su ciclo y la fecha del último período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Estimated date when ovulation occurs (typically 14 days before your next "
"period). This is your most fertile day."
msgstr ""
"Fecha estimada en la que se produce la ovulación (normalmente 14 días antes "
"de su próximo período). Este es tu día más fértil."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after."
msgstr ""
"El período de 6 a 7 días en el que es más probable la concepción. Esto "
"incluye 5 días antes de la ovulación, el día de la ovulación y 1 día "
"después."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Shows which day of your current cycle you are on. Day 1 is the first day of "
"your last period."
msgstr ""
"Muestra en qué día de tu ciclo actual te encuentras. El día 1 es el primer "
"día de su último período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:382
msgid "Cycle Tracking Tips"
msgstr "Consejos para el seguimiento del ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:385
msgid "Consistent Tracking"
msgstr "Seguimiento consistente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"Track your period start dates for at least 3-6 months to get an accurate "
"average cycle length. Mark dates on a calendar or use a period tracking app."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de las fechas de inicio de su período durante al "
"menos 3 a 6 meses para obtener una duración promedio precisa del ciclo. "
"Marque las fechas en un calendario o utilice una aplicación de seguimiento "
"del período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:391
msgid "Note Symptoms"
msgstr "Nota síntomas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Track symptoms like cramps, mood changes, and flow intensity. This helps "
"identify patterns and can be useful for healthcare consultations."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de síntomas como calambres, cambios de humor e "
"intensidad del flujo. Esto ayuda a identificar patrones y puede resultar "
"útil para consultas de atención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:397
msgid "Irregular Cycles"
msgstr "Ciclos irregulares"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:399
msgid ""
"If your cycles are very irregular (varying by more than 7 days), consider "
"consulting with a healthcare provider. Irregular cycles can indicate "
"underlying health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Si sus ciclos son muy irregulares (varian en más de 7 días), considere "
"consultar con un proveedor de atención médica. Los ciclos irregulares pueden"
" indicar problemas de salud subyacentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Period calculators provide estimates based on average cycle patterns. Actual"
" timing can vary due to stress, illness, travel, hormonal changes, or "
"medical conditions."
msgstr ""
"Las calculadoras de períodos proporcionan estimaciones basadas en patrones "
"de ciclo promedio. El tiempo real puede variar debido al estrés, "
"enfermedades, viajes, cambios hormonales o condiciones médicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"If you have irregular cycles, PCOS, endometriosis, or other reproductive "
"health concerns, consult with a healthcare provider or gynecologist for "
"personalized guidance."
msgstr ""
"Si tiene ciclos irregulares, síndrome de ovario poliquístico, endometriosis "
"u otros problemas de salud reproductiva, consulte con un proveedor de "
"atención médica o un ginecólogo para obtener orientación personalizada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare providers for "
"reproductive health concerns, fertility planning, or if you experience "
"unusual symptoms."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" consejo médico profesional. Siempre consulte a sus proveedores de atención "
"médica si tiene problemas de salud reproductiva, planificación de fertilidad"
" o si experimenta síntomas inusuales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:556
msgid "complete"
msgstr "completo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:608
msgid "Cycle"
msgstr "Ciclo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:611
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Período"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:615
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:364
msgid "Ovulation"
msgstr "Ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:48
msgid "Pregnancy Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:14
msgid "Comprehensive Pregnancy Tracker"
msgstr "Seguimiento integral del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Track your pregnancy with our comprehensive calculator. Calculate due date, "
"weeks pregnant, trimester, milestones, and appointments."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de su embarazo con nuestra calculadora completa. "
"Calcule la fecha de parto, semanas de embarazo, trimestre, hitos y citas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pregnancy calculator, pregnancy tracker, due date calculator, weeks "
"pregnant, trimester calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de embarazo, rastreador de embarazo, calculadora de fecha de "
"parto, semanas de embarazo, calculadora de trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your pregnancy with comprehensive calculations and milestones."
msgstr "Realice un seguimiento de su embarazo con cálculos e hitos completos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:24
msgid "Comprehensive pregnancy tracking and calculations"
msgstr "Seguimiento y cálculos completos del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Track your pregnancy with comprehensive calculations. Calculate due date, "
"weeks pregnant, trimester, fetal development milestones, and upcoming "
"appointments."
msgstr ""
"Realice un seguimiento de su embarazo con cálculos completos. Calcule la "
"fecha de parto, las semanas de embarazo, el trimestre, los hitos del "
"desarrollo fetal y las próximas citas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:65
msgid "Pregnancy Information"
msgstr "Información sobre el embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:162
msgid ""
"Enter your pregnancy information using any calculation method, then click "
"Calculate to see comprehensive tracking details including due date, weeks "
"pregnant, trimester, milestones, and appointments."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la información de su embarazo usando cualquier método de cálculo, "
"luego haga clic en Calcular para ver detalles completos de seguimiento, "
"incluida la fecha de parto, las semanas de embarazo, el trimestre, los hitos"
" y las citas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:246
msgid "Milestones Progress"
msgstr "Progreso de los hitos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:262
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:294
msgid "Trimester Progress"
msgstr "Progreso trimestral"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:275
msgid "Weeks Progress"
msgstr "Semanas de progreso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:285
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:392
msgid "Fetal Development Milestones"
msgstr "Hitos del desarrollo fetal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:293
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:398
msgid "Upcoming Appointments"
msgstr "Próximas citas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:322
msgid "What is a Pregnancy Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una calculadora de embarazo?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"A pregnancy calculator helps you track your pregnancy journey by calculating"
" important dates, milestones, and providing information about fetal "
"development. It uses your last menstrual period (LMP), conception date, or "
"due date to estimate how far along you are in your pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Una calculadora de embarazo la ayuda a realizar un seguimiento de su "
"embarazo calculando fechas importantes, hitos y brindando información sobre "
"el desarrollo fetal. Utiliza su último período menstrual (FUM), la fecha de "
"concepción o la fecha de parto para estimar en qué etapa del embarazo se "
"encuentra."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is typically calculated as 40 weeks (280 days) from the first day "
"of your last menstrual period, or 38 weeks (266 days) from conception. This "
"calculator provides comprehensive tracking throughout all three trimesters."
msgstr ""
"El embarazo generalmente se calcula en 40 semanas (280 días) desde el primer"
" día de su último período menstrual, o 38 semanas (266 días) desde la "
"concepción. Esta calculadora proporciona un seguimiento completo durante los"
" tres trimestres."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:336
msgid "First Trimester (Weeks 1-12)"
msgstr "Primer trimestre (semanas 1 a 12)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"Early development phase. Baby's major organs and body systems are forming. "
"Important time for prenatal care, folic acid, and avoiding harmful "
"substances. Morning sickness and fatigue are common."
msgstr ""
"Fase temprana de desarrollo. Los principales órganos y sistemas corporales "
"del bebé se están formando. Momento importante para el cuidado prenatal, el "
"ácido fólico y evitar sustancias nocivas. Las náuseas matutinas y la fatiga "
"son comunes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:342
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 13-26)"
msgstr "Segundo trimestre (semanas 13 a 26)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Often called the 'golden period.' Baby is growing rapidly, and you may start"
" feeling movement. Energy levels typically improve. Anatomy scan usually "
"performed around week 20."
msgstr ""
"A menudo se le llama el \"período dorado\". El bebé está creciendo "
"rápidamente y es posible que usted comience a sentir movimiento. Los niveles"
" de energía suelen mejorar. La exploración de anatomía generalmente se "
"realiza alrededor de la semana 20."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:348
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:462
msgid "Third Trimester (Weeks 27-40)"
msgstr "Tercer trimestre (semanas 27 a 40)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"Final preparation phase. Baby is gaining weight and preparing for birth. "
"Regular checkups become more frequent. Braxton Hicks contractions may occur."
" Baby is considered full term at 37 weeks."
msgstr ""
"Fase de preparación final. El bebé está ganando peso y preparándose para "
"nacer. Los controles regulares se vuelven más frecuentes. Pueden ocurrir "
"contracciones de Braxton Hicks. El bebé se considera a término a las 37 "
"semanas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Last Menstrual Period (most common), "
"From Conception Date, or From Due Date"
msgstr ""
"Elija su método de cálculo: Desde la última menstruación (el más común), "
"Desde la fecha de concepción o Desde la fecha prevista"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:361
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:383
msgid "Enter the required date information based on your selected method"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la información de fecha requerida según el método seleccionado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"If using LMP method, enter your average cycle length (default is 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Si utiliza el método LMP, ingrese la duración promedio de su ciclo (el valor"
" predeterminado es 28 días)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:363
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see comprehensive pregnancy tracking information"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver información completa sobre el seguimiento "
"del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"Review your due date, weeks pregnant, trimester, milestones, and upcoming "
"appointments"
msgstr ""
"Revise su fecha de parto, semanas de embarazo, trimestre, hitos y próximas "
"citas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:376
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Estimated date of delivery (EDD). Calculated as 280 days (40 weeks) from the"
" first day of your last menstrual period. Only about 5%% of babies are born "
"exactly on their due date, but most are born within 2 weeks before or after."
msgstr ""
"Fecha estimada de entrega (EDD). Calculado como 280 días (40 semanas) desde "
"el primer día de su último período menstrual. Sólo alrededor del 5%% de los "
"bebés nacen exactamente en la fecha prevista, pero la mayoría nace dentro de"
" las 2 semanas anteriores o posteriores."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"How many weeks you are into your pregnancy. Pregnancy is counted from the "
"first day of your last menstrual period, not from conception. This is why "
"you're considered 2 weeks pregnant at conception."
msgstr ""
"Cuántas semanas llevas de embarazo. El embarazo se cuenta desde el primer "
"día de su último período menstrual, no desde la concepción. Es por eso que "
"se considera que tienes 2 semanas de embarazo en el momento de la "
"concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Which trimester you're currently in. Each trimester has different "
"characteristics, milestones, and care requirements."
msgstr ""
"En qué trimestre se encuentra actualmente. Cada trimestre tiene diferentes "
"características, hitos y requisitos de atención."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Key developmental stages your baby reaches at different weeks. These "
"milestones show what's happening with your baby's growth and development."
msgstr ""
"Etapas clave del desarrollo que alcanza su bebé en diferentes semanas. Estos"
" hitos muestran lo que está sucediendo con el crecimiento y desarrollo de su"
" bebé."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Typical prenatal care schedule. Regular checkups are essential for "
"monitoring your health and your baby's development. Your healthcare provider"
" may adjust this schedule based on your specific needs."
msgstr ""
"Horario típico de atención prenatal. Los chequeos periódicos son esenciales "
"para controlar su salud y el desarrollo de su bebé. Su proveedor de atención"
" médica puede ajustar este cronograma según sus necesidades específicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:408
msgid "Important Pregnancy Milestones"
msgstr "Hitos importantes del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:411
msgid "Week 4: Neural Tube Forms"
msgstr "Semana 4: Formas del tubo neural"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Neural tube begins to form, which will become the brain and spinal cord. "
"Heart begins to beat. Critical time for folic acid intake."
msgstr ""
"Comienza a formarse el tubo neural, que se convertirá en el cerebro y la "
"médula espinal. El corazón comienza a latir. Momento crítico para la ingesta"
" de ácido fólico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:417
msgid "Week 8: Major Organs Forming"
msgstr "Semana 8: Formación de órganos principales"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"All major organs are forming. Fingers and toes become visible. Baby is about"
" the size of a raspberry."
msgstr ""
"Todos los órganos principales se están formando. Los dedos de las manos y de"
" los pies se vuelven visibles. El bebé tiene aproximadamente el tamaño de "
"una frambuesa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:423
msgid "Week 20: Anatomy Scan"
msgstr "Semana 20: Exploración de anatomía"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Detailed ultrasound to check baby's anatomy. You may be able to find out the"
" baby's sex. Baby can swallow and hair begins to grow."
msgstr ""
"Ecografía detallada para comprobar la anatomía del bebé. Es posible que "
"pueda averiguar el sexo del bebé. El bebé puede tragar y el pelo empieza a "
"crecer."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:429
msgid "Week 24: Viability"
msgstr "Semana 24: Viabilidad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"Baby reaches viability - can potentially survive outside the womb with "
"medical assistance. Fingerprints are forming."
msgstr ""
"El bebé alcanza la viabilidad; potencialmente puede sobrevivir fuera del "
"útero con asistencia médica. Se están formando huellas dactilares."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:435
msgid "Week 37: Full Term"
msgstr "Semana 37: Término completo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Baby is considered full term. Lungs are mature. Baby is preparing for birth "
"and may move into head-down position."
msgstr ""
"El bebé se considera a término. Los pulmones están maduros. El bebé se está "
"preparando para nacer y es posible que se coloque boca abajo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:451
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates. Only about 5%% of babies are born exactly on their "
"due date. Most babies are born between 38-42 weeks."
msgstr ""
"Las fechas de vencimiento son estimaciones. Sólo alrededor del 5%% de los "
"bebés nacen exactamente en la fecha prevista. La mayoría de los bebés nacen "
"entre las 38 y 42 semanas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:457
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:469
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is calculated from the first day of your last menstrual period "
"(LMP), not from conception. This is why you're considered 2 weeks pregnant "
"at conception."
msgstr ""
"El embarazo se calcula a partir del primer día de su último período "
"menstrual (FUM), no desde la concepción. Es por eso que se considera que "
"tienes 2 semanas de embarazo en el momento de la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"Regular prenatal care is essential. Follow your healthcare provider's "
"recommended schedule for checkups, tests, and screenings."
msgstr ""
"La atención prenatal regular es esencial. Siga el cronograma recomendado por"
" su proveedor de atención médica para controles, pruebas y exámenes de "
"detección."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:469
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:481
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare "
"providers (OB/GYN, midwife, or family doctor) for pregnancy care, concerns, "
"or questions."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" consejo médico profesional. Siempre consulte con proveedores de atención "
"médica calificados (obstetra/ginecólogo, partera o médico de familia) si "
"tiene preguntas, inquietudes o atención durante el embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"If you experience any concerning symptoms (bleeding, severe pain, decreased "
"fetal movement after 28 weeks, etc.), contact your healthcare provider "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Si experimenta algún síntoma preocupante (sangrado, dolor intenso, "
"disminución del movimiento fetal después de 28 semanas, etc.), comuníquese "
"con su proveedor de atención médica de inmediato."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:701
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:720
msgid "Week"
msgstr "Semana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:49
msgid "Pregnancy Conception Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de concepción del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date and pregnancy timeline. Track fertile window,"
" ovulation, and implantation dates."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su fecha de concepción y cronograma de embarazo. Realice un "
"seguimiento de las fechas de ventana fértil, ovulación e implantación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pregnancy conception calculator, conception date, fertile window, ovulation "
"calculator, implantation"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de concepción embarazo, fecha de concepción, ventana fértil, "
"calculadora de ovulación, implantación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your conception date and track pregnancy timeline."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la fecha de su concepción y realice un seguimiento del cronograma "
"del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate conception date and pregnancy timeline"
msgstr "Calcular la fecha de concepción y el cronograma del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date and track important pregnancy milestones "
"including fertile window, ovulation, and implantation dates."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su fecha de concepción y realice un seguimiento de los hitos "
"importantes del embarazo, incluida la ventana fértil, la ovulación y las "
"fechas de implantación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:65
msgid "Calculate Conception"
msgstr "Calcular la concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:96
msgid "Estimated date of delivery"
msgstr "Fecha estimada de entrega"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:120
msgid "Date when conception occurred"
msgstr "Fecha en que ocurrió la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:164
msgid ""
"Enter your information using any calculation method, then click Calculate to"
" see your conception date, fertile window, ovulation, implantation dates, "
"and comprehensive pregnancy timeline."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su información usando cualquier método de cálculo, luego haga clic "
"en Calcular para ver su fecha de concepción, ventana fértil, ovulación, "
"fechas de implantación y cronograma completo del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:193
msgid "Weeks Since Conception"
msgstr "Semanas desde la concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:230
msgid "Fertile Window & Ovulation"
msgstr "Ventana fértil y ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:243
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:408
msgid "Implantation Window"
msgstr "Ventana de implantación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:246
msgid "Implantation Start"
msgstr "Inicio de implantación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:250
msgid "Implantation End"
msgstr "Fin de la implantación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:278
msgid "Weeks Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de semanas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:307
msgid "Conception Timeline"
msgstr "Cronología de la concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Conception occurs when a sperm fertilizes an egg, typically happening during"
" ovulation. This is the moment when pregnancy begins. The fertilized egg "
"then travels to the uterus and implants in the uterine lining, usually 6-12 "
"days after conception."
msgstr ""
"La concepción ocurre cuando un espermatozoide fertiliza un óvulo, lo que "
"generalmente ocurre durante la ovulación. Este es el momento en el que "
"comienza el embarazo. Luego, el óvulo fertilizado viaja al útero y se "
"implanta en el revestimiento del útero, generalmente entre 6 y 12 días "
"después de la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Understanding your conception date helps you track your pregnancy timeline "
"more accurately and provides insight into when important milestones occur."
msgstr ""
"Comprender la fecha de su concepción le ayuda a realizar un seguimiento del "
"cronograma de su embarazo con mayor precisión y le brinda información sobre "
"cuándo ocurren los hitos importantes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:349
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:510
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/prime_factorization_calculator.html:267
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:365
msgid "Key Concepts"
msgstr "Conceptos clave"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"The date when the sperm fertilized the egg. This typically occurs during "
"ovulation, approximately 14 days after the start of your last menstrual "
"period (for a 28-day cycle)."
msgstr ""
"La fecha en que el espermatozoide fecundó al óvulo. Esto suele ocurrir "
"durante la ovulación, aproximadamente 14 días después del inicio de su "
"último período menstrual (para un ciclo de 28 días)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. Includes 5 days before "
"ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Sperm can survive up to 5 "
"days in the female reproductive tract."
msgstr ""
"El período de 6 a 7 días en el que es más probable la concepción. Incluye 5 "
"días antes de la ovulación, el día de la ovulación y 1 día después. Los "
"espermatozoides pueden sobrevivir hasta 5 días en el tracto reproductivo "
"femenino."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"The release of a mature egg from the ovary. This is your most fertile day. "
"The egg survives for 12-24 hours after release, so timing intercourse around"
" ovulation is crucial for conception."
msgstr ""
"La liberación de un óvulo maduro del ovario. Este es tu día más fértil. El "
"óvulo sobrevive entre 12 y 24 horas después de su liberación, por lo que "
"programar las relaciones sexuales alrededor de la ovulación es crucial para "
"la concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:370
msgid "Implantation"
msgstr "Implantación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:372
msgid ""
"When the fertilized egg attaches to the uterine lining. This typically "
"occurs 6-12 days after conception. Implantation bleeding (light spotting) "
"may occur but is not always present."
msgstr ""
"Cuando el óvulo fertilizado se adhiere al revestimiento del útero. Esto "
"suele ocurrir entre 6 y 12 días después de la concepción. Puede producirse "
"sangrado de implantación (manchado leve), pero no siempre está presente."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Due Date, From Last Menstrual Period, "
"or From Conception Date"
msgstr ""
"Elija su método de cálculo: Desde la fecha de parto, Desde la última "
"menstruación o Desde la fecha de concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see your conception date and comprehensive timeline"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver la fecha de su concepción y el cronograma "
"completo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"Review fertile window, ovulation date, implantation window, and pregnancy "
"status"
msgstr ""
"Revisar la ventana fértil, la fecha de ovulación, la ventana de implantación"
" y el estado del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:387
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your pregnancy progress and timeline"
msgstr ""
"Utilice los gráficos para visualizar el progreso y el cronograma de su "
"embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception occurred. This is calculated based on "
"your due date, LMP, or known conception date. Conception typically occurs "
"during ovulation, approximately 14 days after the start of your last period."
msgstr ""
"La fecha estimada en que ocurrió la concepción. Esto se calcula en función "
"de su fecha de parto, FUM o fecha de concepción conocida. La concepción "
"suele ocurrir durante la ovulación, aproximadamente 14 días después del "
"inicio de su último período."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception was most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Having intercourse "
"during this window maximizes chances of conception."
msgstr ""
"El período de 6 a 7 días en el que era más probable la concepción. Esto "
"incluye 5 días antes de la ovulación, el día de la ovulación y 1 día "
"después. Tener relaciones sexuales durante esta ventana maximiza las "
"posibilidades de concepción."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"The period when the fertilized egg typically implants in the uterine lining "
"(6-12 days after conception). Some women may experience light spotting "
"during this time, known as implantation bleeding."
msgstr ""
"El período en el que el óvulo fertilizado normalmente se implanta en el "
"revestimiento del útero (6 a 12 días después de la concepción). Algunas "
"mujeres pueden experimentar un ligero manchado durante este tiempo, conocido"
" como sangrado de implantación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:414
msgid "Weeks Pregnant vs Weeks Since Conception"
msgstr "Semanas de embarazo versus semanas desde la concepción"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is counted from the first day of your last menstrual period (LMP),"
" not from conception. This is why you're considered 2 weeks pregnant at "
"conception. Weeks since conception is the actual time since fertilization "
"occurred."
msgstr ""
"El embarazo se cuenta desde el primer día de su último período menstrual "
"(FUM), no desde la concepción. Es por eso que se considera que tienes 2 "
"semanas de embarazo en el momento de la concepción. Las semanas desde la "
"concepción son el tiempo real desde que se produjo la fertilización."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:429
msgid "Last Menstrual Period (LMP) - Day 1 of pregnancy"
msgstr "Último período menstrual (FUM): día 1 de embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:433
msgid "Fertile Window Begins - 5 days before ovulation"
msgstr "Comienza la ventana fértil: 5 días antes de la ovulación"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:437
msgid "Ovulation - Release of mature egg (most fertile day)"
msgstr "Ovulación: liberación del óvulo maduro (día más fértil)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:441
msgid "Conception - Sperm fertilizes egg (typically on ovulation day)"
msgstr ""
"Concepción: el espermatozoide fertiliza el óvulo (normalmente el día de la "
"ovulación)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Implantation - Fertilized egg attaches to uterus (6-12 days after "
"conception)"
msgstr ""
"Implantación: el óvulo fertilizado se adhiere al útero (6 a 12 días después "
"de la concepción)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:449
msgid "Due Date - Approximately 266 days from conception or 280 days from LMP"
msgstr ""
"Fecha de vencimiento: aproximadamente 266 días desde la concepción o 280 "
"días desde la FUM"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"Conception dates are estimates. The exact moment of conception cannot be "
"determined with certainty, but it typically occurs during the fertile "
"window, most likely on or near the day of ovulation."
msgstr ""
"Las fechas de concepción son estimaciones. El momento exacto de la "
"concepción no se puede determinar con certeza, pero generalmente ocurre "
"durante la ventana fértil, probablemente en el día de la ovulación o cerca "
"de él."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"Implantation bleeding is light spotting that may occur 6-12 days after "
"conception. Not all women experience this, and it's different from menstrual"
" bleeding."
msgstr ""
"El sangrado de implantación es un manchado leve que puede ocurrir entre 6 y "
"12 días después de la concepción. No todas las mujeres experimentan esto y "
"es diferente al sangrado menstrual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:50
msgid "Pregnancy Weight Gain Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de aumento de peso durante el embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:14
msgid "Track Healthy Weight Gain"
msgstr "Seguimiento del aumento de peso saludable"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate recommended pregnancy weight gain based on your pre-pregnancy BMI."
" Track your weight gain progress throughout pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el aumento de peso recomendado durante el embarazo en función de su "
"IMC antes del embarazo. Realice un seguimiento del progreso de su aumento de"
" peso durante el embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pregnancy weight gain calculator, pregnancy weight tracker, BMI pregnancy, "
"healthy weight gain pregnancy"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de aumento de peso durante el embarazo, rastreador de peso del "
"embarazo, IMC durante el embarazo, aumento de peso saludable durante el "
"embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate recommended pregnancy weight gain based on your pre-pregnancy BMI."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el aumento de peso recomendado durante el embarazo en función de su "
"IMC antes del embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate recommended pregnancy weight gain based on BMI"
msgstr ""
"Calcule el aumento de peso recomendado durante el embarazo según el IMC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate recommended pregnancy weight gain based on your pre-pregnancy BMI "
"and track your progress throughout pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el aumento de peso recomendado durante el embarazo en función de su "
"IMC antes del embarazo y realice un seguimiento de su progreso durante el "
"embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:65
msgid "Weight Information"
msgstr "Información de peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:77
msgid "Metric (kg, cm)"
msgstr "Métrico (kg, cm)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:81
msgid "Imperial (lbs, in)"
msgstr "Imperial (libras, pulgadas)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:88
msgid "Pre-Pregnancy Weight"
msgstr "Peso antes del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:117
msgid "Leave empty if pre-pregnancy"
msgstr "Dejar vacío si antes del embarazo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:169
msgid ""
"Enter your pre-pregnancy weight, height, and current pregnancy status to see"
" recommended weight gain ranges based on your BMI category."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su peso, altura y estado actual del embarazo antes del embarazo para"
" ver los rangos de aumento de peso recomendados según su categoría de IMC."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:179
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:321
msgid "Weight Gain Status"
msgstr "Estado de aumento de peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:191
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:218
msgid "Current Gain"
msgstr "Ganancia actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:197
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:222
msgid "Expected Gain"
msgstr "Ganancia esperada"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:226
msgid "Expected Weight"
msgstr "Peso esperado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:233
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:419
msgid "Recommended Total Weight Gain Range"
msgstr "Rango de aumento de peso total recomendado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:250
msgid "Weight Gain Progress"
msgstr "Progreso del aumento de peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:279
msgid "Gain Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de ganancias"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:292
msgid "Trimester Weights"
msgstr "Pesos trimestrales"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:302
msgid "Expected Weight by Trimester"
msgstr "Peso esperado por trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:305
msgid "First Trimester"
msgstr "primer trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:309
msgid "Second Trimester"
msgstr "Segundo trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:313
msgid "Third Trimester"
msgstr "Tercer trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:342
msgid "What is Healthy Pregnancy Weight Gain?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el aumento de peso saludable durante el embarazo?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Healthy weight gain during pregnancy is essential for both maternal and "
"fetal health. The recommended amount of weight gain depends on your pre-"
"pregnancy Body Mass Index (BMI). Weight gain supports your baby's growth, "
"placenta development, increased blood volume, and prepares your body for "
"breastfeeding."
msgstr ""
"El aumento de peso saludable durante el embarazo es esencial para la salud "
"materna y fetal. La cantidad recomendada de aumento de peso depende de su "
"índice de masa corporal (IMC) antes del embarazo. El aumento de peso "
"favorece el crecimiento de su bebé, el desarrollo de la placenta, el aumento"
" del volumen sanguíneo y prepara su cuerpo para la lactancia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:347
msgid ""
"The Institute of Medicine (IOM) provides guidelines for weight gain based on"
" pre-pregnancy BMI categories. These recommendations help ensure optimal "
"outcomes for both you and your baby."
msgstr ""
"El Instituto de Medicina (IOM) proporciona pautas para el aumento de peso "
"según las categorías de IMC previas al embarazo. Estas recomendaciones "
"ayudan a garantizar resultados óptimos tanto para usted como para su bebé."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:353
msgid "Weight Gain by BMI Category"
msgstr "Aumento de peso por categoría de IMC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:358
msgid "Recommended gain: 12.5-18 kg (28-40 lbs)"
msgstr "Ganancia recomendada: 12,5-18 kg (28-40 lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Higher weight gain is recommended to support healthy fetal development and "
"maternal health. Focus on nutrient-dense foods and regular meals."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda un mayor aumento de peso para favorecer el desarrollo fetal "
"saludable y la salud materna. Concéntrese en alimentos ricos en nutrientes y"
" comidas regulares."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:367
msgid "Recommended gain: 11.5-16 kg (25-35 lbs)"
msgstr "Ganancia recomendada: 11,5-16 kg (25-35 lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:370
msgid ""
"Standard weight gain recommendations apply. Focus on balanced nutrition, "
"regular physical activity, and gradual weight gain throughout pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Se aplican las recomendaciones estándar de aumento de peso. Concéntrese en "
"una nutrición equilibrada, actividad física regular y aumento de peso "
"gradual durante el embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:376
msgid "Recommended gain: 7-11.5 kg (15-25 lbs)"
msgstr "Ganancia recomendada: 7-11,5 kg (15-25 lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Moderate weight gain recommended. Focus on nutrient-dense foods, portion "
"control, and regular physical activity as approved by your healthcare "
"provider."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda un aumento de peso moderado. Concéntrese en alimentos ricos en"
" nutrientes, control de las porciones y actividad física regular según lo "
"aprobado por su proveedor de atención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:385
msgid "Recommended gain: 5-9 kg (11-20 lbs)"
msgstr "Ganancia recomendada: 5-9 kg (11-20 lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Lower weight gain recommended. Consult with your healthcare provider for "
"personalized guidance. Focus on quality nutrition and appropriate physical "
"activity."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda un menor aumento de peso. Consulte con su proveedor de "
"atención médica para obtener orientación personalizada. Centrarse en una "
"nutrición de calidad y una actividad física adecuada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:399
msgid "Enter your pre-pregnancy weight (weight before becoming pregnant)"
msgstr "Ingrese su peso antes del embarazo (peso antes de quedar embarazada)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:400
msgid "Enter your height"
msgstr "Introduce tu altura"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:401
msgid ""
"Enter your current weight (if you're already pregnant, otherwise leave as "
"pre-pregnancy weight)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su peso actual (si ya está embarazada, de lo contrario déjelo como "
"peso previo al embarazo)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:402
msgid "Enter how many weeks pregnant you are (0 if pre-pregnancy)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese cuántas semanas de embarazo tiene (0 si estaba antes del embarazo)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see recommended weight gain ranges and track your "
"progress"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver los rangos de aumento de peso recomendados "
"y realizar un seguimiento de su progreso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"Review the charts to visualize your weight gain progress and compare with "
"recommendations"
msgstr ""
"Revise los gráficos para visualizar el progreso de su aumento de peso y "
"compararlo con las recomendaciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:413
msgid "BMI Category"
msgstr "Categoría de IMC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"Your pre-pregnancy BMI category determines the recommended weight gain "
"range. BMI is calculated using your pre-pregnancy weight and height."
msgstr ""
"Su categoría de IMC antes del embarazo determina el rango de aumento de peso"
" recomendado. El IMC se calcula utilizando su peso y altura antes del "
"embarazo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:421
msgid ""
"The total amount of weight you should gain throughout your entire pregnancy,"
" based on your pre-pregnancy BMI. This is a range, and individual needs may "
"vary."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad total de peso que debes ganar durante todo el embarazo, según tu"
" IMC antes del embarazo. Este es un rango y las necesidades individuales "
"pueden variar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:425
msgid "Current vs Expected Gain"
msgstr "Ganancia actual versus esperada"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:427
msgid ""
"Compare your current weight gain with the expected gain for your current "
"week of pregnancy. This helps you track if you're on target."
msgstr ""
"Compare su aumento de peso actual con el aumento esperado para la semana "
"actual de embarazo. Esto le ayuda a realizar un seguimiento si está en el "
"objetivo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:431
msgid "Weight Gain by Trimester"
msgstr "Aumento de peso por trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:433
msgid ""
"Weight gain patterns vary by trimester. First trimester typically sees "
"minimal gain (0.5-2 kg), while second and third trimesters see more "
"consistent weekly gains."
msgstr ""
"Los patrones de aumento de peso varían según el trimestre. Por lo general, "
"en el primer trimestre se observa un aumento mínimo (0,5 a 2 kg), mientras "
"que en el segundo y tercer trimestre se observan aumentos semanales más "
"consistentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:437
msgid "Status Assessment"
msgstr "Evaluación de estado"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:439
msgid ""
"Your status indicates whether your current weight gain is on track, below, "
"or above recommendations. Always discuss significant deviations with your "
"healthcare provider."
msgstr ""
"Su estado indica si su aumento de peso actual va por buen camino, está por "
"debajo o por encima de las recomendaciones. Siempre discuta las desviaciones"
" significativas con su proveedor de atención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:447
msgid "Weight Gain Patterns by Trimester"
msgstr "Patrones de aumento de peso por trimestre"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Minimal weight gain: 0.5-2 kg (1-4 lbs). Some women may even lose weight due"
" to morning sickness. Focus on staying hydrated and eating small, frequent "
"meals."
msgstr ""
"Aumento de peso mínimo: 0,5 a 2 kg (1 a 4 libras). Algunas mujeres pueden "
"incluso perder peso debido a las náuseas matutinas. Concéntrese en "
"mantenerse hidratado y comer comidas pequeñas y frecuentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:456
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 14-26)"
msgstr "Segundo trimestre (semanas 14 a 26)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"Steady weight gain: approximately 0.35-0.5 kg (0.8-1 lb) per week for normal"
" weight women. Baby is growing rapidly, and your body is preparing for "
"delivery."
msgstr ""
"Aumento de peso constante: aproximadamente 0,35 a 0,5 kg (0,8 a 1 libra) por"
" semana para mujeres de peso normal. El bebé está creciendo rápidamente y su"
" cuerpo se está preparando para el parto."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"Continued steady gain: similar to second trimester. Baby is gaining weight, "
"and your body is storing nutrients for breastfeeding. Weight gain may slow "
"slightly near the end."
msgstr ""
"Aumento constante y continuo: similar al segundo trimestre. El bebé está "
"aumentando de peso y su cuerpo está almacenando nutrientes para la "
"lactancia. El aumento de peso puede disminuir ligeramente hacia el final."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:478
msgid ""
"These are general guidelines. Individual needs may vary based on multiple "
"factors including age, activity level, medical conditions, and multiple "
"pregnancies."
msgstr ""
"Estas son pautas generales. Las necesidades individuales pueden variar según"
" múltiples factores, incluidos la edad, el nivel de actividad, las "
"afecciones médicas y los embarazos múltiples."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"Weight gain is not linear. It's normal to have weeks with more or less gain."
" Focus on overall trends rather than day-to-day fluctuations."
msgstr ""
"El aumento de peso no es lineal. Es normal tener semanas con mayor o menor "
"ganancia. Concéntrese en las tendencias generales en lugar de las "
"fluctuaciones del día a día."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:490
msgid ""
"Quality of nutrition matters more than quantity. Focus on nutrient-dense "
"foods: fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats."
msgstr ""
"La calidad de la nutrición importa más que la cantidad. Concéntrese en "
"alimentos ricos en nutrientes: frutas, verduras, cereales integrales, "
"proteínas magras y grasas saludables."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:496
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare "
"providers (OB/GYN, midwife, or registered dietitian) for personalized "
"guidance on pregnancy nutrition and weight management."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" consejo médico profesional. Consulte siempre con proveedores de atención "
"médica calificados (obstetra/ginecólogo, partera o dietista registrado) para"
" obtener orientación personalizada sobre nutrición durante el embarazo y "
"control de peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:502
msgid ""
"If you have concerns about your weight gain, significant deviations from "
"recommendations, or medical conditions affecting weight, discuss with your "
"healthcare provider immediately."
msgstr ""
"Si le preocupa su aumento de peso, desviaciones significativas de las "
"recomendaciones o condiciones médicas que afectan el peso, hable con su "
"proveedor de atención médica de inmediato."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:36
msgid "Protein Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:5
msgid "Daily Protein Needs Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de necesidades diarias de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals. Get personalized protein recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus necesidades diarias de proteínas según el peso corporal, el "
"nivel de actividad y los objetivos de acondicionamiento físico. Obtenga "
"recomendaciones personalizadas de proteínas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"protein calculator, daily protein, protein needs, protein intake, muscle "
"building protein"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de proteínas, proteínas diarias, necesidades de proteínas, "
"ingesta de proteínas, proteínas para el desarrollo muscular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Daily Protein Needs"
msgstr "Calcule las necesidades diarias de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus necesidades diarias de proteínas según el peso corporal, el "
"nivel de actividad y los objetivos de acondicionamiento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate daily protein needs based on body weight and activity level"
msgstr ""
"Calcule las necesidades diarias de proteínas según el peso corporal y el "
"nivel de actividad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals. Get personalized protein recommendations and meal "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus necesidades diarias de proteínas según el peso corporal, el "
"nivel de actividad y los objetivos de acondicionamiento físico. Obtenga "
"recomendaciones personalizadas de proteínas y distribución de comidas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:103
msgid "Little/no exercise"
msgstr "Poco o nada de ejercicio"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:104
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:157
msgid "1-3 days/week"
msgstr "1-3 días/semana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:105
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:158
msgid "3-5 days/week"
msgstr "3-5 días/semana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:106
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:159
msgid "6-7 days/week"
msgstr "6-7 días/semana"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:107
msgid "Physical job"
msgstr "Trabajo fisico"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:108
msgid "Elite athlete"
msgstr "atleta de élite"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:114
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:353
msgid "Fitness Goal"
msgstr "Objetivo de aptitud"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:118
msgid "Maintain Weight"
msgstr "Mantener el peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:119
msgid "Muscle Gain"
msgstr "Ganancia muscular"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:120
msgid "Cutting"
msgstr "Corte"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:120
msgid "Bodybuilding"
msgstr "Culturismo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:127
msgid "Advanced Options"
msgstr "Opciones avanzadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:133
msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Opcional"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:140
msgid "For lean body mass calculation"
msgstr "Para calcular la masa corporal magra"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:151
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:612
msgid "Calculate Protein Needs"
msgstr "Calcular las necesidades de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:185
msgid ""
"Enter your body weight, activity level, and fitness goal to see your "
"personalized daily protein recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su peso corporal, nivel de actividad y objetivo de condición física "
"para ver sus recomendaciones diarias personalizadas de proteínas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:195
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:477
msgid "Daily Protein Needs"
msgstr "Necesidades diarias de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:215
msgid "Per kg"
msgstr "Por kilogramo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:227
msgid "Per Meal"
msgstr "Por comida"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:238
msgid "RDA"
msgstr "CDR"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:248
msgid "Athletic"
msgstr "Atlético"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:253
msgid "Bodybuilder"
msgstr "Carrocero"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:294
msgid "Protein per Meal"
msgstr "Proteína por comida"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:307
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:495
msgid "Protein Sources"
msgstr "Fuentes de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:325
msgid "Protein Sources Guide"
msgstr "Guía de fuentes de proteínas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:375
msgid "What is Protein and Why Do You Need It?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la proteína y por qué la necesita?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Protein is one of the three macronutrients (along with carbohydrates and "
"fats) essential for human health. It's made up of amino acids, which are the"
" building blocks of muscles, tissues, enzymes, hormones, and many other "
"important molecules in your body."
msgstr ""
"La proteína es uno de los tres macronutrientes (junto con los carbohidratos "
"y las grasas) esenciales para la salud humana. Está compuesto de "
"aminoácidos, que son los componentes básicos de los músculos, tejidos, "
"enzimas, hormonas y muchas otras moléculas importantes del cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:380
msgid ""
"Adequate protein intake is crucial for muscle maintenance and growth, immune"
" function, hormone production, and overall health. Your protein needs vary "
"based on your body weight, activity level, age, and fitness goals."
msgstr ""
"La ingesta adecuada de proteínas es crucial para el mantenimiento y el "
"crecimiento de los músculos, la función inmune, la producción de hormonas y "
"la salud en general. Sus necesidades de proteínas varían según su peso "
"corporal, nivel de actividad, edad y objetivos de acondicionamiento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:386
msgid "Protein Recommendations by Activity Level"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de proteínas por nivel de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:389
msgid "Sedentary (0.8 g/kg)"
msgstr "Sedentario (0,8 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"RDA minimum for adults. Suitable for people with little to no exercise. "
"Office work, minimal physical activity."
msgstr ""
"CDR mínima para adultos. Apto para personas con poco o ningún ejercicio. "
"Trabajo de oficina, mínima actividad física."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:395
msgid "Light Activity (1.0 g/kg)"
msgstr "Actividad ligera (1,0 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"Light exercise 1-3 days per week. Walking, light jogging, or recreational "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio ligero 1-3 días por semana. Caminar, trotar ligeramente o realizar"
" actividades recreativas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:401
msgid "Moderate Activity (1.2 g/kg)"
msgstr "Actividad moderada (1,2 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"Moderate exercise 3-5 days per week. Regular workouts, sports, or active "
"lifestyle."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio moderado 3-5 días por semana. Entrenamientos regulares, deportes o"
" estilo de vida activo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:407
msgid "Active (1.4 g/kg)"
msgstr "Activo (1,4 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"Active exercise 6-7 days per week. Intense workouts, competitive sports, or "
"physically demanding job."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio activo 6-7 días por semana. Entrenamientos intensos, deportes "
"competitivos o trabajos físicamente exigentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:413
msgid "Very Active (1.6 g/kg)"
msgstr "Muy activo (1,6 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"Very active lifestyle. Physical job, daily intense exercise, or multiple "
"training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Estilo de vida muy activo. Trabajo físico, ejercicio intenso diario o "
"múltiples sesiones de entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:419
msgid "Elite Athlete (1.8 g/kg)"
msgstr "Atleta de élite (1,8 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:421
msgid ""
"Elite athlete level. Professional training, multiple daily sessions, "
"competition preparation."
msgstr ""
"Nivel deportista de élite. Entrenamiento profesional, múltiples sesiones "
"diarias, preparación para competiciones."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:429
msgid "Protein Needs by Fitness Goal"
msgstr "Necesidades de proteínas por objetivo de acondicionamiento físico"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:432
#, python-format
msgid "Weight Loss (+20%%)"
msgstr "Pérdida de peso (+20%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Higher protein intake helps preserve muscle mass during calorie deficit and "
"increases satiety, making it easier to stick to your diet."
msgstr ""
"Una mayor ingesta de proteínas ayuda a preservar la masa muscular durante el"
" déficit calórico y aumenta la saciedad, lo que facilita el cumplimiento de "
"la dieta."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:438
msgid "Maintain Weight (Standard)"
msgstr "Mantener peso (estándar)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Standard protein intake to maintain current muscle mass and support daily "
"activities and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Ingesta estándar de proteínas para mantener la masa muscular actual y apoyar"
" las actividades diarias y la recuperación."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:444
#, python-format
msgid "Muscle Gain (+10%%)"
msgstr "Ganancia muscular (+10%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Slightly higher protein intake to support muscle growth and recovery from "
"training. Essential for building new muscle tissue."
msgstr ""
"Ingesta de proteínas ligeramente mayor para favorecer el crecimiento "
"muscular y la recuperación del entrenamiento. Esencial para la construcción "
"de nuevo tejido muscular."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:450
#, python-format
msgid "Cutting (+30%%)"
msgstr "Corte (+30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"High protein intake to preserve muscle mass during aggressive fat loss "
"phase. Critical for bodybuilders and athletes cutting weight."
msgstr ""
"Alto consumo de proteínas para preservar la masa muscular durante la fase "
"agresiva de pérdida de grasa. Crítico para culturistas y atletas que reducen"
" peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:462
msgid "Select your unit system (Metric in kg or Imperial in lbs)"
msgstr "Seleccione su sistema de unidades (Métrico en kg o Imperial en lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:463
msgid "Enter your current body weight"
msgstr "Introduzca su peso corporal actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:464
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:454
msgid ""
"Select your activity level based on your exercise frequency and intensity"
msgstr ""
"Seleccione su nivel de actividad según la frecuencia e intensidad de su "
"ejercicio."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:465
msgid ""
"Choose your fitness goal (weight loss, maintain, muscle gain, or cutting)"
msgstr ""
"Elija su objetivo de acondicionamiento físico (pérdida de peso, "
"mantenimiento, aumento de masa muscular o corte)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:466
msgid ""
"Optionally enter your body fat percentage for lean body mass calculation"
msgstr ""
"Opcionalmente, ingrese su porcentaje de grasa corporal para calcular la masa"
" corporal magra."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate Protein Needs' to see your personalized recommendations"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular necesidades de proteínas' para ver sus "
"recomendaciones personalizadas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:468
msgid ""
"Review meal distribution, protein sources, and charts to plan your daily "
"intake"
msgstr ""
"Revise la distribución de comidas, las fuentes de proteínas y los gráficos "
"para planificar su ingesta diaria."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:479
msgid ""
"Your total daily protein requirement in grams. This is calculated based on "
"your body weight, activity level, and fitness goal."
msgstr ""
"Su requerimiento total diario de proteínas en gramos. Esto se calcula en "
"función de su peso corporal, nivel de actividad y objetivo de condición "
"física."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:483
msgid "Protein per kg (or lb)"
msgstr "Proteína por kg (o libra)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:485
msgid ""
"The amount of protein per kilogram (or pound) of body weight. This helps you"
" understand the intensity of your protein needs relative to your size."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad de proteína por kilogramo (o libra) de peso corporal. Esto le "
"ayuda a comprender la intensidad de sus necesidades de proteínas en relación"
" con su tamaño."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"How to distribute your daily protein across meals. Typically spread across "
"4-5 meals for optimal absorption and muscle protein synthesis."
msgstr ""
"Cómo distribuir tu proteína diaria entre las comidas. Por lo general, se "
"distribuye en 4 o 5 comidas para una absorción óptima y una síntesis de "
"proteínas musculares."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:497
msgid ""
"Common protein-rich foods and how many servings you'd need to meet your "
"daily requirement. Mix different sources for variety and complete amino acid"
" profiles."
msgstr ""
"Alimentos comunes ricos en proteínas y cuántas porciones necesitarías para "
"satisfacer tus necesidades diarias. Mezcle diferentes fuentes para obtener "
"variedad y perfiles completos de aminoácidos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"These are general guidelines. Individual protein needs may vary based on "
"age, gender, medical conditions, and specific training programs."
msgstr ""
"Estas son pautas generales. Las necesidades individuales de proteínas pueden"
" variar según la edad, el sexo, las condiciones médicas y los programas de "
"entrenamiento específicos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"Distribute protein intake throughout the day. Aim for 20-40g per meal for "
"optimal muscle protein synthesis."
msgstr ""
"Distribuir la ingesta de proteínas a lo largo del día. Apunte a consumir "
"entre 20 y 40 g por comida para una síntesis óptima de proteínas musculares."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"Include a variety of protein sources. Animal proteins (meat, fish, eggs, "
"dairy) are complete proteins, while plant proteins (legumes, grains) can be "
"combined for complete amino acid profiles."
msgstr ""
"Incluya una variedad de fuentes de proteínas. Las proteínas animales (carne,"
" pescado, huevos, lácteos) son proteínas completas, mientras que las "
"proteínas vegetales (legumbres, cereales) se pueden combinar para obtener "
"perfiles de aminoácidos completos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical or nutritional advice. Always consult with qualified "
"healthcare providers or registered dietitians for personalized nutrition "
"guidance, especially if you have medical conditions or specific dietary "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" asesoramiento médico o nutricional profesional. Consulte siempre con "
"proveedores de atención médica calificados o dietistas registrados para "
"obtener orientación nutricional personalizada, especialmente si tiene "
"afecciones médicas o necesidades dietéticas específicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:535
msgid ""
"Very high protein intakes (>2.5 g/kg) may not provide additional benefits "
"and could potentially strain kidneys in individuals with pre-existing kidney"
" conditions. Most people can safely consume 1.6-2.2 g/kg."
msgstr ""
"Es posible que una ingesta muy alta de proteínas (>2,5 g/kg) no proporcione "
"beneficios adicionales y podría sobrecargar los riñones en personas con "
"enfermedades renales preexistentes. La mayoría de las personas pueden "
"consumir de forma segura entre 1,6 y 2,2 g/kg."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:753
msgid "Chicken Breast"
msgstr "Pechuga de pollo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:756
msgid "Greek Yogurt"
msgstr "yogur griego"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:757
msgid "Protein Powder"
msgstr "Proteína en polvo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:758
msgid "Lean Beef"
msgstr "Carne Magra"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:759
msgid "Tofu"
msgstr "tofu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:760
msgid "Lentils"
msgstr "Lentejas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:40
msgid "Target Heart Rate Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Heart Rate Zones"
msgstr "Calcular zonas de frecuencia cardíaca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your target heart rate zones for different training intensities. "
"Includes Karvonen method and standard formulas."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus zonas de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo para diferentes "
"intensidades de entrenamiento. Incluye método Karvonen y fórmulas estándar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"target heart rate calculator, heart rate zones, karvonen method, training "
"zones, max heart rate"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo, zonas de frecuencia cardíaca, "
"método karvonen, zonas de entrenamiento, frecuencia cardíaca máxima"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your target heart rate zones for optimal training."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus zonas de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo para un entrenamiento "
"óptimo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate target heart rate zones for training"
msgstr "Calcular zonas de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo para el entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your target heart rate zones for different training intensities. "
"Includes Karvonen method and standard formulas for optimal training."
msgstr ""
"Calcule sus zonas de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo para diferentes "
"intensidades de entrenamiento. Incluye método Karvonen y fórmulas estándar "
"para un entrenamiento óptimo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:77
msgid "Range: 10-100 years"
msgstr "Rango: 10-100 años"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:82
msgid "Resting Heart Rate"
msgstr "Frecuencia cardíaca en reposo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:89
msgid "Range: 30-120 bpm (measure when fully rested)"
msgstr "Rango: 30-120 bpm (medir cuando esté completamente descansado)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:97
msgid "Standard (220 - age)"
msgstr "Estándar (220 - edad)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:98
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:320
msgid "Karvonen Method"
msgstr "Método Karvonen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:100
msgid "Karvonen method accounts for resting heart rate"
msgstr "El método Karvonen tiene en cuenta la frecuencia cardíaca en reposo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:144
msgid ""
"Enter your age and resting heart rate to see your target heart rate zones "
"for different training intensities."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su edad y frecuencia cardíaca en reposo para ver sus zonas de "
"frecuencia cardíaca objetivo para diferentes intensidades de entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:154
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:358
msgid "Maximum Heart Rate"
msgstr "Frecuencia cardíaca máxima"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:156
msgid "Heart Rate Reserve"
msgstr "Reserva de frecuencia cardíaca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:159
msgid "Resting HR"
msgstr "FC en reposo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:173
msgid "Tanaka"
msgstr "Tanaka"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:178
msgid "Gellish"
msgstr "Gelish"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:192
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:228
msgid "Heart Rate Zones"
msgstr "Zonas de frecuencia cardíaca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:205
msgid "Max HR Formulas Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de fórmulas de FC máxima"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:219
msgid "Zone Distribution"
msgstr "Distribución de zonas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:248
msgid "What is Target Heart Rate?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la frecuencia cardíaca objetivo?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:250
msgid ""
"Target heart rate (THR) is the desired heart rate range you should maintain "
"during exercise to achieve specific fitness goals. Different heart rate "
"zones correspond to different training intensities and provide different "
"benefits."
msgstr ""
"La frecuencia cardíaca objetivo (THR) es el rango de frecuencia cardíaca "
"deseado que debe mantener durante el ejercicio para lograr objetivos de "
"acondicionamiento físico específicos. Diferentes zonas de frecuencia "
"cardíaca corresponden a diferentes intensidades de entrenamiento y "
"proporcionan diferentes beneficios."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:253
msgid ""
"Training in the appropriate heart rate zone helps you maximize the "
"effectiveness of your workouts, whether your goal is fat burning, "
"cardiovascular fitness, or improving athletic performance."
msgstr ""
"Entrenar en la zona de frecuencia cardíaca adecuada le ayuda a maximizar la "
"eficacia de sus entrenamientos, ya sea que su objetivo sea quemar grasa, "
"hacer ejercicio cardiovascular o mejorar el rendimiento deportivo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:259
msgid "Understanding Heart Rate Zones"
msgstr "Comprender las zonas de frecuencia cardíaca"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:262
#, python-format
msgid "Zone 1: Warm-up (50-60%% of Max HR)"
msgstr "Zona 1: Calentamiento (50-60%% de FC máxima)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:264
msgid ""
"Light activity for warm-up and recovery. Improves blood flow and prepares "
"muscles. Ideal for active recovery days."
msgstr ""
"Actividad ligera para calentamiento y recuperación. Mejora el flujo "
"sanguíneo y prepara los músculos. Ideal para días de recuperación activa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:267
msgid "Intensity: Very Light | RPE: 2-3 | Duration: 5-10 minutes"
msgstr "Intensidad: Muy ligera | RPE: 2-3 | Duración: 5-10 minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:271
#, python-format
msgid "Zone 2: Fat Burn (60-70%% of Max HR)"
msgstr "Zona 2: Quema de grasa (60-70%% de FC máxima)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:273
msgid ""
"Optimal zone for fat burning. Low to moderate intensity, sustainable for "
"longer durations. Builds aerobic base."
msgstr ""
"Zona óptima para quemar grasas. Intensidad baja a moderada, sostenible "
"durante períodos más prolongados. Desarrolla una base aeróbica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:276
msgid "Intensity: Light | RPE: 4-5 | Duration: 30-60 minutes"
msgstr "Intensidad: Luz | RPE: 4-5 | Duración: 30-60 minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:280
#, python-format
msgid "Zone 3: Aerobic (70-80%% of Max HR)"
msgstr "Zona 3: Aeróbica (70-80%% de la FC máxima)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:282
msgid ""
"Cardiovascular fitness zone. Improves heart and lung function, builds "
"endurance. Most common training zone."
msgstr ""
"Zona de acondicionamiento cardiovascular. Mejora la función cardíaca y "
"pulmonar, aumenta la resistencia. Zona de entrenamiento más común."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:285
msgid "Intensity: Moderate | RPE: 6-7 | Duration: 20-40 minutes"
msgstr "Intensidad: Moderada | RPE: 6-7 | Duración: 20-40 minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:289
#, python-format
msgid "Zone 4: Anaerobic (80-90%% of Max HR)"
msgstr "Zona 4: Anaeróbica (80-90%% de la FC máxima)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:291
msgid ""
"High-intensity training zone. Improves speed, power, and anaerobic capacity."
" Used for interval training."
msgstr ""
"Zona de entrenamiento de alta intensidad. Mejora la velocidad, la potencia y"
" la capacidad anaeróbica. Utilizado para entrenamiento a intervalos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:294
msgid "Intensity: Hard | RPE: 8-9 | Duration: 5-15 minutes"
msgstr "Intensidad: Difícil | RPE: 8-9 | Duración: 5-15 minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:298
#, python-format
msgid "Zone 5: Maximum (90-100%% of Max HR)"
msgstr "Zona 5: Máximo (90-100%% de FC máxima)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:300
msgid ""
"Maximum effort zone. Short bursts only, improves peak performance. Use "
"sparingly and with caution."
msgstr ""
"Zona de máximo esfuerzo. Solo ráfagas cortas, mejora el rendimiento máximo. "
"Úselo con moderación y precaución."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:303
msgid "Intensity: Maximum | RPE: 10 | Duration: 1-5 minutes"
msgstr "Intensidad: Máxima | RPE: 10 | Duración: 1-5 minutos"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:311
msgid "Calculation Methods"
msgstr "Métodos de cálculo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:314
msgid "Standard Method (220 - age)"
msgstr "Método estándar (220 - edad)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:316
msgid ""
"The most commonly used formula. Simple and easy to calculate, but may not be"
" accurate for all individuals. Best for general fitness purposes."
msgstr ""
"La fórmula más utilizada. Simple y fácil de calcular, pero puede no ser "
"exacto para todas las personas. Lo mejor para fines de acondicionamiento "
"físico general."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"More accurate method that accounts for your resting heart rate. Calculates "
"Heart Rate Reserve (HRR) = Max HR - Resting HR, then adds percentage of HRR "
"to resting HR. Better for personalized training zones."
msgstr ""
"Método más preciso que tiene en cuenta su frecuencia cardíaca en reposo. "
"Calcula la reserva de frecuencia cardíaca (HRR) = FC máxima - FC en reposo, "
"luego agrega el porcentaje de HRR a la FC en reposo. Mejor para zonas de "
"entrenamiento personalizadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:326
msgid "Tanaka Formula (208 - 0.7 × age)"
msgstr "Fórmula Tanaka (208 - 0,7 × edad)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:328
msgid ""
"Research-based formula that may be more accurate for older adults. Developed"
" from studies of healthy adults."
msgstr ""
"Fórmula basada en investigaciones que puede ser más precisa para los adultos"
" mayores. Desarrollado a partir de estudios de adultos sanos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:332
msgid "Gellish Formula (207 - 0.7 × age)"
msgstr "Fórmula Gellish (207 - 0,7 × edad)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"Another research-based alternative that may provide slightly different "
"estimates. Useful for comparison."
msgstr ""
"Otra alternativa basada en investigaciones que puede proporcionar "
"estimaciones ligeramente diferentes. Útil para comparar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:344
msgid "Enter your age (between 10 and 100 years)"
msgstr "Introduce tu edad (entre 10 y 100 años)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:345
msgid ""
"Enter your resting heart rate (measured when fully rested, typically in the "
"morning)"
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su frecuencia cardíaca en reposo (medida cuando está completamente "
"descansado, generalmente por la mañana)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:346
msgid "Select your preferred calculation method (Standard or Karvonen)"
msgstr "Seleccione su método de cálculo preferido (Estándar o Karvonen)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:347
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see your target heart rate zones"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver sus zonas de frecuencia cardíaca objetivo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:348
msgid ""
"Review the zones and choose the appropriate zone for your training goals"
msgstr ""
"Revisa las zonas y elige la zona adecuada para tus objetivos de "
"entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:349
msgid ""
"Use a heart rate monitor during exercise to stay within your target zone"
msgstr ""
"Utilice un monitor de frecuencia cardíaca durante el ejercicio para "
"mantenerse dentro de su zona objetivo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"The highest heart rate you can achieve during maximum physical exertion. "
"Used as a reference point for calculating training zones."
msgstr ""
"La frecuencia cardíaca más alta que puedes alcanzar durante el esfuerzo "
"físico máximo. Se utiliza como punto de referencia para calcular las zonas "
"de entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:364
msgid "Heart Rate Reserve (HRR)"
msgstr "Reserva de frecuencia cardíaca (FCR)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"The difference between your maximum heart rate and resting heart rate. Used "
"in the Karvonen method for more personalized zones."
msgstr ""
"La diferencia entre su frecuencia cardíaca máxima y su frecuencia cardíaca "
"en reposo. Utilizado en el método Karvonen para zonas más personalizadas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:370
msgid "Training Zones"
msgstr "Zonas de entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:372
msgid ""
"Each zone represents a percentage range of your maximum heart rate. "
"Different zones provide different training benefits and should be used for "
"different purposes."
msgstr ""
"Cada zona representa un rango porcentual de su frecuencia cardíaca máxima. "
"Las diferentes zonas proporcionan diferentes beneficios de entrenamiento y "
"deben usarse para diferentes propósitos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:376
msgid "Standard vs Karvonen"
msgstr "Estándar vs Karvonen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:378
msgid ""
"Standard method uses percentage of max HR directly. Karvonen method accounts"
" for your fitness level (via resting HR) and typically provides slightly "
"lower target zones, which may be more appropriate for beginners."
msgstr ""
"El método estándar utiliza directamente el porcentaje de FC máxima. El "
"método Karvonen tiene en cuenta su nivel de condición física (a través de la"
" FC en reposo) y generalmente proporciona zonas objetivo ligeramente más "
"bajas, que pueden ser más apropiadas para principiantes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"These formulas provide estimates. Actual maximum heart rate can vary "
"significantly between individuals based on genetics, fitness level, and "
"other factors."
msgstr ""
"Estas fórmulas proporcionan estimaciones. La frecuencia cardíaca máxima real"
" puede variar significativamente entre individuos según la genética, el "
"nivel de condición física y otros factores."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"Measure your resting heart rate first thing in the morning, before getting "
"out of bed, for the most accurate reading."
msgstr ""
"Mida su frecuencia cardíaca en reposo a primera hora de la mañana, antes de "
"levantarse de la cama, para obtener una lectura más precisa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"Some medications (like beta-blockers) can affect heart rate. Consult with "
"your healthcare provider if you're on medication."
msgstr ""
"Algunos medicamentos (como los betabloqueantes) pueden afectar la frecuencia"
" cardíaca. Consulte con su proveedor de atención médica si está tomando "
"medicamentos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare "
"providers before starting a new exercise program, especially if you have "
"heart conditions, are taking medications, or have other health concerns."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" consejo médico profesional. Consulte siempre con proveedores de atención "
"médica calificados antes de comenzar un nuevo programa de ejercicios, "
"especialmente si tiene afecciones cardíacas, está tomando medicamentos o "
"tiene otros problemas de salud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"If you experience chest pain, dizziness, shortness of breath, or other "
"concerning symptoms during exercise, stop immediately and seek medical "
"attention."
msgstr ""
"Si experimenta dolor en el pecho, mareos, dificultad para respirar u otros "
"síntomas preocupantes durante el ejercicio, deténgase inmediatamente y "
"busque atención médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:567
msgid "Karvonen"
msgstr "Karvonen"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:28
msgid "TDEE Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora TDEE"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE). Find out how many "
"calories you burn per day based on your activity level."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su gasto energético diario total (GDEE). Descubra cuántas calorías "
"quema por día según su nivel de actividad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"TDEE calculator, total daily energy expenditure, calorie burn calculator, "
"daily calories, BMR calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora TDEE, gasto energético total diario, calculadora de quema de "
"calorías, calorías diarias, calculadora de BMR"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your Total Daily Energy Expenditure based on your activity level."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su gasto energético diario total en función de su nivel de "
"actividad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:28
msgid "Calculate Total Daily Energy Expenditure"
msgstr "Calcular el gasto energético diario total"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) to find out how many "
"calories you burn per day based on your activity level and body composition."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su gasto energético diario total (GDEE) para saber cuántas calorías "
"quema por día en función de su nivel de actividad y composición corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:161
msgid "2x training"
msgstr "2x entrenamiento"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:172
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:627
msgid "Calculate TDEE"
msgstr "Calcular TDEE"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:206
msgid ""
"Enter your details to calculate your Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) "
"and see how many calories you burn per day."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus datos para calcular su gasto energético diario total (GDT) y vea"
" cuántas calorías quema por día."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:244
msgid "Activity Multiplier"
msgstr "Multiplicador de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:258
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:310
msgid "TDEE by Activity Level"
msgstr "TDEE por nivel de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:337
msgid "Suggested Macros (for TDEE)"
msgstr "Macros sugeridas (para TDEE)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:341
#, python-format
msgid "Protein (30%%)"
msgstr "Proteína (30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:346
#, python-format
msgid "Carbs (40%%)"
msgstr "Carbohidratos (40%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:351
#, python-format
msgid "Fat (30%%)"
msgstr "Grasa (30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:359
msgid "Current Activity Level"
msgstr "Nivel de actividad actual"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:380
msgid "What is TDEE?"
msgstr "¿Qué es TDEE?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) is the total number of calories your "
"body burns in a day. It includes your Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) plus the "
"calories burned through physical activity, digestion, and other daily "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"El gasto energético diario total (GDEE) es la cantidad total de calorías que"
" su cuerpo quema en un día. Incluye su tasa metabólica basal (TMB) más las "
"calorías quemadas mediante la actividad física, la digestión y otras "
"actividades diarias."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"TDEE is calculated by multiplying your BMR (the calories your body needs at "
"rest) by an activity multiplier that accounts for your daily physical "
"activity level."
msgstr ""
"TDEE se calcula multiplicando su BMR (las calorías que su cuerpo necesita en"
" reposo) por un multiplicador de actividad que representa su nivel de "
"actividad física diaria."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:388
msgid "TDEE = BMR × Activity Multiplier"
msgstr "TDEE = TMB × Multiplicador de actividad"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:394
msgid "What is BMR?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la TMB?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:396
msgid ""
"Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) is the number of calories your body burns at rest"
" to maintain basic physiological functions like breathing, circulation, cell"
" production, and brain function. It represents the minimum energy needed to "
"keep your body alive."
msgstr ""
"La tasa metabólica basal (TMB) es la cantidad de calorías que el cuerpo "
"quema en reposo para mantener funciones fisiológicas básicas como la "
"respiración, la circulación, la producción celular y la función cerebral. "
"Representa la energía mínima necesaria para mantener vivo tu cuerpo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:399
#, python-format
msgid ""
"BMR accounts for 60-75%% of your total daily calorie burn. It's calculated "
"using formulas that consider your age, gender, height, and weight."
msgstr ""
"La TMB representa entre el 60% y el 75% del total de calorías quemadas "
"diariamente. Se calcula mediante fórmulas que consideran su edad, sexo, "
"altura y peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:405
msgid "Activity Levels Explained"
msgstr "Niveles de actividad explicados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:408
msgid "Sedentary (1.2x)"
msgstr "Sedentario (1,2x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"Little or no exercise. Office job, minimal physical activity. Mostly sitting"
" or lying down."
msgstr ""
"Poco o ningún ejercicio. Trabajo de oficina, mínima actividad física. "
"Principalmente sentado o acostado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:414
msgid "Light Activity (1.375x)"
msgstr "Actividad ligera (1.375x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Light exercise 1-3 days per week. Walking, light jogging, or recreational "
"activities. Light physical work."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio ligero 1-3 días por semana. Caminar, trotar ligeramente o realizar"
" actividades recreativas. Trabajo físico ligero."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:420
msgid "Moderate Activity (1.55x)"
msgstr "Actividad moderada (1,55x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Moderate exercise 3-5 days per week. Regular workouts, sports, or active "
"lifestyle. Moderate physical work."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio moderado 3-5 días por semana. Entrenamientos regulares, deportes o"
" estilo de vida activo. Trabajo físico moderado."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:426
msgid "Active (1.725x)"
msgstr "Activo (1.725x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:428
msgid ""
"Hard exercise 6-7 days per week. Intense workouts, competitive sports, or "
"physically demanding job."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio intenso 6-7 días por semana. Entrenamientos intensos, deportes "
"competitivos o trabajos físicamente exigentes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:432
msgid "Very Active (1.9x)"
msgstr "Muy activo (1,9x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Very hard exercise, physical job. Daily intense exercise or physically "
"demanding work. Multiple training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Ejercicio muy duro, trabajo físico. Ejercicio intenso diario o trabajo "
"físicamente exigente. Múltiples sesiones de entrenamiento."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:438
msgid "Athlete (2.0x)"
msgstr "Atleta (2.0x)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Professional athlete level. Multiple daily training sessions, competition "
"preparation, extremely high activity level."
msgstr ""
"Nivel de deportista profesional. Múltiples entrenamientos diarios, "
"preparación para la competición, nivel de actividad altísimo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:451
msgid "Select your gender (affects BMR calculation)"
msgstr "Seleccione su género (afecta el cálculo de BMR)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:452
msgid "Enter your age (between 15 and 80 years)"
msgstr "Introduce tu edad (entre 15 y 80 años)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:453
msgid "Enter your height and weight"
msgstr "Introduce tu altura y peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:455
msgid "Click 'Calculate TDEE' to see your results"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular TDEE' para ver sus resultados"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"The calories your body burns at complete rest. This is your baseline "
"metabolic rate, representing the minimum energy needed for basic body "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"Las calorías que quema tu cuerpo en completo reposo. Esta es su tasa "
"metabólica inicial, que representa la energía mínima necesaria para las "
"funciones corporales básicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:473
msgid ""
"Your total daily calorie burn including all activities. This is the number "
"of calories you need to maintain your current weight. To lose weight, eat "
"below TDEE; to gain weight, eat above TDEE."
msgstr ""
"Su total diario de calorías quemadas, incluidas todas las actividades. Esta "
"es la cantidad de calorías que necesita para mantener su peso actual. Para "
"perder peso, coma por debajo de TDEE; para ganar peso, coma por encima de "
"TDEE."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:479
msgid ""
"Different calorie levels for various goals. A deficit of 500 calories per "
"day typically results in about 1 pound (0.45 kg) of weight loss per week. A "
"surplus of 500 calories per day typically results in about 1 pound of weight"
" gain per week."
msgstr ""
"Diferentes niveles de calorías para diversos objetivos. Un déficit de 500 "
"calorías por día generalmente resulta en aproximadamente 1 libra (0,45 kg) "
"de pérdida de peso por semana. Un excedente de 500 calorías por día "
"generalmente resulta en aproximadamente 1 libra de aumento de peso por "
"semana."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:483
msgid "Macro Recommendations"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de macros"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:485
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested macronutrient breakdown (30%% protein, 40%% carbs, 30%% fat) for "
"your TDEE. These percentages can be adjusted based on your specific goals "
"and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Desglose de macronutrientes sugerido (30 % % de proteínas, 40 % % de "
"carbohidratos, 30 % % de grasas) para su TDEE. Estos porcentajes se pueden "
"ajustar en función de sus objetivos y preferencias específicos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:499
msgid ""
"These are estimates. Actual calorie needs can vary based on genetics, muscle"
" mass, medical conditions, medications, and other individual factors."
msgstr ""
"Estas son estimaciones. Las necesidades calóricas reales pueden variar según"
" la genética, la masa muscular, las condiciones médicas, los medicamentos y "
"otros factores individuales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:505
msgid ""
"Be honest about your activity level. Overestimating activity can lead to "
"consuming too many calories, while underestimating can lead to too few "
"calories."
msgstr ""
"Sea honesto acerca de su nivel de actividad. Sobreestimar la actividad puede"
" llevar a consumir demasiadas calorías, mientras que subestimar puede llevar"
" a muy pocas calorías."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"For weight loss, a deficit of 250-500 calories per day is typically "
"sustainable. Extreme deficits (>1000 calories) are not recommended without "
"medical supervision."
msgstr ""
"Para perder peso, suele ser sostenible un déficit de 250 a 500 calorías por "
"día. No se recomiendan déficits extremos (>1000 calorías) sin supervisión "
"médica."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical or nutritional advice. Always consult with qualified "
"healthcare providers or registered dietitians for personalized nutrition "
"guidance, especially if you have medical conditions, are taking medications,"
" or have specific dietary needs."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene fines informativos únicamente y no debe reemplazar el"
" asesoramiento médico o nutricional profesional. Consulte siempre con "
"proveedores de atención médica calificados o dietistas registrados para "
"obtener orientación nutricional personalizada, especialmente si tiene "
"afecciones médicas, está tomando medicamentos o tiene necesidades dietéticas"
" específicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"TDEE can change over time as your weight, muscle mass, and activity level "
"change. Recalculate periodically to ensure accuracy."
msgstr ""
"TDEE puede cambiar con el tiempo a medida que cambian su peso, masa muscular"
" y nivel de actividad. Vuelva a calcular periódicamente para garantizar la "
"precisión."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:741
msgid "Extreme Gain"
msgstr "Ganancia extrema"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/weight_watcher_points_calculator.html:48
