msgid ""
"Free area calculator to find the area of rectangles, circles, triangles, "
"squares, and more shapes. Calculate square footage, area formulas, and get "
"step-by-step solutions. Perfect for geometry homework and construction "
"projects."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de área gratuita para encontrar el área de rectángulos, "
"círculos, triángulos, cuadrados y más formas. Calcule pies cuadrados, "
"fórmulas de área y obtenga soluciones paso a paso. Perfecto para tareas de "
"geometría y proyectos de construcción."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"area calculator, calculate area, rectangle area, circle area, triangle area,"
" square area, area of a circle, area of a rectangle, area of a triangle, "
"area formula, how to calculate area, square footage calculator, area finder,"
" geometry calculator, area of shapes, trapezoid area, parallelogram area, "
"area converter"
