msgstr "Tipos promedio explicados"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/average_calculator.html:340
msgid "Sum of all numbers divided by the count. Most commonly used average."
msgstr ""
"Suma de todos los números dividida por el conteo. Promedio más utilizado."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/average_calculator.html:344
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/mean_median_mode_range_calculator.html:177
