msgstr "Seleccionar operación"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:91
msgid "Choose the operation: Arithmetic, Bitwise, Bit Shifts, or Conversion"
msgstr ""
"Elija la operación: Aritmética, Bit a bit, Desplazamientos de bits o "
"Conversión"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:96
msgid "Enter your numbers in the selected base format"
msgstr "Ingresa tus números en el formato base seleccionado"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:101
msgid ""
"Click Calculate to see results in all number bases with step-by-step "
"solutions"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en Calcular para ver resultados en todas las bases numéricas con "
"soluciones paso a paso"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:114
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:438
msgid "What is a binary calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una calculadora binaria?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:117
msgid ""
"A binary calculator is a tool that performs arithmetic and bitwise "
"operations on binary numbers, and converts between different number bases "
"including binary, decimal, hexadecimal, and octal."
msgstr ""
"Una calculadora binaria es una herramienta que realiza operaciones "
"aritméticas y bit a bit en números binarios y convierte entre diferentes "
"bases numéricas, incluidas binarias, decimales, hexadecimales y octales."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:122
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:444
msgid "How do I convert binary to decimal?"
msgstr "¿Cómo convierto binario a decimal?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:125
msgid ""
"Enter your binary number, select Conversion operation, and the calculator "
"will display the decimal equivalent along with hexadecimal and octal "
"conversions."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su número binario, seleccione Operación de conversión y la "
"calculadora mostrará el equivalente decimal junto con las conversiones "
"hexadecimales y octales."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:130
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:450
msgid "What are bitwise operations?"
msgstr "¿Qué son las operaciones bit a bit?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:133
msgid ""
"Bitwise operations perform logical operations on individual bits. Common "
"operations include AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), and NOT (~)."
msgstr ""
"Las operaciones bit a bit realizan operaciones lógicas en bits individuales."
" Las operaciones comunes incluyen AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^) y NOT (~)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:138
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:456
msgid "Can I perform binary arithmetic?"
msgstr "¿Puedo realizar aritmética binaria?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:141
msgid ""
"Yes, the calculator supports binary addition, subtraction, multiplication, "
"and division operations with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Sí, la calculadora admite operaciones binarias de suma, resta, "
"multiplicación y división con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:151
msgid "Skip to main content"
msgstr "Saltar al contenido principal"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:168
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/index.html:30
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/index.html:86
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/index.html:136
#: user/templates/user/favorites.html:40
msgid "Math Calculators"
msgstr "Calculadoras matemáticas"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:174
#: Math_Calculators/views/index.py:62
msgid "Binary Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora binaria"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:191
msgid ""
"Perform binary arithmetic, bitwise operations, bit shifts, and number system"
" conversions. Supports binary, decimal, hexadecimal, and octal number "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"Realice aritmética binaria, operaciones bit a bit, desplazamientos de bits y"
" conversiones de sistemas numéricos. Admite sistemas numéricos binarios, "
"decimales, hexadecimales y octales."

