#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"A binary calculator is a specialized tool that performs arithmetic "
"operations, bitwise operations, and number system conversions on binary "
"numbers. It supports conversions between binary, decimal, hexadecimal, and "
"octal number systems."
msgstr ""
"Una calculadora binaria es una herramienta especializada que realiza "
"operaciones aritméticas, operaciones bit a bit y conversiones de sistemas "
"numéricos en números binarios. Admite conversiones entre sistemas numéricos "
"binario, decimal, hexadecimal y octal."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Enter your binary number in the input field, select 'Number Conversion' as "
"the operation, and click Calculate. The calculator will display the decimal "
"equivalent along with hexadecimal and octal conversions."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese su número binario en el campo de entrada, seleccione 'Conversión de "
"número' como operación y haga clic en Calcular. La calculadora mostrará el "
"equivalente decimal junto con las conversiones hexadecimales y octales."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Bitwise operations perform logical operations on individual bits of binary "
"numbers. Common operations include AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), NAND, NOR, and "
"NOT (~). These are fundamental in computer science and digital electronics."
msgstr ""
"Las operaciones bit a bit realizan operaciones lógicas en bits individuales "
"de números binarios. Las operaciones comunes incluyen AND (&), OR (|), XOR "
"(^), NAND, NOR y NOT (~). Estos son fundamentales en informática y "
"electrónica digital."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"Yes! The calculator supports binary addition, subtraction, multiplication, "
"and division. Simply select the arithmetic operation, enter your binary "
"numbers, and get results with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"¡Sí! La calculadora admite suma, resta, multiplicación y división binaria. "
"Simplemente seleccione la operación aritmética, ingrese sus números binarios"
" y obtenga resultados con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:462
msgid "What number bases are supported?"
msgstr "¿Qué bases numéricas se admiten?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"The calculator supports four number bases: Binary (base 2), Decimal (base "
"10), Hexadecimal (base 16), and Octal (base 8). You can input numbers in any"
" base and see results in all bases."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora admite cuatro bases numéricas: binaria (base 2), decimal "
"(base 10), hexadecimal (base 16) y octal (base 8). Puede ingresar números en"
" cualquier base y ver resultados en todas las bases."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:484
msgid "Select the input number base (Binary, Decimal, Hex, or Octal)"
msgstr ""
"Seleccione la base del número de entrada (binario, decimal, hexadecimal u "
"octal)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:485
msgid "Choose the operation you want to perform"
msgstr "Elige la operación que deseas realizar"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:486
msgid "Enter your numbers in the selected base"
msgstr "Ingresa tus números en la base seleccionada"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:487
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see results in all number bases"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver los resultados en todas las bases "
"numéricas."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:488
msgid "View bit comparison charts and step-by-step solutions"
msgstr "Ver cuadros comparativos de bits y soluciones paso a paso"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:496
msgid "Binary arithmetic: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division"
msgstr "Aritmética binaria: suma, resta, multiplicación, división"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:497
msgid "Bitwise operations: AND, OR, XOR, NAND, NOR, NOT"
msgstr "Operaciones bit a bit: AND, OR, XOR, NAND, NOR, NOT"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:498
msgid "Bit shifts: Left shift (<<), Right shift (>>)"
msgstr ""
"Desplazamientos de bits: desplazamiento a la izquierda (<<), desplazamiento "
"a la derecha (>>)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:499
msgid "Number conversion: Convert between Binary, Decimal, Hex, and Octal"
msgstr ""
"Conversión de números: convierta entre binario, decimal, hexadecimal y octal"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:500
msgid "Bit visualization: See individual bits in charts"
msgstr "Visualización de bits: vea bits individuales en gráficos"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:501
msgid "Multi-base display: Results shown in all number bases"
msgstr ""
"Visualización de bases múltiples: los resultados se muestran en todas las "
"bases numéricas"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:502
msgid "Step-by-step solutions for all operations"
msgstr "Soluciones paso a paso para todas las operaciones"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:508
msgid "Number Format Examples"
msgstr "Ejemplos de formato numérico"

