msgstr "Factores primos"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:399
msgid "Factor Size Trend"
msgstr "Tendencia del tamaño del factor"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:413
msgid "Factor Distribution"
msgstr "Distribución de factores"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:445
msgid "What is the Factor Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la Calculadora de Factores?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:447
msgid ""
"The Factor Calculator finds all factors of a given number, determines if "
"it's prime, and provides prime factorization. Factors are numbers that "
"divide evenly into the given number."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de factores encuentra todos los factores de un número "
"determinado, determina si es primo y proporciona factorización prima. Los "
"factores son números que se dividen uniformemente entre el número dado."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:450
msgid ""
"This calculator is useful for number theory, simplifying fractions, finding "
"divisors, and understanding number properties."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora es útil para la teoría de números, simplificar fracciones, "
"encontrar divisores y comprender las propiedades de los números."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:459
msgid "Click 'Calculate Factors' to find all factors"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular factores' para encontrar todos los factores."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:460
msgid "View the prime status (prime or composite)"
msgstr "Ver el estado principal (principal o compuesto)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:461
msgid "See all factors displayed as tags"
msgstr "Ver todos los factores mostrados como etiquetas"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:462
msgid "Review prime factorization and detailed results"
msgstr "Revisar la factorización prima y los resultados detallados."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:463
msgid "Use charts to visualize factor distribution"
msgstr "Utilice gráficos para visualizar la distribución de factores"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:470
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:289
msgid "Understanding the Results"
msgstr "Comprender los resultados"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:472
msgid "Prime Status"
msgstr "Estado principal"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"Indicates whether the number is prime (has exactly 2 factors) or composite "
"(has more than 2 factors)"
msgstr ""
"Indica si el número es primo (tiene exactamente 2 factores) o compuesto "
"(tiene más de 2 factores)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:473
msgid "Complete list of all numbers that divide evenly into the given number"
msgstr ""
"Lista completa de todos los números que se dividen uniformemente entre el "
"número dado"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:474
msgid "Total Factors"
msgstr "Factores totales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:474
msgid "Count of all factors including 1 and the number itself"
msgstr "Recuento de todos los factores, incluido el 1 y el número mismo."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:475
msgid "Proper Factors"
msgstr "Factores adecuados"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:475
msgid "All factors except the number itself"
msgstr "Todos los factores excepto el número mismo."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:476
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:489
