msgstr "No"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:499
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/prime_factorization_calculator.html:305
msgid "Example 3: Large Number"
msgstr "Ejemplo 3: número grande"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:514
msgid ""
"A number greater than 1 that has exactly two factors: 1 and itself. "
"Examples: 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23."
msgstr ""
"Un número mayor que 1 que tiene exactamente dos factores: 1 y él mismo. "
"Ejemplos: 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:518
msgid ""
"A number greater than 1 that has more than two factors. Examples: 4, 6, 8, "
"9, 10, 12, 14, 15, 16."
msgstr ""
"Un número mayor que 1 que tiene más de dos factores. Ejemplos: 4, 6, 8, 9, "
"10, 12, 14, 15, 16."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:522
msgid ""
"Every composite number can be expressed uniquely as a product of prime "
"numbers. For example, 12 = 2² × 3, and 60 = 2² × 3 × 5."
msgstr ""
"Todo número compuesto se puede expresar de forma única como producto de "
"números primos. Por ejemplo, 12 = 2² × 3 y 60 = 2² × 3 × 5."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:4
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:8
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:12
msgid "Fraction Calculator - Add, Subtract, Multiply, Divide Fractions"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de fracciones: sumar, restar, multiplicar y dividir fracciones"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free fraction calculator to add, subtract, multiply, and divide fractions "
"with step-by-step solutions. Simplify fractions, convert to decimals, and "
"solve mixed fractions. Perfect for students and math homework."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de fracciones gratuita para sumar, restar, multiplicar y dividir"
" fracciones con soluciones paso a paso. Simplifica fracciones, convierte a "
"decimales y resuelve fracciones mixtas. Perfecto para estudiantes y tareas "
"de matemáticas."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"fraction calculator, add fractions, subtract fractions, multiply fractions, "
"divide fractions, fraction solver, fraction calculator with steps, how to "
"add fractions, how to subtract fractions, how to multiply fractions, how to "
"divide fractions, simplify fractions, fraction to decimal, mixed fraction "
"calculator, improper fraction calculator, fraction reducer, fraction "
"simplifier"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de fracciones, sumar fracciones, restar fracciones, multiplicar "
"fracciones, dividir fracciones, solucionador de fracciones, calculadora de "
"fracciones con pasos, cómo sumar fracciones, cómo restar fracciones, cómo "
"multiplicar fracciones, cómo dividir fracciones, simplificar fracciones, "
"fracción a decimal, calculadora de fracciones mixtas, calculadora de "
"fracciones impropias, reductor de fracciones, simplificador de fracciones"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Free fraction calculator to add, subtract, multiply, and divide fractions "
"with step-by-step solutions. Simplify fractions, convert to decimals, and "
"solve mixed fractions."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de fracciones gratuita para sumar, restar, multiplicar y dividir"
" fracciones con soluciones paso a paso. Simplifica fracciones, convierte a "
"decimales y resuelve fracciones mixtas."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/fraction_calculator.html:13
