msgid "Additional Metrics"
msgstr "Métricas adicionales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:253
msgid "Decay Curve"
msgstr "Curva de decadencia"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:284
msgid "What is Half-Life?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la vida media?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:286
msgid ""
"Half-life is the time required for half of a quantity of a radioactive "
"substance to decay. It's a constant that characterizes the rate of "
"exponential decay."
msgstr ""
"La vida media es el tiempo necesario para que se desintegre la mitad de una "
"cantidad de una sustancia radiactiva. Es una constante que caracteriza la "
"tasa de decaimiento exponencial."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/half_life_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"The formula for exponential decay is: N = N₀ × e^(-λt), where N is the "
"remaining amount, N₀ is the initial amount, λ is the decay constant, and t "
"is time."
msgstr ""
"La fórmula para la caída exponencial es: N = N₀ × e^(-λt), donde N es la "
"cantidad restante, N₀ es la cantidad inicial, λ es la constante de caída y t"
" es el tiempo."

