msgstr "Comparación de sistemas numéricos"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:268
msgid "8-Bit Binary Representation"
msgstr "Representación binaria de 8 bits"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:299
msgid "What is Hexadecimal?"
msgstr "¿Qué es hexadecimal?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:301
msgid ""
"Hexadecimal (hex) is a base-16 number system using digits 0-9 and letters "
"A-F. It's commonly used in computing for representing binary values in a "
"more compact form."
msgstr ""
"Hexadecimal (hexadecimal) es un sistema numérico de base 16 que utiliza "
"dígitos del 0 al 9 y letras de la A a la F. Se usa comúnmente en informática"
" para representar valores binarios en una forma más compacta."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:304
msgid ""
"Each hex digit represents 4 bits. For example, FF in hex equals 255 in "
"decimal and 11111111 in binary."
msgstr ""
"Cada dígito hexadecimal representa 4 bits. Por ejemplo, FF en hexadecimal "
"equivale a 255 en decimal y 11111111 en binario."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:311
msgid ""
"Convert Mode: Enter a hex value to see its decimal, binary, and octal "
"equivalents"
msgstr ""
"Modo de conversión: ingrese un valor hexadecimal para ver sus equivalentes "
"decimal, binario y octal."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"Arithmetic Mode: Perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, or"
" modulo on two hex numbers"
msgstr ""
"Modo aritmético: realice sumas, restas, multiplicaciones, divisiones o "
"módulos en dos números hexadecimales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:313
msgid "Hex values can be entered with or without 0x or # prefix"
msgstr "Los valores hexadecimales se pueden ingresar con o sin prefijo 0x o #"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/hex_calculator.html:314
msgid "Use uppercase or lowercase letters (A-F or a-f)"
msgstr "Utilice letras mayúsculas o minúsculas (A-F o a-f)"

