msgstr ""
"Calcule el MCM (mínimo común múltiplo) de varios números. Calculadora en "
"línea gratuita con soluciones paso a paso, factorización prima y "
"visualizaciones."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:49
msgid "LCM Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora LCM"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:52
msgid ""
"Calculate Least Common Multiple (LCM) of multiple numbers with step-by-step "
"solutions and prime factorization."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el mínimo común múltiplo (MCM) de varios números con soluciones paso"
" a paso y factorización prima."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:99
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:103
msgid "Calculate LCM"
msgstr "Calcular el MCM"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:157
msgid ""
"Enter two or more positive integers to calculate their LCM (Least Common "
"Multiple)."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese dos o más números enteros positivos para calcular su MCM (mínimo "
"común múltiplo)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:216
msgid "LCM Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación LCM"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:263
msgid ""
"LCM (Least Common Multiple) is the smallest positive integer that is a "
"multiple of each of the given numbers. It's useful for finding common "
"denominators, solving problems involving periodic events, and more."
msgstr ""
"MCM (Mínimo Común Múltiplo) es el entero positivo más pequeño que es "
"múltiplo de cada uno de los números dados. Es útil para encontrar "
"denominadores comunes, resolver problemas que involucran eventos periódicos "
"y más."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:266
msgid ""
"For example, LCM of 12 and 18 is 36, because 36 is the smallest number that "
"is divisible by both 12 and 18."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, el MCM de 12 y 18 es 36, porque 36 es el número más pequeño que"
" es divisible por 12 y 18."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:274
msgid "Click 'Calculate LCM' to find the result"
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular LCM' para encontrar el resultado."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:275
msgid "View the LCM value and prime factorization"
msgstr "Ver el valor del MCM y la factorización prima"

