#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:246
msgid "What is Long Division?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la división larga?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:248
msgid ""
"Long division is a method for dividing large numbers by breaking the "
"division problem into a series of easier steps. It shows how many times the "
"divisor goes into the dividend and what the remainder is."
msgstr ""
"La división larga es un método para dividir números grandes dividiendo el "
"problema de división en una serie de pasos más sencillos. Muestra cuántas "
"veces el divisor entra en el dividendo y cuál es el resto."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:251
msgid ""
"The process involves dividing, multiplying, subtracting, and bringing down "
"digits until the division is complete or a repeating pattern is found."
msgstr ""
"El proceso implica dividir, multiplicar, restar y reducir dígitos hasta que "
"se complete la división o se encuentre un patrón repetido."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:258
msgid "Enter the dividend (the number to be divided)"
msgstr "Ingrese el dividendo (el número a dividir)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:259
msgid "Enter the divisor (the number to divide by)"
msgstr "Ingrese el divisor (el número por el que dividir)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:260
msgid "Optionally set the number of decimal places"
msgstr "Opcionalmente, establezca el número de decimales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:261
msgid "Click Calculate to see the step-by-step solution"
msgstr "Haga clic en Calcular para ver la solución paso a paso."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/long_division_calculator.html:262
msgid "Review the visual division steps and detailed explanation"
msgstr "Revise los pasos de la división visual y la explicación detallada."

