#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/number_sequence_calculator.html:267
msgid "What is a Number Sequence?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una secuencia numérica?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/number_sequence_calculator.html:269
msgid ""
"A number sequence is an ordered list of numbers that follow a specific "
"pattern or rule. Common types include arithmetic, geometric, Fibonacci, and "
"power sequences."
msgstr ""
"Una secuencia numérica es una lista ordenada de números que siguen un patrón"
" o regla específica. Los tipos comunes incluyen secuencias aritméticas, "
"geométricas, de Fibonacci y de potencia."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/number_sequence_calculator.html:274
msgid "Supported Sequence Types"
msgstr "Tipos de secuencia admitidos"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/number_sequence_calculator.html:276
