msgid "Absolute Error"
msgstr "Error absoluto"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:196
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:280
msgid "Relative Error"
msgstr "Error relativo"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:221
msgid "Value Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de valores"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:234
msgid "Error Visualization"
msgstr "Visualización de errores"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:266
msgid "What is Percent Error?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el error porcentual?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:268
msgid ""
"Percent error measures the accuracy of a measurement by comparing the "
"experimental (measured) value to the theoretical (expected) value. It shows "
"how far off a measurement is from the true value as a percentage."
msgstr ""
"El error porcentual mide la precisión de una medición comparando el valor "
"experimental (medido) con el valor teórico (esperado). Muestra qué tan lejos"
" está una medición del valor real como porcentaje."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:271
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Formula: Percent Error = (|Experimental - Theoretical| / |Theoretical|) × "
"100%%"
msgstr ""
"Fórmula: Error porcentual = (|Experimental - Teórico| / |Teórico|) × 100%%"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:276
msgid "Error Types"
msgstr "Tipos de errores"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:278
msgid ""
"The absolute difference between experimental and theoretical values: "
"|Experimental - Theoretical|"
msgstr ""
"La diferencia absoluta entre valores experimentales y teóricos: "
"|Experimental - Teórico|"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:279
msgid "Absolute error expressed as a percentage of the theoretical value"
msgstr "Error absoluto expresado como porcentaje del valor teórico."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:280
msgid ""
"The ratio of absolute error to the absolute value of the theoretical value "
"(unitless)"
msgstr ""
"La relación entre el error absoluto y el valor absoluto del valor teórico "
"(sin unidades)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:285
msgid "Interpreting Percent Error"
msgstr "Interpretación del error porcentual"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:287
#, python-format
msgid "&lt; 1%%"
msgstr "&lt; 1%%"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:287
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:320
msgid "Excellent accuracy"
msgstr "Excelente precisión"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/percent_error_calculator.html:288
