#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free probability calculator to calculate basic probability, conditional "
"probability, joint probability, and union probability. Solve probability "
"problems with step-by-step solutions. Perfect for statistics and math "
"homework."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de probabilidad gratuita para calcular la probabilidad básica, "
"la probabilidad condicional, la probabilidad conjunta y la probabilidad "
"unida. Resolver problemas de probabilidad con soluciones paso a paso. "
"Perfecto para tareas de estadística y matemáticas."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
