msgid "Probability Visualization"
msgstr "Visualización de probabilidad"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:348
msgid "What is Probability?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la probabilidad?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Probability is a measure of the likelihood that an event will occur. It "
"ranges from 0 (impossible) to 1 (certain), or 0%% to 100%%."
msgstr ""
"La probabilidad es una medida de la probabilidad de que ocurra un evento. "
"Varía de 0 (imposible) a 1 (seguro), o de 0%% a 100%%."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:355
msgid "Probability Types"
msgstr "Tipos de probabilidad"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:357
msgid "P(A) = Favorable outcomes / Total outcomes"
msgstr "P(A) = Resultados favorables / Resultados totales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:358
msgid "Probability of A given B: P(A|B) = P(A and B) / P(B)"
msgstr "Probabilidad de A dado B: P(A|B) = P(A y B) / P(B)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:359
msgid ""
"Probability of both A and B: P(A and B) = P(A) × P(B) for independent events"
msgstr ""
"Probabilidad de A y B: P(A y B) = P(A) × P(B) para eventos independientes"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:360
msgid "Probability of A or B (or both): P(A or B) = P(A) + P(B) - P(A and B)"
msgstr "Probabilidad de A o B (o ambos): P(A o B) = P(A) + P(B) - P(A y B)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:367
msgid "Events where the occurrence of one does not affect the other"
msgstr "Eventos donde la ocurrencia de uno no afecta al otro"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Events where the occurrence of one affects the probability of the other"
msgstr "Eventos donde la ocurrencia de uno afecta la probabilidad del otro"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:369
msgid "Mutually Exclusive"
msgstr "Mutuamente excluyentes"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:369
msgid "Events that cannot occur simultaneously (P(A and B) = 0)"
msgstr "Eventos que no pueden ocurrir simultáneamente (P(A y B) = 0)"

