"lado faltante usando el teorema de Pitágoras."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:251
msgid "Triangle Sides"
msgstr "Lados del triángulo"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:277
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/right_triangle_calculator.html:345
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/triangle_calculator.html:351
msgid "Side Lengths"
msgstr "Longitudes laterales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:290
msgid "Squares Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de cuadrados"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:322
msgid "What is the Pythagorean Theorem?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el teorema de Pitágoras?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"The Pythagorean theorem states that in a right triangle, the square of the "
"hypotenuse (c) equals the sum of squares of the other two sides (a and b)."
msgstr ""
"El teorema de Pitágoras establece que en un triángulo rectángulo, el "
"cuadrado de la hipotenusa (c) es igual a la suma de los cuadrados de los "
"otros dos catetos (a y b)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:334
msgid "Find Hypotenuse (c)"
msgstr "Encuentre la hipotenusa (c)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:334
msgid "c = √(a² + b²)"
msgstr "c = √(a² + b²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:335
msgid "Find Side a"
msgstr "Encuentra el lado a"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:335
msgid "a = √(c² - b²)"
msgstr "a = √(c² - b²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:336
msgid "Find Side b"
msgstr "Encuentra el lado b"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:336
msgid "b = √(c² - a²)"
msgstr "segundo = √(c² - a²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:341
msgid "Key Points"
msgstr "Puntos clave"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"The theorem only applies to right triangles (triangles with a 90° angle)"
msgstr ""
"El teorema sólo se aplica a triángulos rectángulos (triángulos con un ángulo"
" de 90°)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:344
msgid "The hypotenuse (c) is always the longest side"
msgstr "La hipotenusa (c) es siempre el lado más largo."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:345
msgid "The hypotenuse is opposite the right angle"
msgstr "La hipotenusa es opuesta al ángulo recto."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:346
msgid "Sides a and b are the legs of the right triangle"
msgstr "Los lados a y b son los catetos del triángulo rectángulo"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:354
msgid "Example 1: Find Hypotenuse"
msgstr "Ejemplo 1: encontrar la hipotenusa"

