msgstr "Calculadora de redondeo: redondear números a decimales"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/rounding_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free rounding calculator to round numbers to different decimal places. Round"
" to nearest, round up, round down, toward zero, and away from zero. Perfect "
