#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:84
msgid ""
"Calculate your exact age in years, months, days, hours, and seconds. Find "
"your zodiac sign, generation, and upcoming milestones."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu edad exacta en años, meses, días, horas y segundos. Encuentra tu "
"signo del zodíaco, generación y próximos hitos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:89
