msgstr "Cálculo del tiempo de transferencia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:77
#: Other_Calculators/views/bandwidth_calculator.py:53
msgid "Bandwidth requirement analysis"
msgstr "Análisis de requisitos de ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:78
msgid "File size calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo del tamaño del archivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:79
msgid "Real-world speed estimates with protocol overhead"
msgstr "Estimaciones de velocidad del mundo real con sobrecarga de protocolo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:80
msgid "Batch file transfer calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de transferencia de archivos por lotes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:81
msgid "Connection type comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de tipos de conexión"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:82
msgid "Data transfer cost calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo del costo de transferencia de datos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:83
msgid "Bandwidth recommendations by use case"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de ancho de banda por caso de uso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:84
#: Other_Calculators/views/bandwidth_calculator.py:54
msgid "Multiple unit conversions"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades múltiples"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:86
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:56
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:58
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:85
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:66
msgid "Interactive visualizations"
msgstr "Visualizaciones interactivas"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:96
msgid "How to Use Bandwidth Calculator"
msgstr "Cómo utilizar la calculadora de ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:97
msgid ""
"Step-by-step guide on calculating bandwidth, transfer times, and file sizes"
msgstr ""
"Guía paso a paso sobre cómo calcular el ancho de banda, los tiempos de "
"transferencia y el tamaño de los archivos"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:102
msgid ""
"Choose from: Transfer Time, Bandwidth Required, File Size, Real-World Speed,"
" Batch Transfer, Connection Comparison, Cost Calculation, or Bandwidth "
"Recommendation"
msgstr ""
"Elija entre: tiempo de transferencia, ancho de banda requerido, tamaño de "
"archivo, velocidad real, transferencia por lotes, comparación de conexiones,"
" cálculo de costos o recomendación de ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:107
msgid ""
"Enter the required values based on your selected calculation type. Include "
"file size, bandwidth, time, or other relevant parameters."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los valores requeridos según el tipo de cálculo seleccionado. "
"Incluya el tamaño del archivo, el ancho de banda, el tiempo u otros "
"parámetros relevantes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:111
msgid "Select Units"
msgstr "Seleccionar unidades"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:112
msgid ""
"Choose appropriate units for file size (bits, bytes, KB, MB, GB, TB), "
"bandwidth (Kbps, Mbps, Gbps, Tbps), and time (seconds, minutes, hours, days)"
msgstr ""
"Elija las unidades adecuadas para el tamaño del archivo (bits, bytes, KB, "
"MB, GB, TB), ancho de banda (Kbps, Mbps, Gbps, Tbps) y tiempo (segundos, "
"minutos, horas, días)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:117
msgid ""
"Click Calculate to get your results with detailed breakdown, visualizations,"
" and step-by-step solution"
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en Calcular para obtener sus resultados con un desglose detallado,"
" visualizaciones y una solución paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:122
msgid ""
"Review the calculated results, detailed breakdown in multiple units, "
"interactive charts, and step-by-step calculation explanation"
msgstr ""
"Revise los resultados calculados, el desglose detallado en varias unidades, "
"los gráficos interactivos y la explicación del cálculo paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:135
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:737
msgid "How do I calculate data transfer time?"
msgstr "¿Cómo calculo el tiempo de transferencia de datos?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:138
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:739
msgid ""
"To calculate transfer time, divide the file size by the bandwidth. For "
"example, a 100 MB file at 10 Mbps would take approximately 80 seconds. Use "
"our Transfer Time calculator for accurate results."
msgstr ""
"Para calcular el tiempo de transferencia, divida el tamaño del archivo por "
"el ancho de banda. Por ejemplo, un archivo de 100 MB a 10 Mbps tardaría "
"aproximadamente 80 segundos. Utilice nuestra calculadora de tiempo de "
"transferencia para obtener resultados precisos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:143
msgid "What is the difference between bits and bytes?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre bits y bytes?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:146
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:745
msgid ""
"A bit is the smallest unit of data (0 or 1). A byte consists of 8 bits. "
"Bandwidth is typically measured in bits per second (bps), while file sizes "
"are usually measured in bytes. To convert: 1 byte = 8 bits."
msgstr ""
"Un bit es la unidad más pequeña de datos (0 o 1). Un byte consta de 8 bits. "
"El ancho de banda normalmente se mide en bits por segundo (bps), mientras "
"que el tamaño de los archivos generalmente se mide en bytes. Para convertir:"
" 1 byte = 8 bits."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:151
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:749
msgid "Why is my actual download speed slower than my bandwidth?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué mi velocidad de descarga real es más lenta que mi ancho de banda?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:154
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:751
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Actual speeds are affected by network congestion, protocol overhead (TCP/IP "
"headers), server limitations, and other factors. You typically get 80-90%% "
"of your advertised bandwidth in real-world conditions. Use our Real-World "
"Speed calculator to account for protocol overhead."
msgstr ""
"Las velocidades reales se ven afectadas por la congestión de la red, la "
"sobrecarga del protocolo (encabezados TCP/IP), las limitaciones del servidor"
" y otros factores. Normalmente obtienes entre el 80% y el 90% del ancho de "
"banda anunciado en condiciones reales. Utilice nuestra calculadora de "
"velocidad del mundo real para tener en cuenta la sobrecarga del protocolo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:159
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:755
msgid "What bandwidth do I need for streaming?"
msgstr "¿Qué ancho de banda necesito para la transmisión?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:162
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:757
msgid ""
"For HD video streaming, you need at least 5 Mbps. For 4K streaming, you need"
" 25 Mbps or more. For multiple simultaneous streams, multiply these "
"requirements. Use our Bandwidth Recommendation tool for personalized "
"suggestions based on your use case."
msgstr ""
"Para la transmisión de vídeo HD, necesita al menos 5 Mbps. Para la "
"transmisión en 4K, necesita 25 Mbps o más. Para múltiples transmisiones "
"simultáneas, multiplique estos requisitos. Utilice nuestra herramienta de "
"recomendación de ancho de banda para obtener sugerencias personalizadas "
"según su caso de uso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:167
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:761
msgid "How do I convert between Mbps and MB/s?"
msgstr "¿Cómo convierto entre Mbps y MB/s?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:170
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:763
msgid ""
"To convert Mbps to MB/s, divide by 8 (since there are 8 bits in a byte). For"
" example, 100 Mbps = 12.5 MB/s. To convert MB/s to Mbps, multiply by 8."
msgstr ""
"Para convertir Mbps a MB/s, divida entre 8 (ya que hay 8 bits en un byte). "
"Por ejemplo, 100 Mbps = 12,5 MB/s. Para convertir MB/s a Mbps, multiplique "
"por 8."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:175
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:767
msgid "What is protocol overhead in data transfer?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la sobrecarga de protocolo en la transferencia de datos?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:178
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:769
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Protocol overhead refers to the additional data sent along with your actual "
"file data. TCP/IP adds about 10%% overhead, HTTP adds 12%%, and HTTPS adds "
"15%%. This overhead reduces your effective bandwidth. Our Real-World Speed "
"calculator accounts for these factors."
msgstr ""
"La sobrecarga del protocolo se refiere a los datos adicionales enviados "
"junto con los datos reales del archivo. TCP/IP agrega aproximadamente un "
"10%% de sobrecarga, HTTP agrega un 12%% y HTTPS agrega un 15%%. Esta "
"sobrecarga reduce su ancho de banda efectivo. Nuestra calculadora de "
"velocidad en el mundo real tiene en cuenta estos factores."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:217
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:207
msgid "Breadcrumb navigation"
msgstr "Navegación de ruta de navegación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:250
msgid ""
"Calculate data transfer time, required bandwidth, and file sizes. Perfect "
"for estimating download/upload times and network planning."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el tiempo de transferencia de datos, el ancho de banda requerido y "
"el tamaño de los archivos. Perfecto para estimar tiempos de descarga/carga y"
" planificación de red."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:257
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:247
msgid "Calculator input form"
msgstr "Formulario de entrada de la calculadora"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:262
msgid "Bandwidth calculator form"
msgstr "Formulario de calculadora de ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:268
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:260
msgid "required field"
msgstr "campo requerido"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:271
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:606
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1019
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1191
msgid "Transfer Time"
msgstr "Tiempo de transferencia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:272
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:612
msgid "Bandwidth Required"
msgstr "Ancho de banda requerido"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:273
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:285
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:315
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:373
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:434
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:449
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:618
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1085
msgid "File Size"
msgstr "Tamaño de archivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:274
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:624
msgid "Real-World Speed"
msgstr "Velocidad del mundo real"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:275
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:630
msgid "Batch Transfer"
msgstr "Transferencia por lotes"

