#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:559
msgid "Calculate Bandwidth"
msgstr "Calcular ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:560
msgid ""
"Enter your values to calculate transfer time, required bandwidth, or file "
"size."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus valores para calcular el tiempo de transferencia, el ancho de "
"banda requerido o el tamaño del archivo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:566
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:498
msgid "User guide and documentation"
msgstr "Guía de usuario y documentación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:577
msgid "What is Bandwidth?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el ancho de banda?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:579
msgid ""
"Bandwidth refers to the maximum data transfer rate of a network or internet "
"connection. It measures how much data can be sent over a specific connection"
" in a given amount of time, typically expressed in bits per second (bps) or "
"multiples like Kbps, Mbps, Gbps, and Tbps."
msgstr ""
"El ancho de banda se refiere a la velocidad máxima de transferencia de datos"
" de una red o conexión a Internet. Mide la cantidad de datos que se pueden "
"enviar a través de una conexión específica en un período de tiempo "
"determinado, generalmente expresado en bits por segundo (bps) o múltiplos "
"como Kbps, Mbps, Gbps y Tbps."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:582
msgid "Transfer Time = File Size ÷ Bandwidth"
msgstr "Tiempo de transferencia = Tamaño del archivo ÷ Ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:585
msgid ""
"Understanding bandwidth is crucial for estimating download/upload times, "
"planning network infrastructure, and optimizing data transfers. This "
"calculator helps you determine transfer times, required bandwidth, or file "
"sizes based on your specific needs."
msgstr ""
"Comprender el ancho de banda es crucial para estimar los tiempos de "
"descarga/carga, planificar la infraestructura de red y optimizar las "
"transferencias de datos. Esta calculadora le ayuda a determinar los tiempos "
"de transferencia, el ancho de banda requerido o el tamaño de los archivos "
"según sus necesidades específicas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:593
msgid "Select the calculation type from the dropdown menu."
msgstr "Seleccione el tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:594
msgid "Enter the required values based on your selected calculation type."
msgstr "Ingrese los valores requeridos según el tipo de cálculo seleccionado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:595
msgid "Select appropriate units for file size, bandwidth, and time."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione las unidades adecuadas para el tamaño del archivo, el ancho de "
"banda y el tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:596
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:528
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see your results."
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Calcular' para ver sus resultados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:597
msgid "Review the detailed breakdown, charts, and step-by-step solution."
msgstr "Revise el desglose detallado, los gráficos y la solución paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:608
msgid ""
"Calculate how long it will take to transfer a file given its size and your "
"bandwidth. Useful for estimating download or upload times."
msgstr ""
"Calcule cuánto tiempo llevará transferir un archivo dado su tamaño y su "
"ancho de banda. Useful for estimating download or upload times."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:614
msgid ""
"Determine the minimum bandwidth needed to transfer a file within a specific "
"time frame. Helpful for network planning and capacity requirements."
msgstr ""
"Determine el ancho de banda mínimo necesario para transferir un archivo "
"dentro de un período de tiempo específico. Útil para la planificación de "
"redes y requisitos de capacidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:620
msgid ""
"Calculate the maximum file size that can be transferred given your bandwidth"
" and available time. Useful for understanding transfer limits."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el tamaño máximo de archivo que se puede transferir según su ancho "
"de banda y tiempo disponible. Útil para comprender los límites de "
"transferencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:626
msgid ""
"Calculate actual transfer times accounting for protocol overhead (TCP/IP, "
"HTTP, HTTPS, etc.). Provides realistic estimates based on network protocols."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los tiempos de transferencia reales teniendo en cuenta la sobrecarga"
" del protocolo (TCP/IP, HTTP, HTTPS, etc.). Proporciona estimaciones "
"realistas basadas en protocolos de red."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:632
msgid ""
"Calculate transfer times for multiple files. Supports both sequential and "
"parallel transfer modes. Perfect for estimating bulk file transfers."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los tiempos de transferencia para múltiples archivos. Admite modos "
"de transferencia secuencial y paralelo. Perfecto para estimar transferencias"
" masivas de archivos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:638
msgid ""
"Compare transfer times across different connection types (Dial-up, DSL, "
"Cable, Fiber, 4G, 5G, Gigabit). See which connection is best for your needs."
msgstr ""
"Compare los tiempos de transferencia entre diferentes tipos de conexión "
"(acceso telefónico, DSL, cable, fibra, 4G, 5G, Gigabit). Vea qué conexión se"
" adapta mejor a sus necesidades."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:644
msgid ""
"Calculate data transfer costs based on file size and cost per GB. Useful for"
" cloud storage and data transfer pricing estimates."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los costos de transferencia de datos según el tamaño del archivo y "
"el costo por GB. Útil para estimaciones de precios de transferencia de datos"
" y almacenamiento en la nube."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:650
msgid ""
"Get personalized bandwidth recommendations based on your use case "
"(streaming, gaming, video calls, etc.), number of users, and concurrent "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Obtenga recomendaciones personalizadas de ancho de banda según su caso de "
"uso (transmisión, juegos, videollamadas, etc.), cantidad de usuarios y "
"actividades simultáneas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:658
msgid "Understanding Units"
msgstr "Comprender las unidades"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:661
msgid "File Size Units"
msgstr "Unidades de tamaño de archivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:664
msgid "bits: Smallest unit, 1 bit"
msgstr "bits: unidad más pequeña, 1 bit"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:665
msgid "bytes: 8 bits = 1 byte"
msgstr "bytes: 8 bits = 1 byte"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:666
msgid "KB (Kilobytes): 1,024 bytes"
msgstr "KB (kilobytes): 1.024 bytes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:667
msgid "MB (Megabytes): 1,024 KB = 1,048,576 bytes"
msgstr "MB (Megabytes): 1.024 KB = 1.048.576 bytes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:668
msgid "GB (Gigabytes): 1,024 MB = 1,073,741,824 bytes"
msgstr "GB (Gigabytes): 1.024 MB = 1.073.741.824 bytes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:669
msgid "TB (Terabytes): 1,024 GB = 1,099,511,627,776 bytes"
msgstr "TB (Terabytes): 1.024 GB = 1.099.511.627.776 bytes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:674
msgid "Bandwidth Units"
msgstr "Unidades de ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:677
msgid "bps: Bits per second"
msgstr "bps: Bits por segundo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:678
msgid "Kbps: Kilobits per second (1,000 bps)"
msgstr "Kbps: Kilobits por segundo (1000 bps)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:679
msgid "Mbps: Megabits per second (1,000,000 bps)"
msgstr "Mbps: Megabits por segundo (1.000.000 bps)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:680
msgid "Gbps: Gigabits per second (1,000,000,000 bps)"
msgstr "Gbps: Gigabits por segundo (1.000.000.000 bps)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:681
msgid "Tbps: Terabits per second (1,000,000,000,000 bps)"
msgstr "Tbps: Terabits por segundo (1.000.000.000.000 bps)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:693
msgid "Transfer Time:"
msgstr "Tiempo de transferencia:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:694
msgid "Time = File Size ÷ Bandwidth"
msgstr "Tiempo = Tamaño de archivo ÷ Ancho de banda"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:697
msgid "Bandwidth Required:"
msgstr "Ancho de banda requerido:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:698
msgid "Bandwidth = File Size ÷ Time"
msgstr "Ancho de banda = Tamaño de archivo ÷ Tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:701
msgid "File Size:"
msgstr "Tamaño del archivo:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:702
msgid "File Size = Bandwidth × Time"
msgstr "Tamaño del archivo = Ancho de banda × Tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:715
msgid ""
"Actual transfer speeds may vary due to network congestion, protocol "
"overhead, and other factors. These calculations provide theoretical "
"maximums."
msgstr ""
"Las velocidades de transferencia reales pueden variar debido a la congestión"
" de la red, la sobrecarga del protocolo y otros factores. Estos cálculos "
"proporcionan máximos teóricos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:721
msgid ""
"File size units use binary (1024-based) conversions, while bandwidth units "
"use decimal (1000-based) conversions, which is standard in networking."
msgstr ""
"Las unidades de tamaño de archivo utilizan conversiones binarias (basadas en"
" 1024), mientras que las unidades de ancho de banda utilizan conversiones "
"decimales (basadas en 1000), que es estándar en redes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:727
#, python-format
msgid ""
"These calculations assume optimal network conditions. Real-world performance"
" may be 10-20%% lower due to protocol overhead and network inefficiencies."
msgstr ""
"Estos cálculos suponen condiciones óptimas de la red. El rendimiento en el "
"mundo real puede ser entre un 10% y un 20%% menor debido a la sobrecarga del"
" protocolo y a las ineficiencias de la red."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:743
msgid "What's the difference between bits and bytes?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es la diferencia entre bits y bytes?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:856
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:902
msgid "Please enter valid file size and bandwidth values."
msgstr "Introduzca valores válidos de tamaño de archivo y ancho de banda."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:871
msgid "Please enter valid file size and time values."
msgstr "Introduzca valores de tiempo y tamaño de archivo válidos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:886
msgid "Please enter valid bandwidth and time values."
msgstr "Introduzca valores válidos de ancho de banda y tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:918
msgid "Please enter valid bandwidth value."
msgstr "Introduzca un valor de ancho de banda válido."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:925
msgid "Please provide at least one file in valid JSON format."
msgstr "Proporcione al menos un archivo en formato JSON válido."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:930
msgid "Invalid JSON format for files."
msgstr "Formato JSON no válido para archivos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:942
msgid "Please enter valid file size value."
msgstr "Introduzca un valor de tamaño de archivo válido."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:957
msgid "Please enter valid file size and cost values."
msgstr "Ingrese un tamaño de archivo válido y valores de costo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1021
msgid "Time required to transfer the file"
msgstr "Tiempo necesario para transferir el archivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1058
msgid "Required Bandwidth"
msgstr "Ancho de banda requerido"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1060
msgid "Minimum bandwidth needed"
msgstr "Ancho de banda mínimo necesario"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1069
msgid "bps"
msgstr "bps"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:1087
msgid "Maximum file size that can be transferred"
msgstr "Tamaño máximo de archivo que se puede transferir"

