msgstr "Calculadora de talla de sujetador"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:68
msgid ""
"Free online bra size calculator. Calculate your perfect bra size with "
"support for US, UK, EU, FR, AU, PK (Pakistan), CA, IN, NZ, IT, ES, DE, JP, "
"CN, BR, MX, ZA and more sizing systems. Get accurate measurements, sister "
"sizes, size conversions, and proper fit recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de talla de sujetador online gratuita. Calcule su talla de "
"sujetador perfecta con soporte para EE. UU., Reino Unido, UE, FR, AU, PK "
"(Pakistán), CA, IN, NZ, IT, ES, DE, JP, CN, BR, MX, ZA y más sistemas de "
"tallas. Obtenga medidas precisas, tallas hermanas, conversiones de tallas y "
"recomendaciones de ajuste adecuado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:75
msgid "Multiple sizing systems (US, UK, EU, FR, AU)"
msgstr ""
"Múltiples sistemas de tallas (EE.UU., Reino Unido, UE, Francia, Australia)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:76
