#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:467
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/shoe_size_conversion.html:109
msgid "Size Comparison"
msgstr "Comparación de tamaños"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:488
msgid "Bra size calculator illustration"
msgstr "Ilustración de calculadora de talla de sujetador"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:492
msgid "Enter your measurements to calculate your perfect bra size."
msgstr "Introduce tus medidas para calcular tu talla de sujetador perfecta."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:509
msgid "What is Bra Size?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la talla de sujetador?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"Bra size consists of two components: the band size (number) and the cup size"
" (letter). The band size is the measurement around your ribcage, typically "
"ranging from 28 to 50. The cup size represents the difference between your "
"bust and band measurements, ranging from AA to N."
msgstr ""
"La talla de sujetador consta de dos componentes: la talla de banda (número) "
"y la talla de copa (letra). El tamaño de la banda es la medida alrededor de "
"la caja torácica, que generalmente oscila entre 28 y 50. El tamaño de la "
"copa representa la diferencia entre las medidas del busto y la banda, que "
"van de AA a N."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:514
msgid "Bra Size = Band Size + Cup Size"
msgstr "Talla de sujetador = Talla de banda + Talla de copa"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"Understanding your correct bra size is essential for comfort, support, and "
"proper fit. This calculator helps you determine your bra size accurately "
"using standard measurement methods."
msgstr ""
"Comprender la talla correcta de sujetador es esencial para lograr comodidad,"
" soporte y un ajuste adecuado. Esta calculadora le ayuda a determinar con "
"precisión la talla de su sostén utilizando métodos de medición estándar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:525
msgid ""
"Select the calculation type: Calculate Bra Size, Size Conversion, or Sister "
"Sizes."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione el tipo de cálculo: Calcular talla de sujetador, Conversión de "
"talla o Tallas hermanas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:526
msgid ""
"Enter your measurements (underbust and bust) or bra size based on your "
"selected calculation type."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese sus medidas (bajo busto y busto) o talla de sujetador según el tipo "
"de cálculo seleccionado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:527
msgid "Select your preferred sizing system (US, UK, EU, FR, or AU)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione su sistema de tallas preferido (EE. UU., Reino Unido, UE, Francia"
" o Australia)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"Review the detailed breakdown, size comparisons, and step-by-step solution."
msgstr ""
"Revise el desglose detallado, las comparaciones de tamaños y la solución "
"paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:540
msgid ""
"Calculate your bra size from underbust and bust measurements. Get your size "
"in all sizing systems, sister sizes, and detailed calculations."
msgstr ""
"Calcula tu talla de sujetador a partir de las medidas de debajo del pecho y "
"del busto. Obtenga su talla en todos los sistemas de tallas, tallas hermanas"
" y cálculos detallados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:546
msgid ""
"Convert bra sizes between different sizing systems (US, UK, EU, FR, AU). "
"Useful when shopping from international brands."
msgstr ""
"Convierta tallas de sujetador entre diferentes sistemas de tallas (EE. UU., "
"Reino Unido, UE, Francia, Australia). Útil cuando se compran marcas "
"internacionales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:552
msgid ""
"Find sister sizes (alternative sizes with the same cup volume). Useful when "
"your regular size is not available or for trying different fits."
msgstr ""
"Encuentra tallas hermanas (tallas alternativas con el mismo volumen de "
"copa). Útil cuando su talla habitual no está disponible o para probar "
"diferentes calces."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:560
msgid "Sizing Systems"
msgstr "Sistemas de dimensionamiento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:563
msgid "US Sizing:"
msgstr "Tallas de EE. UU.:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:564
msgid ""
"Uses band sizes 28-50 and cup sizes AA, A, B, C, D, DD, DDD, G, H, I, J, K, "
"L, M, N."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza tallas de banda 28-50 y tallas de copa AA, A, B, C, D, DD, DDD, G, "
"H, I, J, K, L, M, N."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:567
msgid "UK Sizing:"
msgstr "Tallas del Reino Unido:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:568
msgid ""
"Uses the same band sizes as US but different cup progression: D, DD, E, F, "
"FF, G, GG, H, HH, J, JJ after C."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza los mismos tamaños de banda que EE. UU. pero con diferente "
"progresión de copa: D, DD, E, F, FF, G, GG, H, HH, J, JJ después de C."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:571
msgid "EU/FR Sizing:"
msgstr "Talla UE/FR:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:572
msgid ""
"EU uses similar cup sizes to US. FR uses cm-based band sizes (add 15 to US "
"band size) and similar cup progression."
msgstr ""
"La UE utiliza tamaños de copa similares a los de EE. UU. FR utiliza tamaños "
"de banda basados ​​en cm (agregue 15 al tamaño de banda de EE. UU.) y una "
"progresión de copa similar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:575
msgid "AU Sizing:"
msgstr "Talla AU:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:576
msgid ""
"Similar to UK sizing system with the same band and cup size progression."
msgstr ""
"Similar al sistema de tallas del Reino Unido con la misma progresión de "
"tallas de banda y copa."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:579
msgid "PK (Pakistan) Sizing:"
msgstr "PK (Pakistán) Tamaño:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:580
msgid ""
"Uses UK sizing system. Same band sizes and cup progression as UK (D, DD, E, "
"F, FF, G, GG, H, HH, J, JJ)."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza el sistema de tallas del Reino Unido. Mismos tamaños de banda y "
"progresión de copa que el Reino Unido (D, DD, E, F, FF, G, GG, H, HH, J, "
"JJ)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:583
msgid "CA (Canada) Sizing:"
msgstr "CA (Canadá) Tamaño:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:584
msgid ""
"Uses US sizing system. Same band sizes and cup progression as US (D, DD, "
"DDD, G, H, I, J, K, L, M, N)."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza el sistema de tallas de EE. UU. Mismos tamaños de banda y progresión"
" de copa que EE. UU. (D, DD, DDD, G, H, I, J, K, L, M, N)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:587
msgid "IN (India) Sizing:"
msgstr "EN (India) Tallas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:588
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:592
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:612
msgid "Uses UK sizing system. Same band sizes and cup progression as UK."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza el sistema de tallas del Reino Unido. Mismos tamaños de banda y "
"progresión de copa que el Reino Unido."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:591
msgid "NZ (New Zealand) Sizing:"
msgstr "Tallas de Nueva Zelanda (Nueva Zelanda):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:595
msgid "IT/ES/DE (Italy/Spain/Germany) Sizing:"
msgstr "IT/ES/DE (Italia/España/Alemania) Dimensionamiento:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:596
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:604
msgid "Uses EU sizing system. Same band sizes and cup progression as EU."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza el sistema de tallas de la UE. Mismos tamaños de banda y progresión "
"de copa que la UE."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:599
msgid "JP/CN (Japan/China) Sizing:"
msgstr "Tamaño JP/CN (Japón/China):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:600
msgid ""
"Uses similar sizing to EU system. Same band sizes and cup progression as EU."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza un tamaño similar al sistema de la UE. Mismos tamaños de banda y "
"progresión de copa que la UE."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:603
msgid "BR (Brazil) Sizing:"
msgstr "BR (Brasil) Tallas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:607
msgid "MX (Mexico) Sizing:"
msgstr "MX (México) Tallas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:608
msgid "Uses US sizing system. Same band sizes and cup progression as US."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza el sistema de tallas de EE. UU. Mismos tamaños de banda y progresión"
" de copa que EE. UU."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:611
msgid "ZA (South Africa) Sizing:"
msgstr "ZA (Sudáfrica) Tallas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:619
msgid "How to Measure"
msgstr "Cómo medir"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:622
msgid "Underbust Measurement"
msgstr "Medición debajo del busto"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:624
msgid ""
"Measure around your ribcage, directly under your bust. Keep the tape measure"
" level and snug but not tight. This measurement determines your band size."
msgstr ""
"Mide alrededor de tu caja torácica, directamente debajo de tu busto. "
"Mantenga la cinta métrica nivelada y ajustada, pero no apretada. Esta medida"
" determina el tamaño de su banda."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:628
msgid "Bust Measurement"
msgstr "Medida del busto"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:630
msgid ""
"Measure around the fullest part of your bust, typically at nipple level. "
"Keep the tape measure level and parallel to the ground. Wear a non-padded "
"bra for accurate measurement."
msgstr ""
"Mide alrededor de la parte más ancha de tu busto, generalmente a la altura "
"del pezón. Mantenga la cinta métrica nivelada y paralela al suelo. Use un "
"sostén sin relleno para una medición precisa."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:644
msgid ""
"Measurements should be taken while wearing a non-padded, well-fitting bra "
"for the most accurate results."
msgstr ""
"Las medidas deben tomarse mientras se usa un sostén sin relleno y que le "
"quede bien para obtener resultados más precisos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:650
msgid ""
"Bra sizes can vary between brands. Always try on bras when possible, and use"
" sister sizes if your regular size doesn't fit."
msgstr ""
"Las tallas de sujetador pueden variar según las marcas. Siempre pruébate "
"sujetadores cuando sea posible y usa tallas hermanas si tu talla habitual no"
" te queda bien."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:656
msgid ""
"If you're between sizes, try both the calculated size and sister sizes to "
"find the best fit for your body shape."
msgstr ""
"Si estás entre tallas, prueba tanto la talla calculada como las tallas "
"hermanas para encontrar la que mejor se ajuste a la forma de tu cuerpo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:698
msgid ""
"Bra sizing can vary between brands due to different manufacturing standards,"
" materials, and fit preferences. Always try on bras when possible, and use "
"sister sizes if your regular size doesn't fit in a particular brand."
msgstr ""
"La talla del sujetador puede variar entre marcas debido a los diferentes "
"estándares de fabricación, materiales y preferencias de ajuste. Siempre "
"pruébate sujetadores cuando sea posible y usa tallas hermanas si tu talla "
"habitual no encaja en una marca en particular."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:777
msgid "Please enter valid measurements."
msgstr "Por favor ingrese medidas válidas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:796
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:808
#: Other_Calculators/views/bra_size_calculator.py:200
#: Other_Calculators/views/bra_size_calculator.py:271
msgid "Please enter a bra size."
msgstr "Por favor introduce una talla de sujetador."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:857
msgid "Your Bra Size"
msgstr "Tu talla de sujetador"

