"combinaciones de banda y copa."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:4
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:8
msgid "BTU Calculator - Heating & Cooling Load Calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de BTU - Calculadora de carga de calefacción y refrigeración"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free BTU calculator for heating and cooling load calculations. Calculate "
"room BTU requirements, energy conversions, and cooling loads with step-by-"
"step solutions. Perfect for HVAC sizing and home improvement."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de BTU gratuita para cálculos de carga de calefacción y "
"refrigeración. Calcule los requisitos de BTU de la habitación, las "
"conversiones de energía y las cargas de refrigeración con soluciones paso a "
"paso. Perfecto para dimensionar HVAC y mejorar el hogar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"btu calculator, heating calculator, cooling calculator, energy calculator, "
"hvac calculator, btu per square foot, room heating calculator, air "
"conditioning calculator, hvac sizing calculator, btu conversion, energy "
"conversion calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de btu, calculadora de calefacción, calculadora de "
"refrigeración, calculadora de energía, calculadora de hvac, btu por pie "
"cuadrado, calculadora de calefacción de habitaciones, calculadora de aire "
"acondicionado, calculadora de tamaño de hvac, conversión de btu, calculadora"
" de conversión de energía"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Free BTU calculator for heating and cooling load calculations. Calculate "
"room BTU requirements, energy conversions, and cooling loads with step-by-"
"step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de BTU gratuita para cálculos de carga de calefacción y "
"refrigeración. Calcule los requisitos de BTU de la habitación, las "
"conversiones de energía y las cargas de refrigeración con soluciones paso a "
"paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:12
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:29
msgid "BTU Calculator - Professional Heating & Cooling Load Calculator"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de BTU - Calculadora profesional de carga de calefacción y "
"refrigeración"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Calculate heating and cooling BTU requirements for any room. Free online "
"calculator with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los requisitos de BTU de calefacción y refrigeración para cualquier "
"habitación. Calculadora online gratuita con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:42
msgid ""
"Free online BTU calculator for heating and cooling load calculations. "
"Calculate room BTU requirements, energy conversions, and cooling loads with "
"step-by-step solutions and visualizations."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de BTU en línea gratuita para cálculos de carga de calefacción y"
" refrigeración. Calcule los requisitos de BTU de la habitación, las "
"conversiones de energía y las cargas de refrigeración con visualizaciones y "
"soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:49
msgid "Room size BTU calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de BTU del tamaño de la habitación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:50
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:79
msgid "Area-based BTU calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de BTU basados ​​en el área"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:51
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:80
msgid "Energy unit conversions (kWh, Joules, Calories)"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de energía (kWh, julios, calorías)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:52
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:81
msgid "Cooling/heating load calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de carga de refrigeración/calefacción"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:53
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:82
msgid "Multiple room types and insulation factors"
msgstr "Múltiples tipos de habitaciones y factores de aislamiento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:54
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:83
msgid "Climate zone considerations"
msgstr "Consideraciones sobre la zona climática"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:57
msgid "Multiple measurement units"
msgstr "Múltiples unidades de medida"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:66
msgid "How to Calculate BTU Requirements for a Room"
msgstr "Cómo calcular los requisitos de BTU para una habitación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:67
msgid ""
"Step-by-step guide to calculate BTU requirements for heating and cooling a "
"room"
msgstr ""
"Guía paso a paso para calcular los requisitos de BTU para calentar y enfriar"
" una habitación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:71
msgid "Measure Room Dimensions"
msgstr "Medir las dimensiones de la habitación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:72
msgid "Measure the length, width, and height of your room in feet or meters."
msgstr "Mida el largo, ancho y alto de su habitación en pies o metros."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:76
msgid "Select Room Type"
msgstr "Seleccionar tipo de habitación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:77
msgid ""
"Choose the room type (bedroom, living room, kitchen, etc.) as different "
"rooms have different BTU requirements per square foot."
msgstr ""
"Elija el tipo de habitación (dormitorio, sala de estar, cocina, etc.), ya "
"que cada habitación tiene diferentes requisitos de BTU por pie cuadrado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:81
msgid "Determine Insulation Quality"
msgstr "Determinar la calidad del aislamiento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:82
msgid ""
"Select the insulation quality of your room (excellent, good, average, poor, "
"or none)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione la calidad del aislamiento de su habitación (excelente, buena, "
"media, mala o ninguna)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:86
msgid "Select Climate Zone"
msgstr "Seleccionar Zona Climática"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:87
msgid "Choose your climate zone based on average temperatures in your area."
msgstr "Elija su zona climática según las temperaturas promedio de su área."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:91
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:449
msgid "Calculate BTU"
msgstr "Calcular BTU"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:92
msgid ""
"The calculator will compute the total BTU required based on area, room type,"
" insulation, and climate zone."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora calculará el total de BTU requerido según el área, el tipo de"
" habitación, el aislamiento y la zona climática."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:105
msgid "What is BTU and why is it important?"
msgstr "¿Qué es BTU y por qué es importante?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:108
msgid ""
"BTU (British Thermal Unit) is a unit of energy used to measure heating and "
"cooling capacity. It represents the amount of energy needed to raise the "
"temperature of one pound of water by one degree Fahrenheit. BTU is important"
" for sizing HVAC systems correctly."
msgstr ""
"BTU (Unidad Térmica Británica) es una unidad de energía utilizada para medir"
" la capacidad de calefacción y refrigeración. Representa la cantidad de "
"energía necesaria para elevar la temperatura de una libra de agua en un "
"grado Fahrenheit. BTU es importante para dimensionar correctamente los "
"sistemas HVAC."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:113
msgid "How many BTU per square foot do I need?"
msgstr "¿Cuántos BTU por pie cuadrado necesito?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:116
msgid ""
"The standard rule is approximately 20 BTU per square foot for heating. "
"However, this varies based on room type (bedroom: 20, kitchen: 30, bathroom:"
" 15), insulation quality, and climate zone. Our calculator accounts for all "
"these factors."
msgstr ""
"La regla estándar es aproximadamente 20 BTU por pie cuadrado para "
"calefacción. Sin embargo, esto varía según el tipo de habitación "
"(dormitorios: 20, cocina: 30, baño: 15), la calidad del aislamiento y la "
"zona climática. Nuestra calculadora tiene en cuenta todos estos factores."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:121
msgid "How do I convert BTU to other energy units?"
msgstr "¿Cómo convierto BTU a otras unidades de energía?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:124
msgid ""
"You can convert BTU to kWh (1 BTU = 0.000293071 kWh), Joules (1 BTU = "
"1055.06 J), Calories (1 BTU = 252.164 cal), or Foot-Pounds (1 BTU = 778.169 "
"ft-lb). Use our unit conversion mode for accurate conversions."
msgstr ""
"Puede convertir BTU a kWh (1 BTU = 0,000293071 kWh), julios (1 BTU = 1055,06"
" J), calorías (1 BTU = 252,164 cal) o libras-pie (1 BTU = 778,169 ft-lb). "
"Utilice nuestro modo de conversión de unidades para realizar conversiones "
"precisas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:129
msgid "What factors affect BTU requirements?"
msgstr "¿Qué factores afectan los requisitos de BTU?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:132
msgid ""
"BTU requirements are affected by room size, room type, insulation quality, "
"climate zone, number of windows, number of occupants, and heat-generating "
"appliances. Our calculator considers all these factors."
msgstr ""
"Los requisitos de BTU se ven afectados por el tamaño y el tipo de "
"habitación, la calidad del aislamiento, la zona climática, la cantidad de "
"ventanas, la cantidad de ocupantes y los electrodomésticos que generan "
"calor. Nuestra calculadora considera todos estos factores."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:152
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:76
#: Other_Calculators/views/index.py:44
msgid "BTU Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de BTU"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:155
msgid ""
"Calculate heating and cooling BTU requirements for any room. Features "
"include room size calculations, energy unit conversions, cooling load "
"analysis, and step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los requisitos de BTU de calefacción y refrigeración para cualquier "
"habitación. Las características incluyen cálculos del tamaño de la "
"habitación, conversiones de unidades de energía, análisis de carga de "
"refrigeración y soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:165
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:161
msgid "Calculation modes"
msgstr "Modos de cálculo"

