#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:4
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:8
msgid "Concrete Calculator - Calculate Volume & Materials"
msgstr "Calculadora de hormigón: calcular volumen y materiales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free concrete calculator to calculate concrete volume and material "
"requirements. Calculate concrete needed for slabs, columns, footings, and "
"walls with step-by-step solutions. Perfect for construction projects and "
"home improvement."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de hormigón gratuita para calcular el volumen de hormigón y los "
"requisitos de material. Calcule el hormigón necesario para losas, columnas, "
"zapatas y muros con soluciones paso a paso. Perfecto para proyectos de "
"construcción y mejoras del hogar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"concrete calculator, concrete volume calculator, cement calculator, "
