"Calculadora de hormigón - Calculadora profesional de volumen y material"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Calculate concrete volume and material requirements. Free online calculator "
"with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcular el volumen de hormigón y los requisitos de materiales. Calculadora "
"online gratuita con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:42
msgid ""
"Free online concrete calculator for volume calculations and material "
"requirements. Calculate concrete needed for slabs, columns, footings, and "
"walls with step-by-step solutions and visualizations."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de hormigón en línea gratuita para cálculos de volumen y "
"requisitos de materiales. Calcule el hormigón necesario para losas, "
"columnas, zapatas y muros con visualizaciones y soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:49
msgid "Rectangular slab calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de losa rectangular."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:50
