msgstr "Cálculos de zapata"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:53
msgid "Wall calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de pared"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:54
msgid "Volume unit conversions"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de volumen"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:55
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:61
msgid "Material requirements (cement, sand, aggregate)"
msgstr "Requisitos de materiales (cemento, arena, áridos)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:56
msgid "Multiple mix ratios"
msgstr "Múltiples proporciones de mezcla"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:67
msgid "How to Calculate Concrete Volume and Materials"
msgstr "Cómo calcular el volumen y los materiales del hormigón"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:68
msgid ""
"Step-by-step guide to calculate concrete volume and material requirements "
"for construction projects"
msgstr ""
"Guía paso a paso para calcular el volumen de hormigón y los requisitos de "
"materiales para proyectos de construcción."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:72
msgid "Select Shape Type"
msgstr "Seleccionar tipo de forma"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:73
msgid ""
"Choose the shape of your concrete structure (rectangular slab, circular "
"slab, column, footing, or wall)."
msgstr ""
"Elija la forma de su estructura de concreto (losa rectangular, losa "
"circular, columna, zapata o muro)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:77
msgid "Enter Dimensions"
msgstr "Introducir dimensiones"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:78
msgid ""
"Enter the dimensions of your structure in feet or meters (length, width, "
"height/depth/thickness)."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese las dimensiones de su estructura en pies o metros (largo, ancho, "
"alto/profundidad/espesor)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:82
msgid "Select Mix Ratio"
msgstr "Seleccionar proporción de mezcla"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:83
msgid ""
"Choose the concrete mix ratio (e.g., 1:2:4 means 1 part cement, 2 parts "
"sand, 4 parts aggregate)."
msgstr ""
"Elija la proporción de mezcla de concreto (por ejemplo, 1:2:4 significa 1 "
"parte de cemento, 2 partes de arena, 4 partes de agregado)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:88
msgid ""
"The calculator will compute the volume and material requirements based on "
"your inputs."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora calculará los requisitos de volumen y material en función de "
"sus entradas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:101
msgid "How do I calculate concrete volume?"
msgstr "¿Cómo calculo el volumen del hormigón?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:104
msgid ""
"Concrete volume is calculated by multiplying length × width × height (or "
"thickness) for rectangular shapes, or π × r² × height for circular shapes. "
"Our calculator handles multiple shapes automatically."
msgstr ""
"El volumen de hormigón se calcula multiplicando largo × ancho × alto (o "
"espesor) para formas rectangulares, o π × r² × alto para formas circulares. "
"Nuestra calculadora maneja múltiples formas automáticamente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:109
msgid "What is a concrete mix ratio?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una proporción de mezcla de concreto?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:112
msgid ""
"A mix ratio like 1:2:4 means 1 part cement, 2 parts sand, and 4 parts "
"aggregate. Different ratios are used for different applications - 1:2:4 is "
"common for general construction."
msgstr ""
"Una proporción de mezcla como 1:2:4 significa 1 parte de cemento, 2 partes "
"de arena y 4 partes de agregado. Se utilizan diferentes proporciones para "
"diferentes aplicaciones: 1:2:4 es común para la construcción general."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:117
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:847
msgid "How many bags of cement do I need?"
msgstr "¿Cuántas bolsas de cemento necesito?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:120
msgid ""
"The number of cement bags depends on the volume of concrete and the mix "
"ratio. Each bag typically weighs 94 pounds. Our calculator automatically "
"calculates the required number of bags."
msgstr ""
"La cantidad de sacos de cemento depende del volumen de concreto y de la "
"proporción de mezcla. Cada bolsa suele pesar 94 libras. Nuestra calculadora "
"calcula automáticamente la cantidad de bolsas requeridas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:125
msgid "How do I convert cubic feet to cubic yards?"
msgstr "¿Cómo convierto pies cúbicos a yardas cúbicas?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:128
msgid ""
"1 cubic yard = 27 cubic feet. To convert, divide cubic feet by 27. Our "
"calculator includes a volume conversion mode for easy unit conversions."
msgstr ""
"1 yarda cúbica = 27 pies cúbicos. Para convertir, divida los pies cúbicos "
"entre 27. Nuestra calculadora incluye un modo de conversión de volumen para "
"realizar conversiones de unidades sencillas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:148
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:58
#: Other_Calculators/views/index.py:67
msgid "Concrete Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de Concreto"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/concrete_calculator.html:151
