msgid ""
"Calculate date differences, add/subtract time from dates, find weekdays, and"
" calculate business days. Free online date calculator with step-by-step "
"solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule diferencias de fechas, sume o reste tiempo de fechas, busque días "
