#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:164
msgid "Day Count Result"
msgstr "Resultado del recuento de días"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:194
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type and enter dates to see the day count with detailed"
" step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo e ingrese fechas para ver el recuento de días "
"con soluciones detalladas paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:210
msgid "What is a Day Counter?"
msgstr "¿Qué es un contador de días?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:212
msgid ""
"A day counter is a tool that calculates the number of days between dates, "
"days since a past date, days until a future date, or creates countdowns to "
"specific events. This calculator handles all calendar complexities including"
" leap years, varying month lengths, and year boundaries to provide accurate "
"day counts."
msgstr ""
"Un contador de días es una herramienta que calcula la cantidad de días entre"
" fechas, días desde una fecha pasada, días hasta una fecha futura o crea "
"cuentas regresivas para eventos específicos. Esta calculadora maneja todas "
"las complejidades del calendario, incluidos los años bisiestos, las "
"diferentes duraciones de los meses y los límites de los años para "
"proporcionar recuentos de días precisos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:219
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Days Between, Days Since, Days "
"Until, or Countdown)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Días entre, Días "
"desde, Días hasta o Cuenta regresiva)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:220
msgid "Enter the required dates in the input form."
msgstr "Ingrese las fechas requeridas en el formulario de entrada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:221
msgid "For countdown, optionally enter an event name."
msgstr "Para la cuenta regresiva, opcionalmente ingrese un nombre de evento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:222
msgid "Click 'Count Days' to see the results."
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Contar días' para ver los resultados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:233
msgid ""
"Calculate the exact number of days between two dates. Includes breakdown "
"into weeks, months, hours, minutes, seconds, and business days."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el número exacto de días entre dos fechas. Incluye desglose en "
"semanas, meses, horas, minutos, segundos y días hábiles."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:237
msgid ""
"Calculate how many days have passed since a past date. Useful for tracking "
"time elapsed since events, milestones, or important dates."
msgstr ""
"Calcula cuántos días han pasado desde una fecha pasada. Útil para realizar "
"un seguimiento del tiempo transcurrido desde eventos, hitos o fechas "
"importantes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:241
msgid ""
"Calculate how many days remain until a future date. Perfect for planning, "
"deadlines, and upcoming events."
msgstr ""
"Calcula cuántos días quedan hasta una fecha futura. Perfecto para "
"planificación, plazos y próximos eventos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:245
msgid ""
"Create a countdown to a specific event with an optional event name. Shows "
"days, weeks, months, hours, and minutes until the event."
msgstr ""
"Cree una cuenta regresiva para un evento específico con un nombre de evento "
"opcional. Muestra días, semanas, meses, horas y minutos hasta el evento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:253
msgid ""
"Business days are weekdays (Monday through Friday) excluding weekends. When "
"calculating days between dates, the calculator automatically excludes "
"Saturdays and Sundays. Business days are commonly used in:"
msgstr ""
"Los días hábiles son días laborables (de lunes a viernes), excluyendo los "
"fines de semana. Al calcular los días entre fechas, la calculadora excluye "
"automáticamente los sábados y domingos. Los días hábiles se utilizan "
"comúnmente en:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:264
msgid "Day Counting Methods"
msgstr "Métodos de conteo de días"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:266
msgid "Simple Subtraction:"
msgstr "Resta sencilla:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:266
msgid "For total days, we simply subtract the start date from the end date."
msgstr ""
"Para el total de días, simplemente restamos la fecha de inicio de la fecha "
"de finalización."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:267
msgid ""
"Used for precise year, month, and day breakdowns. Accounts for varying month"
" lengths and leap years."
msgstr ""
"Se utiliza para desgloses precisos de años, meses y días. Tiene en cuenta "
"diferentes duraciones de meses y años bisiestos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:352
#: Other_Calculators/views/day_counter.py:251
msgid "Event"
msgstr "Evento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:356
msgid "Counting..."
msgstr "Cálculo..."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:4
msgid ""
"Day Of The Week Calculator - Find Weekday for Any Date | Free Online Tool"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora del día de la semana: encuentre el día de la semana para "
"cualquier fecha | Herramienta en línea gratuita"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free day of the week calculator to find what day of the week any date falls "
"on, find next/previous occurrences, and count weekdays in a range. Perfect "
"for planning and scheduling."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora gratuita del día de la semana para encontrar en qué día de la "
"semana cae cualquier fecha, encontrar ocurrencias siguientes/anteriores y "
"contar los días de la semana en un rango. Perfecto para planificar y "
"programar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"day of the week calculator, weekday calculator, what day is, find weekday, "
"next monday calculator, previous friday calculator, count weekdays "
