msgid "Occurrences"
msgstr "Ocurrencias"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:267
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:267
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type and enter dates to find weekdays with detailed "
"step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo e ingrese fechas para encontrar días de semana"
" con soluciones detalladas paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:283
msgid "What is a Day Of The Week Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es una calculadora del día de la semana?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:285
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:285
msgid ""
"A day of week calculator is a tool that determines what day of the week any "
"date falls on, finds the next or previous occurrence of a specific weekday, "
"and counts how many times a weekday appears in a date range. This calculator"
" uses precise date arithmetic to handle all calendar complexities including "
"leap years and varying month lengths."
msgstr ""
"Una calculadora del día de la semana es una herramienta que determina en qué"
" día de la semana cae cualquier fecha, encuentra la aparición anterior o "
"siguiente de un día de la semana específico y cuenta cuántas veces aparece "
"un día de la semana en un rango de fechas. Esta calculadora utiliza "
"aritmética de fechas precisa para manejar todas las complejidades del "
"calendario, incluidos los años bisiestos y las diferentes duraciones de los "
"meses."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:292
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Find Day of Week, Next "
"Occurrence, Previous Occurrence, Count Weekdays, or Find All Occurrences)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Buscar día de la "
"semana, Siguiente ocurrencia, Ocurrencia anterior, Contar días laborables o "
"Buscar todas las ocurrencias)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:293
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:293
msgid "Enter the required dates and weekday information in the input form."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese las fechas requeridas y la información de los días de la semana en "
"el formulario de entrada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:305
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:305
msgid ""
"Enter any date to find what day of the week it falls on. Also shows if it's "
"a weekday or weekend."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese cualquier fecha para saber en qué día de la semana cae. También "
"muestra si es un día laborable o un fin de semana."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:309
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"Find the next occurrence of a specific weekday (e.g., next Monday) from a "
"given date."
msgstr ""
"Encuentre la siguiente aparición de un día de la semana específico (por "
"ejemplo, el próximo lunes) a partir de una fecha determinada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:313
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Find the previous occurrence of a specific weekday (e.g., last Friday) from "
"a given date."
msgstr ""
"Encuentre la ocurrencia anterior de un día de la semana específico (por "
"ejemplo, el viernes pasado) a partir de una fecha determinada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:317
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:317
msgid ""
"Count how many times a specific weekday occurs in a date range. Includes "
"visualization."
msgstr ""
"Cuente cuántas veces ocurre un día de la semana específico en un rango de "
"fechas. Incluye visualización."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:321
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:321
msgid ""
"Find all dates in a range that fall on a specific weekday. Lists up to 20 "
"occurrences."
msgstr ""
"Encuentre todas las fechas en un rango que caen en un día laborable "
"específico. Enumera hasta 20 ocurrencias."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:327
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:327
msgid "Understanding Weekdays"
msgstr "Entendiendo los días laborables"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:329
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:329
msgid "The calculator uses Python's weekday() method which returns:"
msgstr "La calculadora utiliza el método Weekday() de Python que devuelve:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:333
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:333
msgid "0 = Monday"
msgstr "0 = lunes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:334
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:334
msgid "1 = Tuesday"
msgstr "1 = martes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:335
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:335
msgid "2 = Wednesday"
msgstr "2 = miércoles"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:336
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:336
msgid "3 = Thursday"
msgstr "3 = jueves"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:337
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:337
msgid "4 = Friday"
msgstr "4 = viernes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:338
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:338
msgid "5 = Saturday"
msgstr "5 = sábado"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:339
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:339
msgid "6 = Sunday"
msgstr "6 = domingo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:343
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Weekdays are Monday through Friday, while weekends are Saturday and Sunday."
msgstr ""
"Los días laborables son de lunes a viernes, mientras que los fines de semana"
" son sábado y domingo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:353
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:353
msgid "The calculator uses the Gregorian calendar system."
msgstr "La calculadora utiliza el sistema de calendario gregoriano."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:480
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:480
msgid "Weekend"
msgstr "Fin de semana"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:499
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:503
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:499
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:503
msgid "occurrences of"
msgstr "ocurrencias de"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:4
msgid "Day of Week Calculator - Find Weekday for Any Date | Free Online Tool"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora del día de la semana: encuentre el día de la semana para "
"cualquier fecha | Herramienta en línea gratuita"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free day of week calculator to find what day of the week any date falls on, "
"find next/previous occurrences, and count weekdays in a range. Perfect for "
"planning and scheduling."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora gratuita del día de la semana para encontrar en qué día de la "
"semana cae cualquier fecha, encontrar ocurrencias siguientes/anteriores y "
"contar los días de la semana en un rango. Perfecto para planificar y "
"programar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"day of week calculator, weekday calculator, what day is, find weekday, next "
"monday calculator, previous friday calculator, count weekdays calculator, "
"day finder, what day of the week, weekday finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora del día de la semana, calculadora de días laborables, qué día "
"es, encontrar el día de la semana, calculadora del próximo lunes, "
"calculadora del viernes anterior, calculadora de contar los días de la "
"semana, buscador de días, qué día de la semana, buscador de días de la "
"semana"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:31
msgid ""
"Free online day of week calculator to find what day of the week any date "
"falls on, find next/previous occurrences, and count weekdays with step-by-"
"step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora gratuita en línea del día de la semana para encontrar en qué día"
" de la semana cae cualquier fecha, encontrar ocurrencias "
"siguientes/anteriores y contar los días de la semana con soluciones paso a "
"paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:50
