"Calculadora de densidad gratuita para calcular la densidad a partir de masa "
"y volumen, calcular masa a partir de densidad y volumen, o calcular volumen "
"a partir de densidad y masa. Perfecto para física, química e ingeniería."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"density calculator, calculate density, mass calculator, volume calculator, "
"density formula, mass density volume, unit converter, density mass volume "
"calculator, material density calculator, liquid density calculator, solid "
"density calculator, density unit converter"
