#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:327
msgid "What is Density?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la densidad?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:329
msgid ""
"Density is a physical property that measures the mass per unit volume of a "
"substance. It is calculated using the formula: Density = Mass ÷ Volume. "
"Density helps identify materials, determine purity, and understand physical "
"properties. Different materials have different densities - for example, "
"water has a density of 1000 kg/m³, while gold has a density of 19,300 kg/m³."
msgstr ""
"La densidad es una propiedad física que mide la masa por unidad de volumen "
"de una sustancia. Se calcula mediante la fórmula: Densidad = Masa ÷ Volumen."
" La densidad ayuda a identificar materiales, determinar la pureza y "
"comprender las propiedades físicas. Los distintos materiales tienen "
"diferentes densidades: por ejemplo, el agua tiene una densidad de 1.000 "
"kg/m³, mientras que el oro tiene una densidad de 19.300 kg/m³."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Calculate Density, Calculate "
"Mass, Calculate Volume, or Convert Units)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Calcular densidad, "
"Calcular masa, Calcular volumen o Convertir unidades)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:337
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dew_point_calculator.html:294
