msgid "Select appropriate units for your inputs and desired result."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione las unidades apropiadas para sus entradas y el resultado deseado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:349
msgid ""
"Enter mass and volume to calculate density. Formula: Density = Mass ÷ "
"Volume."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la masa y el volumen para calcular la densidad. Fórmula: Densidad = "
"Masa ÷ Volumen."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:353
msgid ""
"Enter density and volume to calculate mass. Formula: Mass = Density × "
"Volume."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la densidad y el volumen para calcular la masa. Fórmula: Masa = "
"Densidad × Volumen."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"Enter density and mass to calculate volume. Formula: Volume = Mass ÷ "
"Density."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la densidad y la masa para calcular el volumen. Fórmula: Volumen = "
"Masa ÷ Densidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/density_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Convert density values between different units (kg/m³, g/cm³, lb/ft³, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Convierta valores de densidad entre diferentes unidades (kg/m³, g/cm³, "
"lb/ft³, etc.)."

