#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:157
msgid "Modifier"
msgstr "Modificador"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:160
msgid "Add or subtract from the total (e.g., +2, -1)"
msgstr "Sumar o restar del total (por ejemplo, +2, -1)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:190
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:511
msgid "Roll Result"
msgstr "Resultado de la tirada"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:220
msgid ""
"Select a roll type and configure your dice to see results with detailed "
"statistics and visualizations."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona un tipo de tirada y configura tus dados para ver resultados con "
"estadísticas y visualizaciones detalladas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:236
msgid "What is a Dice Roller?"
msgstr "¿Qué es un rodillo de dados?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:238
msgid ""
"A dice roller is a tool that simulates rolling dice using random number "
"generation. It's commonly used in tabletop games, board games, and role-"
"playing games (RPGs) like Dungeons & Dragons. The dice roller generates "
"random numbers within the specified range, ensuring fair and unbiased "
"results."
msgstr ""
"Un lanzador de dados es una herramienta que simula tirar dados mediante la "
"generación de números aleatorios. Se usa comúnmente en juegos de mesa, "
"juegos de mesa y juegos de rol (RPG) como Dungeons & Dragons. El rodillo de "
"dados genera números aleatorios dentro del rango especificado, lo que "
"garantiza resultados justos e imparciales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:245
msgid ""
"Select a roll type from the dropdown (Single Die, Multiple Dice, or Custom "
"Dice)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de tirada en el menú desplegable (Dado único, Dados "
"múltiples o Dados personalizados)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:246
msgid "Choose the dice type (D4, D6, D8, D10, D12, D20, D100, or Custom)."
msgstr ""
"Elija el tipo de dado (D4, D6, D8, D10, D12, D20, D100 o Personalizado)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:247
msgid "If rolling multiple dice, specify the number of dice."
msgstr "Si tira varios dados, especifique el número de dados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:248
msgid "For custom dice, you can add modifiers to the total."
msgstr "Para dados personalizados, puedes agregar modificadores al total."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:249
msgid "Click 'Roll Dice' to generate results."
msgstr "Haga clic en 'Tira los dados' para generar resultados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:250
msgid "Review the results, statistics, and visualizations."
msgstr "Revisar los resultados, estadísticas y visualizaciones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:255
msgid "Roll Types"
msgstr "Tipos de rollo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:259
msgid "Roll one die of any type. Perfect for simple rolls or testing."
msgstr ""
"Tira un dado de cualquier tipo. Perfecto para rollos simples o pruebas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:263
msgid ""
"Roll multiple dice of the same type. Get total, average, and statistics."
msgstr ""
"Tira varios dados del mismo tipo. Obtenga total, promedio y estadísticas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:267
msgid "Roll custom dice with any number of sides and add modifiers."
msgstr ""
"Tira dados personalizados con cualquier número de caras y agrega "
"modificadores."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:273
msgid "Standard Dice Types"
msgstr "Tipos de dados estándar"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:278
msgid "Dice"
msgstr "Dados"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:284
msgid "Damage rolls, small random effects"
msgstr "Tiradas de daño, pequeños efectos aleatorios."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:285
msgid "Standard board games, most common"
msgstr "Juegos de mesa estándar, los más comunes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:286
msgid "RPG damage, weapon damage"
msgstr "Daño de RPG, daño de arma"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:287
msgid "Percentile rolls, RPG systems"
msgstr "Rollos percentiles, sistemas RPG."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:288
msgid "RPG damage, special abilities"
msgstr "Daño RPG, habilidades especiales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:289
msgid "D&D attack rolls, skill checks"
msgstr "Tiradas de ataque de D&D, pruebas de habilidad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:290
msgid "Percentile rolls, random tables"
msgstr "Rollos de percentiles, tablas aleatorias."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:299
msgid "All dice rolls use cryptographically secure random number generation."
msgstr ""
"Todas las tiradas de dados utilizan generación de números aleatorios "
"criptográficamente segura."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:300
msgid "Each side of a die has an equal probability of being rolled."
msgstr "Cada lado de un dado tiene la misma probabilidad de ser lanzado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:301
msgid "You can roll up to 100 dice at once."
msgstr "Puedes tirar hasta 100 dados a la vez."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:302
msgid "Custom dice can have between 2 and 1000 sides."
msgstr "Los dados personalizados pueden tener entre 2 y 1000 caras."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:303
msgid "Modifiers can be positive or negative and are added to the total."
msgstr ""
"Los modificadores pueden ser positivos o negativos y se suman al total."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:304
msgid ""
"Statistics include minimum, maximum, mean, median, mode, and standard "
"deviation."
msgstr ""
"Las estadísticas incluyen mínimo, máximo, media, mediana, moda y desviación "
"estándar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:410
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:424
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:442
msgid "Number of sides"
msgstr "Número de lados"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:433
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:450
msgid "Number of dice"
msgstr "numero de dados"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:462
#: Other_Calculators/views/dice_roller.py:329
msgid "Modifier must be between -1000 and 1000."
msgstr "El modificador debe estar entre -1000 y 1000."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:475
msgid "Rolling..."
msgstr "Laminación..."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/dice_roller.html:519
msgid "Probability per Side"
msgstr "Probabilidad por lado"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:4
msgid ""
"Electricity Calculator - Calculate Power, Voltage, Current, Resistance "
"Online"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de electricidad: calcule potencia, voltaje, corriente y "
"resistencia en línea"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free online electricity calculator to calculate power, voltage, current, "
"resistance, energy, and cost. Supports multiple calculation methods with "
"step-by-step solutions and visualizations."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de electricidad en línea gratuita para calcular potencia, "
"voltaje, corriente, resistencia, energía y costo. Admite múltiples métodos "
"de cálculo con soluciones y visualizaciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"electricity calculator, calculate power, power calculator, voltage "
"calculator, current calculator, resistance calculator, ohm's law calculator,"
" electrical calculations, energy calculator, electricity cost calculator, "
"electrical power calculator, watts calculator, amps calculator, volts "
"calculator, electrical engineering calculator, PIVR calculator, electricity "
"finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de electricidad, calcular potencia, calculadora de potencia, "
"calculadora de voltaje, calculadora de corriente, calculadora de "
"resistencia, calculadora de ley de ohm, cálculos eléctricos, calculadora de "
"energía, calculadora de costos de electricidad, calculadora de energía "
"eléctrica, calculadora de vatios, calculadora de amperios, calculadora de "
"voltios, calculadora de ingeniería eléctrica, calculadora PIVR, buscador de "
"electricidad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:8
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:12
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:26
