"resistencia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Calculate power, voltage, current, resistance, energy, and cost with step-"
"by-step solutions and visualizations."
msgstr ""
"Calcule potencia, voltaje, corriente, resistencia, energía y costo con "
"soluciones y visualizaciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:13
