#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:811
msgid "Power Formulas:"
msgstr "Fórmulas de poder:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:813
msgid "(Power from voltage and current)"
msgstr "(Energía de voltaje y corriente)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:814
msgid "(Power from voltage and resistance)"
msgstr "(Energía a partir de voltaje y resistencia)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:815
msgid "(Power from current and resistance)"
msgstr "(Poder de corriente y resistencia)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:816
msgid "(Energy from power and time)"
msgstr "(Energía del poder y el tiempo)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:820
msgid ""
"Ohm's law is a fundamental principle in electrical engineering that "
"describes the relationship between voltage, current, and resistance in an "
"electrical circuit. The power formulas allow you to calculate electrical "
"power consumption in various ways depending on the known parameters."
msgstr ""
"La ley de Ohm es un principio fundamental en ingeniería eléctrica que "
"describe la relación entre voltaje, corriente y resistencia en un circuito "
"eléctrico. Las fórmulas de potencia permiten calcular el consumo de energía "
"eléctrica de diversas formas en función de los parámetros conocidos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:825
