#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:868
msgid ""
"Resistance must be greater than zero for calculations involving division by "
"resistance."
msgstr ""
"La resistencia debe ser mayor que cero para los cálculos que implican "
"división por resistencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/electricity_calculator.html:869
