#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:415
msgid "Truck/SUV"
msgstr "Camioneta/SUV"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:416
msgid "Supercar"
msgstr "superdeportivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"RPM must be greater than zero when used as a divisor in torque calculations."
msgstr ""
"Las RPM deben ser mayores que cero cuando se usan como divisor en los "
"cálculos de torque."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:427
msgid ""
"Torque must be greater than zero when used as a divisor in RPM calculations."
msgstr ""
"El torque debe ser mayor que cero cuando se usa como divisor en los cálculos"
" de RPM."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:428
msgid ""
"The constant 5252 is specific to lb⋅ft and HP units. For metric units, "
"conversions are applied first."
msgstr ""
"La constante 5252 es específica de unidades lb⋅ft y HP. Para unidades "
"métricas, las conversiones se aplican primero."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:429
msgid ""
"Horsepower and torque are related but measure different aspects of engine "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Los caballos de fuerza y ​​el par están relacionados, pero miden diferentes "
"aspectos del rendimiento del motor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:430
msgid ""
"Peak horsepower and peak torque typically occur at different RPM values."
msgstr ""
"La potencia máxima y el par máximo generalmente ocurren a diferentes valores"
" de RPM."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:439
msgid "Automotive performance analysis and tuning"
msgstr "Análisis y ajuste del rendimiento del automóvil."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/engine_horsepower_calculator.html:440
