"Free fuel cost calculator to calculate trip fuel cost, cost per mile/km, "
"fuel efficiency (MPG/L per 100km), distance, and fuel needed. Perfect for "
"planning road trips and tracking gas expenses."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de costo de combustible gratuita para calcular el costo del "
"combustible del viaje, el costo por milla/km, la eficiencia del combustible "
"(MPG/L por 100 km), la distancia y el combustible necesario. Perfecto para "
"planificar viajes por carretera y realizar un seguimiento de los gastos de "
"gasolina."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"fuel cost calculator, trip cost calculator, MPG calculator, fuel efficiency "
"calculator, gas cost calculator, fuel economy calculator, gas mileage "
"calculator, fuel consumption calculator, trip fuel cost, cost per mile "
