#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:411
msgid "What is Fuel Cost Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la calculadora de costos de combustible?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"The Fuel Cost Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating fuel-"
"related expenses and efficiency metrics. It helps you estimate trip costs, "
"determine fuel efficiency (MPG or L/100km), calculate distances, and convert"
" between different units. This calculator is essential for trip planning, "
"budgeting, and understanding your vehicle's fuel economy."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de costos de combustible es una herramienta integral para "
"calcular los gastos relacionados con el combustible y las métricas de "
"eficiencia. Le ayuda a estimar los costos del viaje, determinar la "
"eficiencia del combustible (MPG o L/100 km), calcular distancias y convertir"
" entre diferentes unidades. Esta calculadora es esencial para planificar "
"viajes, hacer presupuestos y comprender el consumo de combustible de su "
"vehículo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Total Cost, Cost Per Distance, "
"Fuel Efficiency, Distance, Fuel Needed, or Unit Conversions)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Costo total, Costo por"
" distancia, Eficiencia de combustible, Distancia, Combustible necesario o "
"Conversiones de unidades)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:433
msgid ""
"Calculate the total fuel cost for a trip. Enter distance, fuel efficiency "
"(MPG or L/100km), and fuel price. Formula: Cost = (Distance / Efficiency) × "
"Price."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el costo total de combustible para un viaje. Ingrese la distancia, "
"la eficiencia del combustible (MPG o L/100 km) y el precio del combustible. "
"Fórmula: Costo = (Distancia / Eficiencia) × Precio."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Calculate fuel cost per mile or kilometer. Enter fuel efficiency and price. "
"Formula: Cost per distance = Price / Efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el costo de combustible por milla o kilómetro. Ingrese la eficiencia"
" del combustible y el precio. Fórmula: Costo por distancia = Precio / "
"Eficiencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:441
msgid ""
"Calculate fuel efficiency (MPG or L/100km) from distance traveled and fuel "
"used. Formula: Efficiency = Distance / Fuel."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la eficiencia del combustible (MPG o L/100 km) a partir de la "
"distancia recorrida y el combustible utilizado. Fórmula: Eficiencia = "
"Distancia / Combustible."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Calculate distance that can be traveled with a given amount of fuel and "
"efficiency. Formula: Distance = Fuel × Efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Calcula la distancia que se puede recorrer con una determinada cantidad de "
"combustible y eficiencia. Fórmula: Distancia = Combustible × Eficiencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"Calculate fuel needed for a specific distance. Enter distance and fuel "
"efficiency. Formula: Fuel = Distance / Efficiency."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el combustible necesario para una distancia específica. Introduzca "
"la distancia y la eficiencia del combustible. Fórmula: Combustible = "
"Distancia / Eficiencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:453
msgid ""
"Convert between distance units (miles/km) and fuel volume units "
"(gallons/liters)."
msgstr ""
"Convierta entre unidades de distancia (millas/km) y unidades de volumen de "
"combustible (galones/litros)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:459
msgid "Fuel Efficiency Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de eficiencia de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:461
msgid "MPG (Miles Per Gallon):"
msgstr "MPG (millas por galón):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:463
msgid "L/100km (Liters Per 100 Kilometers):"
msgstr "L/100km (Litros Por 100 Kilómetros):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:465
msgid "Conversion:"
msgstr "Conversión:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"MPG (Miles Per Gallon) is the US standard for measuring fuel efficiency, "
"representing how many miles a vehicle can travel on one gallon of fuel. "
"L/100km (Liters Per 100 Kilometers) is the metric standard, representing how"
" many liters of fuel are needed to travel 100 kilometers. Lower L/100km "
"values indicate better fuel efficiency."
msgstr ""
"MPG (Millas por galón) es el estándar estadounidense para medir la "
"eficiencia del combustible y representa cuántas millas puede viajar un "
"vehículo con un galón de combustible. L/100 km (litros por 100 kilómetros) "
"es el estándar métrico y representa cuántos litros de combustible se "
"necesitan para recorrer 100 kilómetros. Los valores más bajos de L/100 km "
"indican una mejor eficiencia de combustible."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:480
msgid "Distance Units"
msgstr "Unidades de distancia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:483
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:490
msgid "Metric standard"
msgstr "estándar métrico"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:487
msgid "Fuel Volume Units"
msgstr "Unidades de volumen de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:494
msgid "Fuel Efficiency Units"
msgstr "Unidades de eficiencia de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:496
msgid "Miles Per Gallon"
msgstr "Millas por galón"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:497
msgid "Liters Per 100 Kilometers"
msgstr "Litros por 100 kilómetros"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:501
msgid "Price Units"
msgstr "Precio Unidades"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:503
msgid "USD per gallon"
msgstr "USD por galón"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:504
msgid "USD per liter"
msgstr "USD por litro"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:511
msgid "Typical Fuel Efficiency Values"
msgstr "Valores típicos de eficiencia de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:523
msgid "Hybrid Car"
msgstr "Coche híbrido"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:523
msgid "Excellent fuel economy"
msgstr "Excelente economía de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:524
msgid "Good fuel economy"
msgstr "Buena economía de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:525
msgid "SUV/Truck"
msgstr "SUV/camioneta"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:525
msgid "Moderate fuel economy"
msgstr "Economía de combustible moderada"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:526
msgid "Lower fuel economy"
msgstr "Menor economía de combustible"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:536
msgid "Fuel efficiency must be greater than zero for all calculations."
msgstr ""
"La eficiencia del combustible debe ser mayor que cero para todos los "
"cálculos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:537
msgid ""
"Distance and fuel used must be greater than zero when used in efficiency "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
"La distancia y el combustible utilizados deben ser mayores que cero cuando "
"se utilizan en los cálculos de eficiencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:538
msgid ""
"The calculator automatically handles unit conversions between imperial and "
"metric systems."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora maneja automáticamente las conversiones de unidades entre los"
" sistemas imperial y métrico."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:539
msgid ""
"MPG and L/100km are inversely related - higher MPG means lower L/100km."
msgstr ""
"MPG y L/100 km están inversamente relacionados: más MPG significa menos "
"L/100 km."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:540
msgid "Fuel prices can vary significantly by location and time."
msgstr ""
"Los precios del combustible pueden variar significativamente según la "
"ubicación y la hora."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:541
msgid ""
"Actual fuel efficiency may vary based on driving conditions, vehicle "
"maintenance, and driving habits."
msgstr ""
"La eficiencia de combustible real puede variar según las condiciones de "
"conducción, el mantenimiento del vehículo y los hábitos de conducción."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:549
msgid "Trip planning and budget estimation"
msgstr "Planificación de viajes y estimación de presupuesto."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:550
msgid "Comparing fuel costs between different vehicles"
msgstr "Comparación de costos de combustible entre diferentes vehículos"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:551
msgid "Tracking fuel efficiency over time"
msgstr "Seguimiento de la eficiencia del combustible a lo largo del tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:552
msgid "Determining fuel needed for long-distance travel"
msgstr "Determinar el combustible necesario para viajes de larga distancia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:553
msgid "Calculating cost per mile for business expenses"
msgstr "Calcular el costo por milla para gastos comerciales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:554
msgid "Understanding vehicle fuel economy"
msgstr "Comprender la economía de combustible del vehículo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:555
msgid "Planning fuel stops for road trips"
msgstr "Planificación de paradas de combustible para viajes por carretera"

