msgid "Population"
msgstr "Población"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:230
msgid "Thousands"
msgstr "Miles"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:241
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:657
#: Other_Calculators/views/gdp_calculator.py:1038
msgid "Nominal GDP"
msgstr "PIB nominal"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:254
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:661
#: Other_Calculators/views/gdp_calculator.py:1038
msgid "Real GDP"
msgstr "PIB real"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:264
msgid "GDP Value"
msgstr "Valor del PIB"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:345
msgid "Calculate GDP"
msgstr "Calcular el PIB"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:362
msgid "What is GDP?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el PIB?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"Gross Domestic Product (GDP) is the total monetary value of all finished "
"goods and services produced within a country's borders in a specific time "
"period. It serves as a comprehensive measure of a nation's economic "
"performance and is used to compare the economic output of different "
"countries. GDP can be calculated using three approaches: expenditure, "
"income, and production (value-added)."
msgstr ""
"El Producto Interno Bruto (PIB) es el valor monetario total de todos los "
"bienes y servicios terminados producidos dentro de las fronteras de un país "
"en un período de tiempo específico. Sirve como una medida integral del "
"desempeño económico de una nación y se utiliza para comparar la producción "
"económica de diferentes países. El PIB se puede calcular utilizando tres "
"enfoques: gasto, ingreso y producción (valor agregado)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:371
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Expenditure Approach, Income "
"Approach, Growth Rate, GDP Per Capita, GDP Deflator, or Convert Units)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Enfoque de gasto, "
"Enfoque de ingreso, Tasa de crecimiento, PIB per cápita, Deflactor del PIB o"
" Convertir unidades)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:373
msgid "Select appropriate units (millions, billions, or trillions)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione las unidades apropiadas (millones, miles de millones o billones)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"Calculate GDP using: GDP = C + I + G + (X - M), where C=Consumption, "
"I=Investment, G=Government, X=Exports, M=Imports."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el PIB usando: PIB = C + I + G + (X - M), donde C=Consumo, "
"I=Inversión, G=Gobierno, X=Exportaciones, M=Importaciones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Calculate GDP using: GDP = W + R + I + P, where W=Wages, R=Rent, I=Interest,"
" P=Profit."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el PIB usando: PIB = W + R + I + P, donde W=Salarios, R=Renta, "
"I=Interés, P=Beneficio."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:392
msgid "Calculate GDP growth rate: ((Current - Previous) / Previous) × 100."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la tasa de crecimiento del PIB: ((Actual - Anterior) / Anterior) × "
"100."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:396
msgid "Calculate GDP per person: GDP / Population."
msgstr "Calcular PIB por persona: PIB / Población."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:400
msgid "Calculate price level indicator: (Nominal GDP / Real GDP) × 100."
msgstr ""
"Calcular el indicador de nivel de precios: (PIB nominal / PIB real) × 100."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:404
msgid "Convert between millions, billions, and trillions."
msgstr "Convierta entre millones, miles de millones y billones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:410
msgid "Key GDP Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave del PIB"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:412
msgid "Expenditure Approach:"
msgstr "Enfoque de gasto:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:414
msgid "Income Approach:"
msgstr "Enfoque de ingresos:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:416
msgid "Growth Rate:"
msgstr "Índice de crecimiento:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:418
msgid "GDP Per Capita:"
msgstr "PIB per cápita:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:420
msgid "GDP Deflator:"
msgstr "Deflactor del PIB:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:428
msgid ""
"All input values must be non-negative (except profit which can be negative)."
msgstr ""
"Todos los valores de entrada no deben ser negativos (excepto el beneficio, "
"que puede ser negativo)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:429
msgid ""
"Previous GDP and Real GDP cannot be zero for growth rate and deflator "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
"El PIB anterior y el PIB real no pueden ser cero para los cálculos de la "
"tasa de crecimiento y del deflactor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:430
msgid "Population must be greater than zero for per capita calculations."
msgstr "La población debe ser mayor que cero para los cálculos per cápita."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"The calculator automatically handles unit conversions between millions, "
"billions, and trillions."
msgstr ""
"La calculadora maneja automáticamente conversiones de unidades entre "
"millones, miles de millones y billones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Expenditure and income approaches should yield the same GDP value in theory."
msgstr ""
"En teoría, los enfoques de gasto e ingreso deberían arrojar el mismo valor "
"del PIB."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:433
msgid "GDP deflator of 100 means no inflation; above 100 indicates inflation."
msgstr ""
"Un deflactor del PIB de 100 significa que no hay inflación; por encima de "
"100 indica inflación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:441
msgid "Economic analysis and policy making"
msgstr "Análisis económico y formulación de políticas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:442
msgid "Comparing economic performance between countries"
msgstr "Comparación del desempeño económico entre países"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:443
msgid "Measuring economic growth over time"
msgstr "Medir el crecimiento económico a lo largo del tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:444
msgid "Assessing standard of living (GDP per capita)"
msgstr "Evaluación del nivel de vida (PIB per cápita)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:445
msgid "Calculating inflation rates (GDP deflator)"
msgstr "Calcular las tasas de inflación (deflactor del PIB)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:446
msgid "Economic forecasting and planning"
msgstr "Previsión y planificación económica."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:447
msgid "Academic research and education"
msgstr "Investigación académica y educación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:543
msgid "Please enter valid numbers."
msgstr "Por favor ingrese números válidos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:597
msgid "Government (G)"
msgstr "Gobierno (G)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:601
msgid "Net Exports (X-M)"
msgstr "Exportaciones Netas (X-M)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:640
msgid "thousands per person"
msgstr "miles por persona"

