msgstr "Puntuación bruta"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:174
#, python-format
msgid "Handicap Allowance (%%)"
msgstr "Subsidio por discapacidad (%%)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:235
msgid "Calculate Golf Handicap"
msgstr "Calcular hándicap de golf"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:252
msgid "What is Golf Handicap?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el hándicap de golf?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:254
msgid ""
"A golf handicap is a numerical measure of a golfer's potential ability. The "
"World Handicap System (WHS) provides a unified and more inclusive "
"handicapping system for golfers worldwide. It allows players of different "
"skill levels to compete fairly by adjusting scores based on course "
"difficulty and player ability."
msgstr ""
"Un handicap de golf es una medida numérica de la habilidad potencial de un "
"golfista. El World Handicap System (WHS) proporciona un sistema de handicap "
"unificado y más inclusivo para golfistas de todo el mundo. Permite a los "
"jugadores de diferentes niveles competir de manera justa ajustando las "
"puntuaciones según la dificultad del campo y la capacidad del jugador."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:261
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Handicap Index, Course "
"Handicap, Score Differential, Net Score, or Playing Handicap)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Índice de hándicap, "
"Hándicap del campo, Diferencial de puntuación, Puntuación neta o Hándicap de"
" juego)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:273
msgid ""
"Calculate Handicap Index from score differentials. Uses best 8 of last 20 "
"differentials (WHS standard). Formula: Average of best differentials × 0.96."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el índice de desventaja a partir de las diferencias de puntuación. "
"Utiliza los 8 mejores diferenciales de los últimos 20 (estándar WHS). "
"Fórmula: Promedio de mejores diferenciales × 0,96."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:277
msgid ""
"Calculate Course Handicap from Handicap Index. Formula: CH = (HI × SR / 113)"
" + (CR - Par)."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el hándicap del campo a partir del índice de hándicap. Fórmula: CH ="
" (HI × SR / 113) + (CR - Par)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Calculate Score Differential from round score. Formula: SD = (AGS - CR) × "
"(113 / SR)."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el diferencial de puntuación de la puntuación de la ronda. Fórmula: "
"SD = (AGS - CR) × (113 / SR)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:285
msgid ""
"Calculate Net Score from Gross Score and Course Handicap. Formula: Net = "
"Gross - Course Handicap."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el puntaje neto a partir del puntaje bruto y el hándicap del campo. "
"Fórmula: Neto = Bruto - Hándicap del campo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"Calculate Playing Handicap with allowance percentage. Formula: PH = CH × "
"(Allowance / 100)."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el hándicap de juego con el porcentaje de asignación. Fórmula: PH = "
"CH × (Asignación / 100)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:295
msgid "Key Golf Handicap Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave de hándicap de golf"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:297
msgid "Handicap Index (WHS):"
msgstr "Índice de discapacidad (WHS):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:299
msgid "Course Handicap:"
msgstr "Hándicap del campo:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:301
msgid "Score Differential:"
msgstr "Diferencial de puntuación:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:303
msgid "Net Score:"
msgstr "Puntuación neta:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:305
msgid "Playing Handicap:"
msgstr "Hándicap de juego:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:314
msgid "Standard Slope Rating"
msgstr "Clasificación de pendiente estándar"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:322
msgid "Handicap Index ranges from 0 to 54 (lower is better)."
msgstr "El índice de discapacidad varía de 0 a 54 (cuanto más bajo, mejor)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:323
msgid "Slope Rating ranges from 55 to 155 (113 is standard)."
msgstr "La calificación de pendiente varía de 55 a 155 (113 es estándar)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:324
msgid "Course Rating typically ranges from 60 to 80."
msgstr "La calificación del curso normalmente oscila entre 60 y 80."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"WHS uses best 8 of last 20 score differentials for Handicap Index "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"WHS utiliza los 8 mejores diferenciales de puntaje de los últimos 20 para el"
" cálculo del índice de discapacidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:326
msgid "Score differentials must be between 0 and 200."
msgstr "Los diferenciales de puntuación deben estar entre 0 y 200."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:327
msgid "Course Handicap can be negative for very skilled players."
msgstr "El hándicap del campo puede ser negativo para jugadores muy hábiles."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:328
msgid ""
"Net Score allows fair competition between players of different skill levels."
msgstr ""
"Net Score permite una competencia justa entre jugadores de diferentes "
"niveles de habilidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/golf_handicap_calculator.html:329
#, python-format
msgid "Handicap Allowance is typically 100%% for individual stroke play."
msgstr ""
"La asignación de hándicap suele ser del 100% para el juego por golpes "
