"las tareas, la calificación ponderada y el porcentaje de calificación. "
"Perfecto para que los estudiantes realicen un seguimiento de las "
"calificaciones y planifiquen los exámenes finales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"grade calculator, calculate grade, final grade calculator, current grade "
"calculator, weighted grade calculator, grade percentage calculator, grade "
"needed calculator, how to calculate grade, test grade calculator, assignment"
