msgstr "Puntos posibles"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:222
msgid "Calculate Your Grade"
msgstr "Calcula tu calificación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:239
msgid "What is Grade Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la calculadora de calificaciones?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:241
msgid ""
"The Grade Calculator is a comprehensive tool for students to calculate "
"various grade-related metrics. It helps you determine what grade you need on"
" a final exam to achieve your target grade, calculate your current grade "
"from completed assignments, compute weighted grades, and convert percentages"
" to letter grades. This calculator is essential for academic planning and "
"goal setting."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de calificaciones es una herramienta integral para que los "
"estudiantes calculen varias métricas relacionadas con las calificaciones. Le"
" ayuda a determinar qué calificación necesita en un examen final para lograr"
" su calificación objetivo, calcular su calificación actual a partir de las "
"tareas completadas, calcular calificaciones ponderadas y convertir "
"porcentajes en calificaciones con letras. Esta calculadora es esencial para "
"la planificación académica y el establecimiento de objetivos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:248
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Final Grade Needed, Current "
"Grade, Grade Percentage, Weighted Grade, or Convert to Letter Grade)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Calificación final "
"necesaria, Calificación actual, Porcentaje de calificación, Calificación "
"ponderada o Convertir a calificación con letras)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:250
msgid ""
"For assignment-based calculations, add assignments using the 'Add "
"Assignment' button."
msgstr ""
"Para cálculos basados ​​en tareas, agregue asignaciones usando el botón "
"'Agregar tarea'."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:261
msgid ""
"Calculate what grade you need on a final exam/assignment to achieve your "
"target overall grade. Enter current grade, target grade, and final weight."
msgstr ""
"Calcule qué calificación necesita en un examen/tarea final para lograr su "
"calificación general objetivo. Ingrese la calificación actual, la "
"calificación objetivo y el peso final."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:265
msgid ""
"Calculate your current grade from completed assignments. Supports both "
"weighted and unweighted calculations."
msgstr ""
"Calcule su calificación actual a partir de las tareas completadas. Admite "
"cálculos ponderados y no ponderados."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:269
msgid ""
"Calculate grade percentage from points earned and points possible. Formula: "
"(Points Earned / Points Possible) × 100."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el porcentaje de calificación a partir de los puntos obtenidos y los"
" puntos posibles. Fórmula: (Puntos obtenidos / Puntos posibles) × 100."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:273
msgid ""
"Calculate weighted average grade from multiple assignments with different "
"weights. Formula: Σ(Grade × Weight) / Total Weight."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la calificación promedio ponderada de múltiples tareas con "
"diferentes pesos. Fórmula: Σ(Grado × Peso) / Peso Total."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:277
msgid ""
"Convert percentage grade to letter grade using standard thresholds (A+, A, "
"A-, B+, B, B-, C+, C, C-, D+, D, D-, F)."
msgstr ""
"Convierta la calificación porcentual en calificación con letras utilizando "
"umbrales estándar (A+, A, A-, B+, B, B-, C+, C, C-, D+, D, D-, F)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:283
msgid "Key Grade Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave de calificación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:285
msgid "Final Grade Needed:"
msgstr "Calificación final necesaria:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:287
msgid "Current Grade (Unweighted):"
msgstr "Calificación actual (no ponderada):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:289
msgid "Weighted Grade:"
msgstr "Grado ponderado:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:291
msgid "Grade Percentage:"
msgstr "Porcentaje de calificación:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:297
msgid "Letter Grade Thresholds"
msgstr "Umbrales de calificación con letras"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:303
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:247
msgid "Percentage Range"
msgstr "Rango de porcentaje"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:328
msgid "All grade percentages must be between 0 and 100."
msgstr "Todos los porcentajes de calificación deben estar entre 0 y 100."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:329
#, python-format
msgid "Final weight must be between 0%% and 100%% (exclusive)."
msgstr "El peso final debe estar entre 0%% y 100%% (exclusivo)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:330
#: Other_Calculators/views/grade_calculator.py:395
msgid "Points earned cannot exceed points possible."
msgstr "Los puntos obtenidos no pueden exceder los puntos posibles."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:331
#, python-format
msgid "For weighted grades, total weight should not exceed 100%%."
msgstr "Para grados ponderados, el peso total no debe exceder el 100%."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:332
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If final grade needed exceeds 100%%, the target grade is not achievable."
msgstr ""
"Si la calificación final necesaria excede el 100%%, la calificación objetivo"
" no se puede lograr."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:333
msgid ""
"Current grade calculations support both weighted and unweighted assignments."
msgstr ""
"Los cálculos de calificaciones actuales admiten tareas tanto ponderadas como"
" no ponderadas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:334
msgid "Letter grade thresholds may vary slightly between institutions."
msgstr ""
"Los umbrales de calificación con letras pueden variar ligeramente entre "
"instituciones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:342
msgid "Planning final exam preparation"
msgstr "Planificación de la preparación del examen final"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:343
msgid "Tracking current academic performance"
msgstr "Seguimiento del rendimiento académico actual"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:344
msgid "Calculating weighted course grades"
msgstr "Calcular las calificaciones ponderadas del curso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:345
msgid "Determining grade needed for scholarship eligibility"
msgstr ""
"Determinar la calificación necesaria para la elegibilidad para la beca"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:346
msgid "Converting points to percentage grades"
msgstr "Convertir puntos a calificaciones porcentuales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:347
msgid "Understanding letter grade equivalents"
msgstr "Comprender los equivalentes de calificaciones con letras"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:348
msgid "Academic goal setting and planning"
msgstr "Establecimiento y planificación de objetivos académicos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:385
msgid "Assignment Name"
msgstr "Nombre de la tarea"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:393
msgid "Weight (optional, 0 for unweighted)"
msgstr "Peso (opcional, 0 para no ponderado)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:463
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:487
msgid "Assignment"
msgstr "Asignación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:472
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:495
msgid "Please add at least one valid assignment."
msgstr "Por favor agregue al menos una tarea válida."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:568
#: Other_Calculators/views/grade_calculator.py:775
msgid "Target Grade"
msgstr "Grado objetivo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:572
msgid "Final Weight"
msgstr "Peso final"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/grade_calculator.html:578
#, python-format, python-brace-format
msgid "Target grade is not achievable. Maximum possible: {max}%%"
msgstr "La calificación objetivo no es alcanzable. Máximo posible: {max}%%"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:4
msgid ""
"Gravel Calculator - Calculate Gravel Volume, Weight, Cost, Coverage | Free "
"Online Tool"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de grava: calcule el volumen, el peso, el costo y la cobertura "
"de la grava | Herramienta en línea gratuita"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free gravel calculator to calculate gravel volume for rectangular, circular,"
" and triangular areas. Calculate weight, cost, coverage, and unit "
"conversions with step-by-step solutions. Perfect for landscaping and "
"construction projects."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de grava gratuita para calcular el volumen de grava para áreas "
"rectangulares, circulares y triangulares. Calcule peso, costo, cobertura y "
"conversiones de unidades con soluciones paso a paso. Perfecto para proyectos"
" de paisajismo y construcción."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"gravel calculator, calculate gravel, gravel volume calculator, gravel cost "
"calculator, gravel weight calculator, gravel coverage calculator, how much "
"gravel do I need, cubic yards calculator, landscaping calculator, "
"construction calculator, gravel finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de grava, calcular grava, calculadora de volumen de grava, "
"calculadora de costo de grava, calculadora de peso de grava, calculadora de "
"cobertura de grava, cuánta grava necesito, calculadora de yardas cúbicas, "
"calculadora de paisajismo, calculadora de construcción, buscador de grava"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:8
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:12
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:26
