msgstr ""
"Calculadora de grava: calcule el volumen, el peso, el costo y la cobertura "
"de la grava"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume, weight, cost, and coverage for rectangular, "
"circular, and triangular areas. Free online calculator with step-by-step "
"solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el volumen, el peso, el costo y la cobertura de grava para áreas "
"rectangulares, circulares y triangulares. Calculadora online gratuita con "
"soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:13
msgid "Calculate gravel with step-by-step solutions. Free online calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcula grava con soluciones paso a paso. Calculadora en línea gratuita."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:31
msgid ""
"Free online gravel calculator to calculate gravel volume, weight, cost, and "
"coverage for rectangular, circular, and triangular areas with step-by-step "
