#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:375
msgid "Weight Value"
msgstr "Valor de peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:456
msgid "Calculate Gravel"
msgstr "Calcular grava"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:473
msgid "What is Gravel Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la calculadora de grava?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"The Gravel Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating gravel volume,"
" weight, cost, and coverage for various project shapes. It helps you "
"determine how much gravel you need for rectangular driveways, circular "
"patios, triangular areas, and more. This calculator is essential for "
"landscaping, construction, and DIY projects."
msgstr ""
"Gravel Calculator es una herramienta integral para calcular el volumen, el "
"peso, el costo y la cobertura de la grava para diversas formas de proyectos."
" Le ayuda a determinar cuánta grava necesita para entradas rectangulares, "
"patios circulares, áreas triangulares y más. Esta calculadora es esencial "
"para proyectos de paisajismo, construcción y bricolaje."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:482
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Rectangular Area, Circular "
"Area, Triangular Area, Weight, Cost, Coverage, or Unit Conversion)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Área rectangular, Área"
" circular, Área triangular, Peso, Costo, Cobertura o Conversión de "
"unidades)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:483
msgid ""
"Enter the required dimensions (length, width, depth, diameter, etc.) with "
"appropriate units."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese las dimensiones requeridas (largo, ancho, profundidad, diámetro, "
"etc.) con las unidades apropiadas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"Select your preferred result unit (cubic yards, cubic feet, cubic meters, "
"tons, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione su unidad de resultado preferida (yardas cúbicas, pies cúbicos, "
"metros cúbicos, toneladas, etc.)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:495
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for rectangular areas like driveways, walkways, and "
"patios. Formula: Volume = Length × Width × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el volumen de grava para áreas rectangulares como entradas de "
"vehículos, senderos y patios. Fórmula: Volumen = Largo × Ancho × "
"Profundidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:499
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for circular areas like round patios and fire pits. "
"Formula: Volume = π × (Diameter/2)² × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el volumen de grava para áreas circulares como patios redondos y "
"fogatas. Fórmula: Volumen = π × (Diámetro/2)² × Profundidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:503
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for triangular areas. Formula: Volume = (1/2) × Base"
" × Height × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el volumen de grava para áreas triangulares. Fórmula: Volumen = "
"(1/2) × Base × Altura × Profundidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:507
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel weight from volume. Formula: Weight = Volume × Density. "
"Default density: 105 lbs/ft³."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el peso de la grava a partir del volumen. Fórmula: Peso = Volumen × "
"Densidad. Densidad predeterminada: 105 lbs/ft³."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"Calculate total cost of gravel. Formula: Total Cost = Volume × Price per "
"Unit."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el costo total de la grava. Fórmula: Costo Total = Volumen × Precio "
"por Unidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:515
msgid ""
"Calculate coverage area from volume and depth. Formula: Area = Volume / "
"Depth."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el área de cobertura a partir del volumen y la profundidad. Fórmula:"
" Área = Volumen / Profundidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:521
msgid "Key Gravel Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave de grava"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:523
msgid "Rectangular Volume:"
msgstr "Volumen rectangular:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:525
msgid "Circular Volume:"
msgstr "Volumen circular:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:527
msgid "Triangular Volume:"
msgstr "Volumen triangular:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:529
msgid "Weight:"
msgstr "Peso:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:531
msgid "Cost:"
msgstr "Costo:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:533
msgid "Coverage Area:"
msgstr "Área de cobertura:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:542
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:410
msgid "Length Units"
msgstr "Unidades de longitud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:551
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:815
msgid "Volume Units"
msgstr "Unidades de volumen"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:559
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:263
msgid "Weight Units"
msgstr "Unidades de peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:572
#: Other_Calculators/views/btu_calculator.py:132
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:114
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:187
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:254
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:322
#: Other_Calculators/views/concrete_calculator.py:391
msgid "All dimensions must be greater than zero."
msgstr "Todas las dimensiones deben ser mayores que cero."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:573
msgid ""
"Depth is typically measured in inches for most projects (2-4 inches is "
"common)."
msgstr ""
"La profundidad generalmente se mide en pulgadas para la mayoría de los "
"proyectos (es común entre 2 y 4 pulgadas)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:574
msgid ""
"Gravel density varies by type: crushed stone (~105 lbs/ft³), pea gravel (~95"
" lbs/ft³), river rock (~100 lbs/ft³)."
msgstr ""
"La densidad de la grava varía según el tipo: piedra triturada (~105 "
"lbs/ft³), gravilla (~95 lbs/ft³), roca de río (~100 lbs/ft³)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:575
#, python-format
msgid "Always add 5-10%% extra for compaction and settling."
msgstr "Agregue siempre un 5-10%% extra para compactación y asentamiento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:576
msgid ""
"For irregular shapes, break them into regular shapes and calculate "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"Para formas irregulares, divídalas en formas regulares y calcule por "
"separado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:578
msgid "Unit conversions are handled automatically."
msgstr "Las conversiones de unidades se manejan automáticamente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:579
msgid ""
"Cost calculations are estimates; actual prices may vary by location and "
"supplier."
msgstr ""
"Los cálculos de costos son estimaciones; Los precios reales pueden variar "
"según la ubicación y el proveedor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:586
msgid "Driveway and walkway projects"
msgstr "Proyectos de caminos y pasarelas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:587
msgid "Patio and landscaping projects"
msgstr "Proyectos de patios y paisajismo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:588
msgid "Drainage and French drain installations"
msgstr "Instalaciones de drenaje y desagüe francés."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:589
msgid "Base material for concrete slabs"
msgstr "Material base para losas de hormigón."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:590
msgid "Garden paths and decorative areas"
msgstr "Caminos de jardín y zonas decorativas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:591
msgid "Construction and road base projects"
msgstr "Proyectos de construcción y base de carreteras."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:592
msgid "Budget planning and material ordering"
msgstr "Planificación de presupuesto y pedido de materiales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:749
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:775
#: Other_Calculators/views/gravel_calculator.py:1104
#: Other_Calculators/views/gravel_calculator.py:1156
#: Other_Calculators/views/gravel_calculator.py:1206
