#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:4
msgid ""
"Heat Index Calculator - Calculate Heat Index, Temperature, Humidity | Free "
"Online Tool"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora del índice de calor: calcular el índice de calor, la temperatura"
" y la humedad | Herramienta en línea gratuita"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free heat index calculator to calculate heat index from temperature and "
"relative humidity, or calculate temperature or humidity from heat index. "
"Perfect for weather analysis and safety planning."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de índice de calor gratuita para calcular el índice de calor a "
"partir de la temperatura y la humedad relativa, o calcular la temperatura o "
"la humedad a partir del índice de calor. Perfecto para análisis "
"meteorológicos y planificación de seguridad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"heat index calculator, calculate heat index, feels like temperature "
"calculator, apparent temperature calculator, heat index formula, rothfusz "
"equation calculator, temperature calculator, humidity calculator, how to "
"calculate heat index, heat index finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de índice de calor, calcular el índice de calor, calculadora de "
"temperatura, calculadora de temperatura aparente, fórmula de índice de "
"calor, calculadora de ecuaciones de Rothfusz, calculadora de temperatura, "
"calculadora de humedad, cómo calcular el índice de calor, buscador de índice"
" de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:8
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:12
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:26
msgid "Heat Index Calculator - Calculate Heat Index, Temperature, Humidity"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora del índice de calor: calcular el índice de calor, la temperatura"
" y la humedad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Calculate heat index, temperature, or relative humidity using the Rothfusz "
"equation. Free online calculator with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el índice de calor, la temperatura o la humedad relativa utilizando "
"la ecuación de Rothfusz. Calculadora online gratuita con soluciones paso a "
"paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Calculate heat index, temperature, or relative humidity. Free online "
"calculator with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el índice de calor, la temperatura o la humedad relativa. "
"Calculadora online gratuita con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:31
msgid ""
"Free online heat index calculator to calculate heat index from temperature "
"and relative humidity, calculate temperature or humidity from heat index "
"with step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de índice de calor online gratuita para calcular el índice de "
"calor a partir de la temperatura y la humedad relativa, calcular la "
"temperatura o la humedad a partir del índice de calor con soluciones paso a "
"paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:50
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:48
#: Other_Calculators/views/index.py:55
msgid "Heat Index Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:53
msgid ""
"Calculate heat index (feels like temperature) from temperature and relative "
"humidity, or calculate temperature or humidity from heat index with step-by-"
"step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el índice de calor (la sensación de temperatura) a partir de la "
"temperatura y la humedad relativa, o calcule la temperatura o la humedad a "
"partir del índice de calor con soluciones paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:79
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:114
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:138
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:286
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:531
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:544
msgid "Heat Index"
msgstr "Índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:80
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:290
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:890
msgid "Temperature from Heat Index"
msgstr "Temperatura a partir del índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:81
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:294
msgid "Humidity from Heat Index"
msgstr "Humedad del índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:82
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:298
msgid "Convert Temperature Units"
msgstr "Convertir unidades de temperatura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:99
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:123
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:147
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:160
msgid "Must be ≥ 80°F (27°C)"
msgstr "Debe ser ≥ 80°F (27°C)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:106
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:130
#, python-format
msgid "Must be ≥ 40%%"
msgstr "Debe ser ≥ 40%%"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:168
msgid "Temperature Value"
msgstr "Valor de temperatura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:248
msgid "Calculate Heat Index"
msgstr "Calcular el índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:265
msgid "What is Heat Index?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el índice de calor?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:267
msgid ""
"The Heat Index (also known as 'apparent temperature' or 'feels like "
"temperature') is a measure of how hot it feels when relative humidity is "
"factored in with the actual air temperature. It is an important indicator "
"for heat-related health risks, especially during hot weather. The heat index"
" is calculated using the Rothfusz equation, which takes into account both "
"temperature and relative humidity to determine the perceived temperature."
msgstr ""
"El índice de calor (también conocido como \"temperatura aparente\" o "
"\"temperatura que se siente\") es una medida de qué tan caliente se siente "
"cuando la humedad relativa se tiene en cuenta con la temperatura real del "
"aire. Es un indicador importante de los riesgos para la salud relacionados "
"con el calor, especialmente durante el clima cálido. El índice de calor se "
"calcula mediante la ecuación de Rothfusz, que tiene en cuenta tanto la "
"temperatura como la humedad relativa para determinar la temperatura "
"percibida."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Heat Index, Temperature from "
"Heat Index, Humidity from Heat Index, or Convert Temperature Units)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Índice de calor, "
"Temperatura a partir del índice de calor, Humedad a partir del índice de "
"calor o Convertir unidades de temperatura)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:275
msgid ""
"Enter the required values (temperature, relative humidity, or heat index) "
"with appropriate units."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los valores requeridos (temperatura, humedad relativa o índice de "
"calor) con las unidades apropiadas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:276
msgid "Select your preferred temperature unit (Fahrenheit or Celsius)."
msgstr "Seleccione su unidad de temperatura preferida (Fahrenheit o Celsius)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:278
msgid ""
"Review the detailed results, risk category, visualizations, and step-by-step"
" solution."
msgstr ""
"Revise los resultados detallados, la categoría de riesgo, las "
"visualizaciones y la solución paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:287
msgid ""
"Calculate heat index from temperature and relative humidity using the "
"Rothfusz equation. This is the most common calculation."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el índice de calor a partir de la temperatura y la humedad relativa "
"utilizando la ecuación de Rothfusz. Este es el cálculo más común."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:291
msgid ""
"Calculate the actual temperature when you know the heat index and relative "
"humidity. Uses iterative numerical methods."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la temperatura real cuando conozca el índice de calor y la humedad "
"relativa. Utiliza métodos numéricos iterativos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"Calculate relative humidity when you know the heat index and temperature. "
"Uses iterative numerical methods."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la humedad relativa cuando conozca el índice de calor y la "
"temperatura. Utiliza métodos numéricos iterativos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:299
msgid ""
"Convert between Fahrenheit and Celsius. Formula: °F = (°C × 9/5) + 32, °C = "
"(°F - 32) × 5/9."
msgstr ""
"Convertir entre Fahrenheit y Celsius. Fórmula: °F = (°C × 9/5) + 32, °C = "
"(°F - 32) × 5/9."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:305
msgid "Heat Index Formula (Rothfusz Equation)"
msgstr "Fórmula del índice de calor (ecuación de Rothfusz)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:307
msgid "Main Formula:"
msgstr "Fórmula principal:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:313
msgid "HI = Heat Index (°F)"
msgstr "HI = Índice de calor (°F)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:314
msgid "T = Temperature (°F)"
msgstr "T = Temperatura (°F)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:315
#, python-format
msgid "RH = Relative Humidity (%%)"
msgstr "HR = Humedad Relativa (%%)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:317
msgid "Adjustments:"
msgstr "Ajustes:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:319
#, python-format
msgid "If RH < 13%% and 80°F ≤ T ≤ 112°F: Subtract adjustment"
msgstr "Si HR < 13%% y 80°F ≤ T ≤ 112°F: Reste el ajuste"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:320
#, python-format
msgid "If RH > 85%% and 80°F ≤ T ≤ 87°F: Add adjustment"
msgstr "Si HR > 85 % % y 80 °F ≤ T ≤ 87 °F: agregue ajuste"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:326
msgid "Heat Index Risk Categories"
msgstr "Categorías de riesgo del índice de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:331
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:814
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:864
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:914
msgid "Heat Index (°F)"
msgstr "Índice de calor (°F)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:333
msgid "Risk Level"
msgstr "Nivel de riesgo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:334
msgid "Health Effects"
msgstr "Efectos sobre la salud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:338
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:35
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:701
#: Other_Calculators/views/wind_chill_calculator.py:115
#: Other_Calculators/views/wind_chill_calculator.py:117
msgid "Caution"
msgstr "Precaución"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:338
msgid "Fatigue possible with prolonged exposure"
msgstr "Fatiga posible con exposición prolongada."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:339
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:36
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:703
msgid "Extreme Caution"
msgstr "Extrema precaución"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:339
msgid "Sunstroke, heat cramps, heat exhaustion possible"
msgstr "Posible insolación, calambres por calor y agotamiento por calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:340
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:37
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:705
#: Other_Calculators/views/wind_chill_calculator.py:119
msgid "Danger"
msgstr "Peligro"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:340
msgid "Sunstroke, heat cramps, heat exhaustion likely; heat stroke possible"
msgstr ""
"Es probable que se produzca insolación, calambres por calor y agotamiento "
"por calor; posible golpe de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:341
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:38
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:707
#: Other_Calculators/views/wind_chill_calculator.py:121
msgid "Extreme Danger"
msgstr "Peligro extremo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:341
#: Other_Calculators/views/heat_index_calculator.py:707
msgid "Extreme"
msgstr "Extremo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:341
msgid "Heat stroke highly likely"
msgstr "Un golpe de calor muy probable"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:350
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Heat index is only valid for temperatures above 80°F (27°C) and relative "
"humidity above 40%%."
msgstr ""
"El índice de calor solo es válido para temperaturas superiores a 80°F (27°C)"
" y humedad relativa superior al 40%%."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:351
msgid ""
"Heat index calculations are based on the Rothfusz equation developed by the "
"National Weather Service."
msgstr ""
"Los cálculos del índice de calor se basan en la ecuación de Rothfusz "
"desarrollada por el Servicio Meteorológico Nacional."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:352
msgid ""
"The formula uses Fahrenheit for temperature; Celsius values are converted "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"La fórmula utiliza grados Fahrenheit para la temperatura; Los valores "
"Celsius se convierten automáticamente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:353
msgid "Direct sunlight can increase the heat index by up to 15°F (8°C)."
msgstr ""
"La luz solar directa puede aumentar el índice de calor hasta 15°F (8°C)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:354
msgid "Wind can reduce the heat index by increasing evaporation."
msgstr ""
"El viento puede reducir el índice de calor al aumentar la evaporación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:355
msgid "Heat index is most accurate in shaded, light wind conditions."
msgstr ""
"El índice de calor es más preciso en condiciones de sombra y viento suave."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:356
msgid ""
"Elderly, children, and those with health conditions are more susceptible to "
"heat-related illnesses."
msgstr ""
"Los ancianos, los niños y las personas con problemas de salud son más "
"susceptibles a las enfermedades relacionadas con el calor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"Stay hydrated and take breaks in cool, shaded areas when heat index is high."
msgstr ""
"Manténgase hidratado y tome descansos en áreas frescas y sombreadas cuando "
"el índice de calor sea alto."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:364
msgid "Weather forecasting and heat warnings"
msgstr "Previsión meteorológica y avisos de calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:365
msgid "Outdoor activity planning and safety"
msgstr "Planificación de actividades al aire libre y seguridad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:366
msgid "Athletic event planning and heat safety protocols"
msgstr ""
"Planificación de eventos deportivos y protocolos de seguridad contra el "
"calor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:367
msgid "Workplace safety in hot environments"
msgstr "Seguridad en el trabajo en ambientes calurosos"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:368
msgid "Agricultural and farming operations"
msgstr "Operaciones agrícolas y ganaderas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:369
msgid "Understanding heat-related health risks"
msgstr "Comprender los riesgos para la salud relacionados con el calor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:370
msgid "Climate and weather analysis"
msgstr "Análisis climático y meteorológico."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:509
msgid "Risk"
msgstr "Riesgo"

