msgstr "Calcular altura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:351
msgid "What is Height Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la calculadora de altura?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:353
msgid ""
"The Height Calculator is a comprehensive tool for converting height between "
"different units (feet/inches, centimeters, meters), predicting a child's "
"adult height from parents' heights, comparing two heights, and calculating "
"height percentiles. This calculator is useful for personal measurements, "
"medical purposes, and understanding height statistics."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de altura es una herramienta integral para convertir la "
"altura entre diferentes unidades (pies/pulgadas, centímetros, metros), "
"predecir la altura adulta de un niño a partir de la altura de los padres, "
"comparar dos alturas y calcular percentiles de altura. Esta calculadora es "
"útil para mediciones personales, fines médicos y para comprender las "
"estadísticas de altura."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Convert Height, Predict Child "
"Height, Compare Heights, or Height Percentile)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Convertir altura, "
"Predecir altura del niño, Comparar alturas o Percentil de altura)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:361
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:289
msgid "Enter the required values with appropriate units."
msgstr "Ingrese los valores requeridos con las unidades apropiadas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:362
msgid "For feet/inches input, enter feet and inches separately."
msgstr "Para ingresar pies/pulgadas, ingrese pies y pulgadas por separado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:373
msgid ""
"Convert height between feet/inches, centimeters, inches, and meters. "
"Supports all common height units."
msgstr ""
"Convierta la altura entre pies/pulgadas, centímetros, pulgadas y metros. "
"Soporta todas las unidades de altura comunes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Predict a child's adult height from parents' heights using the mid-parental "
"height formula. Provides a range of ±8.5 cm."
msgstr ""
"Prediga la altura adulta de un niño a partir de la altura de sus padres "
"utilizando la fórmula de altura media de los padres. Proporciona un rango de"
" ±8,5 cm."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:381
msgid ""
"Compare two heights and calculate the difference in centimeters and "
"percentage. Useful for understanding height differences."
msgstr ""
"Compara dos alturas y calcula la diferencia en centímetros y porcentaje. "
"Útil para comprender las diferencias de altura."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"Calculate height percentile based on age and gender. Shows how your height "
"compares to others of the same age and gender."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el percentil de altura según la edad y el sexo. Muestra cómo se "
"compara su altura con la de otras personas de su misma edad y sexo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:391
msgid "Key Height Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave de altura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:393
msgid "Height Conversion:"
msgstr "Conversión de altura:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:397
msgid "Height Prediction (Mid-Parental Height):"
msgstr "Predicción de altura (altura media de los padres):"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:400
msgid "Height Comparison:"
msgstr "Comparación de altura:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:412
msgid "Feet & Inches (ft, in)"
msgstr "Pies y pulgadas (pies, pulgadas)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:419
msgid "Conversion Factors"
msgstr "Factores de conversión"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:421
msgid "1 ft = 12 in = 30.48 cm"
msgstr "1 pie = 12 pulgadas = 30,48 cm"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:422
msgid "1 in = 2.54 cm"
msgstr "1 pulgada = 2,54 cm"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:423
msgid "1 m = 100 cm = 39.37 in"
msgstr "1 metro = 100 cm = 39,37 pulgadas"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Height must be between 50 cm (1.64 ft) and 300 cm (9.84 ft) for valid "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
"La altura debe estar entre 50 cm (1,64 pies) y 300 cm (9,84 pies) para que "
"los cálculos sean válidos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:433
msgid "For feet/inches input, inches must be between 0 and 11.99."
msgstr ""
"Para la entrada de pies/pulgadas, las pulgadas deben estar entre 0 y 11,99."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Height prediction is an estimate based on genetic factors; actual height may"
" vary."
msgstr ""
"La predicción de la altura es una estimación basada en factores genéticos; "
"La altura real puede variar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:435
msgid "The prediction range is ±8.5 cm from the predicted height."
msgstr "El rango de predicción es ±8,5 cm de la altura prevista."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Height percentiles are approximate and based on general population "
"statistics."
msgstr ""
"Los percentiles de altura son aproximados y se basan en estadísticas de "
"población general."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:437
msgid "Percentile calculations are most accurate for adults (18+ years)."
msgstr ""
"Los cálculos de percentiles son más precisos para adultos (mayores de 18 "
"años)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:438
msgid "All conversions are precise to 2 decimal places."
msgstr "Todas las conversiones tienen una precisión de 2 decimales."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:446
msgid "Personal height measurements and conversions"
msgstr "Medidas y conversiones de altura personal."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:447
msgid "Medical and health assessments"
msgstr "Evaluaciones médicas y de salud."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:448
msgid "Child height prediction and growth tracking"
msgstr "Predicción de la altura del niño y seguimiento del crecimiento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:449
msgid "Sports and athletic assessments"
msgstr "Evaluaciones deportivas y atléticas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:450
msgid "Clothing and sizing calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de ropa y tallas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:451
msgid "Understanding height statistics and percentiles"
msgstr "Comprender las estadísticas y percentiles de altura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:452
msgid "International unit conversions"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades internacionales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:724
msgid "Range:"
msgstr "Rango:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:730
msgid "Predicted Height (cm)"
msgstr "Altura prevista (cm)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:742
msgid "Height 1 (cm)"
msgstr "Altura 1 (cm)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:746
msgid "Height 2 (cm)"
msgstr "Altura 2 (cm)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:750
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mileage_calculator.html:727
msgid "Percentage Difference"
msgstr "Diferencia porcentual"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/height_calculator.html:758
msgid "Z-score:"
msgstr "Puntuación Z:"

