#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:182
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:515
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:569
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:298
msgid "Watts (W)"
msgstr "Vatios (W)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:279
msgid "What is Horsepower?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los caballos de fuerza?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Horsepower (HP) is a unit of power that measures the rate at which work is "
"done. It was originally defined by James Watt to compare the output of steam"
" engines with the power of draft horses. One horsepower equals 745.7 watts "
"or 0.7457 kilowatts. Horsepower is commonly used to measure the power output"
" of engines, motors, and other mechanical devices."
msgstr ""
"Los caballos de fuerza (HP) es una unidad de potencia que mide la velocidad "
"a la que se realiza el trabajo. Fue definido originalmente por James Watt "
"para comparar la potencia de las máquinas de vapor con la potencia de los "
"caballos de tiro. Un caballo de fuerza equivale a 745,7 vatios o 0,7457 "
"kilovatios. Los caballos de fuerza se utilizan comúnmente para medir la "
"potencia de salida de motores, motores y otros dispositivos mecánicos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:288
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (HP from Torque & RPM, Torque "
"from HP & RPM, RPM from HP & Torque, Convert Power Units, HP from Watts, or "
"HP from Kilowatts)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (HP de Torque y RPM, "
"Torque de HP y RPM, RPM de HP y Torque, Convertir unidades de potencia, HP "
"de Watts o HP de Kilovatios)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:290
msgid ""
"Select your preferred units for torque (ft-lb or N⋅m) and power (HP, kW, or "
"W)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione sus unidades preferidas para torque (ft-lb o N⋅m) y potencia (HP,"
" kW o W)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:301
msgid ""
"Calculate horsepower from torque and RPM using the formula: HP = (Torque × "
"RPM) / 5252. This is the most common calculation for engine power."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los caballos de fuerza a partir del torque y las RPM usando la "
"fórmula: HP = (Torque × RPM) / 5252. Este es el cálculo más común para la "
"potencia del motor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:305
msgid ""
"Calculate torque from horsepower and RPM. Formula: Torque = (HP × 5252) / "
"RPM. Useful for determining engine torque output."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el torque a partir de caballos de fuerza y ​​RPM. Fórmula: Torque = "
"(HP × 5252) / RPM. Útil para determinar la salida de par del motor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"Calculate RPM from horsepower and torque. Formula: RPM = (HP × 5252) / "
"Torque. Useful for finding the RPM at which peak power occurs."
msgstr ""
"Calcule las RPM a partir de caballos de fuerza y ​​torque. Fórmula: RPM = "
"(HP × 5252) / Torque. Útil para encontrar las RPM a las que se produce la "
"potencia máxima."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Convert between horsepower (HP), kilowatts (kW), and watts (W). Supports all"
" common power unit conversions."
msgstr ""
"Convierta entre caballos de fuerza (HP), kilovatios (kW) y vatios (W). "
"Admite todas las conversiones de unidades de potencia comunes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:317
msgid ""
"Calculate horsepower from watts. Formula: HP = Watts / 745.7. Useful for "
"converting electrical power to mechanical power."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los caballos de fuerza a partir de vatios. Fórmula: HP = Watts / "
"745,7. Útil para convertir energía eléctrica en energía mecánica."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:321
msgid ""
"Calculate horsepower from kilowatts. Formula: HP = kW × 1.341. Common in "
"European and metric systems."
msgstr ""
"Calcule los caballos de fuerza a partir de kilovatios. Fórmula: CV = kW × "
"1,341. Común en sistemas europeos y métricos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:327
msgid "Key Horsepower Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas clave de caballos de fuerza"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:329
msgid "Horsepower from Torque and RPM:"
msgstr "Caballos de fuerza a partir de torque y RPM:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:331
msgid "Torque from Horsepower and RPM:"
msgstr "Torque a partir de caballos de fuerza y ​​RPM:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:333
msgid "RPM from Horsepower and Torque:"
msgstr "RPM de caballos de fuerza y ​​torque:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:335
msgid "Power Unit Conversions:"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de potencia:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:339
msgid "Torque Unit Conversions:"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de torque:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:346
msgid "Why 5252?"
msgstr "¿Por qué 5252?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:348
msgid ""
"The constant 5252 in the horsepower formula comes from unit conversions. One"
" horsepower is defined as 550 foot-pounds per second. To convert RPM to "
"revolutions per second, we divide by 60. To convert to foot-pounds per "
"minute, we multiply by 60. The calculation: (550 ft-lb/s × 60 s/min) / (2π "
"rad/rev) = 5252. This constant ensures that horsepower and torque curves "
"intersect at 5252 RPM when plotted on the same graph."
msgstr ""
"La constante 5252 en la fórmula de los caballos de fuerza proviene de "
"conversiones de unidades. Un caballo de fuerza se define como 550 libras-pie"
" por segundo. Para convertir RPM a revoluciones por segundo, dividimos por "
"60. Para convertir a libras-pie por minuto, multiplicamos por 60. El "
"cálculo: (550 ft-lb/s × 60 s/min) / (2π rad/rev) = 5252. Esta constante "
"garantiza que las curvas de caballos de fuerza y ​​torsión se crucen a 5252 "
"RPM cuando se trazan en el mismo gráfico."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:355
msgid "All torque and power values must be greater than zero."
msgstr "Todos los valores de par y potencia deben ser mayores que cero."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:356
msgid "RPM must be between 1 and 50,000 for valid calculations."
msgstr ""
"Las RPM deben estar entre 1 y 50 000 para que los cálculos sean válidos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"The formula HP = (Torque × RPM) / 5252 is valid for rotational power "
"calculations."
msgstr ""
"La fórmula HP = (Torque × RPM) / 5252 es válida para cálculos de potencia "
"rotacional."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:358
msgid "Torque can be entered in foot-pounds (ft-lb) or Newton-meters (N⋅m)."
msgstr ""
"El torque se puede ingresar en libras-pie (ft-lb) o Newton-metros (N⋅m)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:359
msgid "Power can be converted between HP, kW, and watts."
msgstr "La potencia se puede convertir entre HP, kW y vatios."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"The constant 5252 is specific to the relationship between HP, torque (in ft-"
"lb), and RPM."
msgstr ""
"La constante 5252 es específica de la relación entre HP, torque (en ft-lb) y"
" RPM."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"For metric calculations, torque in N⋅m is automatically converted to ft-lb "
"for the formula."
msgstr ""
"Para cálculos métricos, el torque en N⋅m se convierte automáticamente a ft-"
"lb para la fórmula."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:369
msgid "Automotive engine power calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de potencia del motor automotriz."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:370
msgid "Motor and engine performance analysis"
msgstr "Análisis del rendimiento del motor y del motor."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:371
msgid "Industrial machinery power ratings"
msgstr "Potencias nominales de maquinaria industrial"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:372
msgid "Electric motor specifications"
msgstr "Especificaciones del motor eléctrico."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:373
msgid "Power tool performance evaluation"
msgstr "Evaluación del rendimiento de la herramienta eléctrica."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:374
msgid "Marine and aviation engine calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de motores marinos y de aviación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:375
msgid "Power unit conversions for international standards"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de potencia para estándares internacionales."

