#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:263
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/time_card_calculator.html:83
msgid "Calculate Hours"
msgstr "Calcular horas"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:280
msgid "What is Hours Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la Calculadora de Horas?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:282
msgid ""
"The Hours Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating time "
"differences, adding or subtracting hours from times, converting between time"
" units (hours, minutes, seconds, days), calculating total hours from "
"multiple periods, and calculating hours worked with break time deductions. "
"This calculator is essential for time tracking, scheduling, payroll, and "
"time management."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de horas es una herramienta integral para calcular "
"diferencias horarias, sumar o restar horas de tiempos, convertir entre "
"unidades de tiempo (horas, minutos, segundos, días), calcular el total de "
"horas de múltiples períodos y calcular las horas trabajadas con deducciones "
"de tiempo de descanso. Esta calculadora es esencial para el seguimiento del "
"tiempo, la programación, la nómina y la gestión del tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Time Difference, Add/Subtract "
"Hours, Convert Time Units, Total Hours, or Hours Worked)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Diferencia horaria, "
"Sumar/Restar horas, Convertir unidades de tiempo, Total de horas u Horas "
"trabajadas)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:290
msgid ""
"Enter the required times and values in the appropriate format (HH:MM or "
"HH:MM:SS)."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese los tiempos y valores requeridos en el formato apropiado (HH:MM o "
"HH:MM:SS)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:291
msgid ""
"For time differences, check 'End time is next day' if the end time is on the"
" following day."
msgstr ""
"Para diferencias horarias, marque 'La hora de finalización es el día "
"siguiente' si la hora de finalización es el día siguiente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:302
msgid ""
"Calculate the difference between two times. Supports same-day and next-day "
"calculations. Returns hours, minutes, seconds, and days."
msgstr ""
"Calcula la diferencia entre dos tiempos. Admite cálculos para el mismo día y"
" el día siguiente. Devuelve horas, minutos, segundos y días."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"Add or subtract hours from a given time. Automatically handles day "
"overflow/underflow. Useful for scheduling and time planning."
msgstr ""
"Sumar o restar horas a un tiempo determinado. Maneja automáticamente el "
"desbordamiento/insuficiencia del día. Útil para programar y planificar el "
"tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:310
msgid ""
"Convert between hours, minutes, seconds, and days. Supports all common time "
"unit conversions with precise calculations."
msgstr ""
"Convierte entre horas, minutos, segundos y días. Admite todas las "
"conversiones de unidades de tiempo comunes con cálculos precisos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:314
msgid ""
"Calculate total hours from multiple time periods. Add multiple start/end "
"time pairs and get the sum of all periods."
msgstr ""
"Calcule el total de horas de múltiples períodos de tiempo. Agregue múltiples"
" pares de horas de inicio/finalización y obtenga la suma de todos los "
"períodos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Calculate hours worked with break time deduction. Enter start time, end "
"time, and break minutes to get net hours worked. Perfect for time tracking "
"and payroll."
msgstr ""
"Calcular las horas trabajadas con la deducción del tiempo de descanso. "
"Ingrese la hora de inicio, la hora de finalización y los minutos de descanso"
" para obtener las horas netas trabajadas. Perfecto para seguimiento de "
"tiempo y nómina."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:324
msgid "Key Time Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de tiempo clave"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:326
msgid "Time Difference:"
msgstr "Diferencia horaria:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:328
msgid "Add/Subtract Hours:"
msgstr "Sumar/Restar Horas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:330
msgid "Hours Worked:"
msgstr "Horas trabajadas:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:332
msgid "Time Unit Conversions:"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades de tiempo:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:341
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/time_calculator.html:216
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/time_card_calculator.html:192
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/time_duration_calculator.html:229
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/time_zone_calculator.html:263
msgid "Time Format"
msgstr "Formato de hora"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:343
msgid "Times can be entered in the following formats:"
msgstr "Los tiempos se pueden ingresar en los siguientes formatos:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:345
msgid "HH:MM (e.g., 09:30, 14:45)"
msgstr "HH:MM (por ejemplo, 09:30, 14:45)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:346
msgid "HH:MM:SS (e.g., 09:30:00, 14:45:30)"
msgstr "HH:MM:SS (por ejemplo, 09:30:00, 14:45:30)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:348
msgid "The calculator uses 24-hour format (00:00 to 23:59)."
msgstr "La calculadora utiliza el formato de 24 horas (00:00 a 23:59)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:355
msgid "Times must be in 24-hour format (00:00 to 23:59)."
msgstr "Los horarios deben estar en formato de 24 horas (00:00 a 23:59)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:356
msgid ""
"For time differences, if end time is before start time, check 'End time is "
"next day' or the calculator will assume next day automatically."
msgstr ""
"Para diferencias horarias, si la hora de finalización es anterior a la hora "
"de inicio, marque 'La hora de finalización es el día siguiente' o la "
"calculadora asumirá el día siguiente automáticamente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:357
msgid "Time differences are limited to 48 hours maximum."
msgstr "Las diferencias horarias están limitadas a 48 horas como máximo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"When adding/subtracting hours, day overflow/underflow is handled "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Al sumar/restar horas, el desbordamiento/insuficiencia del día se maneja "
"automáticamente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:359
msgid "Break time in hours worked must not exceed total time."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo de descanso en horas trabajadas no debe exceder el tiempo total."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:360
msgid "All calculations are precise to 2 decimal places for hours."
msgstr "Todos los cálculos son precisos con 2 decimales para las horas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Results are displayed in multiple formats: decimal hours, time format "
"(HH:MM:SS), minutes, seconds, and days."
msgstr ""
"Los resultados se muestran en múltiples formatos: horas decimales, formato "
"de hora (HH:MM:SS), minutos, segundos y días."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:362
msgid "For total hours calculation, you can add up to 50 time periods."
msgstr ""
"Para el cálculo del total de horas, puede agregar hasta 50 períodos de "
"tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:369
msgid "Time tracking and timesheet calculations"
msgstr "Seguimiento del tiempo y cálculos de hojas de horas"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:370
