#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:225
msgid "Calculate IP Subnet"
msgstr "Calcular la subred IP"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:242
msgid "What is IP Subnet Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la calculadora de subred IP?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:244
msgid ""
"The IP Subnet Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating subnet "
"information, network addresses, broadcast addresses, host ranges, and "
"converting between CIDR notation and dotted decimal subnet masks. It helps "
"network administrators, IT professionals, and students understand and "
"configure IP subnets for IPv4 networks. This calculator is essential for "
"network design, troubleshooting, and subnet planning."
msgstr ""
"La Calculadora de subred IP es una herramienta integral para calcular "
"información de subred, direcciones de red, direcciones de transmisión, "
"rangos de host y convertir entre notación CIDR y máscaras de subred "
"decimales con puntos. Ayuda a los administradores de red, profesionales de "
"TI y estudiantes a comprender y configurar subredes IP para redes IPv4. Esta"
" calculadora es esencial para el diseño de redes, la resolución de problemas"
" y la planificación de subredes."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:251
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Subnet Information, Subnet from"
" Hosts Needed, Subnet from Subnets Needed, or Convert Subnet Mask)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Información de subred,"
" Subred de hosts necesarios, Subred de subredes necesarias o Convertir "
"máscara de subred)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:252
msgid "Enter the IP address in dotted decimal format (e.g., 192.168.1.1)."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la dirección IP en formato decimal con puntos (por ejemplo, "
"192.168.1.1)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:253
msgid ""
"Enter the subnet mask in CIDR notation (/XX) or dotted decimal format "
"(xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx)."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese la máscara de subred en notación CIDR (/XX) o formato decimal con "
"puntos (xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:255
msgid ""
"Review the detailed subnet information, visualizations, and step-by-step "
"solution."
msgstr ""
"Revise la información detallada de la subred, las visualizaciones y la "
"solución paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:264
msgid ""
"Calculate complete subnet information including network address, broadcast "
"address, host range, total hosts, usable hosts, and subnet mask. Most common"
" calculation."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la información completa de la subred, incluida la dirección de red, "
"la dirección de transmisión, el rango de hosts, el total de hosts, los hosts"
" utilizables y la máscara de subred. Cálculo más común."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:268
msgid ""
"Calculate the appropriate subnet mask and CIDR notation based on the number "
"of hosts needed. Automatically determines the minimum subnet size."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la máscara de subred y la notación CIDR adecuadas en función de la "
"cantidad de hosts necesarios. Determina automáticamente el tamaño mínimo de "
"subred."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:272
msgid ""
"Calculate subnet configuration when you need to divide a network into "
"multiple subnets. Determines the new CIDR and subnet mask."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la configuración de subred cuando necesite dividir una red en varias"
" subredes. Determina el nuevo CIDR y la máscara de subred."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:276
msgid ""
"Convert between CIDR notation (/XX) and dotted decimal subnet mask format "
"(xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx). Useful for understanding different subnet mask "
"representations."
msgstr ""
"Convierta entre notación CIDR (/XX) y formato de máscara de subred decimal "
"con puntos (xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx). Útil para comprender diferentes "
"representaciones de máscaras de subred."

