msgstr "Introduzca el segundo nombre"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:189
msgid "Calculate Love Percentage"
msgstr "Calcular el porcentaje de amor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:190
msgid ""
"Enter two names to calculate love percentage, compatibility score, or "
"analyze name compatibility with detailed step-by-step solutions."
msgstr ""
"Ingrese dos nombres para calcular el porcentaje de amor, el puntaje de "
"compatibilidad o analizar la compatibilidad de nombres con soluciones "
"detalladas paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:206
msgid "What is Love Calculator?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la Calculadora del Amor?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:208
msgid ""
"The Love Calculator is a fun and entertaining tool that calculates a love "
"percentage or compatibility score between two names. It uses various "
"algorithms to analyze name compatibility, including counting letters in "
"'LOVE', finding common letters, comparing name lengths, and analyzing "
"vowel/consonant ratios. While this is primarily for entertainment purposes, "
"it can be a fun way to explore name relationships and compatibility."
msgstr ""
"Love Calculator es una herramienta divertida y entretenida que calcula un "
"porcentaje de amor o puntuación de compatibilidad entre dos nombres. Utiliza"
" varios algoritmos para analizar la compatibilidad de nombres, incluido "
"contar letras en 'LOVE', encontrar letras comunes, comparar longitudes de "
"nombres y analizar proporciones de vocales y consonantes. Si bien esto es "
"principalmente para fines de entretenimiento, puede ser una forma divertida "
"de explorar las relaciones y la compatibilidad de los nombres."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:215
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Love Percentage, Compatibility "
"Score, or Name Analysis)."
msgstr ""
"Seleccione un tipo de cálculo en el menú desplegable (Porcentaje de amor, "
"Puntuación de compatibilidad o Análisis de nombre)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:216
msgid "Enter two names in the input fields (first name and second name)."
msgstr ""
"Introduzca dos nombres en los campos de entrada (nombre y segundo nombre)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:217
msgid "Names can be full names, first names, or nicknames."
msgstr "Los nombres pueden ser nombres completos, nombres o apodos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:219
msgid ""
"Review the love percentage/compatibility score, category, visualizations, "
"and step-by-step solution."
msgstr ""
"Revise el porcentaje de amor/puntuación de compatibilidad, la categoría, las"
" visualizaciones y la solución paso a paso."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:228
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Calculate love percentage using the 'LOVE' algorithm. Counts L, O, V, E "
"letters in combined names and analyzes common letters to determine "
"compatibility percentage (0-100%%)."
msgstr ""
"Calcula el porcentaje de amor usando el algoritmo 'AMOR'. Cuenta las letras "
"L, O, V, E en nombres combinados y analiza letras comunes para determinar el"
" porcentaje de compatibilidad (0-100%%)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:232
msgid ""
"Calculate comprehensive compatibility score based on common letters, name "
"length similarity, and vowel/consonant ratio similarity. Provides detailed "
"breakdown of compatibility factors."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la puntuación de compatibilidad integral basándose en letras "
"comunes, similitud en la longitud de los nombres y similitud en la "
"proporción de vocales/consonantes. Proporciona un desglose detallado de los "
"factores de compatibilidad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:236
msgid ""
"Analyze names for detailed compatibility information including name lengths,"
" vowel/consonant counts, common letters, and unique letters in each name."
msgstr ""
"Analice los nombres para obtener información detallada sobre compatibilidad,"
" incluida la longitud de los nombres, el número de vocales/consonantes, las "
"letras comunes y las letras únicas de cada nombre."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:242
msgid "Love Percentage Categories"
msgstr "Categorías de porcentaje de amor"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:249
msgid "Meaning"
msgstr "Significado"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:253
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:34
msgid "Excellent Match!"
msgstr "¡Excelente partido!"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:253
msgid "Perfect compatibility, strong connection"
msgstr "Compatibilidad perfecta, conexión fuerte"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:254
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:35
msgid "Very Good Match!"
msgstr "¡Muy buen partido!"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:254
msgid "Great compatibility, good potential"
msgstr "Gran compatibilidad, buen potencial."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:255
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:36
msgid "Good Match!"
msgstr "¡Buen partido!"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:255
msgid "Good compatibility, worth exploring"
msgstr "Buena compatibilidad, vale la pena explorar"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:256
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:37
msgid "Fair Match"
msgstr "Partido justo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:256
msgid "Moderate compatibility, may need effort"
msgstr "Compatibilidad moderada, puede necesitar esfuerzo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:257
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:38
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:374
msgid "Needs Work"
msgstr "Necesita trabajo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:257
msgid "Lower compatibility, but love can overcome"
msgstr "Menor compatibilidad, pero el amor puede superar."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:264
msgid "How the Algorithm Works"
msgstr "Cómo funciona el algoritmo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:266
msgid "Love Percentage Algorithm:"
msgstr "Algoritmo de porcentaje de amor:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:268
msgid "Combine both names and count occurrences of L, O, V, E letters"
msgstr ""
"Combine ambos nombres y cuente las apariciones de las letras L, O, V, E"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:269
msgid "Calculate letter percentage: (LOVE letters / Total letters) × 100"
msgstr ""
"Calcular porcentaje de letras: (Cartas de AMOR / Letras totales) × 100"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:270
msgid "Count common letters between the two names"
msgstr "Contar letras comunes entre los dos nombres."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:271
msgid "Calculate common letter percentage"
msgstr "Calcular el porcentaje de letras comunes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:272
#, python-format
msgid "Combine percentages: (Letter %% × 0.4) + (Common %% × 0.6)"
msgstr "Combinar porcentajes: (Letra %% × 0,4) + (Común %% × 0,6)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:273
msgid "Add length similarity factor"
msgstr "Agregar factor de similitud de longitud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:274
#, python-format
msgid "Normalize to 0-100%% range"
msgstr "Normalizar al rango 0-100%%"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:276
msgid "Compatibility Score Algorithm:"
msgstr "Algoritmo de puntuación de compatibilidad:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:278
msgid "Calculate common letters score (based on shared letters)"
msgstr ""
"Calcular la puntuación de letras comunes (basado en letras compartidas)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:279
msgid "Calculate name length similarity score"
msgstr "Calcular la puntuación de similitud de la longitud del nombre"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:280
msgid "Calculate vowel/consonant ratio similarity score"
msgstr "Calcular la puntuación de similitud de la relación vocal/consonante"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:281
msgid "Average the three scores: (Common + Length + Vowel) / 3"
msgstr "Promediar las tres puntuaciones: (Común + Longitud + Vocal) / 3"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"This calculator is for entertainment purposes only and should not be taken "
"seriously."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora tiene únicamente fines de entretenimiento y no debe tomarse"
" en serio."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:290
msgid "Names can be entered as first names, full names, or nicknames."
msgstr ""
"Los nombres se pueden ingresar como nombres, nombres completos o apodos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:291
msgid "Names are case-insensitive and spaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Los nombres no distinguen entre mayúsculas y minúsculas y los espacios se "
"ignoran."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:292
msgid "Maximum name length is 100 characters."
msgstr "La longitud máxima del nombre es de 100 caracteres."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:293
msgid ""
"The algorithm uses letter counting and pattern matching, not actual "
"relationship compatibility."
msgstr ""
"El algoritmo utiliza el conteo de letras y la coincidencia de patrones, no "
"la compatibilidad de relaciones real."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:294
msgid ""
"Results are calculated based on name characteristics, not personal traits or"
" relationship dynamics."
msgstr ""
"Los resultados se calculan en función de las características del nombre, no "
"de los rasgos personales ni de la dinámica de las relaciones."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"Love and relationships are complex and cannot be accurately measured by name"
" analysis alone."
msgstr ""
"El amor y las relaciones son complejos y no pueden medirse con precisión "
"únicamente mediante el análisis de nombres."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:296
msgid ""
"Have fun with the results, but remember that real relationships are built on"
" communication, trust, and mutual respect."
msgstr ""
"Diviértete con los resultados, pero recuerda que las relaciones reales se "
"basan en la comunicación, la confianza y el respeto mutuo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:303
msgid "Entertainment and fun with friends"
msgstr "Entretenimiento y diversión con amigos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:304
msgid "Social media sharing and games"
msgstr "Compartir redes sociales y juegos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:305
msgid "Understanding name compatibility algorithms"
msgstr "Comprender los algoritmos de compatibilidad de nombres"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:306
msgid "Educational purposes (letter counting, pattern matching)"
msgstr "Fines educativos (conteo de letras, coincidencia de patrones)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:307
msgid "Party games and icebreakers"
msgstr "Juegos de fiesta y rompehielos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:308
msgid "Exploring name relationships and patterns"
msgstr "Explorando relaciones y patrones de nombres"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:309
msgid "Fun relationship discussions"
msgstr "Discusiones divertidas sobre relaciones"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:394
msgid "Please fill in both names."
msgstr "Por favor complete ambos nombres."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:448
msgid "Name 1"
msgstr "Nombre 1"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:452
msgid "Name 2"
msgstr "Nombre 2"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:466
msgid "Common Letters Score"
msgstr "Puntuación de letras comunes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:470
#: Other_Calculators/views/love_calculator.py:517
msgid "Length Similarity"
msgstr "Similitud de longitud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:474
msgid "Vowel Ratio Similarity"
msgstr "Similitud de proporción de vocales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:479
msgid "common letters"
msgstr "letras comunes"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:483
msgid "Name 1 Length"
msgstr "Nombre 1 Longitud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:487
