msgstr "Nombre 2 Longitud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/love_calculator.html:491
msgid "Total Vowels"
msgstr "Vocales totales"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mass_calculator.html:4
msgid "Mass Calculator - Convert Mass Units & Calculate from Density"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de masa: convierta unidades de masa y calcule a partir de la "
"densidad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mass_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free online Mass Calculator. Convert between kilograms, grams, pounds, "
"ounces, tons, and more. Calculate mass from density and volume, or find "
"density and volume from mass."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de masa en línea gratuita. Convierta entre kilogramos, gramos, "
"libras, onzas, toneladas y más. Calcule la masa a partir de la densidad y el"
" volumen, o encuentre la densidad y el volumen a partir de la masa."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mass_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"mass calculator, calculate mass, weight converter, mass conversion "
"calculator, density calculator, volume calculator, kg to lbs converter, "
"grams to ounces converter, mass unit converter, kilogram converter, pound to"
" kg converter, ounce to gram converter, metric mass converter, imperial mass"
" converter, mass finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de masa, calcular masa, convertidor de peso, calculadora de "
