#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mass_calculator.html:283
msgid "What is Mass?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la misa?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mass_calculator.html:284
msgid ""
"Mass is a measure of the amount of matter in an object. It is a fundamental "
"property that remains constant regardless of location, unlike weight which "
"depends on gravity."
msgstr ""
"La masa es una medida de la cantidad de materia en un objeto. Es una "
"propiedad fundamental que permanece constante independientemente de la "
"ubicación, a diferencia del peso que depende de la gravedad."

