msgid ""
"Free online Molarity Calculator. Calculate molarity, moles, volume, mass, "
"and perform dilution calculations. Perfect for chemistry students and "
"professionals."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de molaridad online gratuita. Calcule molaridad, moles, volumen,"
" masa y realice cálculos de dilución. Perfecto para estudiantes y "
"profesionales de química."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/molarity_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"molarity calculator, calculate molarity, concentration calculator, dilution "
"calculator, moles calculator, chemistry calculator, M1V1 M2V2 calculator, "
"solution concentration calculator, molarity formula, how to calculate "
"molarity, chemistry lab calculator, molar concentration calculator, mol/L "
"calculator, solution preparation calculator, molarity finder"
