#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/molarity_calculator.html:339
msgid "What is Molarity?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la molaridad?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/molarity_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Molarity (M) is a measure of concentration, defined as the number of moles "
"of solute per liter of solution. It is one of the most common units for "
"expressing solution concentration in chemistry."
msgstr ""
"La molaridad (M) es una medida de concentración, definida como el número de "
"moles de soluto por litro de solución. Es una de las unidades más comunes "
"para expresar la concentración de una solución en química."

