#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mulch_calculator.html:387
msgid "What is Mulch?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el mantillo?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mulch_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Mulch is a material spread over soil to retain moisture, suppress weeds, and"
" improve soil health. Common types include wood chips, bark, straw, compost,"
" and rubber."
msgstr ""
"El mantillo es un material que se extiende sobre el suelo para retener la "
"humedad, eliminar las malezas y mejorar la salud del suelo. Los tipos "
"comunes incluyen astillas de madera, corteza, paja, abono y caucho."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/mulch_calculator.html:394
