#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:336
msgid "What is Ohm's Law?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la ley de Ohm?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"Ohm's Law states that the current through a conductor between two points is "
"directly proportional to the voltage across the two points and inversely "
"proportional to the resistance between them."
msgstr ""
"La ley de Ohm establece que la corriente que circula por un conductor entre "
"dos puntos es directamente proporcional al voltaje entre los dos puntos e "
"inversamente proporcional a la resistencia entre ellos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:344
msgid "Enter the known values"
msgstr "Introduzca los valores conocidos"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:351
msgid "Ohm's Law Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de la ley de Ohm"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:357
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:358
msgid "Power (alternative)"
msgstr "Poder (alternativo)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:365
msgid "Calculate voltage from current and resistance"
msgstr "Calcular voltaje a partir de corriente y resistencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:366
msgid "Calculate current from voltage and resistance"
msgstr "Calcular la corriente a partir del voltaje y la resistencia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:367
msgid "Calculate resistance from voltage and current"
msgstr "Calcular la resistencia a partir del voltaje y la corriente."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:368
msgid "Calculate power using various formulas"
msgstr "Calcular la potencia usando varias fórmulas."

