msgstr "La resistencia debe ser mayor que cero."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ohms_law_calculator.html:387
msgid "Ohm's Law applies to linear circuits"
msgstr "La ley de Ohm se aplica a circuitos lineales."

