msgstr "Calculadora de sueño: encuentre sus horas óptimas de sueño y vigilia"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free online Sleep Calculator. Calculate the best time to sleep and wake up "
"based on 90-minute sleep cycles. Get optimal rest by waking at the end of a "
"sleep cycle."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de sueño online gratuita. Calcula el mejor momento para dormir y"
" despertar en función de ciclos de sueño de 90 minutos. Obtenga un descanso "
"óptimo despertándose al final de un ciclo de sueño."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"sleep calculator, sleep cycle calculator, when to wake up calculator, "
"bedtime calculator, optimal sleep time calculator, REM sleep calculator, "
"sleep schedule calculator, wake up time calculator, best bedtime calculator,"
" sleep cycle tracker, how to calculate sleep, sleep finder"
