msgstr "Consejos para dormir"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:183
msgid "What is a Sleep Cycle?"
msgstr "¿Qué es un ciclo de sueño?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:184
msgid ""
"A complete sleep cycle lasts about 90 minutes and includes light sleep, deep"
" sleep, and REM (dream) sleep. Waking at the end of a cycle helps you feel "
"refreshed."
msgstr ""
"Un ciclo de sueño completo dura aproximadamente 90 minutos e incluye sueño "
"ligero, sueño profundo y sueño REM (sueño). Despertarse al final de un ciclo"
" te ayuda a sentirte renovado."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:190
msgid "Select calculation mode"
msgstr "Seleccionar modo de cálculo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/sleep_calculator.html:191
