#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/speed_calculator.html:12
msgid "Speed Calculator - Calculate Speed, Distance & Time"
msgstr "Calculadora de velocidad: calcula velocidad, distancia y tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/speed_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free online Speed Calculator. Calculate speed from distance and time, "
"distance from speed and time, or time from speed and distance. Supports "
"multiple units."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de velocidad online gratuita. Calcule la velocidad a partir de "
"la distancia y el tiempo, la distancia a partir de la velocidad y el tiempo,"
" o el tiempo a partir de la velocidad y la distancia. Soporta múltiples "
"unidades."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/speed_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"speed calculator, distance calculator, time calculator, speed distance time,"
" mph kmh converter, velocity calculator, average speed calculator, mph to "
"kmh, kmh to mph, speed distance time formula, speed conversion calculator"
