"Free tip calculator to calculate how much to tip at restaurants. Split "
"bills, calculate tip percentage (15%%, 18%%, 20%%), and find total bill "
"amount. Perfect for dining out, delivery, and services."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de propinas gratuita para calcular cuánto dar de propina en los "
"restaurantes. Divida las facturas, calcule el porcentaje de propina (15%%, "
"18%%, 20%%) y encuentre el monto total de la factura. Perfecto para salir a "
"cenar, realizar entregas y servicios."

