"voltaje, el tamaño del cable, la corriente máxima y la longitud del cable "
"para circuitos eléctricos. Soporta sistemas DC, monofásicos y trifásicos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/voltage_drop_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"voltage drop calculator, calculate voltage drop, electrical calculator, wire"
" size calculator, voltage loss calculator, electrical engineering "
"calculator, circuit calculator, voltage drop formula, wire gauge calculator,"
" electrical voltage calculator, NEC voltage drop calculator, electrical "
"design calculator, voltage drop finder"
