msgid "Weight Calculator - Convert Weight Units & Calculate Weight"
msgstr "Calculadora de peso: convierta unidades de peso y calcule el peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free online Weight Calculator. Convert between weight units (kg, lbs, oz, "
"grams), calculate weight from mass, and find your weight on different "
"planets."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de peso online gratuita. Convierta entre unidades de peso (kg, "
"lbs, oz, gramos), calcule el peso a partir de la masa y encuentre su peso en"
" diferentes planetas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"weight calculator, weight converter, convert weight, mass calculator, weight"
" on planets calculator, unit converter, kg to lbs converter, pounds to "
"kilograms converter, weight conversion calculator, body weight calculator, "
"weight unit converter, metric weight converter, imperial weight converter, "
"weight finder"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de peso, conversor de peso, convertir peso, calculadora de masa,"
" calculadora de peso en planetas, convertidor de unidades, conversor de kg a"
" libras, conversor de libras a kilogramos, calculadora de conversión de "
"peso, calculadora de peso corporal, conversor de unidades de peso, conversor"
" de peso métrico, conversor de peso imperial, buscador de peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Convert between weight units, calculate weight from mass, and find your "
"weight on different planets. Free online calculator."
msgstr ""
"Convierta entre unidades de peso, calcule el peso a partir de la masa y "
"encuentre su peso en diferentes planetas. Calculadora en línea gratuita."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Convert weight units and calculate weight on different planets. Free online "
"calculator."
msgstr ""
"Convierte unidades de peso y calcula el peso en diferentes planetas. "
"Calculadora en línea gratuita."

