msgstr "Sol"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:248
msgid "What is Weight?"
msgstr "¿Qué es el peso?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:249
msgid ""
"Weight is the force exerted on an object due to gravity. It depends on both "
"the object's mass and the gravitational acceleration. Weight = Mass × "
"Gravity."
msgstr ""
"El peso es la fuerza ejercida sobre un objeto debido a la gravedad. Depende "
"tanto de la masa del objeto como de la aceleración gravitacional. Peso = "
"Masa × Gravedad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:256
msgid "Enter values"
msgstr "Introducir valores"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:285
msgid "Weight from Mass"
msgstr "Peso de masa"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:287
msgid "Mass from Weight"
msgstr "Masa a partir de peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:289
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:212
msgid "Where"
msgstr "Dónde"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:297
msgid "Planetary Gravity"
msgstr "Gravedad planetaria"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:299
msgid "Earth: 9.81 m/s²"
msgstr "Tierra: 9,81 m/s²"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:300
msgid "Moon: 1.62 m/s²"
msgstr "Luna: 1,62 m/s²"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:301
msgid "Mars: 3.71 m/s²"
msgstr "Marte: 3,71 m/s²"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:302
msgid "Jupiter: 24.79 m/s²"
msgstr "Júpiter: 24,79 m/s²"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:303
msgid "Sun: 274 m/s²"
msgstr "Sol: 274 m/s²"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:308
msgid "Mass vs Weight"
msgstr "Masa vs peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:310
msgid "Amount of matter (constant)"
msgstr "Cantidad de materia (constante)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:311
msgid "Force due to gravity (varies)"
msgstr "Fuerza debida a la gravedad (varía)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"Your mass is the same everywhere, but your weight changes with gravity."
msgstr ""
"Tu masa es la misma en todas partes, pero tu peso cambia con la gravedad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:319
msgid "Weight depends on gravity"
msgstr "El peso depende de la gravedad."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:320
msgid "Mass is constant regardless of location"
msgstr "La masa es constante independientemente de la ubicación."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:322
msgid "Weight on Moon is about 1/6 of Earth"
msgstr "El peso en la Luna es aproximadamente 1/6 del de la Tierra"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:323
msgid "Weight on Jupiter is about 2.5× Earth"
msgstr "El peso en Júpiter es aproximadamente 2,5 veces el de la Tierra."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:324
msgid "Use Newtons for scientific calculations"
msgstr "Utilice Newtons para cálculos científicos"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:331
msgid "Unit conversions"
msgstr "Conversiones de unidades"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:332
msgid "Physics calculations"
msgstr "Cálculos de física"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:333
msgid "Cooking measurements"
msgstr "Medidas de cocción"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:334
msgid "Shipping and logistics"
msgstr "Envío y logística"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:335
msgid "Fitness and health"
msgstr "Fitness y salud"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:432
msgid "Weight must be non-negative"
msgstr "El peso no debe ser negativo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:457
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:491
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:507
msgid "Please enter a valid weight"
msgstr "Por favor introduce un peso válido"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:474
msgid "Please enter a valid mass"
msgstr "Por favor ingrese una masa válida"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:547
msgid "equals"
msgstr "es igual"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:553
msgid "Weight Calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo de peso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:556
msgid "Weight (Newtons)"
msgstr "Peso (Newtons)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:567
msgid "Mass Calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo de masa"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:570
#: Other_Calculators/views/density_calculator.py:666
#: Other_Calculators/views/density_calculator.py:716
#: Other_Calculators/views/mass_calculator.py:656
#: Other_Calculators/views/mass_calculator.py:706
#: Other_Calculators/views/mass_calculator.py:756
msgid "Mass (kg)"
msgstr "Masa (kg)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:583
msgid "Gravity ratio"
msgstr "relación de gravedad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/weight_calculator.html:586
msgid "Weight on All Planets"
msgstr "Peso en todos los planetas"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:4
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:8
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:12
msgid "Wind Chill Calculator - Calculate Wind Chill Temperature"
msgstr ""
"Calculadora de sensación térmica - Calcular la temperatura de sensación "
"térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:5
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:25
msgid ""
"Free online Wind Chill Calculator. Calculate wind chill from temperature and"
" wind speed, find temperature from wind chill, and assess risk categories."
msgstr ""
"Calculadora gratuita de sensación térmica en línea. Calcule la sensación "
"térmica a partir de la temperatura y la velocidad del viento, encuentre la "
"temperatura a partir de la sensación térmica y evalúe las categorías de "
"riesgo."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"wind chill calculator, wind chill index, feels like temperature, cold "
"weather calculator, temperature calculator, wind chill formula, apparent "
"temperature calculator, weather calculator, cold temperature calculator, "
"wind chill factor"
msgstr ""
"calculadora de sensación térmica, índice de sensación térmica, sensación de "
"temperatura, calculadora de clima frío, calculadora de temperatura, fórmula "
"de sensación térmica, calculadora de temperatura aparente, calculadora del "
"clima, calculadora de temperatura fría, factor de sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Calculate wind chill from temperature and wind speed, find temperature from "
"wind chill, and assess risk categories. Free online calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la sensación térmica a partir de la temperatura y la velocidad del "
"viento, encuentre la temperatura a partir de la sensación térmica y evalúe "
"las categorías de riesgo. Calculadora en línea gratuita."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Calculate wind chill temperature and assess risk categories. Free online "
"calculator."
msgstr ""
"Calcule la temperatura del viento helado y evalúe las categorías de riesgo. "
"Calculadora en línea gratuita."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:24
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:40
#: Other_Calculators/views/index.py:57
#: Other_Calculators/views/wind_chill_calculator.py:36
msgid "Wind Chill Calculator"
msgstr "Calculadora de sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:30
msgid "Wind chill calculation"
msgstr "Cálculo de la sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:30
msgid "Temperature from wind chill"
msgstr "Temperatura por sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:30
msgid "Risk category assessment"
msgstr "Evaluación de la categoría de riesgo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:30
msgid "Wind speed input"
msgstr "Entrada de velocidad del viento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:30
msgid "Temperature input"
msgstr "Entrada de temperatura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:41
msgid "Calculate wind chill temperature and assess cold weather risks"
msgstr ""
"Calcule la temperatura del viento helado y evalúe los riesgos del clima frío"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:51
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:59
msgid "Calculate Wind Chill"
msgstr "Calcular la sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:52
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:95
msgid "Calculate Temperature from Wind Chill"
msgstr "Calcular la temperatura a partir de la sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:53
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:130
msgid "Calculate Wind Speed from Wind Chill"
msgstr "Calcular la velocidad del viento a partir de la sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:74
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:110
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:488
msgid "Wind Speed"
msgstr "Velocidad del viento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:84
msgid ""
"Wind chill applies when wind speed ≥ 3 mph and temperature ≤ 50°F (10°C)"
msgstr ""
"La sensación térmica se aplica cuando la velocidad del viento es ≥ 3 mph y "
"la temperatura ≤ 50°F (10°C)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:98
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:133
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:476
msgid "Wind Chill"
msgstr "sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:157
msgid "Wind Speed Unit"
msgstr "Unidad de velocidad del viento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:194
msgid "What is Wind Chill?"
msgstr "¿Qué es la sensación térmica?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:195
msgid ""
"Wind chill is the perceived decrease in air temperature felt by the body on "
"exposed skin due to the flow of air. It makes the temperature feel colder "
"than the actual air temperature."
msgstr ""
"La sensación térmica es la disminución percibida de la temperatura del aire "
"que siente el cuerpo sobre la piel expuesta debido al flujo de aire. Hace "
"que la temperatura se sienta más fría que la temperatura real del aire."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:202
msgid "Enter temperature and wind speed"
msgstr "Introduzca la temperatura y la velocidad del viento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:209
msgid "Wind Chill Index Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula del índice de sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:220
msgid "Applicability"
msgstr "Aplicabilidad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:222
msgid "Wind chill applies when:"
msgstr "La sensación térmica se aplica cuando:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:223
msgid "Temperature ≤ 50°F (10°C)"
msgstr "Temperatura ≤ 50°F (10°C)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:224
msgid "Wind speed ≥ 3 mph (4.8 km/h)"
msgstr "Velocidad del viento ≥ 3 mph (4,8 km/h)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:225
msgid "Below these thresholds, wind chill equals air temperature."
msgstr ""
"Por debajo de estos umbrales, la sensación térmica es igual a la temperatura"
" del aire."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:230
msgid "Risk Categories"
msgstr "Categorías de riesgo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:234
msgid "Little danger from freezing"
msgstr "Poco peligro de congelación"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:238
msgid "Uncomfortable, risk of hypothermia"
msgstr "Incómodo, riesgo de hipotermia."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:242
msgid "Dangerous, skin can freeze in 10 min"
msgstr "Peligroso, la piel puede congelarse en 10 min."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:246
msgid "Extremely dangerous, skin can freeze in 5 min"
msgstr "Extremadamente peligroso, la piel se puede congelar en 5 minutos."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:252
msgid "Temperature Units"
msgstr "Unidades de temperatura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:254
msgid "Used in US"
msgstr "Usado en EE. UU."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:255
msgid "Used internationally"
msgstr "Utilizado internacionalmente"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:262
msgid "Wind Speed Units"
msgstr "Unidades de velocidad del viento"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:264
msgid "Miles per hour (US)"
msgstr "Millas por hora (EE.UU.)"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:274
msgid "Wind chill only affects exposed skin"
msgstr "La sensación térmica solo afecta la piel expuesta"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:275
msgid "Dress appropriately for wind chill, not just temperature"
msgstr ""
"Vístase apropiadamente para el viento helado, no solo para la temperatura"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:276
msgid "Wind chill doesn't affect inanimate objects"
msgstr "La sensación térmica no afecta a los objetos inanimados"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:277
msgid "Higher wind speeds increase wind chill effect"
msgstr ""
"Las velocidades más altas del viento aumentan el efecto de sensación térmica"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:278
msgid "Protect exposed skin in extreme conditions"
msgstr "Protege la piel expuesta en condiciones extremas."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:279
msgid "Stay indoors when wind chill is dangerous"
msgstr "Permanezca en casa cuando el viento helado sea peligroso"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:286
msgid "Weather forecasting"
msgstr "Previsión del tiempo"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:287
msgid "Outdoor activity planning"
msgstr "Planificación de actividades al aire libre"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:288
msgid "Safety assessments"
msgstr "Evaluaciones de seguridad"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:289
msgid "Clothing recommendations"
msgstr "Recomendaciones de ropa"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:290
msgid "Emergency preparedness"
msgstr "Preparación para emergencias"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:396
msgid "Please enter temperature and wind speed"
msgstr "Por favor ingrese la temperatura y la velocidad del viento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:413
msgid "Please enter wind chill and wind speed"
msgstr "Introduzca la sensación térmica y la velocidad del viento."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/wind_chill_calculator.html:430
msgid "Please enter wind chill and temperature"
msgstr "Por favor ingrese la sensación térmica y la temperatura."

#: Other_Calculators/views/age_calculator.py:39
msgid "Precise age calculation in multiple time units"
msgstr "Cálculo preciso de la edad en múltiples unidades de tiempo."

#: Other_Calculators/views/age_calculator.py:40
