#: core/templates/core/index.html:5
msgid ""
"Access 195+ free online calculators across finance, health, mathematics, and"
" utilities. Professional tools for mortgages, loans, fitness, conversions, "
"and more. Fast, accurate, and easy to use."
msgstr ""
"Acceda a más de 195 calculadoras en línea gratuitas en finanzas, salud, "
